Item_Response: Robots are very important in the modern world. Some robots help in hospitals some do rescue missions, some gather information for scientists, some help out farmers, and robots even play around with kids. In hospitals, robots carry medicine to the patients for the nurses and doctors. these robots open doors, maneuver around obstacles, and much more. These robots might be small, but the can carry up to 500 lbs. These robots run on batteries, and they can be charged. If these robots charge for two hours, they can work for twelve hours working in the hospital.           Another robot does search and rescue missions on mines. This robots abilities are almost endless. It can carry water, food, and it can drag injured people to safety. This robot has four wheels that help it roll through tight spaces. It also has a radio transmitter that helps the person communicate with the rescue team. this robot might be small, but it play a huge roll in the world today.          This robot can walk up sides of mountains and volcanoes. It studies the volcanoes magma and its texture. This rrobot can withstand the heat of the volcanoes to get better information. It's spider like legs help it crawl steep sides and move quickly. It helps the scientists get a better understanding of volcanoes. This robot is charged and takes batteries. This robot is the newest break through for science.

Item_Response: Characters:       Robot: Markie Marco Jr. (Mark for short)       The Awsome girls who finds him: Cecelia, and Kasi       Everyone else: extras       Plot:       Setting: Kasi and Cecelia find Markie Marco Jr. (Mark) in a dump. They take him home and dress him up. The next morning they wake up to find him making breakfast. They call  the cops and have him arrested. When Mark gets a paroll, he vistits Cecelia and Kasi. They scream and call the F.B.I. The F.B.I says he is the girls responsability now. The girls grow to like him and they travel to a far of planet call Juberron. Space Adventures with Markie Marco Jr.       Lets start with the simple facts; My name is Makrie Marco Jr., I'm 10 feet tall and a robot. I'm an ordinary robot, like any other, I drink oil with my friends on Friday nights, and go into deep sleep modes on Saturday. A pretty typical robot if you as me. I got into my new mercadees space car with my best bud Leo, (He was programmed with laser eyes and a really annoying voice, gosh I hate that!) to take it for a spin. We crash landed on a planet called Earth. Leo didn't 'survive' the crash. I found some shrubs and went into sleep mode for the night. Next thing I knew i was in a strange house wearing a size 49 dress! There were some alien life forms on the floor sleeping in bags. I poked their cheeks. They opened their eyes and, wait for it.... 'AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH,' they screamed.   'Ouch,' my ear.   'MOMMY!' They yelled in unision. Whats a mommy?   'What is that? Like some sort of toy?' how are these aliens so loud? I stood up and banged my head on the roof. The humans were too loud for me. So I left the house and entered my ship, and went back to Juberron.

When you log on to the Internet, you can control the robot from far away. The robot is put in a room full of kittens. It drags a piece of string for the kittens to chase. When is your turn, you can control the robot to pull the string this way or that way. The kittens jump after the string as you push the controls.       College students in oregon have created robots that play hockey or shouffleboard in there own. All year, the students work hard to design the robots. The robots play the game without any instructions from the students. The robots grab the puck turn, twist and compete to score. In the final test, the robots must push the puck to the goal without being told what to do.

Item_Response: I had a robot poster in my room because I love robots. On a very peculiar day I walked into my room to grab a jacket and I saw the robot cut out of my favorite poster. I figured it was my brother messing with me so I stromed to his room to get my poster back. When I got there he wasn't in there. I wasn't sure where he was because he wasn't outside either. Then I got a good idea.       I looked in his room for my precious poster but I was unsuccesful. Then I got a brillant idea. I ran to my room thinking he hid it in there. When I got there disappoint burned inside of me like a fire. My robot poster was no where to be found. I checked everywhere I could think of. Then just as I was leaving I heard a beep.       I went back in and found robot eyes stairing back at me. This robot looked just like the one from my poster. I grabed what was left of the poster and put it around the robot. The poster looked just like it did before. Except for the fact that the robot wasn't paper. I then heard the robot say something like 'Hi! I'm Robbie. What's your name?' I told him with a shaky voice 'I'm Kiera. How did you get here?' Just as fast as I said that he was gone. I then had my whole robot poster back and with curiousity filling me up I hung it up and cherished it even more.

Item_Response: Today was not the best day for Sebastian Fet. One would think that if you had just been given the world's largest robotics company, TechCorp, you would just feel on top of the world. But it tends to damper your being given a company if that company just happened to be the worlds smallest robotics company, was going out of business, and several of the robots produced for your company did not work. This was exactly the situation of Sebastian Fet, and he honestly didn't want anything to do with the company. He did however, take the company due to the fact his father, Harold Fet, had given it to him. What he did not know, was that being given TechCorp would be the start of quite a grand adventure.               For the first few months of his owning his company, things felt pretty easy because he simply sat at his desk most of the day. A week ago, some guy on the assembly line suggested a new part, and he just said yes to get him to leave. Just normal boss stuff. If he had known what the part was, he may have fired that worker of his, and things at TechCorp would have gone the way things should. But, he didn't, and he'll soon bee wishing for his job he did.               'Hello?' Sebastian said to his phone.           'Ah, so you've finally answered,' an employee replied.           'What could it possibly be, I have ever so many things not to do today,' Sebastian said, with a smile that wasn't seen over the phone.           'It's one of the robots, there is an issue. Please come as soon as possible.' The worker said, and hung up. Sebastian was not happy with this conversation, for he had just been hung up on, and he now had to leave his chair, right when he was getting comfy too.           When Sebastian had arrived, he saw what once may have been his testing room, Before a robot had destroyed it. It was a robot meant to rescue climbers, but it was playing, not rescuing. It was playing very roughly. There was a ball wedged in the roof, and several frisbees that had much to many things broken to list, and what looked like a yo-yo stuck in the roof that the robot itself was dangling from. This robot was obviously needing to be destroyed. But he had an idea, one that could save the rest of his building from goin down in flames.              Sebastian labeled the robot DEFECTIVE-01 so they new which bot was the broken one. He Brought it to a construction company, and had Oferred them the robot as a replacement for a wrecking ball. They accepted, and the wrecking ball man was not in any way happy to lose his job.          The robot, when prompted to destroy the building, had left for some nearby mountains, later to have saved a climber. The robot was not how it used to act, for it almost seemed alive. But of course it wasn't, a silly thing to talk about. When Sebasstian had got to his chair, he found a robot had beat him to it. It was watching tv, and was sipping on some juice! Sebastian felt foolish, but he had tried asking him to get off. 10 seconds had past, before the robot had asked him what he had said, for apparently he didn't hear. Sebastian thought it may be time to take a vacation, but he repeated himself and the robot actually got off. He looked at the machine, and remembered when he thought about when he thought it acted alive. He pulled a chair up for the robot, and started talking to it. They were having quite a conversation, something about cats, but an intern had walked in on the conversation, and droppend everything in her hands on the floor and her jaw had nealy touched the floor.           The intern, who was named juan, had asked who was controlling the robot, but laughed when told nobody. He knew that there was not a robot with opinions about which cat had the softest fur. Robots can't even feel things.           'Well then, if that robot actually talks...' Juan started.           'Which it can,' Sebastian interupted.           'Then how much are you selling it for?' Juan finished, ignoring Sebastian.           'I don't plan on selling it. It feels so alive it sounds wrong to do so. Besides, he does indeed give a gret conversation,' Sebastian answered.           'But sir, TechCorp may actually make some money for once, If you just keep it for your personal plaything, none of us will get any good money,' Juan argued, quite upset with his boss's desision of that robots fate. 'Good conversation. Ridiculous.' Juan thought.           'Oh just leave, I run his company, and I have grown to be very fond of this here bot.' Sebastian said, very annoyed. Juan had left, but he did not want to let that money go down the drain. He was getting minimum wage paychecks as it is. No, he was already thinking up a plan to get that thing sold. In fact, he new a guy that may like a robot with such capabilities as that. He didn't plan on giving Sebastian a slice, however. He had his chance, and he blew it.           Sebastian renamed his robot Gordon, because DEFECTIVE-01 wasn' what Sebastian would think to be a good name. He wondered how Gordon got the way he is, however, and he remembered that part that they included. He decided to go to the factory and see what was happening down there. Things appeared to be normal, and it turned out everything was. He asked if they had a new part, and the workers asked said that one robot had a new part, but since it was acting up they stopped producing them. When he was told the new part, he couldn't believe his ears. It turned out that a scientist named Ronald had succesfully been able to include a partially functioning brain. 'Wait a second, partially functioning?' Sebastian asked, confused, 'What doesn't work?'           'Well... the robot, Gordon, as you named it, has some hearing problems in his left... microphone,' Ronald answered, grinning, 'He has some other problems like he can't control his streangth too well, and he's pretty stupid.'           'Okay, so he's got hearing problems,' Sebastian began, 'and he's stupid? How is he stupid?'           'Well, umm... He's just not too bright.' Gordon answered.           'I didn't know a robot can be stupid. But if you say so. Well I gotta go. Item_Response: The Robot that had it's own mind           There was once a science lad in the middle of a desert, the only things around were   cactus, rattle snakes, and the hot, hot sun. You would think no one would ever wasn't to go there, but this was the perfect place for Dr.Vanbot. He was a scientist that needed a deserted place to build his super bot.            Dr.Vanbot and his mini robots, Bob, Tob, Lob, Kabob, Katob, and Susie, all worked together to build the super bot named Sbtcde, standing for super bot that can do everything. When they finally finished making Sbtcde, taking four years to do, they pluged him in. She had a soothing voice,was suprisingly small,and looked like a bunny, but even though she did not look tough she was very mighty, so they changed her name to Adison.             Adison could do many things but when Dr.Vanbot tried to show her to the government, they rejected her. Dr.Vanbot was disappointed and lost all of his self confidence never paying attention to Adison. Without the doctors support the mini bots made fun of Adison.One day the doctor came out with Adison waiting for him, but he went over to the wall not even looking at Adison and grabbed her plug and gave it a yank. All Adison's lights went of as she slowly was turned off.                  You may think robots have no emotion but Adison was a SBTCDE. After a day of being off Adisons lights turned on in the middle of the night. Every bot was asleep so Adison ran away thinking no one loved her. She drove to the city turning into a car in search of someone to love and appreciate her. She traveled all over until she finally stumbled onto a race track. Not knowing what to do Adison turned into a car and raced using her radar detecting when racers are near and speeding up she won the race.                         The racer in last place had to give up his car because it broke down. Running over to Adison to congratulate the driver discovered that no one was in the car. So he took Adison home. T he man named Jeffery, was a doctor, and o part time miner, racing was just a hobby. When he found out about all the amazing things Adison could do he promised never to un-plug her.                     Adison cold work at the hospital, mine, racing track, and was the perfect friend for Jeffry's daughter, Anabell, because Adison's origanal shape was a bunny. Adison and Anabell played all day and was a great help for Jeffery and Abbly. They lived happily together and had a great future, the end.

Item_Response: I awake.  The alarm in the emergency room is going off.  What happened??  I try to recall of any earlier events, but I can only remember me working my usual shift with Mr. Gower, the robot.  He was helping me deliver the medicine to the doctors and other nurses.  It did seem unusual though... Do I remember him acting like... a human?     I lay up to see nothing but rubble scattered around.  A wave of pain hits me in the head.  I lay back down and turn to my side.  My eyes search the room for something to kill the pain.  There has to be something in here, I am in a hospital.      My hand wonders to the spot on my skull.  Blood.  Great.      I continue my search for the medicine.  I find a bottle of pain killers.  Just two and I'm done.  I lay down and wait for the pain to dwell.      After what feels like an hour the pain is gone.  I reluctantly sit up, still in a daze.  I exit the door into the hallway.  There are heart monitors and medicine bottles distributed up and down the hall.      I see a man laying on the floor.  I rush to help him.  'Frank, What happened?' I search his eyes.  My co-worker stares blankly into my soul. 'Frank please answer.'  When he doesn't reply I shake him.  This does it.  'Frank.'  He only has enough energy to point to the control room that holds the security cameras for the floor.  I gently let him down and tell him if he sleeps he will feel better.  I dash to the room and open it to find the computers nice and neat.  I pull up the footage of the day and fast forward to approximately 4:00 P.M.      I rub my eyes.  Am i going crazy?  Are my eyes deceiving me?  I see Mr. Gower damaging everything in sight!  I panic.  My body starts to tremble.  I feel as if I might break down.  My hand reach for support.  They flail around for a second and I reach what feels like a tracker.  I look at my hands.  It is a tracker.  A tracker for Mr. Gower.     Mr. Gower was made differently from the other robots in the other hospitals.  He has a tracker built into him.  The inventor did this in case he gets stuck in a storage closet and we can't find him.  He is also low on battery level too, so this should help me find him and save the other places he is planning to attack.  He has about two hours left until he breaks down.  Although it's pretty clear Mr. Gower is a bad robot, why would he want to do this?                                                          I exit the hospital with the tracker in my hand. He is on 17th street.  That is two blocks away.  I speed my pace to match the little red dot.  How fast is he going?  I begin sprinting. I turn a corner, then another, then another.  Finally I see a tiny robotic cabinet rolling across the street.  I run towards him and his reaction goes from mad to furious.  I pause in the middle of the street.  I don't realize I'm holding my breath until he stops and waves to me.      What? Wasn't he just racing towards me his beady little eyes glaring at me?  I step closer to him.  He seems to be smiling.  I cautiously continue walking.  He says, 'Your delivery is here.'  I give him a puzzled look.  I search him with my eyes.  His cabinets seem to be ajar.  I step closer.  I realize that was a big mistake.  He has fooled me into a circle loaded with bombs ready to go off.  This may be my last moments in life.  I know if I try to move the bombs will explode.  The bombs count down: 5... 4... 3...     Suddenly, I remember What happened in the hospital:   Mr. Gower and I were making our usual runs up and down the halls. Then making our way to the elevators to go up to the floors above us.  Since we are on the first floor, there are long lines for the elevators.  I decided to take the stairs.  I left Mr. Gower with Frank and descended up the stairs.  On my way down from the 13th floor I fell.  I tumbled all the way down.  I remember people picking me up, taking me to a bed.             I try to open my eyes and I hear voices in the background.  I see light and my whole body cringes.  'You were in a comma,' a doctor says.     'For how long?' I reply confused.     'Two years.'

Item_Response: One day during school Jeff was having a bad day because a kid came up to Jeff and gave him a wedgie. Mr. Jones the science teacher was watching when Jeff got the wedgie. So at lunch Mr. Jones told Jeff to meet him in his classroom after school today. Then after school Jeff meet Mr. Jones in his classroom. He told Jeff that he saw Jeff get that wedgie and wanted to tell Jeff something. Mr. Jones walked to the closet in his room and open it. Jeff was amazed by what he saw in the closet.            Mr. Jones said that 'it can't do anything yet until I find a battery that is strong enough to program it'. 'I'll tell you what, if you come after school again tomorrow I'll tell you more about the robot'. 'Okay' said Mr. Jones.            'Okay' said Jeff. 'Bye' said Jeff.            The next day after school Jeff rushed to Mr. Jones classroom.            Mr. Jones brought the robot out of the closet and said 'I have great news Jeff'. 'I found a battery that is strong enough to program the robot'.            Jeff asked 'why did you build this robot in the first place'.            'I wanted something that can actually cook food in this school' said Mr. Jones. 'I was going to test it at my house this weekend'. 'Want to come over'said Mr. Jones.             'Sure' said Jeff. 'What time should I come over on Saturday' Jeff asked.               'Come over at 11:00 a.m.' Mr. Jones reply.            'See you tomorrow' Jeff said to Mr. Jones.             Saturday came and it was 10:30 when Jeff started to walk to Mr. Jones house. Jeff got there at 10:50 and knocked on Mr. Jones door. Mr. Jones answered the door and said 'welcome'. Jeff walked into the house and asked 'where is the robot' and Mr. Jones said answered 'it's in the kitchen'.Jeff and Mr. Jones walked into the kitchen and sat down at the table to think about what the robot was going to make.                                                                                                                                                                                                                     When Jeff said 'I know hamburgers', they both heard a noise.                                                                                                                                                           So they both went to search around house and when they came back to the kitchen the robot was gone. Then they searched the house again and when they both came back to the kitchen, they both saw the robot by the front door. Mr. Jones went up to the robot and took the battery out and said 'I better find a different battery for the robot, so it doesn't start up again by itself.                                                                                                                                                         The next day after Jeff's science class, he went up to Mr. Jones and said 'Good luck finding another battery,'  and then he left.  Jeff was glad Mr. Jones was there for him.

Item_Response: 'I hate my life!' I cry out, wiping my hand across my working table in my lab. My head is aching, my feet are hurting, I'm covered in sweat, and I don't have my blanket to calm me down. I stomp over to the window and plop myself down in a beanbag chair. I stare outside the window into the Harvard school yard with a flustered face. Everyone in the school was doing something they were good at. What was I good at? Nothing, exept for building robots that don't work and playing with my cat, Zeba.        I heard the doorknob turn, and then open. It was my dormmate, Kevin. He was in a fancy suit, with a briefcase and everything. He walked over to me. He gave me a look as he squished my cheeks and asked, 'What's wrong, Mr. Gumpy Pants? Why are you so sad?' I swatted his hand off my cheeks. He lifted his hands up then went to his bedroom to change.        'So, have you gotten the robot to work?' Kevin questioned. I got off the beanbag chair and siad, 'No. It just wants to not work today.' I paced back and forth for a while until Kevin came out with a clean white T-shirt and shorts. He flopped down on the couch and inspected my robot.        'Well, what's wrong with it?' he asked, surveying my robot carefully. He lifted an arm up. Then the other. He dropped them both. Then he lifted the legs up. I shook my head.        'I don't know. but for some reason, it just wants to be a jerk.' I shook my head. I went back to the beanbag chair. Hot tears were streaming down my cheek. This was my chance to become famous for building a robot that can pull five tons and be able to have the playfulness to play with my cat. Kevin inspected it some more. He stood up and gave it a slight kick. Everything was quiet for a second. then, I could heard motors starting up. I slowly turned my head around. There it was, sitting crissed-crossed-applesause. It's bright eyes were looking at me. I was looking back at it. I cautiously walked toward the robot. My head was pounding with awe. I couldn't believe it. Kevin looked at me with a smile. 'Fixed it!' he cried out, polishing his nails. 'Your welcome.' I still couldn't believe it. It works. It works! I knelt down at the robot so him and I were looking face to face. It was amazing! Kevin bent down next to me.        'So... you going to teach it anything or what?' he asked then turned to my robot and said, 'Shake!' I watched the robot lift it's hand and shake Kevin's outstreched arm. I stood back in amazement. 'Let's see if it can pull you truck.'        'Alright!' exclaimed Kevin.         I placed Betsy in front of Kevin's truck. I placed straps on the pencil shoulders then connected the other side of the straps to Kevin's truck.        'Pull!' I hollered. Betsy did as she was told and started to pull. I saw Kevin's truck move a little, then a little bit more, then a little bit more. It was actully moving a truck! I laughed and looked at the little two pound robot, made by pencils and pieces of wood that I was able to create. I looked at Kevin while picking up the robot as soon as it stopped.        'Let's go try it on something that weighs ten tons!' I exclaimed. Kevin groaned.        'On who, Bigfoot?'

Item_Response: It was the middle of the night, dark as can be, when I heard a noise downstairs. At first I thought it was just the cat but, it was to loud to be the cat. I started shaking thinking to myself, ' What if it is a person stealing all my stuff.' I cautionily headed down the steps. I made sure to be as quiet as possible checking all around me every step of the way. CRASH. I headed for the noise that came from the kitchen. When I reached the kitchen I almost had a heart attack. It was The robot I have been working on for the last month. I finnaly finished it today but, it wouldn't work no matter what I tried. 'Hello,' the friendly robot said. As I cleaned up the mess he made, I spent an hour observing him very carefully. I could barely keep my eyes open, so I made him a spot in the basement and locked him down there. I made sure he couldn't get out before I went to bed.            The next day I let him out of the basement. While fixing breakfast, I tried to have a conversion with him. 'Hello what is your name?' He replied, 'You haven't given me a name yet, master.' ' Fine I will name you Dexter,' I said giving him a name. As the next few days countinued I tried to see how well he interacted with my animals. I commanded 'Will you go keep my animals entertained?' He replied ' Yes, I will get on it right away ,sir.' He went in where my animals lay. As I silently watched, I noticed that he had no problem interacting with the animals.            The Next few days counitned working with him. I decided to take him outside on a leash of course. I called for him,'Dexter, will you come here please.' Dexter came into the the living room where I was sitting. I asked,' Will you put this leash on?' 'We are going outside.' As he put the leash on I walked him outside. I didn't go to far the first few times. I also tried keeping him away from animals and people. As we walked down the street I started a conversion,' How do you like it out here?' Dexter replied, 'It is very nice out here.' 'Do you like it?' 'Yes I do,' I answered. 'What do you like to do?' I asked. He answered, ' Well, I haven't experinced much in the few weeks I have been living but, I enjoy walking out here with.' I was suprised that he could speak that well with barely any training or even picking up the words I used.            As the last few days came I started to let Dexter be without the leash this time and let him roam free under my supervision of course. So, as we walked down the street we made small talk and he asked me questions like what his the world like. One question stood out the most. He asked me if there any robots like me out there. I answered with, ' There most likely is robots out there just like you but, I don't know where I could look for them at. As from then on he started feeling sad.  He never told me but I could tell. I didn't think robots could have emotion ethier. I started to feel sorry for the little guy so, I tried to copy some of him into a new robot. As I secretly worked on many different robots none succed until I oticed something. The night Dexter came alive my cat was down here. There were some certain chemicals that were down that I never experimente with before. I some chemicals in them and nothing. Then after thinking and thinking I came up with the solution. The chemicals mixed with the cat hair and made fuel.            After one week with experiment I made a few pals for Dexter. He enjoyed them and I tried the same experiment that I had with Dexter and they turned out like Dexter with few changes in looks and personalty. Dexter was the smartest with words but, the other were pretty good with speech also. Dexter was so happy that he could have cried if he was able to. I tried creating robut animals and so forth. They had conversions and even acted a little bad sometimes. They also did work and helped around the house and got along good with each other. They were just like mechanical humans.

Item_Response: HAVE FUN WITH THE ROBOTS!               Today we are going to see a robot show. After the robot show we get to go back-stage and see the actual characters. We also get to go to see them in the morning.       We are here! Finally, I have been waiting for this all morning. We got in and checked in to the back stage because we got to hang out with the members before the show started and after the show ended. One of the members asked all of us as a class if we wanted a tour with the robots and I screamed YES!!!!!.  Their was different people to talk about robots there and different kinds of robots there. The type of robots that were there was Gemini-Scout a Dante 2 a Mr.Gower and a Agribot.          My teacher was Mr.Gower he talked about robots a lot. That is why they named a robot Mr.Gower. Mr.Gower said that a robot can work at a hospital, helping doctors and nurses bring medicine to the patients.                                                     Agribots pick fruit from trees. It can pick berries, oranges, grapes, or even apples. Agribots are not used that often on farms. The reason for that is farmers are very interested in  the robots but they don't have as much money as other farmers.                                                      The Dante 2 was made to work for interesting jobs. Dante 2 goes into volcanoes and looks for vents, or holes, in the crater. The robot has eight legs.           There is A LOT more other facts, so lets get back to my day. After we went  on tour we went out where our seats was and then sat down and the show started to begin. I said to the girl beside me 'this is going to be good'.  The first part they were talking about there trips around the world. Then they had a little play we went to. The play was called (Fantastic Robots Coming to Town).  When the day ended we all went back to school and our parents picked us up I guess what I learned to day is that robots can have a lot of fun but they have to have so time to work.  Robots have a lot of interesting jobs. We all had a great day and we hope we can go back again.

Item_Response: It was a sunny July day and my family and I were out on a picnic. We were all enjoying our icecream cones when we heard a noise coming from the sky. We looked up and saw a space ship coming down into our atmosphere. As soon as my mom noticed that it was coming down straight over us, we ran away in panic. And that's when it all started.        'Crash!' We all ducked down and covered our faces. When everything cleared up we walked slowly to where the space ship had crashed and found a robot sitting in the drivers seat. The robot's leg had been blown off in the explosion, I carefully placed it wear it normally should be. My mom used some glue to paste the leg back onto the robot. Then we all backed up and my dad called 911.        When the police and ambulance got to the park we were picnicing at, they said that 'NASA had called and was wondering if there were any signs of a missing robot in a space ship. And the robot was supposed to go to the International Space Station but hit a meteorite and came flying down. It was meant to be a handy helper to astronauts that came to the ISS.'     When the robot whos name was actually Clevlis was resting in the hospital my family and I visited him and we became really good friends.       A couple of years later we ware watching the news and apparently Clevlis tried again to make it to the ISS, and it turns out he did!!! I guess a robot can due more things than people think they can.

Item_Response: He's Alive!                        One summer day, while the children were playing, and their mother was cooking, their father was in the garrage, working on his robot.          'Watcha doin'?'asked Lucy.          'I'm working on my robot,'said Dad.          'Ok.' said Lucy, 'But you better be in time for dinner. Mom is almost done and she doesn't want you to be late again.'          'Ya, ya, ya. I'll be there,'said Dad.          'Ok. I'll see you there,'said Lucy.                   'Your here! I thought you wouldnt make it.'          'I told you I would come, Dad said. Anyways, what's for dinner? I'm starving!'          'Were having potatoes and steak,'said Mom          'Well, we better start eating,' said Dad. 'We don't want it to get cold.'          Lucy and Willy both screamed 'Yea!' and hopped up to the table.                   'This is good food,'said Dad.          'Yes, it is,' agreed Mom.          Suddenly, Lucy Screamed, 'What is that?!'          Lucy's dad turned around as quickly as he could and saw his robot standing right there.          He screamed,'He's alive!'          'Who is?'asked Lucy.          'My robot! It works!' replied Dad.                         'I get to play with him first,'said Willy.          'What did you name him,' asked Mom.          'I haven't named him yet,'replied Dad.          'You should name him Roger or something,'said Lucy.          'Yea!'said Willy.

Item_Response: A boy named Jack Taylor was riding his brand new bike in his driveway when he stumbled upon a key. The key had a golden, brassy color to it. Jack was a very curious boy, so he wondered what the key opened. Jack quickly ran inside to show his father Thomas his newly found treasure. Thomas identified the key as his great grandfather's.   His great grandfather was a phsycopath obbsessed with robots and space.At his time mechanical objects were almost unimagenable to the general population but he was no general population.       Thomas's great grandfather Gerald Taylor was born in 1856 in the small town of Roseburg, Oregon. As a child his family migrated from Ohio on the Oregon Trail.   From a young age he was facsinated by unworldly objects. Item_Response: The Alive Robot            One day, there was a young girl named Angelina. It was a sunny day in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. This young girl had a dog robot named Fluffy. Fluffy and Angelina were best friends. It was summer when the amazement happened. Little Angelina, only 9-years-old, playing with Fluffy in her backyard. After using all their energy, they went inside the house for lunch. They ate a lot, so they had to take a short nap.        After an hour, Angelina and her dog woke up. She exclaimed, 'Fluffy, you look so real. What did you do to make it look like you have real fur?' Then, Fluffy barked. All of a sudden, the confused girl said, 'Are you sick? Your bark isn't the same.' A few seconds later, she realized what had happened. Her robot dog became real. She thought to herself, 'This must be a dream!', so she pinched herself. She then said (realizing that something very exciting happened), 'Ouch! Fluffy! You became a real dog!'        When her parents heard her screaming joyfully, they asked, 'What happened?' Angelina told her parents the whole story. At first her parents thought that she just was imaging everything, but Angelina's parents saw the evidence (Fluffy as a real life dog). After this coincidence, the 2 of them lived happily ever after.

Im positive because, its at the place i always stare at when im trying to sleep. The robot is proped in the corner. It is about 5.5 feet tall. The robot is a beautiful sparkling silver. Has two feet like a human except the about a foot long. Some robot has really long feet. I think the rovot is designed to look like a human, because it has bright fire engine red hair. The har is back in two Long braids. Tied at the end with ocean blue ribbions. The robot has eyes that are shut. Obviously the robot needs a mirrior becouse it has just a lot to much eyeshadow.  The robot has a dress on. The dress is a light pink. like the pink in the sky when the sun is setting. The dress is long sleeves. The dress is covered with white polka dots. Each polka dot is about the size of a quarter. The dress on the robot isnt like human dresses nor is her hair, its metal along with the rest of its body. I decide i want a closer look at the robot. So i stretch out of bed. BRRRR!!!! My feet touch the freezing cold floor. It feels like stepping on ice barefoot. So i quiky run over to slippers and slip my feet in. It warms my whole body quikly like sitting next to fire on a cold winter day. As the warmth of my feet spread to body i quitly tip toe over to the robot. When I reacht the robot i crouch down. While i look into the robots face i suddenly realize the robots eyes are open. I scream bloody murder as i spring out of the room. Down the brightly painted hall. Down the wooden stairs. Threw the messy living room. Into the drak kitchen. I flip on the lights. Where is everyone i wonder. At the grochery store, out- No i dont have time for this i interupt my thoughts. Where can i hide? I wonder as is spot the door to the basement. I run to it open the door and grabe a flashlight from the near by shelf. I quikly flash it on run down the squeeky,  old wooden stairs. Farther i go into creep darkness. .           I quikly flip on the light. Countinue running. I open up the door to the gym. I run threw the huge gym. Into the library i go. Library! Since when did i have a library. Wait since when did i have a basement. Sice when was my bedroom upsataris. Since when did i have a gym! I figured it out this isnt my house! I have to get out. I see a door in the back of the room. I run to it. I put my hand on the freezing cold brass door Knod and open the door. It leads to stairs. Up the stairs i run. I opne another door at then end of the stairs and am outside. I need a break im breathless. So i run the to neighboors back yard and take a break. Sit down and rest. Then i hear the gate slowly creek open and see the robot heading my way. I cant move im in so much shock i cant move. The robot reaches me. One hand move towards me and grabs me. Then it pukks me up. Drags me into the shed and says. This is my secret play house. Wanna play dollies? Suddnedy i realize its a nice robot.

Item_Response: Once upon a time there was a little girl and a little boy looking for there dad. Their names were Ashley Ann Walker and Sander William Walker. Their dad's name is John Haiden Walker. Ashley and Sander new that their dad worked for the mining, but he hadn't been home for days. So one day they were walking to the park and they past a garbage can and they seen two wheels sticking up, so they got the thing out and they seen that it was a Gemini-Scout robot. They seen that it was broke but they had a grandpa who fixes cars, robots, etc. So they called up their grandpa and he answered and they asked,' Can you please help us fix this thing that we got, because it broke.' So their grandpa came over and he saw that it was damaged pretty bad but he didn't want to say anything. So the next day he had fixed it, and then the kids said thank you and looked up the name of Gemini-Scout and it said that the Gemini-Scout was a robot that helped the mines fined the lost minors orlet them know that there was terrible gas or something. Ashley and Sander gasped with releif. They knew that they could find there dad with it, but they noticed that it was only 2 feet tall and they wondered how it would carry their dad out. But they kept reading and it said,' They might not look strong but they are.' So Ashley and Sander started to go down to the mines and they got to the cave and looked in and it was pitch black. So they yelled for their dad and there was no response. So Ashley but the robot down and gave the remote control to Sander, because the remote control looked like a Xbox controler and she knew that Sander loved to play Xbox. So they seen the camera and turned it on so now they can see where the little robot was going. And so they say yellow, orange, and red on the camera and they new it was their dad. So the little robot pulled him back all the way where Ashley and Sander were. They seen they he wasn't in good condition so they called 911 and they came as fast as they could. So they got him to the hospital and told Ashley and Sander to stay outside. And then Ashley and Sander seen a robot kinda like theirs. They did also see that the robot could talk so they looked it up and it was named Mr. Gower. They seen that Mr. Gower helps the doctors, they bring them medicene most of the time. So they seen it go into their dads room and they heard him talk! They jumped for joy to the boice of their father and they went in to give them a great big hug and kiss!       So ten years later Ashley got married to Stue Wisley and they had 8 kids. Four girls and four boys! Their names were Brooke, Sophie, Scarlett, Jamie, Bill, Charlie, Sam, Joe. And Sander got married to a beautiful young girl named Samantha and they had 2 kids there were 1 girl and one boy and their names were Claire Marie and Justin william. The End!!!       By: Brianna Sanderson!

Item_Response: We were at the store on a cloudy, rainy, foggy day when all of a sudden my brother, Alex, had told my mom, Sarah, and I that his toy robot came to life. 'Alex, I'm not going to tell you again, your robot is not alive.'          'Yes mama it is alive it just talked a second ago.'             'Whatever,' I said                   From that day forward I knew that nothing would ever be the same again. I din't know who or what to believe and I didn't know who or what not to believe. My brother's robot is named Bob, I felt that he was my parent. Bob fed me, kept me company, and so much more beyond that. Bob was a role model for my brother and I. Now get this, he even cleans our rooms!                    Bob eventually was taken away from us and was given to  a scientist. We knew he was better off there, but we missed him desperatley and wanted him back. While Bob was away he was trained to to climb into the ground and retrieve hurt people and climb into volcanoes and pick up information. The scientists decided that he wanted to take Bob away on an expidition across America. Thats when my brother and I knew we had to go get our little Bob                      Later that night Alex and I packed out bags and took a long bus ride to the scientists house where we saw Bob on the fornt porch. The house was an old faded yellow with ugly white shutters. Bob had changed tremendously,  he wasn't gray anymore he was bright red and was wearing something that a scientists would wear. My brother and I looked at eachother,'BOB,' we yelled and ran over to him. All of a sudden this nasty scientists walked outside. He had a moles all over his face and reminded me of a witch. 'This is ours, I believe,' we said and took off laughing faster than we've ever ran before. Bob started to say something, but was cut off by the rumbling of the bus. When we got on he said that the scientists didn't even know that he was actually alive and could talk and care for people, he was just using me. 'I'm so happy you guys found me!' 'Awwwww,' we said,We are happy we found you too.'

Item_Response: One day Flynns teacher told him he has a science project. Flynn said 'Is there anything in particular we have to do?'Yes actually you have to use your imagination!' Ms.Flowers has always has been Flynns favorite teacher.Suddenly an idea popped into Flynns head. He told his best friend danny what he was going to do for his project.Danny thought it was a great idea to make a robot for the assignment.Danny said'Wow how are you going to pull that off?'Flynn hasn't put a lot of thought into it so he said 'I have to look up ideas on the internet.'' 'Can i come over to your house today?'asked Danny.'Sure why not I'll help you come up with ideas.'Sounds great my mom will drop me off at 3:00.'                         When Danny came over to Flynns house they got started right away. Danny's idea for his science project is putting a needle through the a balloon without it popping.When Flynn got on the computer he went straight on to Google. he typed in'How to build a robot?'Answes popped up everywhere but Flynn only stuck with one.Once he got all the materials he built the robot of his dreams. He was so professional he made a switch to turn it on and off. When he turned it on it didnt work so he tried it again still nothing one last time and nothing happened.'Whats going on?'asked Danny. 'I dont know somethings wrong.'they aked Flynns mom and she said nothing but,then she said 'we'll fix it later once we come back from dinner.''                   When they got out of the car they went into a chinese restraunt called Lucky duckling. When they got in they ordered the mom gave Flynn and Danny a dime so they can go to the wishing well.When they got over there Danny wished for a new skateboard.   Then Flynn wished for his robot to work.When everybody was done eating they got their fortune cookies and ate then read the fotune and   both Danny and Flynn got the same fortune saying 'your wishes will come true'.                     When they dropped off Danny Flynn and his mom and dad went home.When Flynn went into his room his robot was working and walking around and talking. Flynn went rushing to his robot and talked to him.The robot said ''Hello Flynn how are you doing today?'   'Good now that your alive!'Robot said get some sleep if your going to show me off tommorrow in class.''ok'                    When Danny was done showing his trick Flynn went on the podium he showed everybody his robot.Everyone loved it and asked him to make him talk and ms Flowers gave him an A and he went off happy with his robot forever.

Item_Response: Martin VII           Dr. Jykell was in his laboratory again. Potions bubbled, gases hissed, and electricity surged through wires and circuits. Dry ice was sitting in a corner, and clouds were rolling out of the bucket. The laboratory was littered with screws and broken glass and crumpled blueprints were scattered all over the dusty tiled floor. In the middle of the pigsty sat Dr. Jykell, who was a rather cranky old scientist, mumbling to himself how annoying it was to construct the same thing seven times, without any success. He was tired, and he sleepily took his wrench and fixed up some loose bolts on the chunky piece of metal lying before him. The machine looked complex though, as it had a series of buttons and gadgets and whatnot attached to it. Dr. Jykell's piggish eyes looked smaller than ever as he squinted, attaching a wire which was connected to a battery to his machine. He looked expectantly at his invention. Nothing happened. He grunted, then yawned widely. He told himself that he truly needed some sleep.                                                                     Suddenly, as he was turning away, a series of beeps erupted from that machine. Dr. Jykell spun around and was greeted by his machine, his robot standing up with his multicolored lights flashing and beeps filling the room. Dr. Jykell's eyes widened. He jumped up and down, as high as his stout little body could go, shouting out of joy. He did a little dance and sang in his gravelly voice! He finally skipped over to the robot and said, 'Your name will be....Marvin! Yes, yes, it will be Marvin-make it Marvin the Seventh, for you're my seventh yet successful try! Yipeeee!!'                                                                                                                            As it happened, Dr. Jykell was not just a scientist, but also a very honored manager of a coal mining industry. He installed a camera, a thermal camera, an air detecting device, and a first aid kit in his beloved Marvin VII. Marvin VII helped Dr. Jykell very well, in ways that not even a human could! He detected and saved many of  the doctor's miners and found new places where coal could be found.                  Marvin VII was like family to Dr. Jykell. The doctor felt like his invention could understand him. 'You know,' Dr. Jykell was saying to Marvin, 'You did well today. You saved Brady, Tony, Jackson, and Ryan- my best miners! You dragged them out of certain death and led them to safety. I have to say, I'm very proud!'                 Marvin VII swiveled his neck around and looked at Brady, Tony, Jackson, and Ryan. They had only a few cuts and bruises, rather than broken limbs and death. Marvin was satisfied with is work. 'Beep boop bopitty pop click zzzzip!' he replied. He loved Dr. Jykell as much as Dr, Jykell loved him.

Like mentioned above, the robot can help you get medicine, put you or anyone else to bed, and can help you take care of kids. One day everyone's lives will be much easier.

Item_Response: Mrs.Janice was about to announce the class's science assignment everyone stood waiting, wondering what she was about to say. Then she said loud and clear ' Our class assignment is to... build a robot and make a poster board to go with it!' Everyone stared shocked and surprised. Some of them didn't even know what a robot was. Amy (one of the students) raised hand and Mrs.Janice asked what Amy needed and Amy said 'What kind of robot? And how are we supposed to build one?' Mrs.Janice ignored her for a second and then replied 'Well, you buy the parts and design your own.' Amy stared at her and said 'That sounds to difficult!' Mrs.Janice started to wonder what was so hard about it. Next she said ' I will give you each a sheet of paper that gives you a list of some resources so you can get an idea of how to make your robot.' Then she held up a paper that read: 'Good resources for making or researching a robot; http://WWW.umm.edu/news/releases,/robot.htm;http://WWW.economist.com/node/15048711...' And it went on. After everyone finish reading the paper the bell rang and the students went home.                As Amy walked home she thought about how difficult it would be to make a robot. Amy thought about what supplies she would use and how. She thought about how she would design her poster board. She realized it would just be easier if she didn't complain. When she got home she was still alone knowing this she tried to remember why. Then she remembered that her mom and dad were at work. She was a loner anyway and did not like help. She got to work on her poster board. Threw a dash of glitter, smeared a little paint and pasted pictures. When she was done she started on her robot(which was the longest and hardest part.) She didn't know where any wires were except for the computer so she raced towards it knowing it would be a piece of cake to yank just a few wires from her dad's new computer. After she had the wires she looked up how to connect the wires in order to make the robot move. The website said to design the machine first. So Amy took some metal and bent it into the shape of a sphere and added eight legs just like the Dante 2. Next she made a crane at the top so it could grab and carry stuff. And right behind the crane she added a seat and steering wheel. The reason Amy added the seat and steering wheel is so she could ride her robot. After all of the designing was done Amy threaded the wires into the right spots and put the correct programming into the correct areas. It wasn't quite done yet though because Amy had to decorate the big robot. So she ran to her room and dug through her draws and found hot pink glitter paint, purple glitter, blue glitter, puppy stickers and a baby blue seat cushion. Next she ran back to the living room and got to work. First Amy painted the robot, not missing a single spot. Second Amy put sparkly polka-dots all over using a pattern of blue and purple. Third she put the cute little puppy stickers inside of each colorful little polka-dot. Lastly she tied the seat cushion onto the raised seat. Amy's robot was going to be the best robot ever.            Amy kept trying to get control over her robot but it was very difficult and confusing. Amy could move just not steer it. it worried her because the assignment was due tomorrow and each student was supposed to demonstrate how their robots worked. Amy decided that maybe her robot just needed some fresh air so she rode him to the park. Eventually she started to gain control over the tall robot. After awhile Amy decided her robot wasn't good enough; she wanted a waterproof robot that can go into heats as high as two thousand degrees Fahrenheit. So she rode her robot to the store and bought insulation and waterproof spray. When she got to the check out she paid the cashier and walked outside to where she sprayed her robot with the waterproof spray and put the insulation on her robot. Now her robot was the best. She had control and it was waterproof.             Today was the day of the presentation. Amy felt nervous but relieved. But she knew she could do it. She got dressed in her spotted polka-dot dress with her hot pink flats. She felt a knot in her throat as she hopped onto her robot. She sat, her back laying on top of her poster board. And they started walking, keeping an eye on the road. She felt so tall and strong as a cool breeze blew through her hair. As Amy and her robot approached her school she felt scared. Her robot step into school, all of the younger kids staring in awe at the sight of a real robot. Amy just ignored them as she walked down the sixth grade hall towards her class. She commanded her robot to open the door with his crane and he did. Amy dropped her stuff off and went outside for morning recess. She walked outside wondering what the presentation will be like.              After recess all of Mrs.Janice's students rushed inside like a stampede. Amy felt clueless as she walked through the doors of the school. Amy sat at her desk wondering who will present first. Then she heard her teacher talking she was about to announce who was presenting first. Then she heard '...The presenter will be... Amy!' Amy was so shocked she almost threw up. Amy slowly walked up to the podium and recited her speech. Next she showed the class how it worked and walked back to her seat. Then she heard her teacher say 'Wow, give Amy a round of applause!' And everyone clapped for her. She blushed at the thought of everyone liking her robot. All there was left to do was watch the other classmates' presentations. First Carl's, then Bob's, third Sally's and so on. Amy didn't really have a favorite because she loved them all. And Mrs.Janice loved them all to.

Item_Response: As you may know, there are many robots in this world. But, there are specific robots for everyday ordeals. There are robots for rescue work, medicine deliveries, and for driving your car. Let's see which robots do these jobs.               You know how there are robots that do rescue work. One special robot for that is called the Gemini-Scout. Not only does the Gemini-Scout do rescue work, it also searches for items in the mines. It also collects information inside the mines. Not only that but it can also test the air to see if it is healthy or not. Then, the scientists on the mines can tell whether to enter or not. Also, if the Gemini-Scout finds a lost or injured person, there is a two-way radio to find them. Doesn't the Gemini-Scout sound like a vital need? I think so.                       Medicine is vital to an ill person. Why not have a robot to deliver it faster? That is why we have Mr. Gower. His job is to deliver medicine in gigantic hospitals. The doctors and nurses already do too much work doing surgery and all. We need to help those people! Mr. Gower is an important part of being in a hospital. Did you know that the Mr. Gower robot is so strong that it can lift up to 500 pounds? Just think, that can be full of vital medicine for to save peoples' lives. Isn't that fascinating?                          Finally, there are robots that drive a car for you! There is a car called the Google Car. This was introduced in Nevada and it is literally changing the world. Plus, the Google Car can control its own speed. That way, there won't be as many speeding tickets. Since this robot was full on changing the world, the state of Nevada wanted to send a law to the state Legislature to allow the Google Car to be used on the road. It is soon to be passed but if we try, the law might be passed.           Now do you see why robots are so indispensable to our lives. What would we do without robots? I have no clue.

Item_Response: One summer afternoon in Hamptonville,North Carolina,Jack and his brother John just got out of school and it's going to be fun under the sun, or so they thought.Their parents came home with a pretty good sized box.'Kids we have a suprise for you.' 'What is it.',they asked at the same time.Close your eyes and you will see.       They closed their eyes.'Suprise!'It's a pet dog.Well sort of.It's a robot pet dog.        'You can play with it but you don't have to feed it or take it outside.'But this robo dog is very special and they don't even know it yet.'I love it' cried out Jack.'Me too.' 'I'm so glad' said their mom.           'Hello Jack and John'said a radom voice.they looked around in curiosity.'Down here'said the voice.They looked down in amazment.'Who are you'asked the family.'I do not know,you have not given me a name yet.' 'I say lets call him Sparky'said Jack.'That's a good name said their parents.              'What else can you do Sparky'asked John?'I can do a lot of stuff' said Sparky.'Ican help tou with work,I can play with you if you are boerd,I can also act like any normal house dog or even an outside one as well.' 'Can you do tricks?'Asked their dad.'I said I can act like a normal dog cant I?'              'Let's see it then shall we.' Roll over,play dead, and shake. 'Wow, I guess I was wrong.'said dad.'We need to show him too the world he's a really big achivement in science history.'                 'But it is to much of a chance for scientists to take him away and study how he came to life.'Said the to brothers.Okay.'Yes!' Later that day they got to know Sparky a little bit better.'Mom!Dad!' Yelled the brothers.'We learned a lot about Sparky and where he is from.'                  'What?'asked their mom.'Sparky was originaly supposed to be a Dante 2 robot which is the kind of job where he is supposed to go into volcanos and explore it. 'Wow!' 'I know and that was a year ago but he got mixed up for a play robot and still to this day researchers are still looking for him.' 'But before mom could answer there was a knock on the door, we peeked through the window there was researchers outside.                    ''We need the robot please.' 'Can we help you?' 'Yes you can that robot is to advanced for human kind,we need him to go into volcanos and help us gather information,he is also Gemini-Scout he must help us get some miners out of the mine not so far from the volcano before the volcano erupts and kills all of the miners inside.' 'Please he is our only hope of getting them out alive.' 'Take him he has been good help to us so he will be goos help to you to.'                    ''Can we go see him in action mom.' 'I guess.' Once they saw him in action he succefully reterieved the miners and thank the lord the volcano went off thank to Sparky because he gave the researchers whst they needed in order to stop the volcano.

Item_Response: I was working on my robot one day, I had just put in the last piece in when something extraordinary happened.It came to life!I was so scared, but I didn't run. I was curious to find out how , how could it possibly come to life? I went to a scientist to see if he could tell me how this is possible. 'There is no explanation',he said.'I am sorry I couldn't be of assistance.' I could tell he would be working on the subject for a while.              At home I thought for a moment. What could this robot do? I pushed a button. This made the robot talk,cool! I told him my commands and he did them. I told him to make dinner and then do the dishes afterward. He did exactly what I told him. One day something happened ,and he wouldn't do what I told him to do. He said he wanted to leave. He wants to go to another house and help them. He had a great time but he has to go. I say goodbye and walk to my bedroom. I never saw him again.

Item_Response: This story is going to be about a robot that suddenly comes to life.            One day a young boy goes to the store with his mom and buys a toy robot. When the boy and his mom gets home he opens his toy. He plays with the robot for hours the goes to bed. The next morning he wakes up and can't find his robot he looks everywhere but still can't find. He goes downstairs and he sees his toy walkingaround and cooking breakfest.           He asked his mom if she made breakfest but she said no. So he goes into the kitchen and takes his toy upstairs to his bedroom.when he goes to his bedroom the robot starts to talk to him and he finds out that his toy had came to life.            He goes outside and finds out that the robot can do alot of stuff. For example it can run throw a baseball and even climb trees! He tries to tell his mom that his toy came to life but she don't believe him.             The next day when he wakes up his toy was doing the exact same thing as last time. He takes it outside and he plays with it all day. When he goes in he goes to bed wakes up and does the exact same thing the next day.              That is my story about a robot that comes to life.

Item_Response: It's a regular day at the hospital and Ms. Melon is going around delivering medican. She bumped into a nurse and the nurse's coffee spilled on Ms. Melon. Sparks started to come out of her and she and then she opened her eye's and started moving around but not like she used to it was like a human. The nurse she Knocked over was scared how about how she was more like a human than a robot she still looked the same but that was it.       She still continued her job but everybody treated her like a human they even gave her primisson to take care of the sick people. She was moved up to a nurse but she still got to deliver medican like she always did. She was not told what to do no more but she did have times when she would think she was still a robot.       She mostly only worked with the kids because she loved them she thought it was  fun taking care of them and talking to them. After she worked she got off and went walking around people looked at her like they was scared but she didn't let that bother her she liked living like a human. She met a lot of people and she liked that now she had friends she even stayed with one until she could afford her own home. She used to stay at the hospital when she was a regular robot.       A few days pasted and she was taking care of children and she got called and said they wanted her delivering medican so she went and did that job and she remeberd what it was like being a robot. She would always think of that she missed it but she had to realize she had to a human.

Item_Response: Sally's New Assistant            Once upon a time there was a six year old girl named Sally, who was playing with her toy robot. She named her toy robot Fia. Sally loved Fia more than anything. Sally took Fia to Target at 6:00 P.M and left her at Target. Sally noticed when she got home and her parents did not take her back to Target. Then something happened!        Sally woke up in the morning and went to eat breakfast and saw Fia. She did not know how Fia got back to her house because robots cannot walk! Then. Sally relized Fia was a huge robot who could walk, serve you breakfast, lunch and dinner, and drive. Fia was Sally's personal assistant!        Sally's parents were still sleeping so Sally wakes up her parents. She walks her parents to Fia and shows them how Fia is her personal assistant, but when Sally shows her parents, Fia she strinks down back into a toy. Sally tells her parents that she is a life size robot but they do not believe her so they go back to bed. But right when Sally's parents leave Fia turns back into a life size robot. Sally talks to Fia and asks why she does not want her parents to see. Fia says, 'I want this secret between me and you. Ok Sally?' Sally says,'Yes, I understand.' Sally and Fia promised to keep it between them until Fia gets more comfortable around Sally's parents.        As time goes on, Sally's parents find out about Fia and like Fia. Fia helps them cook dinner, clean the dishes, and clean the house. Fia got a car so she takes Sally everywhere like to soccer practice, mall, Target, and much more. Fia is the best thing that as happened to Sally and her parents.        That is what happened to Sally the six year old and her favorite robot turned into a life size robot. Sally's, and her parents life are much better with a robot who helps around the house for free!

Item_Response: R2D3 The Robot           It was a normal day for the robot named R2D3. He was getting his master his coffee without a thought in his head. R2D3 was a very rare robot. No other robots in the world had some the of the qualities he had! He had two eyes one was a thermal camera and another was a normal camera. He had a jet pack and unlimited fuel. He was made of the most rare metals in all of the world. His head was made out of Platinum. His body was made out of Titanium. Each of his legs were normal iron but every wire inside him was made out of gold! His data base could only recall a little bit about his master. He was the most famous robot creator in the world. His name was Liam Rosten of England. His creator made him have everything for every situation. He was a very unique robot, a very unique robot indeed.                 One morning he awoke cold and shivering. He was huddled in a corner where he was usually charging. 'What is this. Wait how am i talking to myself!' He looked down at his hands and saw what looked like his owners hands. His stomach growled and he wondered 'what is that?' He was scared his heart was racing it was getting hard for him to breathe 'what is happening to me!' He screamed a loud scream not a high pitched one. He heard someone coming down the stairs it was his owner. ' By gods boy what are you doing in my house? Sir it is me R2D3. Your not my robot he is, wait where is my robot!' R2D3 was scared his heart was racing again it was getting hard for him to breathe 'Help Me' His owner rushed to the kitchen and got him a cold rag and put it over his head and then he asked, 'Who are you.' This time he asked it in a calm voice. R2D3 replied 'R2D3 your robot.'                 R2D3 stayed at the house for several more days while his owner kept asking who are you. Then one day R2D3 had thought of a way to show him that he was his owner! he said, 'Mr. Owner could you please come here with all of R2D3's information?' 'Sure why not.' Then R2D3 started to say his serial number and everything about him. His owner watched in awe. He had never shared any of R2D3's information with anyone so he must be him! His owner hugged him and said, 'Welcome back.'

Item_Response: That's when it all happened that day. I was on my laptop searching for a robot. There were all types of robots that I didn't need. There were Gemini-scout, Dante 2, Mr. Gower, and Agribot. I knew I didn't need a Gemini-scout because I'm not a mine, and I definitely didn't need a Dante 2 because I'm not a scientist. The rest were useless to me. So i searched on another website and found a robot, HRP-4c, that i thought was interesting and the cost wasn't that much, too. I ordered it. now all I had to do was wait.            A week later, I got a package in the mail and surprisingly, it was the robot. I was so happy when I got it . now i could have a friend to watch over the house. I turned only the security on and left the house. As I was leaving I grabbed the keys. I called my friend and let her know I was free to hang out with her. I drove to her house and  to be honest I had a fun time. We watched a movie and ate ice cream. We even played truth or dare. it was the best time i had in a while  and I was happy to enjoy the moment. but all the fun was gone when I had to go home. I got in the car and drove home. it was 11:00 pm and I hadn't realized how tiered I was. I went to bed. The next morning was for me to get down to business with the robot and figure out how to use it. It was morning and as tired as i was i got up and started looking online on how to control the robot. I found that there was a button on the back that you could switch to Manuel and it would do normal things like house chores. I also found that there was another button and it was used for  a type of playing mode for kids or adult. I soon figured out that it could dance and sing! I loved the robot now.               That's when it all started. I left again to hang out with her. I came back again at the same time. Suddenly, I heard a noise and a crash. It was coming from the kitchen I grabbed a bat and headed down stairs. THE ROBOT! Some how it was on by itself it started swinging at me and breaking stuff. I was so shocked I didn't have time react that it knocked me out and I was conics. Later my friend went to drop off my jacket and saw me hurt. She called the cops. '' Is she going to be okay?'',she asked the cops. she's fine just an accident she must of left the robot on, that all '', he said. '' no I didn't I came down the stairs and it was on by itself it's haunted'', I said. But they didn't believe me. they left and cleaned the mess up. '' Maybe their right I probably didn't shut it off''', I said to my friend. She agreed to live with me until I was safe.                  She moved in the next day. We went to sleep early that night. Then I heard it. She heard it. We both went down stairs the robot was on once again. But this time the robot had red laser eyes and was staring right at me. I this time I reacted and so did Amanda,(my friend) we hit the robot with the bat. That didn't work. so instead we hit it even harder. After we hit it 20 times, and almost got hit by the lasers it was defeated. We had done it. It was over and done with. Amanda ripped the batteries out and I through the robot in the garbage to have it at the dump tomorrow. She was right, she had stood with me until I was safe and I am safe now with her.Later that day I moved to her house to live with her, forever.

Item_Response: THE ROBOT WHO NEARLY ENDED THE WORLD AND THE ONE WHO SAVED IT                    Once there was a teenage boy named Matt Jensen, he was one of the most popular and smartest kids at his school.  He was partnered up with a straight A student, Ryan Trace, in the science fair.  Their assighnment was to build a robot with multiple functons.  Matt knew he had to build something that would astonish the judges. He didn't know what it should do or how he could do it.  He had the idea of making a remote controlled robot untill he saw all of the compotitions robots, all remote controled.  He decided he would build an A.I, an artaficial intelegance robot, one who could make decisions speak and even help people in need.  He and his partner did it.  It was a human like robot with super human strength and it looked like a human but it was a pale white metel. but there were multiple problems. One of the other smart cotestants Mark Gilvouski found the blue prints and tried to make one himself.  He had changed a lot of things about the robot, he gave it more emotions such as anger and hate.  Soon this new robot had figured out it was more advanced than humans and begun making more exactly like him but without leadership skills so they would listen to him.  The day of the science fair came and when Matt and Ryan Presented his robot Marks robot saw and had became furious.  Matt suggested that the name the robot and Ryan named him Raziel.             Meanwhile Mark had named his too, he named him Crowly.  he had soon launched a full out attack on the town, it seemed all hope had been lost.  Raziel had known this and started to make robots exactly like him, but by the time he had finished Crowly had already controlled the state and somehow without the militarys knowladge had gained controll of the U.S nuclear and automated weapons.  Raziel had finnaly decided to fight back.  There was an enourmous batle and most of the robots defeated eachother, but Raziels side was winning do to the fact that he built them eaquil to him unlike Crowly.  Soon Crowly had became worried and launched his automated defenses but they were no match for Raziel.  He had soon came to the room where his rival was hiding and controlling them.  Raziel had a huge tavantage though because he knew their only weekness elctricity.   after battling for a long time he got him into a large body of water and used an upgrade he made to himself, an electric pulsar. they were both destroyed and the world rebuilt itself and the creators of the robots destroyed the blueprints forever.           Twenty seven years later, Matts kid, jeremy, found the early blueprints to Crowly.  He made a remote controlled replica and put the core in that so he wouldn't repeat history.  But what he didn't account for was that it was an A.I core so it gained a counsious over time.  Soon it was aware of it's surroundings, then it was aware it was being controlled.  It started trying to fight the commands it's owner gave it.  Sometimes it could, sometimes not, but soon it was so strong there were only a few commands it would follow.  It had gotten so bad that Jeremy shut it off completely, but it turned itself back on and ripped out it's own circutboard for the remote controll setting.  the robot went on a killing spree trying to get rid of the humans.  he had to rebuild an almost exact model of Raziel with an electric pulsar and destroy the robot wich he did.  He died by the rebound of the pulsar which he had built wrong.  The building he was in caught fire destroying the blueprints and the early ones forever.                                                    THE END

Item_Response: This story talked about the robots that they are building to help people out. They talk about five kinds of robots. One was Mr. Gower, he helps out at hospitals to bring things. For example he brings medicine to the patients. He can also talk, ride on elavators, and runs on batteries.            Another, robot that they talked about was Dante 2. It climbs in volcanoes, and tells the scientist if it is safe to go in. It figures out if there are dangerous gases in the volcanoes. With Dante 2 scientist can now explore a volcanoe from their labortories.            They also talked abput a Geemini Scout which rescues and searches mines that are under ground. Its remote control is like the one that you would use to play a video game. This robot has a two-way radio to talk with others. It also uses a thermal camera which uses heat sensors to find other people.          The Agribot is a farming robot. It picks fruit when it senses that it is ready. For example there is one in Japan that does that. In Massachusetts scientist are growing cherry tomatoes with robots. They have even created a green house for that! There may not be as much robots today, but maybe in the future there will!

Item_Response: One day, a robot went on a trip to investigate a volcano. After it gathered all the information, it came back to the science lab to be recharged. The day after, the scientist went to the robot where it was supposed to be charging but it wasn't there. The charger was back in its place and the scientist heard something strange, something that sounded like spider legs but louder and heavier. 'Hello,' said the robot. The scientists were shocked that the robot spoke to them.       ' How did the robot talk? We only created this robot to gather information from a volcano!' Exclaimed a scientist.       ' I'm alive, so now my brain knows what humans know. I have emotions too and I don't need to recharge anymore,' the robot told.       Days after, the scientists were having lots of fun with the robot because that now it's smarter with emotions, they don't always have to be alone too. When they need to research a volcano, the robot can talk through a bluetooth that the scientists created for the robot incase it gets lost. Everything became more easier that day when the robot became alive.

Item_Response: Once there was a robot who's name was AWSM-17x. It was not an Android as you would imagine, But a small, 2.5 ft tall, 3 ft long robot shaped like a football with legs, the legs being 1.5 ft tall while the football-shaped 'head' itself is only 1 ft tall. The first leg was not like a human leg, but like two shiny metal poles about 1 inch thick attached by a small, steel hinge, and was attached to the head at the end of one pole, and attached to a claw-like foot at the end of the other. The other leg was exactly the same. Inside his head was a mechanical brain made to work like a human brain.          Small AWSM-17x had one big problem -- he never could do anything he wanted to because he had no arms. He couldn't turn pages to read, couldn't write, couldn't use a controler for a video game, or even turn on his shiny steel television that was in his cave-like house.          That wasn't his only problem, however. There was also RBO-13z and BLLY-6u. RBO-13z was a titanium android that looked like a shiny, gold skinned person approxamently 7ft and 3 inches with dirty blonde metal 'hair' and was extremely skinny. BLLY-6u was 5ft 7 inches, had silver, iron 'skin' and dark-brown strands of metal for hair. He was an android, but had four arms and was extremely strong, with metal, interior armor that made him look bulk. Every day RBO-13z and BLLY-6u bullied AWSM-17x.          One day, RBO-13z and BLLY-6u ribbed the metal skin off of AWSM-17x's sides, reveiling two folded in arms that he used to protect him self and was never bullied again.
