Item_Response: One day my friends and I were walking home from school. We all decided we would come to my house to do our project. When we got to my house I unlocked the door and a note fell down. I guess my mom left a note saying she was at work. They said it was okay if we stayed alone. My friends and I all walked in and sat down. I got our materials out and set them on the table. 'This is what we need to build our robot' I say. 'Lets get started' Diane says. Everyone digs in the table and starts getting everything they need.                                'Ill work on the legs' Selah says.                                                         'Ill do the arms' Diane says.    'I will start doing the head' Anthony says.   'Then I guess ill do the stomach' I say.               It took hours but we finally finished our masterpiece. Our amazing robot stood right in front of our eyes. We were so concentrated on building the robot we lost track of time. It was 8:30 and they forgot to call their parents. Diane called and her parents said she can sleepover. Selah and Anthony called and they said the same thing. We were already getting our sleeping bags ready when we forgot to put the robot away. We put the robot in the closet and turned out the lights. 'Goodnight' Anthony says. Everybody repeats the same thing and drifts to sleep. BEEP BEEP I AM A ROBOT. I jump up quickly and wake up everyone. They hear the sound and jumped.   'What is that noise' Selah says.   'I don't know but it was creepy' Diane says.   'We will have to see for ourselves' I say and grab a flashlight.               We crept downstairs slowly and quietly with the light shining in the dark. 'I want my mommabear' Anthony says. 'Stop being such a baby' Selah says. 'Okay were about to find something creepy and you guys think its the perfect time to argue'? Diane says. Selah and Anthony stayed silent until we got to the bottom of the stairs. 'Stop shaking Anthony' I say. 'Well sorry' he says. Selah and Diane let out a giggle. I nuged them in the stomach. 'Look there's a light' I say. They all gasped when they saw it. 'Is that our ROBOT' Anthony yells. 'I think it is' Diane says. I hear clicks. 'What is that sound' I say. Diane and Selah shrug their shoulders. I turn around and see Anthony taking pictures with his iphone. 'Stop it' I tell him. He stops taking pictures. We need to get a closer look.                 I AM A ROBOT. WHAT IS MY NAME. We stare at the robot. We look at the table and theres cups of coffee everywhere, but not in a mug. It looked like it had the logo of starbucks on it. 'Your name is Starbucks' Anthony says. We all nod. I AM STARBUCKS. We laugh wow our robot is alive I thought. 'Guess whos getting an A on our project, WE ARE'! Selah says. ''How about we celabrate with starbucks' Diane says. ''Okay good I love starbucks'' Anthony says. ''WHAT WOULD YOU LIKE'' Starbucks asks Anthony. 'We will all have a Javachip. ''HERE YOU GO HAHA'' Starbucks says. We all drink our starbucks. This was an interesting night.

Item_Response: Two sisters, Kelly and Denise, were doing their chores. They were currently washing dishes, Kelly washing, Denise drying. They had just missed out on going to the park with their friends because their mom wanted them to do their chores.   'I wish we had somebody else to do our chores.' Kelly sighed washing a bowl that looked like it had chili in it.   'Like a robot or something.' Denise agreed.   'Yeah EXACTLY!'   'The robot would clean our room, do all our work, and be our servent.'   'Ooh I think they have those now.' Kelly said.   'Yeah probably for trillions of dollars.' Denise sighed.   'You know who might have trillions of dollars laying around?'   'Who in this world has that kind of money just laying around?' Denise asked.   'Aunt Trudy.'   'Oh yeah!' Denise remembered. 'But she wouldn't just give us a robot that cost that much.'   'My 16th birthday is coming up!' Kelly said with a grin from ear to ear.        After their chores they started sending letters to their Aunt dropping subtle hints about a robot. Like 'I would come visit you auntie but we have so much work!' and 'For my birthday I want a way to do my chores really fast and go visit you!' Eventually Kelly got frustrated when Aunt Trudy wasn't getting it. 'Can I get a robot for my birthday? I hope it's not too much to ask.'       A week later, It was Kelly's birthday. No robot. A week later, No robot. 2 weeks later, No robot.   'I'm starting to think Aunt Trudy just won't get us that robot.' Denise said.   'Yeah but it's okay,' Kelly explained, 'We didn't necessarily need one.'   Right after Kelly said that the doorbell rang. Kelly went to go answer it. It was the delivery guy.   'Sign here for your package.' he sighed dryly.   Kelly signed the paper and he wheeled a crate into their living room.   When he left, the girls started jumping up and down screaming of excitement. Denise went over to the crate and looked at it.   'How do you open it?' She asked.   'With a crow bar dummy.'   'Well do we own any crow bars? Dummy.' Denise shot back.   they both ran around the house turning everything upside down looking for one. Then their mom came home. 'What happened in here!?!' she yelled.   'Oh umm I got a package from aunt trudy and we need a crow bar.' Kelly smiled.   'Why would I have a crow bar in the house?' their mom asked.   Both girls shrugged their shoulders. 'Any person with a brain, Has them in the garage.'   the girls ran down the hall to the garage. 'Clean this mess up when you finish!' their mom yelled down the hall.       When they got to the garage, they looked around. 'What does a crow bar look like?' Denise asked.   'I dunno.'   'wow,' Denise sighed. 'We're looking for something but, we don't know what it looks like.'   'It's over there.' Their mom said from the doorway. Both girls jumped.   'How'd you get over there?' Kelly asked.   'I flew a jet.' She said sarcastically. kelly got the crow bar and ran into the living room. they were in there for 2 hours trying to open the crate.   'I have to do everything?' Their mom asked. She opened the crate with the crow bar and there stood befoe them, A ROBOT!!!   They put in one huge battery , as tall as a toddler that they found in the crate, into the robot. He turned on as Kelly was reading the instructions.   'I think he's  a Gemini Scout,' Kelly said.   'Woah, Kelly look it came with an xbox remote!' Denise exclaimed.   'No that's the remote for the robot.' she said. she moved him around and from then on they had a robot.

Item_Response: Oliver walks around to see to making of his robots. A scientist goes up to him and gives him the progress report.            'Everything is fine here sir,'said the scientist.            'Good. As soon as thy are done making them, I would like to test them,'said Oliver.            'Yes sir,'said the scientist.           Finally, the robots were ready. The robots were put in a training session to test their skills when in the army. The presentation was being given to General Ross To see if they were fit and ready for action in the field. Then out of nowhere lightning struck one of the NS-5s and fell to the ground. The robot somehow became alive and started to run away. The robot ran out into the desert far from the base.               'Where am I,'said the robot.              'Who am I,'said the robot.                 'HEEEEEEEEEELLLLLLLLLLLLLP!'screamed the robot.               The robot runs through the desert not knowing what to do. Finally, the robot sees a city. The NS-5 sprints to the city. The robot find out that it was the city if Las Vegas. The robot observes the whole city and collects data from what it sees. Then the robot looks around the city and is bewildered by everything he sees.                 'WOW,' the robot said. 'This is amazing. I wonder if I could stay here.'             And the robot did stay there for the rest of his life. The robot named himself Clark Kent and he just learned from what he saw and experienced and just lived there for the rest of his life.

Item_Response: I-Butler                              'THE ROBOT IS OUT OF CONTROL!!!' . A few days earlier, I wanted to do something because I was bored, so I went to this place called the TOYS R US. I thought it would be a fun place but it was some kids store. Still I went in there and I saw this toy robot for sale. It was as tall as me and called the 'I-BUTLER'. So I got it and brought it home. As soon as that happened, my friend, Jon called me and asked,'Are you free today?'.'Yeah.' I replied. 'REALLY!' he said barging in my door. I did need  some help controlling so I asked him to help me. 'Sure.' he replied. So we started to fix the robot and when it was done. It didn't work. 'What!We did for nothing!'. 'But it was for a bargain!'. I thought we had to wait so we went to get pizza and played in the arcade. 4 hours later, 'It still didn't work!' So we started kicking it. 'I'm going to return this tomorrow.' I said. The day after, I saw a whole through the door. 'JEFF JEFF JEFF JEFF JEFF!' Jon said while running through the door. 'The robot is al...'. 'I know.' I said  'It's alive.' So I dressed up and followed the robot. 'THE ROBOT IS OUT OF CONTROL!!!' Jon said. We saw these laser guns on the ground. 'It's COD all over again.' Jon said. When we got to the robot in the town square. we quickly started to shoot it. 'SHOOT THE KILL SWITCH!' Jon to me. So I started to shoot it and it fell and made a huge hole. 'Finally I could return it.'

'How did you come alive Gooby? I thought you didnt work?', said Bob   'I came alive in the night. You were alseep. Item_Response: It all started when Danny an average young scientist born in Rhode island decided to try to make his own HRP-4c robot. At first all went well he made a robot that acts like a middle age man. He was able to play sports with him, watch TV with him, and even ride on him as a car with the click of a few buttons. That all changed when one day Danny was driving home from Starbucks and accidentally spilled his coffee on the manual controls causing the robot to go haywire. Then the robot transformed into an eight foot giant with armor and fully equipped weapons.             Danny then fainted and as he woke up he thought to himself  'hmm how much damage can he do in one hour' he sighed 'wait one hour!?!?!' with that he rushed inside to turn on the news. the TV blared to life stood up and ran off along with all of his electrical units including his I phone. All he could see was a part of the news saying 'breaking news an army of electrical units are attacking the state leaving us trapped here on Rhode island. Someone please help us!' as it ran off.             Five minutes later his friends came pounding on the door yelling'please let us in were all gonna die'. 'No where not were going to destroy those machines' Danny said with a bit of doubt while letting them in. How are going to defeat those giant monsters he thought. then he realized something. 'Follow me' he said while leading them to his basement. 'Here you guys are going to need armor and blasters to take these creeps down.             A while later the were fighting the machines taking them down one by one. 'There are too many' Danny yelled over the sound of the blasters. 'Wait a minute the source of the machines is my HRP-4c robot.' he realized ' we have to destroy him so the rest will power down' with that they were off to search for his robot in his backup car. Once they got to it his friends distracted the robot while Danny went to the robot's power panel and dismantled it. The town was saved and all of the machines were gone. So then later the state was rebuilt and back to normal.             With that Danny decided to never make his own machine ever again. With only few people with severe injuries and less than fifty with minor injuries Danny paid up for most of the damage made and went back to living his normal life without any robots in his life and at the age of eighty-one he died a peaceful life.

Item_Response: My Best Friend Rosie                                                   By Ann Lin            A long time ago, I used to have a robot. You probaly think I'm crazy or it was just a dream, but I'm not kidding. Her name was Rosie. She was my best friend, but something horrible happened. Then, something extraordinary happened a year after. Let me explain how all of this started.            My dad works at a robot factory. At the factory, they make robots for every purpose. I had always wanted one, so on my birthday he got me a robot. I remembered every word he said.            'This is Rosie. She's going to be your new friend.'            I couldn't believe my ears! All these years he had said I was too young to have one and that it would be a big responsiblity to oil it and blah, blah, blah. Now, look at it! I turned on Rosie and smiled at her. ( Yes, I know, she's not a person, but she was like one to me. ) Rosie waved to me. At that moment, I knew we were going to be best friends. I played with her all day.            A year had passed. We had so much fun together! We went to carnivals, Disneyland, and so much more. Rosie was amazing. She helped me with my homework, helped me study for all my tests, praised me about my projects, and comforted me when I was sad or upset. She was worth way more than a million dollars to me.            This is a pretty happy story so far, right? Well, that's going change. One day, Rosie and I were hiking together. The mountain was steep and Rosie helped me up. When we got to the top, there was a beautiful waterfall there. I knew Rosie would short-circuit in the water and I made sure she wasn't too close to it. We spent about two hours up there, enjoying the sunshine and the scenery. I collected shiny pebbles while Rosie took pictures of the birds. It was almost lunchtime, so Rosie and I headed down the mountain. While hiking down, there was a small pile of rocks that we slipped on. Down we fell. SPLASH! We hit the lake at the bottom of the mountain. I had cut myself on some sharp rocks at the bottom. I got out quickly, knowing that the water would get electrified with Rosie being in there. Then, something flashed through my brain. Rosie! I ran toward the water and found a piece of metal glinting in the sun. I called my dad and he came as quickly as possible. ( He dropped us off at the parking lot. ) He helped me move Rosie into the car. A while later told me that Rosie was dead.            'WHAT?!' I cried.               I ran into my room and cried while my parents put Rosie into the shed. Every single night I began to cry myself to sleep. I had wonderful memories of her, but it wasn't enough.            A year passed since the death of Rosie. I decided to visit her. I went to the shed and cleaned her and oiled her. I sighed and said, 'Why Rosie? Why?' I turned around was about to leave when I heard a sound. It had sounded like metal clanking. Then, I heard her voice. My eyes widened when I turned around. She was back! I screamed with happiness and hugged her. Rosie hugged me back.

Item_Response: The Robot Disaster          Once there was a scientist named Dylan. He was making a robot that had a very complex wiring system. All was going great. When he tried to turn it on though it didn't work. After ten minutes of trying to turn it on it finally came on. It was all fine at first just a human and a robot talking. Then Dylan Criticize The robot. Most robots do not have feelings but this robot had such a complex wiring system that it got emotionally mad. The robot was very mad in fact that he wanted to take over the human race. So, Dylan did the only thing he could think of he turned of the switch. The robot sat there motionless. Dylan went to bed after that.          Dylan woke up with a bang! He looked at the time, it was 3:30A.M. He went into his living room and saw a huge hole in the wall. He looked outside and saw the robot hands in the air yelling, 'HAHAHA!' It came alive. The robot that I invented came alive! Dylan thought in his head. I will deal with it in the morning. With that he went back to bed.           As Dylan woke up he remembered what the robot did last night. Maybe it was a dream? He thought. He stepped back into his living room and saw the huge gap. So, it was real. He went to grab the controller but found it on the ground crushed into tiny peaces. Oh no, he thought. Then he got into his car and left for the laboratory.          The robot now named, ring leader, started to get other robots to stand up and help him on his path of destruction to get the human race taken over. now all of the robots he tried to get were either with him or destroyed.          As he got to the laboratory he told the other scientist what happened and how he probably got many other robots to join him. After many arguments they figured out that there is going to be a war. But they had a plan they thought that the robots he could get were not going to be water proof. So they got many fire hoses and went off.          Somehow the robots new about this war going on so they were already in a defensive line while the trucks were looking for them. the finally found them and the war began.          Water was spraying out everywhere and the robots had bubbles? The bubbles were useless compared to the water cannons. So they made their way through all of the bubbles from all of the robots. Then they found the captain of the infantry. He was water proof! Then a solider came to the front of the truck and said, ' I thought this was going to happen,' He got out a RPG and shot him into million of tiny peaces. He got back in and they were face to face with the ring leader. Cannons sprayed and RPG shot the ring leader was now into billions and billions of peaces. That is what ended, what is now called The Robot Disaster.

Item_Response: I was dreaming. Dreaming of a robot. I have always wanted a real robot. I have toy ones, but they just aren't the same. They don't talk, or do real things. But that all changed on one special morning.       I woke up. I look at the clock. It 7:00 a.m. and it's my birthday! I jump out of bed and run downstairs. My mom is making me breakfast of eggs and toast, and my dad is reading the paper. My baby sister is eating her cheerio's. 'Happy Birthday honey!' said mom. 'Happy Birthday squirt.' said dad. And baby Jane tried to muster out a 'Haffy Birfday!' I was so happy!       That day at school everyone wished me happy birthday! I couldn't wait to get home and open my presents! Maybe this year I would get a real robot! When I got home, my told me we had to eat dinner first. So after dad got home we ate. Then she said it was time to open my presents! I got a marble track, some new toy cars, some very needed new socks, and the new model toy robot! I loved it, but I was still a little dissapointed. Then we ate my cake. It had a picture of a robot on it. That made me even more sad, knowing my robot would never be real. But it was my birthday! I had to be happy with the other things I got.And tomorrow all my friends were coming over! So I made a wish and blew out my candles. Then I told my parents I needed a good nights rest and went to bed.       The next morning I felt groggy and tired, even though I had went to bed early. I felt something poking me. It wasn't mom, because I use my alarm clock to wake myself up. And we don't have a pet. I rolled over and to my great surprise there was a robot sitting in the middle of my room drawing with my paper and markers. I said, 'Hello', a little hesitantly. He replied, 'Hello! My name  is Risto-Bot. I'm your new friend!' I was shocked, and didn't know what to say! All I could muster up was, 'Where did you come from?' He said, 'I am your birthday wish come true!' Then I said, 'But we have to hide you from mom and dad!' And just as I said it he was out my door heading for the steps. He was too fast, I couldn't catch him. Mom and dad were as surprised as I was! I told them the whole story. They listened intently, and tried to understand my explanations. And when I was finished, they said I could keep Risto-Bot! 'Yaaaaa!' Shouted Risto-Bot.       At my birthday party, all my friends loved Risto-Bot! We played with him, and he danced and sang, and played party games with us too! Then Henry asked me, 'Where did you get him?'. And I smiled to myself and replied, 'Somewhere very special, Henry. Somewhere very, very special.'

Item_Response: Jeremy and The Penguin Named Pip                                                                                                                                                                                                               There once was a little boy named Jeremy who's dad was an inventor. He had always wanted a pet penguin as a best friend but couldn't get one because they would need a special living condition and need other irregular things like fish everyday. His dad thought about it and decided to make an official robot penguin. The robot he created had rubber for skin, a plastic beak and 150 different voice controls. The best thing was it didn't need to eat and did not worry about the temperature. Jeremy was going to be so proud!                The dad decided to give it to him on his birthday which was two days away. He put a party hat on it, put in a box and wrapped it up. On Jeremy's birthday, he saw the box and wondered what was in it. He then opened it and his jaw fell to the ground. He screamed with joy and ran to the bedroom. The penguin followed him still with the hat on. Then for the next three hours, they sat in his room, figuring out the penguins commands. His favorites were dance and back-flip. Jeremy decided to name the penguin Pip. Pip followed Jeremy everywhere he went. Everybody was jealous and Jeremy had found the best friend he had been looking for.                Eventually, Pip had his own pool and home in the backyard. They played and played and as Jeremy got older and older, he did less stuff with Pip but still cared about him. Then when Jeremy got married, Pip was the best penguin to his wedding. But, when Jeremy had children, he gave Pip to them to play with even though Pip was still loyal to Jeremy. Jeremy eventually got so old that when he died, Pip almost exploded from the sadness. He then made a huge decision. Pip decided to make Jeremy's children just as happy as he had made Jeremy.

Item_Response: My Inspiration, Come To Life                                                             by Brooke Wolford            Once, I went to the beach. I can remember the warm, salty breeze sweeping over me. I could also remember the ocean waving in the distance, calling my name, beckoning me to jump into the watery depths of the unforgiving sea. But I waited, and I resisted the urge to do so. When I left the beach, I remember how relieved I was to be able to get out of the heat. And of course, I was also sad that I had left the ocean.       'Brooke, it's time for school!' I woke up from my slumber with a shake. I couldn't believe that I had another dream about the ocean. I thought that I would never have another dream about the sea, but I guess I was wrong. I  got out of my bed, and my feet softly hit the floor. I forced myself to move myself over to my dresser, which was located by my door. I threw on some clothes, eat break feast, and then I ran off to the bus stop.       When I arrived at school, I walked to my homeroom class, which belongs to Mrs. Hartman. My teacher is very nice, but she always seems to give me and my class a lot of homework every night. I then sat at my desk, and I straightened my books up, only so they would look good on my desk. I was the only person in the classroom for ten minutes, but then later on more and more of my classmates started to fill the classroom. When the class was settled, Mrs.Hartman entered the room, and she looked even more classier than before. 'Class,' She spoke with a loud, booming voice, 'We are going to do a class project. You all must take part in it, and there will be no exceptions for late work!' Then, after Mrs.Hartman had finished her first sentence, someone sneezed. Everyone in the classroom started to laugh, and Mrs.Hartman started to turn a dark shade of red. Oh no, this isn't good! Every time the teacher turned red in any of my classes, that meant that they were really mad. But I could tell that Mrs. Hartman was very mad, because I could see the red veins popping out of her neck.        After Mrs. Hartman had given the class a huge speech about how bad we were being, she finished the rest of her sentence that she had been saying. She had told us that we had to make a robot, and it had to work. My first thoughts on the project were terrible, because I had never been good at making gadgets. But then I thought positive things, because I knew that it was going to be fun for me to do, and I would learn new things.       That night, I rode the bus home. When I first stepped into my house, I ran into my room and started to make my robot. I just wanted to get the assignment done with, only because I wanted some free time for myself. A good nap is just what I needed, so I figured that when I was done making my robot, I would take a nice nap.       It took me five hours, but I finally completed the task of making a working robot. The robot I had made was small, and it was small enough to fit into my locker. It's purpose was to give you a massage that would knock your socks off, and it seemed to work perfectly fine. I decided to name it Paul, because that was one of my friend's names. My old friend used to come over to my house about every day, but then he moved to a different state. I placed Paul next to me, and I started to rub the mechanical hands that I had placed on him so he could give a massage. Then, I started to drink some soda. It was a bad idea, because one moment later, I had spit the soda all over Paul! The creepy thing was, Paul started to shake wildly, and then I heard a voice. The robot was speaking!       I started to panic, because I had never heard a robot speak to me before. But then I realized that the robot was friendly, so I sat next to Paul again. 'Do you think I am a good robot' Paul asked carefully. I replied with a yes, and then I took my nap. Me and Paul have the best of friends ever since.

Item_Response: 'That is a cool looking robot!' exclaimed Tom. Tom was a ten year old boy who had noticed an old broken down robot in a small scrap pile near his house. He quickly picked the robot up and ran to show his friends. 'Look at this robot I found!' he exclaimed as he approached his friends. One of his friends looked at the the robot and said, 'It doesn't even work.' Tom quickly turned back to his house and walked away. 'You're just jealous.' he said. On arrival to his house he set the robot down. 'I'm sure I could fix you.' he said. Then, the robot's eyes began to glow.              'I'm alive!' the robot shrieked. Tom fell back surprised. 'Cool now I have a robot to go on adventures with, hooray!' Tom shouted joyfully. 'Hooray!' the robot replied. Tom quickly ran out side to tell his friends. When he came back the robot was making bacon. 'I'm Bacon-bot!' the robot said. 'Cool he makes bacon!' Tom exclaimed. Tom quickly sat down to eat.              'That is the best bacon I've ever had!' Tom said happily. 'Bacon is good!' the Bacon-bot said. Tom loved his new bacon making robot so much that when he was older he made a whole type of food making robots. Now there is is no more hunger thanks to food-bots. 'The end.' Tom said after finishing his story. 'That is a great story.' his teacher said. 'Who knows maybe I'll create the first food-bot!' Tom said. 'Maybe someday.'

'great'nate thought, 'were gonna move again' nate said out loud,'aren't we?'.       'good heavens no!not again!' his dad exclaimed.'since today's your birthday im going to give you your present', he pulled out a large cart with a figure on it. Item_Response: Many years in the future there was a planet called Tatooine. There is sand everywhere and it was abanded by alot of people. That's right, people like us lived there. There were alot of robots. Alot of them forgotten. One day a man named Micah who still lived in Tatooine Loved exploring things and finding robots that have been forgotten. One day Micah found a robot way deep into the ground from the great sandstorm many years ago. He was in shock what robot he found. THe rarest robot ever made in Tatooine. It has been extinct for 50 to 70 years. It was called G5-4BA. It is kind of like C-3PO from star wars but a little different. He was about 5'10 feet tall, blue, has legs and arms. Also from what he read they said the robot can talk. He picked it up and walked away.                                                             Moments Later.....       He got and and he fixed up the robot. It was not easy. He worked for about three days for it to be finished. Then it was done. He flipped the switch to turn it on then all of a sudden the robot moved. Micah was happy. he screamed 'It's alive It's alive.' G5-4BA was helping him find more robots and helped him around the house. But one day something changed. G5-4BA was different. He wasn't helping or anything. most likely he was making it worse for Micah. Then at the end of the day he went rogue. Micah ran away and he read a manual about that kind of robot. It said on page 6 'Beware sometimes the robot might go rogue. It was programed to kill the ones who were hurting the people and who were stealing money from people.' Micah quickley looked up and there was G5-4BA standing right in front of him. He had red eyes and he was ready for strike. Then Micah asked 'why do you want to kill me i did nothing wrong.' Then G5-4BA said 'I've been working so long for wou and when i looked up my history you originally got rid of my species. I heard you talking in your room planing to get rid of me to. So now i'm gonna show you how it feels like to be stuck in a sand pit for about 70 years!' Then he grabbed Micah and he stuck him into the hard sand about 12 feet into the ground and he couldn't get out. Years later G5-4BA rebuilt Tatooine and it was a robot planet. They lived happy for thier rest of their lives.

Item_Response: Plan/Timeline:   1. A kid named Timmy comes home from school wearing a red shirt.   2. He walks in and \dad just made a life-size bull that acts like a bull to be used at a rodeo instead of using real bulls.   3. The bull attacks Timmy with such rage at his red shirt.   4. Timmy takes down the bull and finds a new skill in bull handler.   First draft:   One day, just like any other day, Timmy was walking home from school and his mind was running again.  He was scrawny and short, but loved sports of any kind.  The problem was Timmy wasn't good at any.  Not even racing little tiny race cars.  Timmy wished that his dad, who seemed to be a insane scientist, would create an invention that would make him good at sports.  Any sport.   As Timmy walked up his driveway, the garage door opened and Timmy's dad rolled out on his back.  He was in his work clothes, which was a white jacket, big safety glasses, and torn old loafers.  His face was estatic with excitement as he rose to meet Timmy.   'Hey Little Tim Tim!' he said as he picked up his 9 year old son and held him up in the air.  'I just finished a masterpiece invention!'  He set little Timmy down and led him to a large mass covered by a white sheet.  'One, two, three!'  The sheet shot off of the massive object as Timmy stared at it.   It was a bull, a robotic bull.  It had regular bull legs and face, but was made of metal.  Timmy's dad flipped a switch and it roared to life.  It looked straight at Timmy.   'RUN TIMMY!  YOU HAVE A RED SHIRT!' Timmy's dad yelled, but Timmy didn't run.  He was determined to find the one sport he was good at, even if it wasn't really a sport.  He danced right to left with the bull, who's eyes lit up red.  He eventually raced to the wall of the garage and stopped.  The bull turned on it's shoulder and charged!  Timmy lept away at the last second as the bull crashed into the wall and shattered to pieces.  Timmy was an excellent bull handler.   Revised version:   It was like any other regular day for Timmy.  Walking home after school with his head down and mind running like a marathon.  Timmy was a scrawny and short little kid, but he still loved any sport he laid eyes on.  There was only one problem with this, Timmy was good at none.  From being quarterback in football or even racing miniature Hot Wheels as if they were racing cars, Timmy was hopeless.  He dreamed that one day, his father would find an invention that would make Timmy good at one single sport.   Timmy walked up his driveway and opened his garage door to see his dad sitting on the ground like a small child waiting for him.  'Hey Tim!' he said.  'Not gonna waste a second here showing you this new machine!'  He didn't give Timmy he usual after school hug, but stood up and jogged over to a massive object covered by a white sheet.  He whipped the sheet off of the object and a dark brown animal stood there.   It was a bull robot designed for rodeos, so that real bulls weren't ever hurt.  Timmy's dad flipped a switch in it's behind and it's eyes lit up red and glared straight at Timmy.  The looks were deadly.  Timmy looked down at his red shirt and realized he was in deep trouble.   'RUN TIMMY!  NOW!' his dad screamed sprinting as fast as possible out of the garage.  That was one thing that Timmy was bad at, running.  Timmy stood his ground as the bull sprinted at him.  He lept to the side leaving the bull to run into the garage wall at full speed.  It hit the wall with a large bang and fell apart.  Timmy had one strength for sure now, handling bulls.

Item_Response: One day , I was walking down an alley and I saw something that looked like a robot . I was to scared to touch it or get to close to it . After a few minutes , I got the courage to pick it up and examine it . I kept turning it and turning it to see if it was safe enough to take it home . Then , I saw red button on its back . I pressed it and the robot fell out of my hands .              Even though it wasn't safe to take it home , I just took it . I sat it down on my desk and waited for a long time to see if it would do anything . I waited so long that I fell asleep . While i was waking up , I saw a figure that looked like something standing up . I opened my eyes wide and saw the robot just standing on my desk observing my room . I got up from my bed and walked over to it . 'Hi,' I said . 'Hello,' said the robot . I was in shock and passed out .               I woke up the next morning not knowing what happened . Then I looked to my left and saw the robot playing catch by himself with one of my rubber balls . I really didn't know what to do but stare at the robot . I was amazed and shocked . Finally , I got the guts to walk up to him and play with him . After minutes or so , he didn't want to play anymore and frowned . ' Whats the matter,' I said . ' I'm lost and I miss my parents,'the robot said . 'Don't worry , we will go look for them tomorrow, I promise,'I said .                   Then , my mom barged into my room and asked 'Who are you talking to?' ' No one,' I said . 'Oh okay,' she said. She gave me the evil eye like if she I was hiding something from her .' We need to find you a special place for you to hide so no one will know you are here with me because if someone knew , they would freak out, ' I said. 'Sounds good to me,' the robot said .               The next morning I got dressed and left the house with the robot in my hand . I was on a mission to find a robot's parents . We, the robot and I, we walking down the street when all of a sudden , two other robots came out of a corner yelling ' James , where are you!' No one seemed to notice the two robots walking down the street .'Are those your parents?' I asked James . 'Yes!' he yelled out . James crawled out of my hands and ran to his parents . He turned back and said, ' Thanks for everything. ' 'No problem,' I said . I will never forget the day I met James .

Item_Response: The Robot Who Comes Alive                     For years, and years at a time, Max Fizkin wanted to build a real live working robot. But whatever he did seemed like a failure. He was trying to make the ER99, one of his robots to come alive and work as if he were a human. He tried everything in the book, but nothing seemed to work. Again, he tried everything he could possibly do.He worked day and night.        Finally, he got mad at his failure. So mad that he punched the robot in the heart. but after he felt very shamed of himself. He turned and looked at the robot, he seen something was glowing in his eyes like a light kinda. the eyes started blinking! Max ran over there and looked at it. The robot began to speak. 'Hello human', RE99 had said.   Max stared at him in disbeliefe. Sudddenly a huge smile on his face came. RE99 Also smiled.       Max talked to the robot and learned it could do so much more than he wished for. It was like a human. Max knew him and his robot could win thee science fair this Friday.

Item_Response: K-Martin             It was a stormy and gloomy Monday in New York City. The sounds of traffic boomed through the night and the air was surrounded by smoke and gas. A dump located at the end of town was filled with disgusting smells and the sound of rats. Along with it was an abandoned, unpowered, robot. It was supposed to be the 'greatest machine in existence' but the scientists had no luck, so they just threw it away.What they didn't know was that they just threw away the best invention that could set foot on Earth.             The storm was getting worst as thunder started, and suddenly, a lighting bolt struck the broken robot's body. The robot was starting up after the lighting bolt struck. It was a miracle! The robot was awake! As the robot stood up he didn't know where or who he was. He was a bright red robot with wheels as legs and his arms were long and skinny. After he was trying to understand what happened, he walked out of the dump and started heading towards the city.             As he was walking a little poor kid was walking near the street and saw him. The robot wasn't alarmed because he knew the kid wouldn't hurt him. The kid was however alarmed at the robot. But the robot said, 'I come in peace!' The kid glared at him and said, 'Who even says that. Anyways what is your name machine?' The robot did not reply because he didn't know if he had a name. But as he was thinking he saw a billboard nearby. 'K-Martin, yes, K-Martin is my name.' He said. 'What is yours child?' 'Julio' he replied, 'Julio is my name.'            After that the robot vanished. 'What!' cried Julio, 'Where are you!' But K-Martin was nowhere to be found. 'Geez, I must be going crazy.' Julio said. Then he went home.   Next morning, Julio went outside to get the newspaper. Then suddenly, as he looked at the front cover, it said, 'Living robot found.The next world sensation is here!' As Julio stares at the newspaper in amazement, he looks down in the reading and one word sends a smile to his face: K-Martin.

Item_Response: Main character is named Tony and Rick Robot is named Richtophen It was designed for providing company                   It was a bright sunny, August day in Southeast Michigan. Tony Jack was in his lab working on a special project.  'What is it your making Bruce?' said Dr. Rick Stolinger.        'I am making the perfect compainion for anyones desires.' Tony replied.   'What it is ment to do?' asked Dr. Stolinger.   'It is ment to keep company for any one who needs it. It will be able to talk in many different accents to make it more comfortable around the owner. It also will be able to do simple chores like wash dishes, work in the garden or bring you a snack or drink.'   'Wouldn't that make it a servant?'   'Not quite because it will be limited to the amount of service it can do.'   'That is very smart, do you mind if I join and help creat this masterpice.'   'That would be great.'       As the day went on the two men collected parts and technology for their robot. The robot was about five and a half feet tall so that it dosn't overwelm the owner with its hight. Item_Response: Meet the Huckleberry Family   By Merritt D.       The Huckleberry Family is a special family, because they have a robot that can speak, talk, walk, and do actions. Joe Huckleberry, the dad of 1 child, he is a scientist, he likes to do wacky inventions and likes to watch the show, Berrybusters. Freda Huckleberry, the wife of Joe, and the mother of Billy, she is the freak of the family, and does not like germs in the house. And the last of the Huckleberrys', Billy. Billy loves to have fun and likes to get in trouble with his neighborhood friends. They live in a small town in the U.S. Virgin Islands, Huckletown.       One sunny, shiny day to come outside, Joe is in his basement, again. Billy is playing outside and ding-dong ditching their neighbors. He always has lots of fun. This time, Billy always visits dad in the basement. Billy discovers that his dad is making a robot. Billy watches and asks questions to dad all day long. not long before Billy's bedtime, dad finishes up his workshop. He closes the door to the basement and starts watching the TV show, 'Berrybusters'. Billy goes up stairs, brushes his teeth, and heads up into his room. He says goodnight to his mom and dad as they come upstairs. As they start to get distracted, Billy starts heading down the flights of stairs to the Basement, luckily, he knows the combination to go downstairs, as he opens the door to the basement.       Billy closes the door very silently, and turns on the light. He found vast assortions of machines, to Ray-Guns, to even the rare Automatic-Snowmaker-9000. As he looks around, he found the robot he saw eariler that day, he takes a look at it, observing each piece, without making a sound. He saw that the arm was disessembled, so he found a small hammer and started pounding a nail and the two machinery in together. He saw a light gleam in the center of his one eye, and the sound from the robot started running. Billy could hear a 'What was that?' from upstairs and heard walking around. Billy hid behind a large crate as he heard a walking noise from the upstairs.       He looked up, and he saw his mom holding a broom stick head-up. He ducked away as he heard a voice saying 'Hello there, Freda!' she started yelling and screaming as she is whacking her broom stick at the robot. Joe came down and observed the incedent. He looked around the room and was asking himself 'how could this happen?' Mom calmed down and looked at dad and said 'Whats this?' In return, dad said 'Its my newest invention, but i never but on the arm, who did it?' mom shrugged and walked back and forth. Dad also said 'It doesnt talk, either. The mouth is just for decoration.' The robot starts walking around. 'It doesnt walk, too!' He is very surprised now. From the other side of the room, the robot started talking. 'My friend billy stapled my arm together, Joe!' He was very surprised, and he asked the robot 'Where is Billy?' The robot replied 'Behind the large crate, sir!' He looked behind the large crate and there was no sign of Billy.       Billy had traveled upstairs, the back way, and hopped in bed like lightning. The next day Billy asked Dad 'what was all the ruckus last night?' he replied 'You know the robot i was building last night?' 'Yeah.' 'Well, last night, it turned came to life.' Billy was shocked, also, he had smelled a delightful smell of Pancakes with syrup. He had beckoned Billy into the kitchen until he had seen the Robot cooking breakfast for the whole family. Billy had many questions that evening, but he had solved them himself. He became great friends with the robot and named him Hubert. He was a great companion and he loved Hubert.

Item_Response: It was the moment I had waited for my entire life, I had finally saved up enough money to buy a robot dog. Its fur glistened in the bright light, and it's dog ears were almost real looking.  Its tail wiggled in jerky, robot-like motions, but I didn't care. Ever since I was little, I have wanted a pet dog, but I have allergies which makes it so I can't get a real one. Today, my dreams were finally coming true.       It had taken me two years to save up for the dog, due to its generous price tag, but it was so worth it. I handed the woman at the counter my money, and she handed me the robot dog. I have had a name picked out for it since I was two; Chick. He looked like a real dog, and from what I've heard, he acted like one too, except for the fact that he didn't shed, need to go outside, or eat. He was the perfect dog for me.       As soon as we arrived home, I put the batteries in him, and watched him come to life. He was cuter than in the pictures, and best of all, he was mine. I threw the ball to him to see what would happen. He bolted over to the spot that the ball landed, and picked it up in his mouth. Using the remote, I made him come. He was absolutely perfect for me and my lifestyle.       Two months later, I was still obsessed with my new companion. I had taught my little sister how to use him, and she fell in love with him too. Every day after school, I got him out and he was always happy to see us. We never got tired of our perfect puppy. He was all that I have ever wanted, plus more.       'Come, Spot!' I shouted at my dog. He came, with the click of my remote. 'Sit!' I said. Then, I clicked my remote, and he listened. He had solved so many of my dreams and I was so proud to have him. He was the ideal pet, and extremely low maintenence. I loved him, and he filled my life with joy. I couldn't imagine life without him.

'Wow, I did not Just see that.' said Miranda who was staring in awe. 'Pretty cool, huh,' said Joshua, 'I found it in that old abandond army base. Who would leave this type of technology just to turn into a rustpile. That thing looks like something out of Star Wars.' 'Cool, hey what does this button do.' Miranda was refering to a small green button on the bottom of the wrist controller. 'I don't know, might be the off button.' Joshua pressed it and BOOM! Miranda was the first one to come to. 'Josh, Josh were are you!' Miranda screamed. 'Huh, where am I. Josh said. Wheres Robo-Bling.' Robo-Bling was never found, but the next day half the country newspapers reported an unknown flying object with one distinct figure,diamond eyes.

Item_Response: Robots Alive!                                                                 In a summer day scientists were gathered in their lab trying to figure out a mysterious robot. They spent days trying to figure out what the robot could do. Until one day they gave up and they went home. They were still wondering what the robot could do so they went back to the lab. The scientist searched and searched and they finally found a mysterious button. 'Its about time to know what this robot could do' said Mr. Camacho one of the scientist.                           The next day Mr.Reyes said he will be the brave one and he would press the button. Once he pressed the button the robot was alive. The robot dashed through the big glass window in the lab. Mr.Allen tried to run after the robot but the robot was to fast. Nobody could had ever reached the robot. Until Mr.Camacho ran like lightning after the robot with no fear. Mr. Camacho jumped onto him and he pressed the button.                            Everybody in the neighborhood ran out to see what was happening. They all saw Mr. Camacho with no fear dragging the robot back to the lab. Mr.Camacho became the new hero of the neighborhood. For then he was named The Macho. The robot was destroyed and never again will the neighborhood see it again. 'We did a good job on destroying that robot' said the three scientist. They all lived happily ever after!

Item_Response: 'I'm going to build a robot!' Said Tommy. 'He'll be able to play catch with me and be as strong as the hulk and as fast as a cheetah.' Everyone thought the idea of a boy building a robot with these attributes was crazy. 'He'll never be able to do it.' Said his brothers and sister. he didn't care he was determined to build it no matter what.      Later that night Tommy gathered all the materials he would need to build his new friend. Four arms so the robot could multi task, two legs with springs for feet so it could jump extra high, camouflage paint so the robot would look cool and blend in, a torso with the strength of five men combined, and finally a head with a crown so the robot would be like a king.       Tommy spent day and night figuring out ways to put his new robot together. He tried everything from glue and tape to nuts and bolts. Finally once he finally was able to put him together with some screws he was finally completed. The robot stood Six feet tall and was as strong as 10 grown men put together. Everyone was amazed  that such a young boy was able to put together such an amazing invention. Now the only thing left was to give him a name. Tommy looked through his journal for a good name when finally he came across the name Roboto he thought this name was perfect.      Everyone continued to congratulate him on his invention, but his greedy siblings just wanted him to make more so they could sell them for money. 'Just make more so we can make some money.' 'NO Roboto is special just for me.' They continued to argue until the siblings realized there was no way Tommy would change his mind. Tommy continued to enjoy his new friend everyday. One day they would spend the day outside playing catch and the next learning to play an instrument. There was an unless amount of things they could do together. Tommy enjoyed every monent at his friend's side and so did the robot.      The robot also helped around the house by doing chores like cleaning dishes, taking out the trash, and doing laundry. Tommy's invention was so helpful with everything that one day he eventualy decided to share it with the world. He made tons of these so that people everywhere could have a new family member to help around the house and to play with.       Tommy's invention would soon change people's lives in terms of chores and having a new person to hang out with. And could one day change the world.

Item_Response: Robots              Most people will think that robots are used specifically for scientific research, but this is not the case.  Robots can be used for fun and excitement, like the new robot 'Fred.'  'Fred isn't just your average robot.  He can dance, sing, play musical instruments, and play different sports, but this is only the start.   Let me tell you a little about Fred's life and what he is capable of doing.              Fred was walking around town when he saw a flyer with the words, 'Help needed!  Job opening for amusement park designer.  Fred, being programed with the skills to build and design an amusement park, decided to try out for this job.  When he interviewed for the job,the manager said, 'Why are you, a robot, interviewing for a human job?'  Fred just shrugged and built a roller coaster right next to the building in less than a minute. The manager starred in amazement at the quickly built structure and announced, 'You've got the job!'  Fred nodded as he rode the roller coaster back to the ground.              The next day, Fred was working on the new amusement park when he spotted another opening for a pet-sitter at Pet's Delight. He quickly ran over to the pet store, faster than anyone has ever ran before. Fred, once again, interviewed for the job where the manager questioned him.  'Why are you here? ROBOT ALERT!!!'  Fred responded, 'I am here to interview for a pet-sitter.' The manager said in a shakey voice, ' S-show m-m-me what y-you g-got.'  Fred played with the kittens and dragged around a piece of string for them to chase.  The manager of Pet's Delight was suprised that the robot got along so well with the kittens and gave him the job.                    When Fred came back to the science lab where he was made, he was covered in oil from the roller coaster and string an cat fur from the pet shop.  'I'm not even going to ask,' said one of the scientists.  'Looks like you've had quite a day,' said another.  'That was a really crazy and fun day!' Fred said.  'Can I go back to town tomorrow?'  'Of course!' responded another scientist.  There was no response, because Fred had fallen asleep.

Item_Response: B-572         There was four of us: Carl, Joe, Steven, and me, Johnny. We sat at the corner of First Street and Bubblegum Lane in awe, because what we saw you could never imagine. The robot was alive. Lets go back to the beginning when it all started.       'Are you done yet?'       'Can I see? Ugh! Move Steve!'       'Is it possible for you two to shut-up for at least two minutes!'       'Fine, but Joe took my fake nickel!'       'N-uh!'       'Uh-uh!'       'Guys! Come here!'       I had just finished B-572, a robot we had been working on for the past year. He was going to be a new part of the group to hang out with.      'Whoa, this guy looks epic!' said Steven.      'Totally! But where's Carl?' asked Joe.      'Right here fellas!'      'Come check this out!' We shouted.      'Well, ain't she a beaut!' Carl said       'Thanks. Should we start her up?' I asked.      'Yes!' They said enthusiastically.      I flipped the switch. Light shined through the smooth metal exterior. It shook, made some noises, then suddenly stopped. And smoke started to rise from B-572.      'No!'      'This can't happen!'      'Dang-it!'   We all complained in frustration. This whole year in our garage seemed like an entire waste. I didn't get it. We spent every single precious moment we had on this robot, making sure every detail was   precise and accurate.       'I'm not letting this happen.' I said.       'What more can we do?' Carl questioned.       'We can figure out what's wrong with it. We made B-572, we can fix B-572.' I said.        So a couple more days went by, and we did everything we could.        'This is becoming a waste of time.' Joe said.        ' I know,' I sighed, 'let's just head over to the dump.'        'Ok.' they agreed.      That's when something amazing happened. We heard a voice.        ' HE-LLO. MY NAME IS B-572. WHAT IS YOURS?'        'Oh my gosh!'        ' No way!'        ' This can't be happening!'         But it was. When everyone turned around, we saw the sleek robotic eyes of B-572.        'Yes! We did it!' I shouted.        We headed home as quickly as we could.        'HOW ARE YOU TODAY? DO YOU WANT TO PLAY A GAME?'        'Yes! B-572, we do want to play a game!' Steven shouted.        So the two of them played fuse-ball for the rest of the night. It was such a success, that we got into Time Magazine! We knew that B-572 would forever be one of our greatest friends.

Item_Response: I started to play pokemon ruby awhile back. I always enjoyed playing pokemon with my main goal to catch em all. Well, i enjoyed playing it untill it happened. It all started with me playing pokemon, on friday. i was trying to catch a nincada, seeing if the shedinja rumor was true. I caught it, and leveled it up. I nicknamed him MÏka. I started to wonder when MÏka would evolve. I battled another nincada and it started to evolve. I got the ninjask and shedinja, but somthing was wrong. Shedinja wasn't its usual texture. It had red eyes and had a bloody tear in its right eye. its body was black. Suddenly, i han an urge to use it. I fought a Pikachu, but pikachu's face had a sad expression on it. Pikachu's ears were drooped and his face was in a frown. The pikachu made my Shedinja faint, but instead of it saying:Shedinja has fainted, it said:Shedinja has DIED!  I looked in my party slots and it wasnt there. The battle ended, and i started to freak out. I thought 'What the heck was that?'. Then the screen turned white and all that was on it was a grey jiggily puff with red eyes. The room started to darken even though it was daytime. The screen was still white and the only light was coming from the screen. I was scared. I tryied to run but the door wouldn't budge. Scared to death i chucked the gameboy at the wall. it broke. It was a terrible decision. The gameboy screen parts were still white and the jiggly puff was on the floor still animated. It seemed to be getting bigger/closer. I prayed it was only getting bigger. I was wrong. The jiggly puff came out of the screen and only said one word. 'Jigglypuff'. It started to chase me, and i ran into the door trying to escape. it opened and i ran out of my house trying to get away. It caught up to me. It turned back into a gameboy and i saw a note that read:Play it or die. With no choice i played it. I battled jigglypuff. Then i realized somthing. I didnt walk through my door and i didnt touch it. Was i dead? No it cant be. i tried to walk throught a wall, and it didnt work. so what was going on? I kept playing, and defeated jiggly puff. In the game my character was transported to a room with all the gymleaders on the floor looking dead. The color red was all around them. I saw graves with their names on it. Suddenly, the jigglypuff was there, and a textbox came up and it read:Jiggly puff wants you to join the game. Jigglypuff wants you tp play with you. The screen turned white again and i screamed. then every thing went black. and i was dead.

Item_Response: The Robots That Change Lives                                             Their are lots of robots in the world. But did you know that their are robots that can work in mines and on farms help doctors and save lives. Some even explore volcanoes. Trust me we are not the only ones that work hard.                        One robot that is very important is the Gemimi-scout. He is a remote controlled robot that does search-and-rescue in mines under the ground. He is less that two feet has wheels and very strong. He can carry food water and other supplies. He can even drag injured people to safety. Wherever he goes he collects information of the area around him to make sure it is safe for people. To see he has a thermal camera that uses heat sensors to find living things. He may be small but he can do big things.                         This second robot can go to a place we can't go. He is called a Dante 2. He climbs into volcanoes to gather information for scientists. He has eight legs that help him with climbing steep volcano walls. He is built to survive very high heat temperatures. Dante 2 looks for vents, or holes, in the crater. He then collects information about the gases. He is a very important robot for scientist.                         The last robot i would like to talk about is Mr.Gower. He is a robot that works in hospital,he helps doctors and nurses bring medicine to patients. He looks like a small medicene cabnet with wheels.  He can go anywhere in the hospital.  He is strong enough to pull 500 pounds. He runs on batteries that charge for two hours and delivers medicine for twelve hours. Mr.Gower can also talk hundreds of phrases. Mr.Gower is a very important contribute to the medical society.

Item_Response: Robots Narrative Performance Task             By:Natalie deMartino                     Can robots save lives?  There are many robots incluiding Agribots, Mr. Gower, Dante 2, and Gemini-Scout.  Each of these robots have a different purpose. Some robots can even do things that humans cannot.              An agribot is a robot that picks fruit.  It might pick berries, grapes, or apples.  Agribots are not yet wildly used, but farmer are very interested in what these robots can do.  Because picking a strawberry is different than picking an apple, agribots come in different shapes and sizes.  Some have giant arms that are towed behind trucks.  Others are able to move around on their own.  In Japan, there is a strawberry-picking robot that can sense the color of the berries.  This helps the robot knopw when each berry in ripe.             Mr. Gower is a robot that works in hostipals, helping doctors and nurses bring medicine.  The body of the robot is a stack of locked drawers that store medicine.  Nurses and doctors can unlock the drawers when the medicine is needed.  Mr. Gover can go anywhere in the hospital.  It can ride elevators, steer through hallways,  and move things that get in its way.  The robot is so strong that it can pull 500 pounds.  Mr. Gower runs on batteries.  After charging for two hours,  the robot can deliever medicine for twelve hours without stopping.  Not only does it work long days, but Mr. Gower can talk.  It has been programed to say hundreds of phrases.  For example, it can say, 'Calling elevator' or 'Your delivery is here.' 'Mr. Gower does work that doctors, pharmacisits, and nurses used to do.  This allows them to focus on other important tasks.             Dante 2 is a robot with an interesting job--- it climbs into volcanos to gather information for scientists.  like a spioder, this robot has eight legs.  This helps i9t climb the steep walls of the volcan.  It is also built to survive very high heat.  when a volcano is too dangerous for scientists to enter, Dante goes instead.  Dante 2 looks for vents, or holes, in the crater.  Then the robot collects information about the gases that come out of the vents.  In the past, scientists could not learn as much about volcanoes, but Dante 2 is changing that.  Now scientists can study a volcano up close while they remain safe in their laboratories.            Gemini-Scout is a remote controlled robot that does search-and-rescue work in mines under ground.  The robot is less than two feet tall and has wheels.  It can go up and down stairs and make tight turns, and it can even roll through water.  The robot is smaill, but is strong.  Gemini-Scout carries food, water, and other supplies.  It can even drag hurt people to safety.  Whereever it goes, Gemini-Scout collects information.  For example, it tests the air for gases and then tells miners when the air is safe.  The robot also has a thermal camera to help it find mkiners.  A thermal camera uses heat sensors to find living things.  When the robot finds the trapped miners, the miners can use its two-way radio to talk with the rescue team.  This robot was built to be easy to use.  Its remote control is the same one that is used for some video games.  If you've ever played a video game, you may know how to use Gemini-Scout.

Item_Response: I was walking towards my laboratory when I heard these really strange noises like....binge,boom,bang,crash,ban,bonk,and dink. I thought it was really strange to hear those noises especially coming from in there.The noises started to get louder so I started to run it got even louder so I ran even-faster at this point. I got worried .Once i hit my laboratory I opened it up as fast as I could.I was so relieved to see that my robot Crash had just fell onto my new project and messed it up and I was upset that I had to start all    over.       My robots name is Crash I made about two months ago. One day I went out to grab lunch and when I returned my robot came to life. It was on top of my desk playing with my computer. I was really freaked out by this but after a while I got used to it.I had a robot and I had to accept it because I didn't want to throw him out.When I walked into my lab I found out that Crash could talk and I was really surprised so I took him to talk to my friends to show him off.       My friends were Natalie,Vanessa,and Bernice .When I showed them my invention they said I was crazy because Crash didn't want to talk because of his shyness.On the way back to my lab Crash was talking as much as he could I was really disappointed that crash didn't want to talk in front of my friends.I just got back to my lab and found out that Crash knows how to do lots and lots of tricks.I went back to my friends and tried to show them what Crash could do but he was to shy and to nervous to do any tricks.Crash made me get a little upset again because he didn't want to do any tricks .       When I walked into the lab Crash was not talking or moving or even doing any of his tricks.I tried to figure out what was wrong.I told Crash that he was my best friend but he didn't even move. I felt as if Crash because I wanted to show him off to my friends . He was pretty upset with me and didn't want to talk to me.I still feel really bad for trying to show of Crash to my friends.       When I woke up this morning I ran to my lab in my blue pajamas.I was worried to find Crash still upset with me.I unlocked the lab doors and couldn't find him any were.I was so worried what kind of trouble he would be in.I went back to my house and was relieved to find Crash on my kitchen floor.I asked Crash what he was doing on my kitchen floor and he answered he was making breakfast I told him that robots don't eat food but he said that robots were the same as humans and they eat breakfast to and he was taking apart my microwave and I had to get a new one but Crash was forbid to touch it.       I was on the internet trying to find out what kind of robot he was called Mr.Gower. Mr. Gower was Crashes real name but I still wanted to call him Crash.The only reason I still call him Crash is because he is always crashing into problems.Today I took Crash to show my friends that he talks and he does tricks.My friends said they were really sorry for telling me that I was really crazy.I forgave them.I went to the store and bot a newspaper and Crash was in the front page of the newspaper.I was walking towards my lab today and heard lots of noises like the one I heard when I found out Crash could talk.

Item_Response: In this paper i will be talking about robots. How they live, what they do, and how they help people. The first robot I will be talking about is the Gemini-Scout. The Gemini-Scout is a remote controlled robot that does search-and-rescue work in mines under ground. The robot is les than two feet tall and has wheels It can go up and down stairs and make tight turns, and it can even roll through water. The robot is small, but is strong. Gemini-Scout carries food, water, and other supplies. It can even drag hurt people to safety. wherever it goes, Gemini-Scout collects information. The robot also has a thermal camera to help it find miners. A thermal camer uses heat sensors to find living things.             Another robot I would like to talk about is Dante 2. The Dante 2 is a robot with an interesting job it climbs into volcanoes to gather information for scientist. Like a spider, this robot has eight legs. This helps it climb the hight heat. When a volcano is too dangerous for scientist to enter, Dante goes instead. Dante 2 looks for vents, or holes, in the crater. Then the robot collects information about the gases that come out of the vents. In the past, scientist could not learn as much about volcanoes, but Dante 2 is changing that. Now scientist can study a volcano up close while they remain safe in their laboratories.               Mr. Gower is another good robot I would like to talk about. Mr. Gower is a robot that works in hospitals, helping doctors and nurses bring medicine to patients. Mr. Gower looks like a small cabinet on wheels. The bodyof the robot is a stack of locked drawers that store medicine. Nurses and doctors can unlock the drawers when the medicine is needed. Mr. Gower can go any where in the hospital. It can ride elevators, steer through hallways, and move things that get in the way. The robot is so strong that it can pull 500 pounds. Mr Gower runs on batteries. After charging for two hours, the robot can deliver medicine for twelve hours without stopping. Not only does it workd long days, but Mr. Gower can talk. It has been programed to say hundereds of phrases.               Last but not least, AGRIBOTS. Agribots are a robot that picks fruit. It might pick berries, oranges, grapes, or apples. Agribots are not yet widley used, but farmers are very interested in what these robots can do. Because picking a strawberry is different than picking and apple, agribots come in all shapes and sizes. Some have giant arms that are towed beheind trucks. Others are able to move around on their own. In Japan, there is a strawberry-picking robot that can sense the color of the berries. This helps the robot kniw when  each berry is ripe.

Item_Response: I was walking through the forest on a nice warm day. I was wearing a tank top and shorts with rainbow flip flops on. I am beet red from the hours of sun I have gotten over the last couple of days. There can only be one thing I'm doing, VACATIONING IN HAWAII!!!! Back to the point I was walking through the forest and saw what looked like a shooting star appear across the night sky. The only thing was, it was the middle of the day. All of the sudden it hit the ground with a hard explosion. I walked over to where i thought it landed. Right there in a large crater was a rusty robot obviously broken. But all of the sudden its eyes open and it said one not-so-simple word. 'Wall-e'.       I was so suprised I just passed out on the spot.       When I woke up I had the robot bent over me hitting my head with a rock. I sat up and looked around, I was in the crater I fell in but it was the middle of the night. I wondered greatly why this robot was here, so I asked it. It replied in this realy annoying robot voice,' I have been sent here from the future to warn you about an oil leak right off of the coast of Maui that will be met with a wildfire that will appear right when the oil spill happens.' ' The oil will then catch on fire and set fire to all of the underground oil resevours that surrond the world.' ' This fire will alight every single inch of land on earth.' 'The only people that will live will be on a boat or on an airplane.' 'Everyone will die'. 'Wow, so how do I stop it' I said.' You have to go down to pier 21 and put out a fire.'       I left Wall-e in the crater and hiked back down the mountainside. I stole a motor cycle to get to Harbor 21 faster. I hoped on. The problem was I didnt know a thing about motorcycles. I tried to remember what Jonothan DeHart taught me years and years ago about riding a dirt bike. The issue was this wan't a little 80cc dirt bike but a 650cc Kawasaki Ap racer that can go 200 mph. I started it and heard the huge engine roar. I let off the clutch only an inch and I took off. I was almost ripped off the bike. I zoomed down the streets of Maui going 90 mph. It seemed that in no time I was passing all of the docks. 26,225,24,23,22, than finally 21.       I hopped of the bike and burned myself on the exhaust. I ran to the dock and saw a boat that said 'J and M oil co.' I went on the boat and headed to the oil drill. On the boat ride I saw a boat with people holding flamethrowers. I automaticly knew they would be the cause of the fire. I pushed my boat to full throtle and ramed right into them. There boat blew up and the threat was eliminated. I wanted more credit for saving the world but it all just ended with me going back ome to America.

Mr. Gower swirled around trying to lose the kid, but his grip was too tight. Then they buped into a big medicine drawer labeled DANGER KEEP AWAY. All of the liquids fell on to Mr. Gower and he started to glow.        He started transform into a big huge fighting robot. He flicked the boy off and started to walk back down to the doctor. When the doctor saw he was amazed and asked what had happened to him. The robot could now talk. He told his story and showed Dr. Gor how now he armed with big weapons of destruction. The doctor called the government to see what they could do with Mr. Gower.        The government came lightning fast. They examined the robot with great curiosity. They realized they could use this robot for military purposes. They carried him away in a huge crate and from that moment on he wasn't Mr. Gower, he was Mr. Destructive.

Item_Response: The Robot That Gave Life   By Tyler Chu       One peaceful day, on the planet Earth, lived a 11 year old boy named Bill. Since the day he learned about science, Bill wanted to build his very own robot.       Bill was a great scientist and loved everything about robots. Today was the day he was going to make his own robot. First, he started to plan everything out. Furthermore, Bill was going to make his robot out of metal and plastic. He told his parents about this wonderful idea, but they disagreed. Bill was sad for the rest of the day. Then the rest of the week, then the month. One day, something magical happened. On Bill's 12th birthday, his parents gave him permisson to build his very own robot.       To start his project, Bill hurried to the hardware store, and bought some metal, spray paint, wood, and plastic. Bill built it quickly and it turned out really nice. For the final touch, he spray painted his robot red and yellow. In addition, his masterpiece was completed, and named Iron Man M8. Bill was extremely proud of his accomplishment, but he had to go to bed since he had school tomorrow.       The next day, Bill woke up, and...his project had disappeared! Bill rushed out of the house and his robot was flying. The robot had come ot life! Bill was surprised, and his robot flew him to school. Today was the day that Bill would show his creation as his science project. Everyone was amazed. Iron Man M8 could help people when they are injured, store medicine, can talk, and can be used as Bill's armor. When Bill went to lunch everyone wanted to use it as their armor, and Bill was annoyed. Someone was hurt from playing a basketball game, and Iron Man M8 gave him medicine and healed him. Bill always wanted to build a robot that could do things like his favorite robots, Gemini-Scout, and Mr. Gower.       Bill was so proud of his accomplishment, but one day he was really sad. He used Iron Man M8 to fly home at the speed of life. His parents told him some really bad news. They got a call from the local hospital asking if they could keep his robot as a helper. Bill was a sad as ever, and he would have to leave his best friend. Bill just bonded his him and now he would have to be taken away. On the other hand, Bill realized it was for the best and that Iron Man M8 would be taken away.       One year later...       When Bill was the age of 13, his parents got another call from the hospital. His parents rold him that the hospital was very thankful and that Iron Man M8 saved 100's of people. Also, they told him that he could have his robot back. Bill was as as happy as a bird who found its nest. He got his robot back and made a few changes. Iron Man M8 was now made of unflamable metal and plastic. So that would mean that he could now be used to gather information from volcanoes. Ever since the day that Bill decided to build a robot, his creation made the lives of other people as happy as can be, but most importantly he had made a new best friend.

Item_Response: One day Artemis was eating lunch when she heard a knock on the door. When she opened it nobody was there, only a small envelope, she took it and went back inside. How odd, she wondered that somebody would just leave an envelope on my door step and not explain. She opened the envelope to find a light grey colored paper inside with a robot drawing in the middle. The robot was white and had blue eyes, it floated and had arms that grafted into its body. All of a sudden the paper started glowing, Artemis dropped the paper and started to back up. The glowing was so bright she had to close her eyes and turn around. When it stopped, she turned to look and in the place of the paper was the robot.       'My name is Elsie the Multi-bot. How may I be of service?'       'What is a Multi-bot?'       'It is a robot that can do anything.'       'Sweetness.'       Some time has passed and since then Artemis and Elsie became best friends. Until one day the S.A.P.R.M came.       'What are the S.A.P.R.M?' asked Artemis.           'They are the Space Authority Patrol Robot Men, and they are here for me.' said Elsie.       'Elsie let me tell you a secret. I am a superhero.'       'Do you have a partner or team?'       'Yes I have a team.'       'Call them.'       An hour later Whisper partner to Speedy who has super speed, Miss Martian partner to Martian man who has martian powers, Super the partner to Extremist who have the powers of super strength laser vision etc. were all at the home.       'Where are Red and Robin?' asked Whisper.       'Right here.' said a voice.       Out from the shadows walked a boy and a girl, Little Red Riding Hood and Robin. Red was the Partner to Kitty who both have no powers and Robin was the partner to Shadow who also had no powers.           'It has been so long you guys, now lets beat those aliens.'       About two hours, a destroyed town and a bunch of under age superheros later and you get a successful battle. Elsie got to stay wit Artemis and all the super-kids stayed in touch. All was peaceful until Red disappeared, but that's another story.

Item_Response: Boom! All the sudden a big huge explosion goes off in our back yard. I went outside and looked there was a huge hole and a robot inside of it. Then I heard a roaring sound and the robot came to life. ' Hello Master'. Is the first thing it said to me. Then it climbed out of the hole and came up to me.'What would you like me to do master'. I stared at it then said'can you dance' the robot then played music and danced and singed.   I thought this was a dream, but then it all changed. The robot said'are you a human I hate humans if i see them i instently destroy them'. Right then and there I ran away the robot at my heels.'Master where are we going', it asked me.'Stay here' I said then I took off runing home.             When I got home I turned on the tv it was on the news then all the sudden there it showed the robot that I had found and it showed it exploding building.I quickly went straight to my bedroom where I kept my copper bb-gun then I ran after the robot. When I got there the robot asked why humans were on planet then I took out my BB-gun and shot the robot it hit him but all it left was a dent then the robot came after me shooting lasers and rockets I ran into my home where I knew he couldnt get me and started to think how I could beat the robot. I thought and I thought then I suddenly gob an idea I remembered the self destruct button on the back of it. I had to distract it some how so I could hit the button.             When I got to the center of the city there the robot was about to eat the mayor. I then ran up behind it quickly hitting the self destruct button and moving the mayor out of the way. Then the robot exploded leaving nothing but a note. It said 'thank you so much for deafting this robot it has been going from planet to planet destroying them all'. Then   I went and watched tv then another explosion came from our back yard. I went outside and looked there was a huge hole and a robot inside it.'Not again I said' then I ran up and searched for a self destruct button and hit it. Then it was gone again thats when I asked my mom if we could move to a different town. She said yes then we packed up and moved.
