Item_Response: One regular sunny day I was sitting at home watching T.V. Then my dad walked in and said that we were going to a robot museum. I loved robots. I got ready and we were on our way. When we got there there were robots everywhere. Some were small, some were big, some were gold, and some were red. As I admired the huge museum I saw a big empty room with something laying in the middle of it. I told my dad, and he said I could go take a closer look at it. As I approched the unknown figure I wondered what it could be.       I finally reached the creature. It was a robot. At first I was not so amazed or surprised, because there were robots everywhere. I stood there, in that big empty room wondering why it was laying there alone. Later on an assistant who worked there walked up to me. He said ' What are you doing?' I replied 'I was just wondering why this robot was laying here all alone?' He told me that when the creaters of the robot made it, it never worked or came to life. They researched, got robot specialist to come and look at it and much more, but nothing worked. So after a while they got tired and decided to through it in this big empty room that know one ever went into. Then I was interested.       The assistant asked me if I had any more questions, and I did. I asked him if I could try and make the robot come to life. He said I could but it probrobly won't work. Then he left. My heart did kartweels. I was so excited. I had always wanted to work on a robot.   There was only one problem, I did't know how to! I looked around for supplies, but all I found was a door. I went inside. It was where the  the creaters of the robot woked on the robot. I took some tools and then went back into the room with robot in it. Then I got to work.       I tried everything, but nothing worked. 'I guess the guy was right,  I can't make the robot work just like no one else could' I said to my self. I walked away in sham with my head hanging down ready to go find my dad. All of the sudden I heard a noise. I turned around and to my surprise the robot was alive. I screamed! 'I did it' I shouted. The assistant came running in. WHen he saw that the robot was alive he started screaming too. He asked me how I did it. I told him that I just clicked a couple buttons, walked away and then when I tured back around it was alive! Neither of us could believe it.       I asked him if it ever got named. He said it didn't, but since I got it to come alive he said that I could name it. After thinkig for a while I decided to name it Miricale Bob. I chose that name because he was a miricale and because I like the name Bob. I got my dad and told him the whole story. He was so proud of me. I thought to myself 'I can fix a robot and make it come to life but a robot specilist can't!' I must have been a pro.       Long after that when my dad was puttig me to bed he told me I would make a great scientist. That made me really happy. Thats my adventure story of how I made a robot name Miricale Bob come to life. It was the best day ever!

Item_Response: The Robot           One afternoon the craziest thing happened to me. My robot, Carlos, was doing my homework while I was watching TV. 'So Carlos,' I said, 'how is my homework coming along.'   'Great,' said Carlos, 'almost done.'   'So you don't mind if I go down to my friend Kyle's house,' I said.   'Well,' said Carlos, 'I kinda want to spend some time with youuuuuuuuu.'   'Are you OK Carlos,' I said, 'what happened to your voice.'   All of sudden Carlos fell out of his chair and fell on to the tile floor. 'Carlos,' I yelled, 'are you OK.' I picked him up and set him down on the couch. 'Carlos, Carlos,' I said, 'are you OK.' Then it happened, Carlos got up off the couch and said, 'Must destroy Cameron.'   'Carlos!' I yelled. I got up and started to run for my life. 'BING! BANG! BOOM!, ' I kept hearing behind me. I turned around and saw Carlos shooting lasers at me. 'Ahaaaaaaa,' I screamed. I ran upstairs into my room and locked myself in my closet. 'I think I lost him,' I whispered. All of a sudden, BANG!, Carlos smashed the door open. I ducked under his humungous  metal legs and ran downstairs out the door. 'What to do, what to do, Yes,' I said. I ran over to the bushes in my front yard and hid behind them. BOOOOOOOM! I saw the front door fly into the street. THUMP, THUMP. I heard him walking right in front of me. 'Yes,' I said. Then Carlos turned around and saw me hiding in the bushes. 'Not again,' I said. I got out of the bushes and ran toward my friend Kyle's house. 'Yes,' I said, 'I finally got away.' When I turned around to see how far away Carlos was, he wasn't there. 'What the heck,' I said, 'where did he go.' Right when I turned around he was in front of me.   'Oh come on,' I said. He flew right in front of me. 'See you later, CAMERON,' said Carlos. Then Carlos picked me up and threw me on the ground. My stomach dropped and a chill went down my spine. I looked up at the horrible beast and saw a self destruct button on his chest. 'Yes,' I said in my head, 'all I have to do is jump up and press the self destruct button.' I jumped and pressed the button and all of a sudden, BOOOOOOOOM! my robot Carlos was gone. Now I have learned my lesson to never, ever have a Robot.               THE END

Item_Response: The box was jumping around rapidly as I walked closer to it. My dad usually brought home some of the most extraordinary expirements that had come from his lab. ' Go ahead, open it!' my dad encouraged. I was a little bit nervous about opening the box, for I knew nothing about what was inside. ' This better not be one of those singing robots again! I barely got sleep the night that you brought that mess home!' my mom said angerly. I tore open the box slowly and carefully to find a little furry robot puppy jumping around . ' There you go! A puppy!' my dad said.  'Dad, that was very thoughtful of you, but you know that I am highly allergic to dogs.' I said sadly. ' Not to worry! This dog is not made of real dog fur. Instead, we made it out of fake fur so that you could enjoy all of the wonders of having a dog!' my dad said. I have never been able to have a dog due to my severe allergies of them, so this was definitely exciting to know that I could finally have a pet dog. ' Thank you Dad!' I said happily. ' Well, at least it isn't one of those singing robots again.' mom said.            It was Saturday that my robot dog started actually acting like a real dog. I was awaken by all of the barking that it was making. I opened up the door to my bedroom to let the little guy in. He burst through the door with excitement in his robot mechanical eyes. He started to jump up and down around me. I knew that he probably wanted me to pick him up. I knew this because of all of the dog books that I have read in my life. I reached down to pick him up when suddenly, he jumped right into my arms. ' Hi there little guy!' I said. He started to bark and curl up in my arms. 'Aww!' my mom said. ' Mom! Why are you in here!' I said. I was a little bit shocked to see her up so early in the morning. She normally woke up at 7:30, and right now it was only 6:30.'Why are you up so early mom?' I said in confusion. 'Well, Sparky here woke me up because of all of the barking that he was doing.' she said. 'You gave him a name already?' I said in dissapointment. I wanted to name him something more exciting, like Elvis or Gizmo. 'Well I'm sorry! I did not know that you already named the little guy.' she said. Sparky then looked up at me and licked my face with a little rubber tounge.            I brought Sparky outside to see what he could really do. 'Ok, Sparky! Can you do any tricks? Roll over!' I said. Sparky looked at me, then got onto his back and rolled over. I couldn't believe it! I thought that I would have to make a fool out of myself and try to teach him how to roll over. 'Good boy, Sparky!' I said. 'Ok, here is a tough one, but I bet you can do it. Play dead!' I said. Sparky then acted as if he was dizzy, then fell onto the ground. 'Good job!' I said. Sparky was probably the best dog that anyone could ever have. ' Malory! Breakfast is ready!' my mom yelled. 'Coming!' I said. I scooped up Sparky and brought him into the house.            'Hey dad! Can Sparky eat dog treats like other dogs?' I said. 'Well, not exactly. We made him some special treats that help boost his energy level, or re-charge his battery. If you want, you can give him one after breakfast. I keep them in my tool box.' dad said. After I finished my breakfast, I went down into the basement where my dad kept his tool box. I first looked on the first shelf, then to the second shelf, where I found a bag with a dozen cookie-like treats. 'Sparky!' I screamed. I heard tiny footsteps coming down the stairs, through the movie theater room, then into dad's workroom. 'Who wants a treat!' I said. Sparky started jumping around and circling me. 'Sit!' I commanded. Sparky sat onto the floor with one tiny thump. 'Good boy!' I said. I held the treat up then handed it to him. He gulped it down like it had nothing to it. 'You are the best dog any girl could ever have!' I said. I picked up Sparky and gave him a hug. He then brought out that little rubber tounge of his and licked my face.

Item_Response: My name is Samantha, I am 10 years old and I can't talk or   hear. I was born deaf and people tell me that at first sight you would think that I am normal. The thing is though, I'm not normal, nothing about me is. I attend my town's public school which has regular kids, with regular lives. All of the other kids can see, feel, hear, smeel, and taste. I  can only do four of those. When I turned 7 my parents got me a small robot that can hear and speak. It translats to me what I need to know when people try to talk to me.           This robot turned into my best friend soon, because none of the   other kids at school would even say 'hi', before they had a reason to ignore me because I couldn't hear either way, but now I can. I gave my robot a name a few weeks after I got her, I named her Crissy. Crissy basically looked like a little doll that could be dressed up and played with. I didn't play with Crissy though, I spoke to her. I was learning what words ment and how to say them even if I couldn't hear. Sometimes when I got frustrated I gave up and we just used sign language.           One night I was asleep in bed when I had this wierd dream that   Crissy came to life and tried to take over the world. I woke up crying because I never wanted her to do that, I wanted her to always be my best friend. I got up and looked around for her, she wasn't in her case (I like to call it a bed) and wasn't on my night stand were she sometimes is. I started to panick, 'Had I left her at school?' I thought to myself. I started walking around the house calling her name. Finally I cameto the kitchen. She was on a chair sitting on a pile of books that were stacked as though she had done it herself.  I slowly, trying to get the correct words out of my mouth asked 'What are you doing down here?'. Crissy turned her  head swiftly in my direction and stared straight into my soul.           It is now a few months after the night that Crissy came to life   and I realized that she does it often. I have lost track of the times I have seen her move without me controlling or telling her what to do. She seems more real this way, not evil, more human and more like a friend. I have begun to learn more complitcated words that I can speak and I have made it through the school year without feeling so bad about hearing. I am taking an english class over the summer to learn complete sentences and advanced words. I wonder if there will be any one like me there?

Item_Response: There was a boy named Tim. He was smartest kid in the school.  So being the smartest kid has some perks like you having to do the older and bigger kids homework. Tim really didn't have any friends exept for a boy named Joey. Joey was the wierdest kid in school.            When Tim and Joey were walking home from school they got thier usual bullying. Then went to Tim's house. 'Well, they where nice today.'said Tim.'Yea,' said Joey 'they didn't give me a weggie this time but they did take my DS'. 'We should start doing our homework, Bill's homework, Jake's homework, and Eric's homework.' said Tim.'Ok' Joey said as they headed towrds the basment, thier spot to hang out.'What's that?' Joey asked in a really surprised vioce.' It's a robot I'm working on. It's name is 'The Bully Defeter' also known as TBD.' Tim said as proud as he could be.'It's still not done yet but when it is the bullies better watch out.' Tim was standing next to a large object that was mostly silver with purple painted like a shirt, blue painted for the pants and black painted for the shoes. The robot looked like a human.         The boys started to do thier  homework at the dinner table. Tim's mother when to the mall to buy Tim new clothes and Tim's dad was at work so Tim and Joey were home alone. ' Hey Tim, what is the answer to number ten?' Tim answered ' Twenty-six.' At that moment the boys heard a loud crash form basement.' What was that?'asked Joey. Tim shuruged his shulders. The boys ran downstairs. There was more loud crashes  as the ran and to thier surprise the TBD was trying to hurt Tim's fish! 'It's alive.' Tm said in shock. 'This is so cool!'Joey said            When Tim realized what was happening he yelled 'Stop!' and the TBD stoped and said 'Yes masters, Tim and Joey.' Joey was jumping around like a made crazy person. 'It's alive!' he repeated over and over agian.Tim walked over to theTBD and touched it. ' TBD, don't hurt the fish they are friends.'' 'Yes master' When Joey was done jumping around he said ' So is it programed to hurt things?' 'Unless we tell him not to' Tim said. ' It will do any thing we want it to.' Item_Response: The Party              I immediately woke up after hearing a loud 'crash' noise.  I jumped out of bed and looked out my bedroom window.  I only saw a bright blue sky and puffy clouds that looked like cotton balls nothing that could make a sound.  I heard the noise again coming   from downstairs.  I dashed down the stairs into my kitchen.                       It was a robot!  It had come alive!  It had a square head with red glittering eyes, pink lips,and a hard metal body.  It looked like the robot that picked berries on our farm.      'Hello call me  Lucy.'the robot said.                                               What are you doing in my kitchen?'I asked.                                       'I'm making you breakfast hope you like your eggs scrambled.'she   said.                                                                                               'How are you alive I just thought  you picked our berries on  the farm.'I asked.                                                                                     'I do many other things than just pick berries and make breakfast.  I don't know how I came alive I don't remember anything.  Everything was so foggy.'the robot said.     'Let's get you upstairs into my room before my parents wake up and see you.'I said.         We ran upstairs and slammed the door shut.  'I want to have this dream to have a party!How about tonight?   'said Lucy.     'Are you crazy we can't have my parents find out about you.'I said.     'Oh, come on it is a week end.  We can do anything we want.'she said.        'Well okay, but I have to have my parents permission and you have to behave.  I'll go ask my parents be right back.'         'Mom dad I had a great idea that I could have a party tonight and plus it is a weekend and-'     'Sure you can it is a little short notice but you have been keeping up your grades.'my dad said.     'Thank you thank you thank you thank you thank you!'I excitedly said.     'Here is $25.00 for the party supplies'my mom said.         'I'm back Lucy!  Guess what they said!  Yes!'I said.   'Yes!  My first party!  I have heard you humans talk about what is called a party.  So what is a party?   'A party is when you invite your friends over and you can do any sort of fun stuff and eat lots of  pizza!  There is a cool party place down the street that we can get the supplies!'   'Let's go!'          'Here we are Lucy!  The Party Palace!'I said.   'Wow this is so exciting but this place looks a little burnt down and old! This is going to be the best party ever!'she said.   'It is on the outside but not on the inside.Lucy the party will be a costume party.   'Great idea but what are you going to be?   'I'll  wear my which Halloween costume from last year.  I think we got everything we need.'         'Let's start setting up.  We will have the party in the grauge.'I said.       'I'll start calling your friends from your phone book.'she said     'Okay but only the circled ones.'I said       'I have been on the phone for one whole hour calling all of your friends but none of them can come.'   'I'm so sorry!  I just got the best idea!  We can have a party by ourselfs!  I'll go get dressed in my costume.'I said.         'Okay the first thing you do at a party is you can dance.'Give it a try!'I said.   'The only dance I know is the robot.'Lucy said.   'Next we eat!'I said.   'Yum this pizza stuff is really good.  And now what do we do?'She asked.   'We have to go to bed!'I said sadly.   'Well I guess this is good by.'she said depressed.   ' I will take good care of you on the farm and keep you company in the fields.'I said.   'One more thing, tell your dad I need an oil change.'she said.   'I will'.I said as I squeezed her tightly.   'See you in the fields!I said.

Item_Response: One time there was a little girl named Ally, when she got home she was telling her mom about what she learned in school.Ally said 'mom guess what I learned about today' then her mom said 'what did you learn about today' Ally said 'we learned about robots'. Ally asked if she can build her own robot .her mom said yes. Ally and her mom went to the store to get the robot parts. When they wre finished getting what they needed they went home and started to work on it. Everyday when Ally got home they kept on working on it. The next day when Ally got home the robot was finished. Everyday they were teaching it to talk and walk and help with things. Three days later the robot could walk talk and do anthing else. They were tring to think for a name for the robot. Then they finaly thougt of it they named it  Little Helper Robot. After Ally got home from school Ally and Little Helper were setting up for dinner. After they set up for dinner Little helper would cook dinner. After dinner Little Helper would clean up the mess.           In the moring Little Helper would wake up Ally and her mother. After she woke up Ally and her mother she made breakfast. After Little Helper made breakfast she helped Ally get ready for school. After Ally was at school Little Helper would Mop the floors and clean Ally's bedroom. Once Ally got home from school they all went for icecream. After they went out for icecream they went back home. That night they made there own pizzas for dinner. Ally's pizza was peporoni and sausage. Ally's mom's pizza was plain old cheese. Little Helper's pizza was Hawain. After that they all watched a movie in the livingroom. After the movie was done they all went to bed. Little Helper tucked Ally into her bed.               The next day Ally and Little Helper herd a big boom. They both jumped out of bed to see what happend. When they went into the kitchen all they saw was glass everywhere.   Ally was crying because all she saw was her mother lying on the floor. Ally's mom told her to get the phone and dial 911. The ambulance was there as fast as possible. The ambulance took little helper and Ally with there mother. Once they were in the hospital room the doctor told Ally and Little Helper they can't stay in the hospital beacause there mother is seriously injured. Ally's mom told Little Helper to take good care of Ally because she was going to be the hospital for a long time.               The next few days were upsetting for Ally because she didn't get to tell her mom about her day. Later in the day she was much happier because her and Little helper would go to the store and get something to eat. After they got back they would play out side untill it got dark. Item_Response: The day started out normally at Metropolis City for The Robinson family at their mansion ,while the children Max and Ruby were at school, Jane is at the house helping the robots do their work.The man of the house Mark Robinson is the most important man at Metropolis because he was the man who invented all the robots you see all around. One day he saw his wife tired from cleaning she fell asleep on the couch Mark was also tired of this so he went to the basement were he was building Festus a robot that would help his wife and their children.       He stayed their all night trying to perfect Festus but when he was almost close the robot broke down.Mark was so mad he threw his wrench against the wall,''I was so close to finishing it, but it always breaks down!''He gathered all of Festus' pieces and put them all on the table.then he realized what the problem was,''The problem is the core I'm using to power him up, it's to weak his body breacks down.''So Mark kept using different cores rubies, wave stone, crystals, and quasi magic stones.Until he found a diamond and used it.Finally he had done it he created the first working robot ever.He was so excited he ran outside and started yelling,''I did it, I did it!''       Everyone just thought he was crazy until he brought out the robot and showed everyone.They just said,''oooooo,aaaaaaaaa,It's impossible.''Mark even showed them what Festus could do and how he was powered .The people were all impressed by Festus they all started yelling out prices Mark had to make Festus yell out so they would stop.''It's not for sale so put away your money I just made it so my wife won't have to work so hard at the house.''       They all started to protest until a huge limousine pulled up and a tall man in a black  suit walked out.''So your the one everyone is talking about, Mark Robinson is tour name right.''Everyone was quiet until Mark spoke''Yes that is my name, who are you.''''I am Mr. Million and I am here because I heard that someone managed to make a robot and I also came here so that person could be hired.''Everyone was shocked to here the news, but Mark just stayed normal and calm''Well I'm the one who made it so you're looking for me.''''well I'm giving you an opportunity to join my company.''Nobody moved'' I'm sorry but I'd prefer to work by myself in my study to make more robots.'' Silence filled the air and everyone held their breath''If that is what you wish alright , but this offer has closed.''        Everyone left after the limousine vanished nobody asked again for Festus ,but Mark did keep making robots and soon he made a huge factory of working robots all over the world that he became a millionare for selling robots.He kept some robots for his wife and some for the children. The world and the city became a better place for everyone everywhere.

Item_Response: Story is about: A girl writing an essay about robots. Make sure you read all of it!   Some parts of the story are not real.          Robots have many jobs. They can save lives, dance, sing, climb and rescue people, and work.They will be more things they can do in the future but, now let's think about robots in the present time.If I had a robot it will be named M123-M26M and it will be a karaoke machine/toaster. It will have purple eyes, a red body, and blue feet. With stripes on it.It will be a girl and it will be my buddy.But unfortunately, I don't think there is a robot that can do that ,instead I would have one of these.Theses are the robots I dreamt of coming alive and all of them are real! I thought it would be perfect for writing an essay.           They are lots of robots in the world that are designed to save lives. One of them is a robot named Mr. Gower can do many things like carry important things, talk, and can pull five thousand pounds. Mr.Gower's main job is saving people's lives .Mr.Gower saves lives by bring the right medicine to them. Mr.Gower's job is hard for people like us because you might bring the wrong medicine and kill the person who needs it.You also need to know what the person is allergic to because if they are highly allergic to peanuts and the medicine to give has peanuts in it. That would be a big problem. Mr.Gower is still saving lives and let's respect him for that even if he is a robot!            Another robot that is helpful is Dante 2. Dante 2 has an interesting job. His job is to climb into volcanoes to gather information to give to scientists.Dante 2 has eight legs that are helpful for climbing.Dante 2 is built to survive in high heat. Dante 2 looks for vents and holes, in a crater. Dante 2 then collects the information about what kind of gases come out of them.       Who can forget about the fruit picking Agribots! Agribots are robots that pick fruit. They pick berries, oranges, apples, and grapes.Lot's of people don't use Agribots because they are not world wide use yet.On the other hand, farmers are very interested on the skills that they have. If a plant is too dry a Agribot will water it. Agribots are a good farming robots.             Some robots play with others.There is one robot called Robbie. Robbie is a babysitter who takes care children whose parents don't have time to play. Robbie always has time to play.Robbie is an endless fun machinery.               There are also dancing and singing robots too! They can move and groove to the rhythm. The finest  move and groove is HRP-4c who can sing and dance! If there is any birthday party around the block HRP-4c is the right robot. HRP-4c might also like performing on stages without having to worry about getting nervous because he is a robot and robots are special!            Gemimi -Scout is a robot that is remote-controlled and does a search and rescue work in mines under the ground. It can go up and down the stairs.Wherever it goes. it collects information.Gemimi-Scout is an easy built robot. It is small but,very strong.It can carry food, water , and other supplies.              Robots always help and always will help people no matter what. I have showed you couple of example of real robots around the world. Those are just a couple there thousands of robots helping today! Even if their definition of helping is fruit picking, saving lives, researching , or even dancing and singing! I wonder which one I should choose .                       Mr.Gower : Life saving robot. Agribots: Fruit picking robot. HRP-4c:Dancing and singing robot. Gemimi-Scout: Collecting information and carry supplies. Robbie:Babysitting robot.   Dante 2:Collects information and goes into volcanoes for scientists.                 That's easy all of them! I was just talking to my friends when all of a sudden, we heard a big crash. Then I heard my principal, Mr. Griffin on the speaker saying, 'get down something strange is happening to all of our technology and sparks are flying everywhere.' Thats when we saw it, the computer sprouted legs and started walking around like it was just a regular sunny day. Then a strange voice came out of him saying, 'hello, my name is Brother Of Blame. You can call me B.O.B or Bob for short.'  I heard the voice of my friend Linda in the back of the room. She was a nice, smart and short girl with a lot of bravery. She said, ' why have you come alive all of a sudden.' Bob answered, ' I am here to serve as a friend to all and help the people in need. I have found out about all the bad things goung on in the world and something in the air changed that made me alive.' Now i was starting to get a little more curious and I could tell I wasn't the only one because my friend Brooklyn asked the next question and the most wierd one of all. ' Will you ever grow hair, or will you always be bald?' Bob was so stunned by the question that it felt like a million years had gone by before he finally answered. ' I will never grow hair because I am a piece of tecnology and can not grow hair.' Then we spent the rest of the class asking questions to the extremly weird creature. Item_Response: It was just Riley, Joanna, and I, slurping on our ICEEs in the park on a warm, sunny day in Columbia, South Carolina. While Joanna was informing us about her trip to the beach, Riley pointed off to the distance with his mouth wide-open. 'W-w-what is t-t-that?!' Joanna was silent and turned to look. Instantly her mouth dropped wide-open, too. Wondering what this was about, I decided to look, too. The thing we saw, whatever it was, had definitely not roamed Sunny Park before.        The three of us ran over to the slide, where a giant toaster oven was sliding down. Anna was right beside the slide pacing back and forth, worried. 'Anna, what happened?' I asked. She shook her head. 'I was at home, and I was hungry. My mom said that I needed to make my own breakfast. So I did. I put two Pop-tarts in the toaster oven.. and that's where things went wrong.'        'I accidentally put the two in the same slot. My mom left to go to the grocery store and my dad was in bed. Right when the toaster oven make its noise, the toaster oven came to life! It clanked down onto the tile in the kitchen and waltzed right out the door. I was scared to tell my dad so I chased after it. You know, it can go extremely fast.' 'What are we going to do to stop it?' Riley asked. Joanna's face sparked with excitement. 'I think I know,' she exclaimed.        Joanna climbed up the ladder to the top, where the robot toaster oven was. 'Come here,' she softly whispered. 'It's gonna be okay.' The toaster oven screeched and slid down the slide, all the way to the bottom.. where it's owner just happened to be. 'I WANT MY POP-TART BACK!!!' yelled Anna. 'Quick!' I yelled. 'Hurry!' She quickly yanked the two Pop-tarts out of the toaster oven. It malfunctioned for a minute and then shut down.        'Thanks, guys. I was really scared. How was I supposed to explain to my dad why my toaster oven ran out of the house?!' Anna returned to her house, and in the future, was cautionary not to put the Pop-tarts in the same slot ever again.

Item_Response: John sighed with boredom. He had been in the St. Louis hospital for five hours now because of an incident in which he broke his leg. He had to stay for a whole night in the hospital, and he couldn't even get out of bed. The doctors were very busy, and he would have to wait a while to get a cast. After an hour, a nurse came in to give him pain killers for his leg. At her side was a small robot. 'Who's this?', John said, indicating the robot. Instead of the nurse replying, the robot said, 'I am Mr. Gower, I help in the hospital.' The nurse then opened the drawers on Mr. Gower's body and took out some medicine. Once he had got it, the doctor came in and got ready to put on the cast. 'Just relax, this won't hurt much at all.' the nurse said. The doctor got scissors from Mr. Gower and began. after a half hour, he was done and John was feeling better. Then, Mr. Gower came up and said, 'We are done now, are you better?'.'Yes, thanks for asking.' John replied. The next day, after a restless sleep, John left the hospital. Before he left, Mr. Gower said'Goodbye I'll miss you.'

Item_Response: It was a usual day at the lab- testing chemicals, fixing space suits and working on the robot. The boss ordered us to make a robot that we could send to space to learn more about our atmosphere. I has always been fascinated wit the robot and one day while I was taking some samples to another room I accidentally jostled the machine. When I turned around to check on it it started to vibrate. I put my hands on it to see if it was warm and it shot into the air through the skylight taking me with it! As we shot through the air I remembered that we had built a small compartment inside the robot for the boss to go up to space in. I quickly scrambled to open the door and get inside. It was a lot more relaxing inside the capsule (if you could say that) and pretty soon I fell asleep.   When I woke up i was in a strange hut. it looked like it was made of reddish mud and had a domed roof. Just as I was about to get up the door opened and in stepped the robot! ''Your refreshments are here Sir,'' he said in a metallic voice. He handed me a bottle of some fizzy stuff that when I drank tasted like soda pop. Then, right before my eyes he changed into a sort of spaceman! He had turned into a human! As I sat there in awe I decided that I ought to say something. 'What is your name?, I questioned. ''Kubli'', he answered. Did you make this hut? Yes. ''I will show you what I've made'', he said. As I followed him outside I recognized that we were on Mars. We went a little ways and I saw that Kubli had cleared away a landing pad and on it was a spaceship!   Later that day we were soaring in Kubli's spaceship toward home. I can't wait to see the look on my bosses face when we tell him our adventures!

Item_Response: The Zombie Robot              The Robot was out of battery for two years sitting in the attic. Me and my sister were sitting on the couch and we herd a loud nose coming from the attic the robot was a zombie robot. So I went up stairs to check it out. I think that was the worst idea I'd ever had.I opened the attic door and went up.                  At first i did not see anything but then i saw the red glowing eyes. They looked liked the devils eyes. Then it started to get up I thought to myself that thing has been of of battery for ever and it never had glowing eyes that were red. I shut the door and thought what i was going to do. I did not want to tell my sister because she would flip.But that did not last long a axe came flying through the door. This thing was dangerous very dangerous.                   I had to think of something fast really fast. I was thinking of something when it poped in to my head. Item_Response: Ronald the Robot was a regular humanoid robot but he didn't know that today would be life changing. As he was slowly being packed to go to a scientist in Hollywood, California he thought his life had been perfect, he didn't want to go he wanted to fight but he couldn't move. He thought about the beautiful answering machine always giving him compliments. 'There goes ronald.' A security gaurd yelled to the other scientists. Ronald was getting shook like wild and couldn't stand it, finally though he was put in the airplane. As ronald listened to the rumble of the engine he knew it was gonna be a long, very long trip.           When the plane finally landed Ronald was worried if the the scientist would be nice, for all the people at the other lab would spoil him. 'CRACK!' Ronald was face to face with the new scientist, his box wasn't there only underneath his plastic feet was the wood from the box. Ronald knew he fell asleep and the box woke him up but he slept through the whole car ride. As Dr. Theorat (or so his nametag said) picked Ronald up and brought him into his lab,ronald was fighting, or he wanted to. Ronald got put on his desk so he could watch Dr.Theorat while he was mixing alixers, potions, and foods into a big bowl. When Dr. Theorat was done mixing the stuff he sucked some into a turkey baster then went to Ronald and said 'Hello my friend are you ready for something exiting?' just as he said that he dumped the turkey baster liquid on Ronalds head. Ronald felt a tingle then in the flash of an eye Ronald could.           Ronald shook his arms, did he? He shook his head, he was soaked, did he? Dr. Theorat chuckled then said 'He He, silly robot now that potion made you able to do any thing a human can do, I have been working on it for 13 years and now it works!' Ronald ran then yelled 'YAHOO! I've been wanting some independance!' Ronald and Dr. Theorat were now the best of friends and lived the rest of their lives that way

Item_Response: The Short Circut                                 In the city of Chicago, IL, there was an ancient ground,out in the country, that was dark and mysterious. On top of the hill there was a tall dark brown oak tree, that had somrthing under it, something that you cannot imagine. Behind this one tree, there is a horizon, in the front there was a silutee of the tree. Nobody ever knew why it was so scary.                     There was two sisters Stephannie and Alyssa who lived in the country, to the far right of this hill. One sunday morning, they discided to go to find artifacts, for a project, so they went to the hill. They came across the tree at about 2:00 pm, they noticed a tree, Stephannie thought just by looking there was a story told in the history of this tree. 'Should we dig here.' Shephannie asked. Alyssa who was only 13, looked nervously at the tree like she saw a vision. 'We should go somwhere else.' 'No, we have to do this project, I dont want to get held back, for not doing this project.' 'B-B-B-ut I-I dont want to!' Alyssa stuttered. 'Well this a dicision you're gonna have to make.                    The sisters have already started digging, Alyssa starts sweating from all of the hard work, and she is really nervous what she will dig up. 'Stephannie all I am finding is roots, when can we go home.' 'In ten minutes we will have a break, okay.' 'Okay.' 'Wait a second I see somthing!' 'Really what is it!' 'I dont know its big, shaped like a square, and its silver!' Suddenly Stephannie grabs it out of the ground it was exactly hoe she didcribed it.'What is it.' 'Well by looking at its shape I would say its a robot.' 'A robot!' Alyssa suddenly feels this erge to faint, as her face is as white as the snow. Then, the book that Alyssa brought with her turns to a certain page, 537. Stephannie looks at her watch it is 5:37pm the same number as the page in the book. 'Oh my God!' The robot starts making noises, and it was speaking perfect Engilsh to the girls.'Hello. I am 360-456' Oh my god, it spoke to me!' 'Wow! We have got to tae this to school.' 'But mom and dad will freak out!' 'Mom and dad are at a bussiness trip in Flordia. They wont know.'                  The girls brought the robot home, because the robot was old, and small they called it short circut. Alyssa could not go to sleep all night, with the robot staring at her. The robot got the girls an A. Alyssa got to the habit of the robot, but culd not get over it at night still, she the robot do some stuff while she was at school. Stephannie on the other hand, used the robot to take care of her, to feed them, because they're parents were gone. A few days later, Alyssa got a call from they're mom and dad saying that theywould be back the next day. 'Stephannie! Stephannie! That was mom and dad they're gonna be home tomarrow! We have got to get rid of that robot.''I guess so. But how they're gonna be here in 13 hours. We cant bury this robot now, we daont have much time.'The girls got out to the hill to bury it, they had to rush it was almost time for they're parents to get   there.                  Finally, the girls burried the strange robot, they suddenly realized that they were not gonna do anything like that when they're parents.'We could've told my parents and kept it until, they told us to.' ' Yeah, but just dont do that again.'                                                                                                          By Brooke McHugh

Item_Response: The Creation!       There once was a mad scientist,it was the year or 1823 and the sky's were gray and gloomy. The scientist did not speak English,he was German. Since he could not communicate with anyone,he was lonely.As the day went by he was often found looking out of his window for a friend to talk to.But no one showed up. To be honest, the real reason that he was lonely was that everybody in town was afraid of him. The mad scientist had a lot of experiments that he was working on in his basement. There was talk in the town about witchcraft. He truly had enough of it! The mad scientist decided he was going to make a friend who would be able to talk with him, to laugh, and to share memories with him.       The mad scientist went about his house looking for things that he wanted to do with this robot and for characteristics that he enjoyed. He first searched in the kitchen. There was a deck of cards laying on the wooden table that he brought with him from Germany. He absolutely loved cards. The scientist searched in the cupboard he found a wooden stirring spoon. He also loved to cook. He then went to the living room he found his favorite TV show, Myth Busters. The scientist traveled up the tall stairway,up to his bedroom. He gathered a pile of pictures of him and his family.       The mad scientist picked up the pictures and began walking downstairs. He traveled from room to room gathering his items up.After he got everything he went into his basement. He layed everything on the table,and began working. Twisting,bolting,screwing,tightening up every little piece of his friend so he would be perfect.Time past the night grew darker and the scientist fell asleep.       In the morning the scientist awoke from the sound of card deck being shuffled. He looked up and there his friend was! The scientist sprung out of his old chair and said ''hello.'' The robot looked up with the brightest smile on his face and said ''hi want to play cards with me?'' To the scientists surprise the robot knew how to speak German!       They were both so excited that they finally had some one they could call a friend! For the rest of the day they played cards and watched Myth Busters.

Item_Response: There was a robot named: XPL-453, who loved doing work for other people. He had owners who loved him very much (just because he was cool and was worth A LOT of money). He had Jetpack legs and feet, he was yellow, he could eat the kids' food secretly so they would not get in trouble, he did all of the chores, he put the babies to sleep in a matter of seconds, and he could run to the grocery store and buy anything that you needed in 1 minute. But one day he ' Broke Down' His owners were so mad, they broght him to a real hospital without thinking. The doctor laughed and said: 'ARE YOU KIDDING ME? He is a robot, not a human.' 'We know, said the owners, But he is very sick and we need him for- the doctor cut the owner off. 'I think i know what the problem is. Come with me.' 'Thank you.' said the owners together. The doctor then said, 'All he needs is a little oil, I can fix him in no time.' 'A little bit of oil a little?' 'Yes, just a little, said the doctor, But it will be quite a price, for him being a robot.' 'We will pay anything to get him fixxed for the- ' What was that?' 'Nevermind.' 'Hmmmm.' said the doctor. 'what! said the owner, is he OK?' 'Yes, but I don't think he needs oil at all.' 'What does he need then.'   'Oh, well umm, I am not really sure how to put htis but um, we, I mean, I don't think he is going to make it.'   'What do you mean?!'  'Well, how old is he?'  '21, why? Is he going to be ok? Why do you need to know how old he is?!!' The owner started to cry. ' If he is 21 years old, his life is complete. I'm sorry.' The doctor then left the room. ' how are we going to make money for the family if he is gone?' ' I don't know.'  'Well, think of something!'  'Stop it, we can always get another robot.'  'No, it just won't be the same.' That owner walked away. Nobody knows where she went, she was gone forever.                                                                                                              Story by: Cheyenne Venables

Item_Response: If you were to have a robot of some kind what will it be like? Very big with jets, wheels, legs, wings, slime, or hovering? Well, your little robot will come out of your dreams and come to life. You just need to imagine it coming and being curious about robots and technology for instance:             If I were to have a robot come to life it would be like this: It will have four wheels with jets, a camera, mini radio, lots of strength, takes energy from the sun, is red and black striped.             I had this dream, until it happened... I got a letter in the mail saying that they needed a design for a robot so they can mail in a blue print to build it, That gave me an idea. So I got to it, I wrote my dream robot design and mailed it to the company.       (1 month later)             I had forgotten all about me mailing the design to the company until I checked the mail box and saw a big envelope, I said, 'what's this?!' it had said, 'thank you for your help, here is $1,000 for making the blueprint a big hit!!!' Then inside was the 1,000 dollars and a free blueprint of how to build the robot, then I remembered, I sent the design to this company 1 month ago!       So I had gotten to work at building my robot. First, I had to get the materials, Second, was to follow every step, 1-103. Once I was done, I took a picture of it and I and I sent it to the whole city!       So remember me and then you can make a robot of your dreams and stick to it don't just throw away the idea.                                                                     Sincerely,                                                                       Me

Item_Response: Robot Saves the Day!                 One morning there was a teenage named James who loved to drive. He was 17, had his drivers license and he was a good driver. He drove smart and safe. Also though he bought a Google robot just in case he had to take a nap he would let the Google robot built in the car take over. Today the Google robot saved his life.                 One day James was on his normal day driving back home from school. Today it was a very early rush hour so there were a lot of drivers driving at the time James was trying to get home. James lived with his parents about 30 minutes away from his school.                 James was very tired that day when it was a Monday, but James was a stubborn person and kept on driving. 'Ugh I am so tired,' James said as he drove down the road. Soon he dozed off.                 Then the Google robot sensed that James was sleeping as it was a green light and his hands wasn't on the wheels and his feet weren't on the pedals. The Google robot took over the car seeing that James had his navigating system set to take him home the Google robot did exactly that. The Google robot stopped at red lights, went at the right speeds, and drove how a good driver would.                When the Google robot got home and stopped the car, James woke up. 'Whoa! What! Where am I?' James shouted in a puzzled way. After James got his hold of his senses he figured out that he was in his garage, the engine was off, the car was in the condition it was before he took the car out. He wasn't aware that the Google robot saved his life, but he was thankful that he was in the garage after he dozed to sleep on the road.                 When the week ended James took a look at his car trying to think of anything that could've gotten him home at that day when he dozed off. Thats when he finally remembered when he bought the car he also bought a Google Robot also. 'Well!' James said 'I finally figured that out and I am thankful that I am home right now!'

Item_Response: My Robot               One day girl name Meg was building a robot for her science project. She was to make a mini version of a robot that would be in every house to take care of people that she thinks will look like in the future. Well, that very night when she put this red cord to this blue cord a little shock happened and the robot started to say 'Hello my name is Bob whats yours?'. Meg freaked out and called her mom to come see. Her mom said' Meggie that is such an adorable robot you got there.' Meg answers 'don't call me that and look my robot can talk! ' Oh that's wonderful you will  get an A on your assignment!'                  The next day Meg went to the library to read about robots and how they could be made. She found that some robots can climb volcanoes to gather information for scientist that cant stand the hot arid heat. This robot is called Dante 2. Meg knew her robot would not fit with that information,  Because her robot almost set on fire by the stove that was on. Meg went to a different book she found a robot that can work in hospitals by helping doctors and nurses bring medicine to patients. This robot looked like a small cabinet on wheels its name is Mr.Gower. Then Meg saw it her robot was a Mr.Grower robot.Because on time she wanted milk and her little robot dragged a gallon of milk by her. Meg was surprised but ignored it till now.                   When Meg got home from the library she told her mom that she was going to change her robot a little and, not to come up stairs while she doing it. Meg made the robot a little bigger so it can carry stuff and not to drag it and then she put a voice control box in it so someone can give it demands. Later that day Meg to her mom to come up stairs. When her mom got to her room her mouth dropped and said 'what the heck did you do to your robot!' 'Its beautiful!' she continued. Meg told the robot to go get a cup of coffee for her mom and coke for her the robot quickly but gently and went and completed her tasked.                       The  next few weeks she had her robot do her chores and clean her room. But one day when meg told the robot to go and get her mom some chips then the robot started to yell out '123567492309757566 bye' and flew out the window and exploded in the sky. She yelled that her robot exploded her mom said it was the time anyway. Meg is trying to make a new one but every time she fails.                                                               THE END

Item_Response: He's Alive            It all started when I bought a robot at the Robot Store on my birthday and the robot was a machine or car that drives by itself so I bought one so i don't have to care about driving as much.When I bought the car it kept doing strange things....            The radio kept turning on and off on it's own.The car kept leaking whenever I filled up the gas.It got scary one night while I was sleeping the robot car made a bunch of noises so I went to the garage to see what was happening it was alive i screamed!'Wwwwhattt iss haaapppening' I stuttered. 'ahhhh!'the car screamed.'You can talk!' I said while freaking out.'I'm alive!!!!!!!!!!!' I thought i was dreaming but when I woke up I heard the robot say,'good moring .' So just pretended to think the car was a person but unfortunetly it did not work.           Later  the robot approached me and when I was going to the store and he said 'want a ride ' and I replied 'sure??' After coming back from the store i went to bed and when i woke upo it was my bitrhday and my parents got me a car and i said to the car 'oh not again!!!!'

Item_Response: Something Unexspective and New              So we made this robot about five months ago and left it in the janitors closet for some while. We kept hearing banging noises from the closet. So our instructor decided we should cheak out whats in there. When we went in there we found the robot we made as a group five months ago.               'wow!' we exclamied our robot was dancing and jumping just like we designed it to do! We thought it would never do what we wanted so we gave up. I guess that wasn't such a good idea to keep it in the closet and give up.                So we decided to make a new robot and the one we had already had would work together with the new one. So as we worked on the new one we were starting to build we used websites to help us. But then i thought 'Hey guys we need a name for it!' We all decided on a name for the new robot to be named Fish. It would be able to fly and swiim. It would be able to fly 80 mph. and swim a 500 free style in  one minute and fivty six seconds it will be extrodanary!                 Once it was made we couldnt believe how cool and different it was to any other robot. It could do everything we wanted it to do, it was amazing. Our class had a good time learning about it and creating it we hope we could do it again.

Item_Response: Robots Saving the world                     One day their was a robot named the Mega tron he was named after a football stars nickname 200 years ago. He was used to play games such as dance and play catch much like the robot HRP-4c which was a robot of 2013 nearly 200 years ago, but technology has come a long way since then.                                Mega tron also has a special power when the city needs him he goes from a normal robot to a giant machine and helps protect his people from the recent invaders from mars, but there was something that not even Mega tron could enticipate.                        'CRACK'  the normal blue sky opend up and turned a redish black and a giant space ship appered opening the sky and then closing it back up so the people of New York City could not escape. Their only hope was to have the 18 mega trons defend the 13,000 marshens the numbers were looking bad but the mega trons all formed into one  Mega tron which was twice the size of the empire state building! One by one the Mega trons were taking the marshons apart they felt it was to easy after there was only 1,000 left.                  The suprise came 100,000 more marshons droped from the sky. All the Mega Trons were super tired and couldn't fight much more but they could just her the terriours cries from their children so they all seperated back to 18 diffrent units and split into groups again each one taking each marshon just demolishing them but then almost a quarter of the way there they lost 10 units in the battle which got them really angry and they started to keep it going half way through they didnt loose another unit, but it didnt matter how much they didnt want to give up they just were to fatiuged, so they called in their main stash of Mega trons from D.C and were almost unbeatable they saved New York City and the dead robots were repaird and as good as new!!!!!!!!!!

Item_Response: One day I was making a robot in my garage.I named the robot Jeff. It took about three weeks to finish making the robot.I equipped him to help people who need things to be carried and he collects information for scientists.Jeff can talk too.He can transform into a car.I am really proud what I just made.           For the next month my robot and I have been having alot of fun together.He's helped me with getting through tough times and he's my friend.We go to watch sports together.       He serves me like he goes to me a can of soda,he takes the blame for something I did.He helps me with my homework and cleans my room for me.He even cleans the house. I hope I can keep him forever.           When I woke up one sunny morning I went to check on him when I saw he was gone.Later I went to look for the robot in the town.I found him,but he was doing some strange things like riding on roller coasters,working as an employee,and dressing up like a real person.       I was speechless.I asked him why did you run away and he said 'I want to be robot who can do what he wants to do'.           'I want to play sports and go watch sports with my robot friends.''I want to feel the thrill of being treated like a real person and I don't want to be kinda like a servant for you.'                     I understoood that he needs to be a person and live free instead of being controlled by me.So,I said'You can be leave and be a free robot'.       The robot felt a thrill in him so he said 'goodbye' and left to a place with other robots to make friends with and potentially find a wife.The robot was really famous in robot land he was a proffesinal basketball player.       This place he was going to was called robot land.They kept in touch sometimes he came over to my house.We will always be best friends.

Item_Response: 'BOOM!' I heard a boom in my room so i rushed over there to see what happened. I saw my toy robot ALIVE! It was cleaning my room and doing my homework and all types of stuff! At first I thought I was dreaming but then it hit me, really it hit me and it hurt. It was so cool it looked just like a normal person but with metal plates on it, it was red and blue and it was wearing some of my clothes.           I did not want to tell anyone because they'd think I'm CRAZY! I kept him in my closet for a day. At night it beeps like crazy it wont let me go to sleep, so  shut him off with a switch he had on his back. The next morning he woke me up at 6:00 am and he tied me on a wagon and it went for a walk which for normal people it's a sprint! he was going 80 miles a minute! it almost blew my hair away! When we got home I had some bruises from falling off so much. We had great times together he was my BEST FRIEND!  But a couple of weeks later I heard a BOOM from my room when I walked in, he was blown up.

Item_Response: ROBOTS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!        There are many kinds of robots today. Even though they seemed like an impossible story, today they are helping us in many ways. Two ways that robots help us today are they carry matierials such as medicine, water, and food at many different places. They also help with geography by studying volcanoes, planets, etc. As you can see robots are a major item in our world now and forever until they find something else.        An example for a robot that can transport matierials to many places would be Mr.Gowser, a shelf-like robot that travels through hospitals giving doctors, nurses, surgeons, etc. medicine and tools. Some robots can do this and more. Like the Gemini-Scout, who travels through mines with food and water, and also can check the air for gasses and tells the miners if its safe to go into somewhere.        There are also robots that help with geography and science: i.e., a robot named Dante 2 can climb up volcanoes and go into them withstanding the heat. Before scientists couldn't study volcanoes, but now if they can't go in, then they send Dante 2 or any other robot.        There are many robots that help in the world today, but these are just a few. There are many others that do many other jobs. And some are yet to come.

Item_Response: The Day Of The Science Fair                                  On Febuary 17,2012 they had papers to sign in a science fair.The fair wasn't till March 23.This girl named Jessica signed in and then gave her paper to the principal,there was only 15 people selected.Jessica was one of those 15 people.                       On Saturday March 17,2012 there was a girl named Jessica.Jessica joined a science fair at her school.She wasn't ver shure what to do for the science fair.Then she came up with a smart idea.Jessica dicited to build a robot.She was up day and night trying to make a robot.Jessica was going to take a brake from building a robot till she saw the date.Jessica said to herself today is March 21 and the science fair is in March 23.Jessica rushed to the garage. till she finally finished,Jessica made the robot so it can walk,talk,and tought it to be helpful.Jessica made it talk by putting a speaker inside of the robot.She said all the words she can think of,then she said hopefully it talks back in a correct sentence.So Jessica said ''hello robot''.Jessica thought it wasn't going to work until the robot said hello whats your name,Jessica smiled and said im going to name you Junior.She said by the way my name is Jessica.Then ever scince that day Jessica and Junio have been best friends.Then the science fair came.Jessica and Junior left.They went to the fair and Junior and Jessica won the science fair.                                            Ever scince the day Jessica build Junior shes been thinking what can i do for Junior to make him helpful.Till she talks to Junior very nice and he nows how to react with other people they have been thinking he has a brain like us humans so they Jessica said you should come with me to school so you can help teachers and students.                                                               Jessica said you are so smart and i think you need to get a job.Junior said i could but I dont think they would acsept someone like me.Jessica said no trust me your just like one of us humans.they went to go looking for a job untill Junior found one.He went to go ask for a aplication in the beach as a lifegard. Item_Response: The Day My Three Robots Came Alive                                             One Monday morning I was bored, so I thought of what kind of project to do for the science fair that week. So I got a text from Samantha saying have you figured out of what your going to do for the science fair that is coming up. I said yes, I do im going to make three robots. Samantha texted me back what are you going to name the three robots I said i would name the first one Wiz Khalifa, the second Drake, the third Arturo.                                      So I started to work on my three robots . the first one that i finished was   Wiz Khalifa . Then the second Drake it was kind of alot of hard work to do each one took and hour and a half. So for the last one Samantha had came over to bulid it, like they all say that team work is faster. It actually was true. So anyways after that I rested for the rest of the day Because the next day was school and the day after is the science fair.                        Its 6:00 in the morning I wake up, get ready and go to school. During school I was thinking about the robots I created the day before. I was also thinking about the next day after that which was the science fair. So it was time to get off school and i came back to my house I had heard my phone ringing it was Samantha i answered and she said was I done with the robots i replied yes. she said im going come and check them out OK, I said for sure yeah. So as I waited for here to get there i hear a very loud noise in the kitchen i thought it was my dog.                                        I went into the kitchen and said Princess my dogs name. No one answered all off a sudden............ one of the robots which was Drake started singing 'started from the bottom'. And the other one which was Wiz Khalifa started singing 'black and yellow'. Those were the funny ones the one the creeped me out the most was Arturo. And that one just was saying a bunch of random things that creeped me out. So I decided to record the robots and post it on Youtube and it turned out to be a hit on the robots. So I took the robots to the Science fair and they got first place for the most talented robots just for them singing.........................I LOVE MUSIC!!!!!!!!!!!!!<3

Item_Response: The New And Inproved       Dr. Von A. Newton was in his lab at T.A Labratories. He was working on a broken down Mr. Grover (a robot used in hospitals). When he came apon a peice if rusting metal on the head of the robot. Dr. Newton took out the peice of metal and noticed that Mr. Grover was moving without a command or anything. He was grabbing stuff Dr. Newton needed. The Dr. happened to have a dog in the the lab and Mr. Grover started to play with Dr. Newton's dog!       'Wow!' the Old Docter Mr. Grover had, exclamed, ' I can't believe you got him to work I thought he was forsure a gonner!' Dr. Newton said ' He not only is fixed but more improved than ever! He can go fetch stuf without a command. Also he will play with pets or people if they need company!' The Old Docter said ' How about we sell these new kind of robots to the public. They'll  love it!'       The next year both the Dr.'s had 200 robots made new and improved. They were in the market the next month. The people of the world loved the new robots, the Dr.'s were becoming rich. After a while the robots started developing a mind of their own. They were taking over the house that they lived in and the people were scared.       The Dr.'s, to fed up with their own glory, didn't even know this was happening. Then the robot that they had for 3 years now, developed a mind.       The Dr.'s found a way to reset the program so the robot will die. Then they told the public to do the same. It worked, but both Dr.'s got thrown in jail for it.

Item_Response: How I, The Billy Bob Joe Bot 3000, Got My Own Brain              I was suppose to be the best of the best. The most high-tech robot on the face of the Earth. I could fly, swim, run, lift up thousands of pounds, talk like a normal human, never destroy Mr. Owner, and be obedient. Then my life changed because of one little girl. This is how I, The Billy Bob Joe Bot 3000, got my own brain.             On May 2, 2058, Mr. Owner brought his daughter, Angela, to work. School had bin cancelled for little Angela and since Mrs. Owner was ill ( no cure to asgriopreteous yet, sadly) Mr. Owner had to bring her.             At lunch, I was told to go to the charging room to, well..., charge.   But the little rascal Angela must have followed me. As I got set to charge, Angela said,' Biwwy Bob! Biwwy Bob! Wook at me!' Being used to her childish talk, looked over and saw was terrible. If I had had a heart and mind back then I would have had a heart attack. Angela was touching the Forbidden Box. It was a box I programed never to go near or touch. And here, a little four year old girl was yet to open a box, forbidden to a incredibly powerful robot?             Since I was programed not to go near it I said,' Dear Angela, please put the box down.' In reply she yanked the top of the box and threw it. Her toss was terrible, but I ran anyway. Right into the path of the box.             The box hit my side. Out of it slithered a black goo. It was spreading all over me and when I tried to take it off, it just stuck to my hands.             When it finally over took over I felt.... different. Like I could control myself. And  most of all I had a sensation to protect Angela. Be her friend. I knew Mr. Ex-Owner would be super mad at me. But now I had a new owner. I had my own mind and could disobey, but I had to do what was best for her. That was my knew prograning.My knew owner is .............................. ANGELA.

Item_Response: BU-ford          Crash! there came a loud noise from the labritory. Will shock his head in his hands.          Ealrer that week Wills toy robot BU-ford had come a live. Even though it is ''state of the art'' it was rather clumsy. BU-ford could hardly walk without tripping, muchless run.          BU-ford was trying to be more helpful ,but that really didn't happen.He was trying to make a sandwich for himself (because he had come alive) he needed food.          Will came walking briskly in from the dining room where he had been doing homework. he saw on of his mothers favorite piece of china on the floor, smashed to pieces.          ''BU-ford, don't use the fine china to make a sandwich.'' will said in a complantiant voice.the robots ''face'' became downish and gluum.          '' Yes master Will''.          Will relised he had become mean and shnubish to the robot friend,''Its fine I'll clean it up.'' Will said.thats when he locked on the counter... jam,  strawberrys, peanutbuter and chocolate litered it. will gave a sigh   .      God this robot couldn't be more of a buredin, Will thought. Will ceaned the kitchen the beast he could. then huried off to bed          Early that morning BU-ford was awake trying to ponder what had happnd the night before. What shall I do. I can't do much. He thought   then he ha an idea. a light bulb literly turned on in his head. he did a maniachal laugh and rubbed his hands saying ''MUWUHHAHMUWUHA!''           Will came down stairs sying dased '' What was that racket?''           ''Nothing'' came the repliy.           Will was off to school the one place he thought he could get away from the robot of clumsyness. boy was he wrong.          The first hour was mathmatics he walke in and there in the middle of the room was it the robot. Will was supprised how well he had made friends then he rellised what he was talking about, this is what he heard...            ''I was walking up a active valcano, (too dangerous for humans) to studie it'' he paused for emphasis,'' Boom! It blw up in me face. I got out of there. Next i worked in a hospitale in Guato  takin medicen to pacients an doctors. But my favorite job was being a shofure. I got to drive so many cars. Hey, Will, get over here'' he gestured.             Will picked him self up, and strolled over. I am happy that he  made friends. And it was true he was happy.

Item_Response: The Best Christmas Present Ever                             One Christmas morning, a young boy named Billy got a very special present. He unwrapped the paper and was amazed at what he saw. It was a toy robot! He was filled with joy and ran up to his room to play with it. That night Billy went to bed and fell asleep. A few hours later, Billy started to hear noises and got a little scared. He hid under the covers and soon fell asleep again. A little while later, Billy heard the noise again and found out it was in his room. He looked down and saw his robot moving and talking to him. Billy was amazed and scared at the same time. So he decided to see if he could communicate with it and he could! he found out it could do a lot of things like do homework and cook food. Billy had never been more suprised and amazed in his life!                    Ever since Billy knew that the robot could do all this stuff, he has been best friends with it. As soon as his parents found out what the robot could do, they were fritened! So they threw him away in the garbage. When Billy go home from school and found out what had happened, was devistated. The robot missed his new friend so he went back to Billy's house without the parents knowing and hid in Billy's room. Billy was so happy to see the robot. He was still in trouble for not telling his parents what had happened so he made sure he hid the robot really well. His parents found out not long after and saw how much he loved the robot so they let him stay. So from there on the robot and Billy were best friends.

Item_Response: Nepzar1                The night was slowly crawling past time. It was only 12 pm but it felt like 2 for Rodney Revell. He was up in theese late hours of the night to finish his science project. He had to build a robot then turn it in on the following day. Rodney had been trying to build this robobot for hours but he couldnt get it to work. Finally as the clock struck 4 am Rodney decided to give up. Angered, he headed to his room down the hall from the workshop he had been working in. His robot would fail him and he would fail the project.               On the day the project was due he got up before he could get on the bus to go to school. When he went to the work bench where the robot that he called the nepzar1 was being built he found the robot was missing. He looked all around but nepzar1 was no where to be found. Suddenly he heard a crash in the kitchen and his mother scream.               Swiftly, Rodney ran out of the workshop and into the kitchen. His mother was up against the couch in the family room with a knife in her hand yelling intruder in the kitchen. Rodney grabbed the knife out of his mothers hand to arm himself as he approached the kitchen. When he entered the kitchen he met face to face with the intruder. It was nepzar1! He was alive. His eyes were made out of soda cans and were illuminating a pale blue. His mobility was working as well he had little treads that rolled with him where he wanted to go. His main body, was an old microwave Rodney had found so he could store things in himself. and his arm was a simple grabber that nepzar1 could use to pick things up. Rodney let out a cry of delight as he saw his completed project working as programmed. In a squeaky voice nepzar1s first word was master. His mother came in madder than bee in a vacum cleaner. Not funny Rodney she said.                  Rodney glanced out the window and saw his bus. Got to go mom he said as he flew out the door. Rodney grabbed nepzar and got on the bus. His first class was science so he could drop nepzar off and present him to the class. Rodney saw big bots and small bots but none were as special as nepzar1. When it was rodneys turn nepzar and him walked side by side up to the whiteboard. He told the class everything he could do. his teacher, Miss Ignaranus, gave rodney an A plus

Item_Response: The One Thing That Worked          On a cold night in December, Rickie was up late fiddling in frustration with his robot pieces wishing that something would work. But that wasn't the way it was, no nothing worked for him.             He finally gave up and and sadly climbed into his bed. He hoped that one day that something amazing would happen upon him. 'Amazing things only happen in fairy tales.' Rickie thought to himself before he glanced at a photo on his nightstand. it was of him and his father a month before he passed away.               Within a minute, Rickie dozed off.            'Rickie! Rickie!, time to catch the bus!! Quick, before Your oatmeal gets cold!.' This was the usual wake-up call he got on a school morning from his mom. He knew that if he stalled, he wouldn't be in a good position, so he threw on his uniform and hustled downstairs. In those few minuets, he had no time to notice something peculiar on his desk.             At school, Rickie trudged through the noisy hallway. There were lockers slamming, girls giggling and sneakers squeaking on the tile floor. He would much rather be at home where it is quiet, constructing a robot and enjoying some rich hot coco.             Then, something snapped him out of daydreaming. 'Hey, Rickie! ' It was the voice of Mark, the one who appeared to not have a heart. Rickie didn't want to turn around but he did anyway. 'What do you want Mark?' Rickie replied with an impatient tone. ' Still into playing  with your little robot toys?' 'You know Mark I'm sick and tired of you always bugging me. If you do it again you'll be sorry.' 'And what can you do to me?' That was the last straw. Rickie was going to strike a blow...              At that moment, Mrs. Clancy the principal scolded Rickie and Mark. ' To my office now!' The boys talked with her and both were sent home early. Rickie's mom was working so he walked the treacherous walk to has house.              At his house Rickey was relieved to be at has desk once more. Sometimes Rickie wished he could fly away. Then he noticed a glowing gadget on his desk. He studied it for a minute and realized. it could fit in his robot and maybe make it whole. So he put it in but nothing happened.... until it started to levitate and slowly fly around his room. He had no idea where that piece came from but all he knew was that his robots had a chance and if he needed to fly away from at all, in a way he could.

Item_Response: A Robot That Came to Life   By, Alex Ferron                Scientists have been working on a robot that could do anything that a human being can do. Tomorrow it will be seven years since they've started this project and they only need two more pieces until the robot is up and active. Two days from now, their shipment for the pieces will come. Finally they add the last two pieces to the robot. They turn on the power switch and bam it came to life, but all of the it started going wacked and sparking. They had to shut it down.            All except for one scientist gave up. That one scientist found the problem after three months of hard work. It took him another two months to get the supplies and fix the problem. He started up the robot and it worked! The robot controled through a video game controller. Then, he got the idea of giving it a mind of its own. It took him two months to complete this task, but it was worth it. The other scientists were amazed when they heard the news. They decided to let himpic the name of the robot.

Item_Response: The Robot that Comes Live                                    By Katie English                    Ones there was a boy named Jermy he loved to builed things he was mostly fasanated with robots. One day for a science project he wanted to build a robot, so he went to his basment and got the miterials and started to make it. Jermy was putting wiers in when all os a sudden he herd a noise. He said ''what was that' Jermy was alittle scared . But then he looked at his robot.                               Was that you'Jermy said with a scared voice. The robot replied with a calm vocie'yes master, I will surve you a you wish master''. The next day was the day that Jermy had to hand in his project. As he walked into class he was a lttle scared to see what the other kids would say. He was thinking to him self that the kids would say it is cool but he did not know what the teacher would say. Item_Response: Sparky             The first time I saw him, I was sitting in my dads lab at the college where he teaches. 'I have a surprise for you.' He said. 'Wait here.' He walked into another room, and when he came back he was holding a large box. 'Whats in there?' I said. 'You have to wait and find out' I tore the box open like a child on Christmas. When I saw what was inside, I gasped. 'Wait, a real robot?' I said in awe as I set it down on the counter. 'Yes, and its all yours. You know how you said you wanted a dog? Well, here it is. It acts like a dog, except you don't have to let it out to go to the bathroom or feed it.' I thought to myself wow, this is amazing. it has fur and everything! 'You made this? That why you were gone so much!' I said. 'Oh thank you! Thank you, thank you! I said while giving him a huge hug. 'What are you going to name it?' my dad said. 'I think I'm going to name it sparky! That seems like a perfect name for him!' It was true, it was a perfect name for him. He was a black and white puppy almost up to my knees. 'Well, why don't we start to head home. Your mom doesn't know about this yet, so I think we should go home and tell her.'             When we got home, mom was so surprised to see a robotic dog walking into her home, she was jumping up and down like a little girl. 'Henry! You made this? It's amazing!' She said. 'Honey, you are so lucky to have a dad like this. He's going to be the next Eienstien, I'm sure of it!' My dad and I just looked at each other and started laughing. 'His name is Sparky. Isn't he cute?' I said while bending down to pet him. 'I'm hungry. Can I have something to eat?' I said at the same time my stomach started growling. 'Sure, what would you like. Pizza? I just made some, it's still warm.' 'Sure. That sounds really good. Thanks mom.'             'So this is the living room, Sparky.' I said when we walked into the living room. I was giving sparky a tour of the house. Whenever I led him into a different room, he started wagging his tail. 'Oh! I almost forgot the best room in the house, my room!' As I led him into my room, he started barking and wagging his tail so much, it looked like he was going to fall over! 'Well, it looks like it's time for me to go to bed. After I brushed my teeth, washed my face, and did everthing I jumped in bed with Sparky, not even noticing the glowing red eyes staring at me through the window.
