Item_Response: In the town of Walton lived a man named Bryan. Bryan was an old man who lived alone and worked on a robot in his garage every night. He wanted to make a robot to keep him company on the long and boring nights he spent alone. One night the robot had came alive! Bryan decided to name the robot Rob. After a couple of months, Bryan got very sick. He was always sitting in his bed. Rob decided to go and check on him. Bryan was not moving, so Rob decided to wake him. That night Bryan would not awake. Rob later found out that Bryan had passed.                 Rob was a playful robot. He decided that he wanted some company, so he got a puppy. His little puppy`s name was Jack. Every night he would go out on a walk with Jack around town. Now even though Rob was a robot and Jack was a dog they had lots in common. On their walks they would stop by a cafe, there they would get bundles of attention. Attention was one thing that as a robot, Rob and Jack had deeply enjoyed. They would also stop by the park once in a while. There they would play fetch with the other robots and pets that were there.                 Today was an extra special night, it was Jacks 1st birthday! Today Rob decided to go a different way into town so they could stop by a new dog store that just opened up down the road. Rob went to go grab his rain coat and a little coat for Jack due to the rain. In matter of minutes they were off and headed down the road. About 30 minutes into the walk Rob started to worry, there was nothing in sight. They suddenly stop, right there in front of them was a huge forest. 'Oh no were lost!' shouted Rob.                 Rob decided to just head back home. As him and Jack turned around there were even more trees. Rob climbed up the trees to get a better idea of where they were, but just saw more trees in the distance.They tried every direction there was, but just ended up in the exact same spot. ' What do we do now?' Rob asked. Jack even knew something was wrong and started to cry. All of a sudden, Rob remembered  that Bryan had put a chip in his head to monitor his behaviors. He assumed this chip could direct him and Jack back home. Rob tried and it worked! 'Hey, Jack look, were back home!' exclaimed Rob. 'Home sweet home,' mumbled Rob.

Item_Response: it all started when a group of scientists were working on a robot. they had been working on it for 6 months. they were having trouble  with  the robot and they had other things to do. finally scientist 1 said ' we cant finish this robot!!!' scientist 6 said ' what? we have to! we cant just leave all this hard work!' scientist 1 said ' we have to! we don't have the technology to finish.' scientist 2 said' i guess your right. guys lets go work on something else.' they all finished their job for the day and everyone left.            Scientist 1 went to pick up his daughter from school and realized he left his phone. he drove back to the lab and looked for his phone. he couldn't find it anywhere. his daughter came in wondering what was taking so long and she saw the robot lying on the table. 'Wow! this is so cool!' she said. scientist 1: oh that, its not finished. we are going to throw this away. 'what? why? its so cool though! hey! can i have it?' she said. 'well, it might be really dangerous. but i guess i can take out the cord that makes it turn on. sure.' said scientist 1. ' Yay!!! I'm so excited!' she said. 'okay lets go home now. i just wonder where my phone went.' little did they know that with the phone magnetically attached to that robot without the cord was just what it needed to come alive.           the next day was the daughters day for show and tell day at school. she put the robot in a big box and took the bus to school. she arrived with everyone staring at her. her teacher said, ' what is that?' she said,' its my show and tell .' 'oh. okay well everyone listen up. this is your show and tell presentation.' said the teacher. ' okay ' she opens the box and walking out comes  the robot.' everyone gasps. she just stands there. then a phone rings. Item_Response: Robots           One day there was a robot called The Editor.  It was made by a company called Skynet. It was a house robot and a hospital robot. So they went back outside to see if the eyes were still red and they were. Then all of a sudden the robot started to talk. They ran away and the robot started chasing them. The same was happening to all the robots in the world. The robots were attacking everybody.               The Sally and Robert didn't know what to do. Then one man came and his name was John Connors. He was destroying all the robots but they were to many. So he called in his team. He told the kids 'come with me if you want to live'.So they went with him in a helicopter and they destroyed all the robots.               Then Robert woke up. It had all been a dream. He was so relieved. He looked over at Sally and she was all right. Everything was all right. So Robert went back to sleep.

Item_Response: The Unbelievable Discovery       It was a sunny afternoon, in the small village of Dandan, located on the island of Saipan which is in the Pacific Ocean.  It was usually quiet there every single day, but that day was not one of those days.  As I was walking past my garage   I heard a very loud and strange sound which starled me in the beginning.  I took a couple steps front, and a couple steps back to see if anything would happen.  Nothing had happen.       I decided to go in my garage to see what was making that noise, but it took a lot of courage for me because I am always easily scared.  I took some deep breaths and slowly opened the garage door.  As I picked it up, I could see that the light was not turned on, which meant it was pitch black in there.  I held my breath and tipped toed inside, as I tried to reached all over the walls to find the light switch, I stumbled on something very perculiar.        All of a sudden, the light turned on and I could see everything that was happening.  I looked down to see what I stumbled upon, and it was a robot!  It wasnt just any kind of robot, it was a very unique kind of robot.  It was not like any other robot I have seen on television.  It had a fluffy body which was shaped in a diformed kind of way.  It only had one eye which was always twitching for no reason.  It had wheels for feet and an opening on the tummy.       I blinked in disbelief while I examined the robot. It looked friendly and not harmful at all.  I pet the back of the robot, it just looked at me and smiled with it weirdly shaped mouth.  ' I wonder what it can do?', I asked myself.  There was a bright red button on the opening of the tummy.  I pressed it and othing happened.  I took a huge step back and thought for a moment.         All of a sudden the lights turned off, and then I saw differnt kinds of colors flashing everywhere.  There was smoke coming from the robot. I stood there in shock, not knowing what to do.  The robot calapsed and it slowly opened.  Streamers came out from it, shooting everywhere inside the garage.  Music started playing from it and there was candy and little gifts all over the ground.  i couldnt belive it!  For the first time in history, I discovered a party robot!

One person was crying because  the robot was helping her and she just didn't know anything about the robot.After one year passed the robot finally came back . After months everyone was getting mad at the robot and didn't like him no more because he dint respond to the questions about why he desapeared so quickly and not telling nobody. Then years passed and the girl finally asked him why he was so misterius and desapeard with out telling nobody. When the girl asked that crying  the robot thought about it and then told her because he was turning into a person. Then  the girl just started  to cry louder and louder. After like three years passed the robot desapeared again and a new person came.

Item_Response: My Robot?                                                                    One sunny day I was in my backyard looking for my shoes because my little sister keeps hiding them. I looked every where but still, I couldn't find them. I'm in a hurry because I'm having a student council meeting at my school. I'm the student council vice president. Suddenly, I find broken metal pieces on the grass. 'Maybe i can use these metal pieces for my school project,' I said excitedly. After that, I finally found my shoes and then I ran to school.                                                                                            After I came back from school, I did my homework and then I went to my room. Suddenly, I remembered about the metal pieces I found in my backyard. Then I thought to myself 'What if i build a robot.' I knew building a robot wasn't going to be easy but I have to at least try my best. After that i started building the robot.I stayed up all night working on my project.' I cant wait to show my new robot to the whole school!' I thought to myself.

Item_Response: Once upon a time there was a little boy who had only one friend. Joey, was the boy's name, and he had a problem. He was very lonely and was bullied at school. After school one day he came home to find a letter in his mail box, 'You have been randomly chosen to receive out a toy dog.' Joey read aloud, 'this dog can do many amazing things. And you are in luck, your toy will be here soon!' Joey was completely enlightened and couldn't wait.       Three days later Joey found a box in the mail. 'That can't be right,' He thought as he looked down at the box that was no bigger than his thumb, 'The box is so small.' So, Joey walked into his room and opened the tiny box. A little, itty-bitty, metallic dog fell out of the package holding a piece of paper. 'WOOF WOOF!' said the dog. Joey was surprised at the bad quality of the toy. Joey put the dog into his dresser and left his room. When he came back the dog was running around, even though he was only an inch tall. Joey realized he had come alive, he didn't really think it over because he was to surprised by the dog.       So, Joey decided to read the paper, 'Congrats on your new puppy! your toy will do amazing things! He will play fetch, grab your newspaper, teach him tricks, cuddle with you, and much, much more! your dog won't ever need to go to the bathroom, and just feed him table scrapes. Furthermore, he will grow when ever you want (as big or small) just tell him to grow or shrink and he will.'       'I'll name you Spot!' said Joey astounded. 'WOOF WOOF!' responded Spot. Joey then commanded Spot to grow to a normal sized dog. And he did. The two boys played together for the rest of the day in Joey's room. The next day Joey realized that he didn't tell his parents. He already loved Spot and didn't want him taken away, so Spot remained a secret. Joey said, 'Spot, shrink down, be quiet, and get into my backpack.' Spot did as he was told.       At school Joey met up with his friend, Bob. At lunch Joey show Bob Spot. Bob was also surprised by Spot. 'how did you get him?' asked Bob. 'He came in the mail. I wasn't really expecting him.' Bob took some pictures of spot so he could remember him. None of them realized that the school bully, Sam, was watching them. Joey had spot get back into his bag as they walked to class. Item_Response: The Robot Who Came Alive           In the foggy morning of July it was the same, boring routine for all the nurses and doctors. They had to get up go to work and concentrate for their busy day ahead of them. Although, this wasn't just an ordinary day for a special robot named Jerrry. Jerry was a ' Mr. Gower' kind of robot, this means that Jerry carried medicines and zipped through elvevators, and  stairs to get to the docort and nurse fast! Jerry was the best robot in the hospital! Right when nurses and doctors called for medicnes Jerry would be there within a heartbeat! However, for the past couple weeks the word was getting out that the ' Famous Jerry' was unblievable! That day visitors were wanting to see Jerry including an evil man. This evil man had no known names, for he switches his names so he can keep his identity hidden. That evening, the evil man disguised himself as a doctor and put a potion that would make Jerry a human, so he could work for him. Once he stteled it in Jerry's small cabinet while he was charging, he dashed out to look as if he wasn't there. In only a couple of minuets the hospital would soon be filled with smoke, with no one not knowing where they were. 'BOOM!' Jerry heard screaming and commotion and dashed out from the hospital. He now realized he was human.           Jerry could now here himself breating and couldnt stop running till he reached a coffee shop. He didn't know where he was and what had happened. Soon he saw the hospital he grew up in on the news! He couldnt believe that it was closed, and who would do such a thing! But he realized the big question, how was he human, and what can he do to get back? He had plan but didn't know if it would turn out fine, but the number one thing Jerry had to was to be safe and get his life back.

Item_Response: It all starts when Morgan and Hudson plan on creating a robot to be the 'hero of the Earth'.Hudson says he wants to make the robot in shape of Morgan,so he puts him in a sort of escape pod,then he closes the door and the next thing that happens is Morgan is gone.He has teleported to some building full of ....kids.            Alex and Trent are on their lunch break when Morgan comes to them,thinking they look 'trustworthy'.'Where am I'Morgan asks them.'You're on Mars'says Trent jokingly.Alex punches him softly and says'You're in a school,in Ohio.Morgan looks confused.He pulls his sleeve back and reveals some sort of watch.Without saying a word,he presses a button and waves goodbye.But he doesn't move at all.He looks back at his watch and there is some taco sauce on his watch.Trent pulls back his shoulders and says'Sorry dude'.Morgan looks angry and sighs'The name is Morgan''Alex and that is Trent'replies Alex.'Well that Trent of yours just ruined my time tr-uughh watch'says Morgan.'I said sorry!'screams Trent.'Well here's the deal,My partner is creating a robot that wants to nuke the world.'What do you want us to do?'says Trent.'Shut up Trent,you've done enough already'Alex tells Trent.Andrew comes over,looking as if he rules the world.'What's going on,who is that?'   'That is Mo-'  'I'm Jacob'Morgan interrupts.           'Ohhh really?'Andrew sarcastically replies.BOOM!.Everybody faints.Alex awakes and realizes that Morgan is strapped on a wall,bleeding.There is a hole in the wall and Trent is missing.In the background,you can see Andrew trying to fight back to some stranger.Alex gets up but falls back down,noticing that he is also strapped.Andrew then grabs a remote and presses a random button.Alex and Morgan are now free.Morgan seems really angry,walks up to the stranger and gives him a 'taste of his own medicine'.There is a machine that flies up into the air.A computer announces'Nuke will be laucnhed in 5,4,3..'Trent comes in and grabs the robot and slams it back into the ground.Andrew then turns and tazes Trent and freezes Morgan with a freeze ray.Andrew comes toward Alex but Alex is able to escape and lock Andrew in a chamber.But the robot still remains...          Trent and Morgan are still paralyzed in the building.Andrew puts the building on self destruct mode.Alex has to make a choice.The world,or his friends.He goes on a high speed chase on the robot because the robot is about to destroy the world with the nuke.'5 minutes remain until self destruction'Andrew tells Trent and Morgan.Hudson,however is still alive and freezes and Andrew.'You're a traitor'Hudson tells Andrew.Hudson saw that    Andrew gave Alex the key to destroying the robot.Hudson is about to de-activate the self destruction,when Alex shuts down the robot.Alex has no idea what he has done.         Hudson is going after Alex now.Not him,but another robot,named the HA-J4.Alex has no other friends to help him,him being an orphan and not really popular.He has to save the world himself.         BOOOM.The building has self destructed.Alex is about to save Morgan and Trent once it blew up right before his eyes.He goes back to the school and grabs Trent's unfinished taco.He puts it in his pocket and goes to a nearby volcano.He wants to spread 'Trent's'ashes in the volcano.Once he arrives Andrew tackles Alex.'Prove your loyalty to me'Hudson says,smiling.He grabs Alex and throws him in the volcano.Morgan arrives with Trent and they teleport both of them and save Alex.'How did you get out of there?''My watch was still working'chuckles Morgan.Alex gives the taco back to Trent.But really,the taco is a robot....

Item_Response: Beep...  Beep...  Beep... A steady red light flashes on the tiny three centimeter robot as Sally spotted her robot, nicknamed the Factor 1.  Sally asked,' Have we finished our chores?' 'Yes, Sally,'the Factor 1 replied in a stiff voice, skillfully throwing a dirty paper towel into the trash bin next to Sally with one of its mechanical arms.             Sally sighed,' I'm bored.' There was nearly nothing to do when Sally's babysitter, Richie, was in the house.  With his trusty thermal camera, Richie could spot Sally a mile away, even if Sally went on the fastest scooter.  'What about a walk in the woods?'the Factor 1 suggested.  ' We aren't allowed to go there!' Sally exclaimed. '... Which makes it a perfect hideout from Richie... Factor 1?' 'Yes?''We're going for a hike in the woods!' Sally announced.               As Sally packed a peanut butter and jelly sandwich into her stuffed backpack, Factor 1 kept a keen eye out for Richie.  Richie was saying his farewells to Sally's parents, who were going to an all night dance party.  'Affermative,' Richie declared as Sally's parents gave him the last of their instructions.  ' Now is a good time, Sally,' Factor 1 whispered as Richie waved to thered car.   'Come on,' Sally said as she slipped past the back door.  Richie closed the front door just as Sally closed the back door.  Richie has excellent hearing, so if Sally closed the door too late or too soon, Richie would have heard it.               Crunch, crunch, crunch.  As the fall leaves crunched under Sally's feet, Sally raced silently along the rushing creek water.  As Sally saw an opening, she sat behind a tree trunk and munched on some barbaque chips. Factor 1 scurried into Sally's view and rested on a cusion of leaves.  Trees surronded Sally, the canopy high in the air.  Rays of white moonlight burst through the leaves and shone on Sally's shoes.  ' I think there is something in the trees,' Factor 1 muttered as it approached a huge object behind the trees.  Sally silently followed in wonder and curiousity. 'A robot!' she excitedly exclaimed as she saw the robot covered in moss and with animals scurrying around.  As she turned the On switch on, the robot rumbled with life and white light blinded Sally.  The animals ran away in fear as the mighty robot stood.  'Back off!' a familiar voice cried as an orange light flashed in the darkness.  In robot rankings, yellow was the highest, then comes orange, blue, purple, pink, red, green, and finally white.  An orange light was considered strong to Sally and to the giant robot. 'Where am I?'the giant thundered as it took a step foward. Richie came into view.   A light appeared on the giant unknown robot and it was black.  'Stop, Richie!  Look at the light color!' Sally said as she noticed the black light. Black represented blank or nothing. Richie lowered his laser and the three went home with a new friend, now named Giant.                                                                          The End

Item_Response: The Arrow scout. The arrow scout is a robot that helps people go in the right direction. For example if they are lost in the mountains or woods the arrow scout can help you go in the right direction. The arrow scout can find you easily at day and at night how? The arrow scout is a ground robot that can not be harmed by animals or bad weather.The arrow scout has an emergency kit inside the robot if someone is hurt. It just pushes the kit out and you can simply get it quick. The arrow scout has a camera that sends photos to search teams and labs.                      The arrow scout can help search teams too. The arrow scout can also go in water and point to the direction a tsunami is going to come that way.The arrow scout helped a scientist named Ryan that was lost and injured find his way back to the lab. The arrow scout can also provide protection mostly at night from harmful creatures how? people ask. it has a special light that scares animals away it may sound weird but it is not. People ask why is it so big? the creators say it is big because it might get crushed or covered in snow.The arrow scout is so strong it can carry and pull 600 pounds that is why it is also big.The arrow scout is a magnificent robot that can save alot of lives and helped alot of people. It was first used in a training site in  Atlanta,Georgia. It was a success and no problems ever happend. And so it was created a robotin 1995 and is still used today and  scientist and the creators of the arrow scout trying to make changes to it.

Item_Response: The rise of 3-PIO the Robot                              One day in the city of computer wold, Doctor Stella was thinking on how much she would love to have someone to accompany her to Nevada to the Science Center Contest.                                                                           Her daughter Stephanie and son Adrian went with her to Building shop and saw some one throwing away a broken toy. It was hard to tell what it was from a distance, but when they got closer they saw it was a broken robot named 3-pio. They begged their mother if she could fix it but she said,'No, it is to old and rusty'.                                                                                                      Later when they were leaving, Adrian snuck the robot in his mothers purse. When they got home he snuck the robot into his room and started trying to fix it. His mother called him so he put the robot in the sun where he thought no one would find it. But Stephanie found the robot and told her mother. Stella was furious with Adrian for taking the toy home, but he told her that he would take good care of it if she would just fixed it.                         Stella came out the room with the robot in her hand and turned on a switch that made the robot come alive, the robot asked Adrian who had brought him here? Adrian said that he did so the robot told Adrian that he was his master and he would obey Adrian's every command. Adrian's mom told him that when he dies out of energy to just put him in the sun. One day 3-pio told Stella if he could come with her to the science center contest. Stella said,' That she would be thrilled for him to come.'                                          A couple days later              Stella tells him to stay calm when we enter the Science Center ,but when he got in he couldn't believe what he was seeing. He kept asking Stella to buy him things but at the end when they got home Stephanie and Adrian were screaming at their mom for buying him everything he wanted and she didn't buy them anything.                      3-pio came out and told them that he was sorry that he didn't get them anything, and said he would share with them. But Adrian screamed at 3-pio and told him that he didn't want his stinking stuff that he bought. But finally Stella said,' Kids remember that hes just a robot and he knows no better than we all do so leave him alone and Adrian go take 3-pio to get some sun', but when Adrian got a second to be alone with 3-pio he told him to leave.                     3-pio left with a broken heart and kept running to were he found a spot to stay there was a little boy named Luis, he told Luis that if he ever needed help that he come back. When Luis came to talk to 3-pio he was  gone he was so sad but, Luis understood that 3-pio was going back home with his family.                                  Soon later Adrian told his mom what he had said. She told him that he did very wrong and that now he was going to have to find him soon because it was going to rain. Adrian never found him until........ one day after it rained and found 3-pio on the ground dripping wet, he told his mother to fix him. She came out with him. Adrian told 3-pio he was sorry and that he would never let him leave again.                    But one day when 3-pio was walking around the neighborhood he saw a little boy that looked just like Luis. When he got closer the little boy ran to him and hugged him. Luis told him that his family had died and that he was looking for him. 3-pio told him that he could stay in his home with his family. When they got home the family welcomed Luis to the family. Luis told 3-pio that he had never felt this much love before. The entire family celebrated that  3-pio came home and the new family member Luis.                                            The End

By Courtney Austin                  Hey Patty, Greg and I were thinking it would be to have a pet so we are going to the store to get one.So they were at the store they looked and looked but they didn't see anything we all liked. So we went to a new store called Robot Pets.The store had every thing from seals to a dog with puppies.The store was having a very big sale every thing was a dollar. We each had a a dollar so we got our own pet.My sister patty chose a dog and her 3 puppies cause you got puppies with the mother for free.My brother chose a dinosaur.I chose a litter of 6 kittens with the mother.We all got supplies for our pets.          Patty got a 3 pound bag of  battery puppy chow.She got a 3 story dog house,4 leashes,and a very big dogy bed.She had her friends help get each a name.She paid for her stuff and took her stuff to Greg's SUV.She named the momma dog LUCKY the 3 puppies SPOT, MILK SHAKE,and SADYE.          Greg called his dinosaur   .He got a bag of raw battery meat that did not last long.He got a XXX LARGE HARNESS,a big Dino house ,and a very very very big Dino bed.His Dino had to go out side in the back yard because he could not behave.Hey now he knows why the cashier suggested the name mischief.He almost got ridd of him but while he was at school i trained mischief. Item_Response: 6th Grade Scientist Drew           Scientist Drew was finishing up his robot, when he makes a mistake. The mistake was that he puts the red and the blue wire together. When he was suppose to put the blue and the green wire together. When that happens his robot comes to life. He is so astonished he faints. Before his robot can ask any questions about why he is alive. When Drew faints his robot catches him before he fall on the floor and puts him on his bed.          When Drew awakens he sees his robot looking at him and names his robot Starr. The next day Drew goes to school. While he is doing his work, he thinks that he should modify his robot. So that it can do his homework, so then he can have more time to himself. At lunch at school he starts making ideas so that he can modify the robot when he gets home. He starts thinking I should make two slits, so that one can be were you put two pieces of paper and one so that the finished work comes out.          When he gets home he starts modifying the robot. He puts two slits one that gets two pieces of paper. The other slit would be for the other work. He puts a computer chip. So then the work will be correct. Then he puts in a piece of paper for a handwriting sample.          The next day he gets homework, so he decides to see if Starr works. It works!!!!! When he gets to school he is so happy he blurts is out to his friend Jason. Jason believes it and wants Drew to prove it to him. Drew proves it to his friend by using his homework. Jason tells Leena, that doesn't like either one of them. To make them sad she tells the teacher and the teacher believes Leena. The teacher makes a house visit and questions Drew about the robot. Drew tells the truth about Starr, because he doesn't like to fib to people and Drew's mom tells him has to destroy, because he is cheating. So then Drew takes out the computer chip and destroys the robot with a sledge hammer.                                         THE END!!!!!

Item_Response: The helping Robot!       Robots can be a big help and they can also   save people if there hurt. Robots can actually   do anything. Even helping the earth.           There was this odd thing on the road picking up trash. So, of course I would walk to it , slowly. I went behind a bush next to it. I couldnt believe my eyes. it was a machine like a robot cleaning the road. To me it looks like a metal trash can. Is it?       It saw me. It spoked. He said 'My name is Trashy , I clean up the earth , I got hit by a lightning bolt. Then all of sudden i was alive.' I thought i was dreaming but no I wasnt. 'Then how do u know how to speak,clean,and walk. I can see you have legs and arms and thats creepy but still how?' I asked. He sat next to me and explained 'I guess im this some type of robot now that knows to do everything, just how you learned to do things when you were a kid, I did also. I been like this for one year. I guess your new here because you never seen me before.' I was silent for a minute and I guess this isnt a dream, its real. I was in real life. Talking to a robot!       He told me about how he got legs and arms. Someone attached those to his body. After he told me facts about all the robots he knows. One robot he told me about was Mr.Gover. That robot helps the doctors and nurses in the hospital. It brings them medicine so they can do there more important jobs. Then theres Gemini-Scout, who works in mines under the ground. The robot is less then two feet and has wheels. Its strong though, if someone is hurt he can drag them to safety. Gemini also carries food,water, and other supplies. Dante 2 has a very risky job. That robot goes in volcanoes to get information. He has 8 legs to climb up the steep and rocky ground. Its also built to survive VERY hot heat!       Trashy wished he had a very important job. 'You do!' I said 'you have the most important job. If you never clean up our earth then animals die, it would stink, but it would mostly look like a Dump. You save lives, you save animals lives or babies too. They dont know what to eat and if they run from there parents and they dont know, the babies would eat it, and probally die. Your job is important and helpful.' Trashy never thought of it that way. He always wondered why did he get made it to this robot can afterall. was it a lesson? Though he wasnt a big help before. Even when he wasnt alive he only had trash put inside of him, he never did anything except keep the animals away. 'your right!' trashy yelled, 'I am helpful and if i never were alive this world would be actually a trashcan. Where people just throw stuff away and dont care!'. 'correct' i announced.       We learned about robots, helping the earth, and cheering up friends. Theres hundreds of robots people build today. They keep us company and help out. Robots are fascinating in every way. Today we invented many things, but not a lot of robtos. Dont you think we should?, I do!

Item_Response: Human Robot       One lovely after noon n the great city of Paris something fell from the sky. One Tourist shouted, 'Whats that!? Another man said,' Im not quite sure'. Then a brave police officer said,' Lets go check it out'. So him and some other people started aprroching the strange thing. All of a sudden the mysterious thing started to move. Every one jumped back and started running.       The creature sat up in confusion. Then the Brave policemen called for back up. He had told the policeman that a wierd and mysterious 'thing' had crashed into the ground on Maine Street. When the brave policemen saw the 'thing', he then realized it wasnt so much as a thing ,but a 'Robot' from Space!       When the other police man orrived they all surrouded the 'Robot'. They wern't what to do. The 'Robot' had arrived in a little tiny rocketship, that looked verry futurisct. While the policemen were talking on what to do they heard a strange noise.       They looked over and saw the robot standing up. Then the 'Robot' spoke 'Hello I come in piece'. I bring no harm  to your planet'. ' I come from the planet of  JitSu.   The police man stood there in shock. One police man responded,' What is your name 'Thing'. 'Just call me Ribit' said the 'Robot'. 'Sure thing' said the cop. 'I came here just to studies about your Planet Earth.       The cop said,' How about I make you a deal? 'What kind of deal? said Ribit.' We give you all the information about Earth that we have, if you give us all the information you have about your Planet JitSu'.'Deal', said Ribit. 'One day you can even come visit my planet if you would like to'. That would be a pleasure',  the cop responded. ' I most go now, my people need me' said Ribit. 'Good luck and goodbye.'       So from then on they kept trading information about their planets. This made them very intellegent on eachothers planet and universe. This helped scientist learn a lot more that lovely year in Paris.       THE END

Item_Response: Amazing Robots           Today we think of robots as inventions of the future. Robots actually have many interesting jobs and some dangerous jobs. Their is some robots that can save lives like a superhero , robots used in mines for search-and-rescue or can be used to play video games in the mine, and their is even a self-driving car that lets you take a nap while the car is moving. With all of these all of these robots the everything would be so awesome.           One of my favorite robots is the Google car. It's a self-driving car that can even let you take naps, drive up to 700 miles per hour, it can talk to you, it also has a laser mounted on the roof, and the best part is that it can transform into a transformer! It is the best car their is. This car is possibbly the best car you can get mainly because it can turn into a transformer. Okay the transformer part might not be true but everything else is.           The next best robot is Mr. Gower. Its a robot that helps doctors everywhere save lives. In the hospital it helps doctors and nurses bring medicine to patients. Mr. Gower looks like a cabinet on wheels. It can ride in elevators, steer through hallways, and move things that are around 500 pounds! Mr. Gower might sound like a boring robot but outside the hospital he's a superhero. He doesn't just save lives in hospitals he also saves lives be defeating super villans, and stopping crime fighters.           Another robot that's pretty cool is the Gemini- Scout. While at work in the mines Gemini-Scout does search-and-rescue missions. This robot is about two hundred feet tall with wheels. When this robot rescues two miners these two miners can use the robots two-way radio to talk to a search and rescue team or just make prank calls. When the miners are on break they can play with the robots built in game system. This robot even has games that lets the miners jump into the game. Don't you think that's awesome because I do.            As you all know robots are pretty cool. You might of seen some pretty cool robots before but I assure you nothing can top these awsome robots. You got a car that can turn into a transformer, a robot that's can save lives working at a hospital or as a superhero, and a robot that works as a search-and-rescue robot in mines or used to play videogames at the end of the day. If I had one of these robots it would be so awesome but you know that's mot going to happen.

Item_Response: One morning a twelve year old kid named, Jake was walking in the park whe all of a sudden a big  box appear front of Jake. Jake look all the ways but people were just walking, using their cell phones, sitting on the grass, etc. but none of theme seem to notice the box not even the people that pass next to Jake. Jake got the box that weight a lot.             When Jake was at his home's backyard he open the weird box and back off amazed of what he saw in the box. He got in he knees and got a 5ft gold cube with a blue circle in the top face of it. He click it and weird noises. Then a golden robot with blue eyes came out of cube that had diissapear.             The 7ft tall robot open his metallic mouth and said,'I am GCR-2025.' Jake run away in horror into his house. Jake watch GCR-2025 carefully and then the robot saw Jake and toward him ready to smash Jake then Jake the robots eyes weren't blue they were red.             Jakes 5 last seconds of life were weird. All heard was his mom telling him,'Jake,Jake' then Jake woke up and he was on bed. Then Jake remember he need to go to the park to visit his grandma. At park Jake was walking with his grandma joking but Jake stop he couldn't move he saw a big box some feet in front of him and said to himself,'not this time.' and continue walking with his grandma ignoring the box.

Item_Response: 'My Robot'                   When I was 6 years old, I had a disease. It kept me from walking, and so, I set out on my journey.   My journey was to find a way to help me get around better, but I knew my time was running out. I had to act fast, or soon, my legs wouldn't support me, and I would have to be stuck in bed, or worst, be in the hostpital, having surgery on my legs, that would take them away from me forever.        The next day, I packed my bags, and set on my journey, alone. I was frightened, but I knew, if I was to make it threw this, I would have to keep going. My wheel chair was quite new, but it would not last me forever. I found myself in a world full of people, of what seemed to be, rumiging threw the most horrific smell I have ever smelled in my life. It seemed to be trash, or some type of old, and disgusting food, that had been left out for days at a time. But I remembered that I had packed my food, and so I wouldn't have to go begging at the doorsteps of the cruel neibors, that lived in the huge hotels of the city.         As for the poor, I felt more at home with them, they were conciderate, and understood my oppinions towards the 'High Rancked' people in the hotels. I was still on my journey, but I had to delay it, for I knew that I had to help the poor. So, I gave them the few dollars I had left over from  my pocket money. It wasn't much, but they were grateful.          When I got back on track with my journey, I now had to hurry, it was getting dark, and I was still looking for a place to take shelter. Thats when I met 'Gemini-Scout'. He was a robot that stood no more than two feet tall, and was as strong as 25 men commbined into one! He took me inside his home, which was not much, but I didn't care, all I wanted was to commplete my journey. He knew how desperrate I was, and he knew how much I really wanted to commplete my journey, so we made a compremize. He was to take care of me, while I was to take care of him. All he had ever really wanted, was to look after someone, but no matter where he looked, there would be no one to look after. And no mater where he went, he never really found what he was really looking for.          So, ever since that day, he has been living with me, in my own hotel, where we feed the poor everyday, and make sure we take care of one another. He is 'My Robot.                                                                                      -foreverways-                                                                                                                              BY: Amanda F. Martin

A scientist named Frankendoodlestien made a robot named Mr. Gower who was made to help at hospitals so the doctors didnt have to do as much.           Mr. Frankendoodlestien was very proud of himself, but then the robot was goin out of controll! The scientist tried to stop him but the robot smacked him in the face and he went flying through a wall!           Then the robot noticed the hole in the wall and he headed straight for it. When they arived at the hospital all of the sudden he turned into his last personality. A man who was a little bit mentaly challenged and did not like other people. So he ran into the hospitals' bathroom and locked himself in there. Then the nurse found out that was the robot Mr. gower they were suposed to get. Item_Response: Robots everywhere are making a difference and they are suprising people every day. Some are helping to save lives,some are doing research for scientists,and some are even playing with children which could be very helpful.         First we have the Gemini-scout. This little fella is less than two feet tall an can save lives. He is a search and rescue robot that works in mines. He can carry water and food to the injured and he can drag the injured to safety this little robot is very strong.         Second is the robot Dante 2 who has a pretty cool job. He gets to go in volcanos and gathers information for scientists. He has eight legs like an arachnid to help him climb up the steep spewing mountains. Dante 2's body is specially created t withstand extreme heat so he wont melt. He looks for vents and hole in the volcano and studies the gases to help out. Humans wouldn't have as much information on volcanos.          Third is Mr. Gower this robot helps doctors and nurses by getting and carrying medication. This friendly robot is also very stong he can carry over 500 pounds and he runs on batteries which can be charged for two hours he can go twelve hours nonstop this robot can also talk and say things like 'your delivery is here.' and 'calling elavator?'         Agribots are next and these robots are little farmers that grow plants by themselves. If a plant is dry he'll water it. They alo know what colors fruits are to pick them if they are ripe. These could help on a farm.         Next the google car this robot is a car that drives itself. This car knows when ther are drivers coming into their lane and if some one is cutting them of. It knows when to stop at a red light and when go when it's green. This car has actually been tested on freeways and highways in California and Nevada.          Last but not least play robots that can actually play wth children. There is not a specific name for this robot because there are many. One of these robots HRP-4c can actually dance and sing, I bet that will keep your child busy.           Robots are being created and are helping and assisting every where soon these robots may be in your house. Some save lives, some play with children,and some do research these are amazing things that should be known and I hope they soon will be.

Item_Response: The Robots       Once opon a time, in a neighborhood where everyting is just so...perfect. Nothing wrong ever happens there, everybody loves to be at that place because its just so peaceful and everyone is very respectful. But, there's one family in the neighborhood that stands out, there the unquie ones, everybody gets scared when they come by, everyone just stares as they walk,their mouths open so big that not even an ant can crawl under. But the reason why they are so afraid of them so much is because they aren't like the ones in the neighborhood, there not humans. Insted of having skin, heart, and blood running through your body there body is made out of metal. They don't have to breath or eat to survive. But yet they can still do the same things that humans can do and even more. They are robots the only family that there is on earth. There's a father, mother, a son, and a daughter. Item_Response: When Apollo 11 landed on the moon, the astronauts saw something extrodanary. They saw these metal machines that seemed to be living there for a while. They brought one of these back for NASA. NASA told them that they could not tell anyone of their amazing discovery and the space program made the dicovery top secret and classified.       Ever since Apollo 11 landed on the moon, they sent more and more humans to the moon to get more machines. They decided to call these machines 'Robots'. They brought so many robots from the moon to earth, NASA and the US goverment decided to sell these robots into the US trade center. Sales were booming and everyone wanted a robot of their own. Everyone has a robot. The goverment trained the robots to do everyday things like sing, dance, play, and take care of kids while their parents are gone. The other countries all over the world envy the US and decide to go to the moon to get some of their own.       Some countries like Russia, Germany, and Japan have launched their own sapce programs to get robots for their own. The United States decided to race all these countires back the moon. The race started on May 15, 2972474. One man helped the US build their space sho called the SS Atlantis. This mans name is Danious Ceasrai. This man was a german man who moved to america in late 2972473. Danious made this ship so that it was fast as the speed of light times 99999999. His bosses names were Frenchious Fabulous, and Madious Masterious. They were robots and had expirience in space before.       They told Danious 'build a ship that will never be forgotten'. This inspired him to make the best ship the world has ever seen in the un iverse and go get some robots before the other nations of the Earth do. He would lead his crew to the moon and back on a mision to bring bak the most robots. Fortunatly for him, he got there a year before everyone. While he was there, he trained some of the robots to be soldiers and fight off the Russians and Germans and Japanese.   He trained these robots very well and they were loyal to him. When the germans came, the germans were not prepared for war and rushed back to earth. The japanese came also unprepared and rushed back. Last but not least the Russsians came with guns and laser cannons to fight off the robots and win the victory aaginst the Americans.       It was a long and cold galactic war over control of the moon. The russians fought hard but the robots fought harder and beat the russians. the russian general Jonious Beadious accepted his loss and retured home to russia. Danious became a hero and became the leader of the moon army. No one ever judged his power and no one ever fought him again,.

Item_Response: I had the weirdest experience last week with my Xbox. Not playing it, but it literally 'playing' with me. Last Tuesday I was minding my own  business playing Call of Duty: Black Ops 2 quickscoping people like a boss, and being the complete MLG PRO I am I decided to quickscope using a Diamond Thermal Scope DSR-50 with Fast Mag. Then, weird stuff happened. Everyone else in the game lagged out, and me being the host I had no idea why the game did not switch hosts (or why they would) or restart the game. I was forever alone, quickscoping walls on the map Turbine, when my controller started rumbling like crazy. It felt like my controller was having a seizure, so I thought I would take it to the hospital (Gamestop) and then my Xbox turned off. My brain derped and I was totally confused. Then, I saw my Xbox grow legs and arms from my four controllers and some extra wires. Then, he started talking.       My Xbox called himself 'Serial#XXTHISISNOTREALXXSKNCVM1235433' I was really confused with his name and therefore there would be no way my awesome and all-mighty brain would remember it, so I just named him 'Nug.' From the start, I knew Nug and I would be best buddies. Me and Nug went everywhere together, I took him to go get candy (he couldn't eat it because Xboxes can't eat candy so I basically got twice the sugary and teeth rotting delights). I took him to get ice cream. And I took him to school the next day. People tried to steal him but he went beast mode and protected himself. From that point on, I knew he learned a lot from my awesome skills on video games. I sat down at my table with my homies Justin, Ryan, Lucian, and Jake (pronounced haw-kay), and they were confused. Justin asked 'Mishan what are you doing with your Xbox? How obsessed have you gotten?!' I said 'My Xbox came alive and we are best bros.' Ryan said 'You really had to take it to school?' I came back with 'My Xbox was a him, and yes I had to. My grandma hates technology.' Jake said 'Good idea, but won't your grandma be bored all alone?' I said 'Well, she's like that everyday. Also Xbox (who I named Nug) really loves me. We're as good friends as you and I are.' Then, after a long day of school I went to my after-school place Learning Edge. The Asians (the place is probably 90% Asian) there have probably not seen an Xbox before, nor have they met one like Nug. It was a silent day, but a fun one. Nug helped me with my homework because he had the internet on his side! Then I walked home, and something went weird.       Nug told me that he loved me. I said that I loved him too (not in any homosexual manner, but more of a friend way). He started getting a bit too close to me, but I was fine with it. It was probably the first time he had ever crossed streets. Cars scared Nug and he always seemed to bark at them. I don't know why he did that, but he is himself, and with his ¾ full memory unit, he was getting a little crazy. I was fine with that though. I told Nug my deepest secrets on the way home, and he promised not to tell anybody. When I told him that I liked a girl though, something went wrong.       Nug started to short circuit, and the turn-on button turned red. I asked him if he got the 'Red Ring of Death' and he said 'NO.' I have to admit, someone as manly and good looking as me got a little bit freaked out, but of course I always know when something is wrong. He grew bigger, and bigger, and bigger, and of course, even bigger, untill he was officially considered to me as 'Bigger than my ego.' And that is really big. Nug started smashing stuff and exclaiming 'NUG ANGER!!!' Nug was really pissed, I could tell. Usually when people get mad, they get mad. This, was bigger than mad. All this destruction of the town of South Pasadena, just because I told him I liked a girl. This looked like a job for, Hobonugget! Defender of all and the ultimate winner of everything. Who was this majestic Hobonugget? Me. I ripped off my shirt and started flying into the air. I gave Nug a huge slap that sounded like 'Smackle' and a giant punch that sounded like 'Fap!' Then, Nug fell to his knees (or extention cords), and died. We all knew, I was way too good for him.       I fixed the city. I bought a new Xbox. I got more girls loving me (they were all rejected by me nicely, but still I have them in my mind just in case they are ever 'needed.' Lastly, I replayed all of my video games and learned to not be as much of a good quickscoper. I was talking to my friend Desmond about this, and he believed me and responded to what happend in two words. Screw logic. We all had a good laugh, and had a good time, but there was one thing that didn't end well. Nug died. At least there were no casualties and there was nothing destroyed but El Pollo Loco. With Nug's enlarged parts, they were able to sell the parts of Nug to Microsoft and made millions of dollars. This is also the story of how El Pollo Loco became a huge resteraunt chain. They expanded with the money they made from Nug. And for Hobonugget, he will save the day again, not today, tommorrow, but some other day.

Item_Response: once a pone a time a robot came alive. His name was Bobby. I was training him to help people and do what I tell him to do such as get me a drink or get me a snack. So one day I asked him to get me a drink so he went down to the kitchen to get me a drink.But he never came back.  He has been down there for 5 minutes already. So I decided to holler to him,so I yelled Robby where are you. There was no response, so I hollered again. Then I heard glasses and cups breaking and being thrown. Then I decided to go down there. When I got down there Robby was freaking out there was glass everywhere. So I  said whats wrong. He didn't answer. So I decided to take his battery's out. When I did that he stopped freaking out. So I started to think why he was doing that. Item_Response: I was walking in the darkness searching for house materials. I had a flashlight on my hand and started searching. There was a huge machine I found on the ground. It was a robot made in Japan. I took it home to clean it and fix it. I felt really curious about what type of robot it was and what kind of job or thing it does. There were a lot of butterflies in my stomach just to show this to my mom. And I know that she will be really surprised when she sees this really creative and smart robot.       I dragged the robot home to clean it and to fix it. All of a sudden, my mom came and her mouth was wide open. She froze for a minute. I knewsomething great and surprising was going to happen. All of a sudden like a thunderbolt, my mom said, 'What is that?! Is that a not useful robot or what?!' I didn't want this to happen to my mom, I wanted her to be very proud of me and be very excited. This is important because she was asking what type of robot it was. Then she said, 'Dint' I tell you to bring house matericals?' This is important because this means that I forgot about the house materials. Careless.       After that happened, I started examinating the robot. All of a sudden, it rapidly woke up and started to go outside to pick apples out of my tree. I said, ' This robot is an agribot! It's a robot that picks fruit.' This is important because agribots can help us pick fruits so that we don't have to pick them. To be honest, we were actually lazy so we were commanding the robot to do our job instead of us, just like a slave. My mom said , 'Oh my goodness! Wow, this robot is really useful!' This is important because this made her happy and froget about the house materials.       Now, since we have the agribot, we didn't have to buy expensive food anymore! Now we can just use the agirbot for searching for fruits and picking them! My mom said, 'This is a very smart robot! I think we should stay home everyday!' I knew she would be really happy and I actually wanted this to happen. This means that she is really happy and she would use the robot everyday. I said, 'This is the happiest day of my life!' No words can explain how happy and excited I was. This means that I was very lucky and I was very happy to have this robot.       This agribot was very useful for me and my family. If my mom haven't told me to go search for house materials in the darkness, I wouldn't have gotten this happy. I was very lucky to bring that robot home.

Item_Response: It's Alive                                      All of a sudden I just felt a pulse a tingling sensation run down my back.It felt like I had been locked away for years I had cramps all over my body and I couldnt move.I decided to get a look around at my surrondings it looked as though I was in a old dusty room theyre where boxes all around me it looked as though something or somebody had just abandoned theyre stuff.                      I finally gathered up enough of courage to walk and when I did I found what looked to be a hole on the floor,but when I got closer I  realized it was connected to something it was a ladder.I saw a speck of light so,I decided to pull down the ladder and climb down it.When I did I found a room totally diffrent from the room I had just been in.This room was more brighter,more welcoming and for some strange reason I felt at ease.Then I heared someone coming,and I hid behind this bookshelf type thing.When I peeked out theyre was a human staring right at me!I was so scared I had no idea whet to do.                            The human must have been as scared as I was beacause thing i know shes trying to run away from me.If I had enough skill at this whole talking thing I would have tould her I was harmless and just trying to fingd my way home.Actually I dont have a home, or I just dont remember where it is.The human finally got enough courage to come back to where I was and then the strangest thing happened she picked me up,actually held me like I wasnt some kind of monster.It had been three good long weeks since I met this human and she has took me in taught me things I would have never known.She taught me how to talk,read,play and eat.It has been a pretty amazing time with the human I hope I never leave.She is like my family since I never had one.                          I would like to think her for taking me in like a son.I know its not easy having a thing like me living wiht you but she treats me like im normal not a monster.I hope she keeps me for the rest of my life.

Then Sydney picked up the controller and threw it and the car drove over and grabbed it and came back. It was as if a dog took over it's body. We raced home to tell everyone the news. Then it was time to go to sleep but the car had little headlights on the front that worked like eyes and it drove into evey room and it would wake up everybody so my dad put it outside and then it started to bark at the birds. Item_Response: The Robot       It all started when we took a class field trip to the Science Center. 'Come on class it's time to get on the bus,' exclaimed my teacher, Mrs. Dell, as 32 kids piled in to the big yellow school bus. Moments later we arrived at the coolest place ever, the Science Center!     'Welcome to the Science Center,' said a cheerful voice. 'Are you guys ready to see our newest robot,' the class tour guide asked. Screams of joy and excitement burst into the air, we were going to see the very first robot that can be programed to do anything you want. 'Then lets go!,' she said, leading us into a dark room.      'Ladies and gentleman, boys and girls, prepare to see the one and only...T-BOT 5000!,' announced a man with a microphone behind the curtains. Then, the navy blue curtains opened and right there was a five foot tall, black robot with brand new rubber wheels, metal arms and a futuristic face. The class stared for a moment then stood up and started cheering and clapping for this amazing new creation.      'Thank you, Thank you,' said a man walking up onto the stage. 'As you all know, the T-BOT 5000 can do anything you tell it to, watch,' he said, pulling out a remote that looked a bit like an X-box controller, but with letters and many other buttons. 'I am now telling it to go to the cupboard and bring me a water bottle,' he said nervously looking down at the remote. Seconds later, the robot exited the room. We sat on the edge of our seats, egarly waiting for the robots return when suddenly, in came the robot with a water bottle filled with ice cold water. Once again, the class clapped and cheered for the amazing invention. A few tests later, Mrs. Dell told the class we had to go. On the way out, we were given a small key chain that looked just like the robot to remember the awesomestuff we did today.      That night, when I got home, I sat upstairs in my room thinking how amazing it was to see the robot.  'I wish I had my own T-BOT 5000,' I said, looking down at the key chain and suddenly my tiny key chain turned into a real robot! I stepped back and found the remote sitting on my bed, so I picked it up and pressed the letters spelling out 'MAKE MY BED' thinking I had nothing to lose. The robot got to work immediately fluffing my pillows and pulling back my purple covers. 'SO COOL!' I thought ti myself.       The next day when i got home from school I walked in and found T-BOT vacumming! 'Hi honey,' my mom exclaimed, 'I found this in your room making your bed for you I looked around and found the remote and thought I'd try it out!,'      'Ok,' I said laughing, then skipped up the stairs to my room. It was pretty cool having a robot to do anything you want.      Later that day, I went outside to shoot hoops and T-BOT came too. Turns out, he's a pretty good basketball player!

It could play with pets, clean up after you, or simply be your best friend. But there was something really strange about this robot.       My robot and I were playing in the backyard and something really strange happened I went inside to get a glass of water and i came back out and my robot was gone. Without thinking I started to panic.  I ran inside and screamed 'DAD! DAD! THE ROBOTS MISSING!'   We looked for hours but we still couldnt find him. The next day came and we still couldnt find the robot. Another day went by. Than another.       Before I knew it a week flew by and we still couldnt find him. One afternoon I was outside walking my dog and I heard someone in the bush. I thought it was just a bird so I just put my headphones back in and continued walking my dog. The next day came and I was outside was my dog again and i heard the same noise from the same bush so I started to walk faster. I heard it again and I ran all the way home. I didn't think much of it because i thought it was an animal or something, so I didn't tell anyone. But, boy was I wrong.         The next day came and i still heard the same noise from the same bush. I just continued walking. The next day came by and i still kept hearing that noise from that same bush. Then another came by and I still kept hearing and ingoring it. Two weeks flew by and i still heard it.          One Afternoon, I was out just walking around, I passed by that bush and i heard a the noise so without thinking, I looked over at that bush and I found a... a... A ROBOT! Not just any robot, OUR robot! I was so happy. I picked him up, but i don't think this was our robot. It was a little smaller, it looked like a human five-year-old. Than someone tapped me on the shoulder. I couldn't beleive it. IT WAS OUR ROBOT FOR SURE!             We all went home. Then something really strange happened. Our robor, our robot kid ( I quess), and I were all sitting out in the living room when all the sudden, our robot turned into a human. The little kid turned into a ROBOT! WHAT?! Without really thinking I jumped and hug him. I don't know why I did what I did. But, then they said that he and the little kid had to go and thats the last time I saw our robot or the little kid.

I put the oven on and put  him in it. He melted! I was so happy! Even though I was grounded for a year because I broke the oven. Well at least now I know not to put metal in the oven! From that day forward we never saw a robot again.

By: Alexandra Szurna            Once again I had the WORST day at my new school in Detroit, MI i moved here from Ludington, MI on Saturday. I started going to school here on Monday of this week and its only Thursday. I have made one friend since I've been here. It's not been easy I can tell you that right now! So I'm walking home alone and I see a house, the house everybody only talks about. Supposedly he is a crazy inventor that lives by himself and everybody says that he killed his wife. But I don't believe any of it! So like I said i was walking his and I saw a little blue head sticking out of a trash can. Now it wasn't a human head it was a robot head? I took it out, there was a note on it. I read it aloud, 'YOU MAY FIND BUT DO NOT SEEK, YOU MAY GO BLIND YOU WILL BE WEAK!' I took the robot guy home, letting the note fall to the ground. What I didn't notice was the old man watching me through his window.        I call Stacy-my new friend-over to look at this.        'I bet I could get 10 bucks out of the guys at our school for this,' I told Stacy.        'Where did you get that?!?' Stacy yelled. I was more alarmed than anything else.        'Um that old guys house,'        'AAAAGGGGHHHH! You can't steal from him! He'll kill you and eat you up like he did to his wife!'        'It was in his trash can with a little note attached to it,'        'What did the little note say?!?'        'It said you may find but so not seek, you may go blind you will be weak,'        'It was a WARNING!'        'I don't care, you're no fun,' I said pushing her out the door.        'Hey! I'm not supposed to be home until dinner at 6!'        'Whatever,' I said slamming the door in her face.        I walked up into my room to get the robot. But when I went up there the robot was walking around the room. He was shooting lasers; the rhyme was making sense, you may find, but do not take! You may go blind from the lasers. But why would you go weak?        The next morning I found out the meaning of you may go weak. I, tired as could be, walked down the stairs yawning every other minute. When I got to school I had drank enough coffee to barely keep me awake. I had also realized I had forgotten the robot at home. Great I forgot the robot and the boys are actually looking at me; wait a minute the boys are looking at me?        'Stacy!!! Where are you?!? STACY!?!'        'I don't want to talk to you!' Said Stacy at her locker.        'What? Why? What did I ever do to you?!?'        'Um, I don't know? Does last night ring a bell?'        'Oh yeah sorry about that. Um you're probably never gonna forgive me are you?'        'You know I shouldn't forgive you but I told you at the beginning of this week that I would give you 3 strikes. You now have 2 okay?'        'Yes, I know, I promise I will be a better friend!'        'Strike 2,'        'What why?!?' I asked        'Just kidding. Don't be so hard on yourself okay?'        'Um, right, hehe. Let's go to class, we're gonna be late,'        'Okay, come on!' I started running after her.        At 3:40 I was on my way home from school. When I got home, and I walked in, something about my house was different. What is so different about my house? I asked myself. Then it hit me. My house was CLEAN! Did I ever mention that I have 4 little siblings? 2 twin little brothers and 2 twin little sisters. Well with 4 three-year-old's running around your house, it's NEVER and I mean NEVER going to be clean. My siblings must still be at day camp-a camp and daycare for 2-5 year-old's. And my mom must have taken the day off to clean.        'MOM!' I yelled 'MOM!' I yelled again 'MOM! I'M HOME!' I yelled for the last time.        'SORRY HUN, I DIDN'T HEAR YOU!' She walked downstairs holding Fifi my mom's beloved miniature poodle that hates my ever since I tried to drown her after she ate my favorite barbie dress-what I didn't know is that dogs-poodles-could swim. She growled at me.        'Oh shut-' I started        'Megan-' my mom started        'Okay, okay. You know that when the twins get here their just gonna wreck the house right?'        'Wait you didn't clean the house Megan?'        'No, why? You didn't?' I gulped        'No? But I do know who did clean the house,'        'Who?' Before she could answer I sprinted up the stairs to find the robot playing with the twins.        'This-is-great-fun,' the robot said        'Who are you?' I asked the robot.        'I-am-Robbie-the-babysitting-and-cleaning-robot-I-have-come-to-help.'         'Cool,' I said, 'Now I don't have to babysit them!!!' I walked into my room with the biggest smile EVER on my face, humming a song the twins also sing.        That was my story on 'OMG MY ROBOTS ALIVE!' I hoped you liked it! Thanks for reading!       - Lexi

Item_Response: One day in Paradise, Ohio, there was a little boy named Anthony was sitting on his dusty doorstep. He was thing to himself, 'Why does Ohio have to be so boring? I want to change the world by showing them a little Ohio boy can be smart too!' So that's just what he did. (After he watched a few episodes of MicGuiver) The little boy found his old backpack, packed some clothes, and a couple of ham and cheese sandwiches.                                                              10 YEARS LATER...         'Sir, the robot is ready for the awakening.'          'OK I'm on my way make sure the batteries are ready.'           'Will do sir.' came the reply         'I have done it,' thought Anthony, 'At the age of 18 I have created the worlds first robot. I proved a little boy from Ohio can do it.' He thought as he stood up. He started to walk to the awakening of the robot to see if he really did do it.        When Anthony got there, the room was packed full of scientists who were here to watch the awakening of the robot. 'This is it, the moment you all have been waiting for! A change in the Earth's history, the first ever robot!' Everybody clapped. Then all got silent. Anthony walked over to the table and looked at the robot. Then he carefully placed the battery inside and turned the robot on with the flick of a switch.                                              'BOOM'        The room went silent as a cloud of smoke filled the room. All of the sudden the room cleared. Anthony looked at the robot and saw... That it had worked! A small Ohio boy had actually created a robot! This was the happiest day of Anthony's life.        'So what does it do?' asked one scientist        'What's it's name?' asked another scientist        'This robot is called... Mr.Gower! This robot will work in hospitals and help doctors and nurses deliver medicine to patients who need it. This robot will run on batteries and after charging this robot for two hours you will be able to use this robot for twelve straight hours without stopping. This robot is also programmed to say hundreds of phrases. I will also be working on making other  robots that will help in mines, help us study hard and dangerous places such as volcanoes, pick fruit and help farmers, and much, much more. 'Does anybody have name requests? If so write them on this piece of paper and turn them in. I look forward to seeing you all at our next meeting, but first, who wants to try out my robot first?' Lots of hands shot in the air. While they were trying out the robot Anthony decided to take a look at the requested names. He took a few out of the big pile.       1) Gemini Scout       2) Dante 2       3) Agribots        Anthony thought to himself 'This road that I am heading down, is going to be a long, but fun, trip.                                                            THE END

Item_Response: The Museum Surprise       'I'm so excited!' I said on the way to the Gerald R. Ford Museum.My friend Athea,and I were on our way to the Museum for the day.It was sunny,but not that hot.'Were here!' said Athea.That's when our day got crazy.       'I'll pick you guys up in 3 days!' said my Mom.We ran inside and went to the robot section first.'Cool!' we all said at the same time.'Look!' Athea said.It was a time machine!We all looked at it in fascination,then a tourist said 'DON'T TOUCH!'.He looked at us sternly,'Ill be watching you....'.       'Lets go.' I said.Athea started walking away.'Hey!Where are you guys going?'.I walked under the rope,Athea following me,we put our hands on the machine.'NO!!!!!!!'said the tourist guy....then blackness.       'Uggg....Athea?'I said,'Where am I?!?!'.I was in a hospital bed.On the right was Athea.I looked at the calendar across the room...'3015?!?!?' I thought.'Your medication is here' said a voice,it came in the room.'AAAHHHHH!!!!!!!'.We  screamed.A doctor came in and said'Whats going on here!?'       'Where are we?!?!' said Athea.'Were in 3015!!!' I said.'Calm down girls!' said the doctor,'I'm Doctor Doughnut and this is Mr.Gower,hes a robot.'.'I'm going to tell you how you got here.'       'We got an emergency call from our ambulance saying some little girl found Ms.Athea on the sidewalk on the way to school.She was also in a concussion.Then two boys came in the hospital carrying Ms.Hailey.They said they found her on their bike ride on the bridge.It was weird though because they were in the hospital a week ago.'       'Wait!!' said Athea,'My boyfriend went missing a week ago, so was Hailey's.'.She put a smug smile on her face.'HES NOT MY BOYFRIEND!!!!!!!!' I said blushing,'what were their names?'.He looked at us weirdly.'James Perez and Phillip Youngman,their here now if you want to see them...Mr Gower,go get James and Phillip please.'       'Athea!' James said,'how did you get here?'.'James!'.Athea started crying because she was worried that he was gone forever.'Phillip?!' I said,'how did you guys get here?'.He looked at me worried,'the same way you guys did.'.He looked mad,'Its was that STUPID time machine!'.       'We need to get out of here!' James said softly,'Phillip and I found out in 72 hours all the robots are going to turn evil and kill every human in this time!' He said not to softly this time.'Then we need to find a time machine...quick.'       'Athea.Athea.ATHEA!!' I said.'Heres your clothes,Phillip and James are waiting.'.We go out into the hallway,'Hide!' whispered Athea.We run out into the night,James and Phillip grab their bikes and Athea and I grab roller blades.'Lets head down Mapple Street,its a short cut to the museum.'.We turn right suddenly...'Hult!'.A Robo-Policeman was standing at the intersection of Mapple and Olive Ave.'Oh no!Keep going straight!' I yelled.       We got away,but we were lost big time.'We need a map or something!That cop could be right behind us!' Athea screamed.'Calm down Athea!' Phillip says.'I have my cell,plus it has a map.' I suggested,'Were in the woods,so we need to go West to get back to Mapple Street.'.We start going west,we make it to Mapple,but something sudden happens.'Hello Hailey'.       'Who is that?' James asks warningly.'Its me,Micheal' says Micheal.He comes out of the alley with a bike.Then we hear sirens,Robo-Police sirens!'RUN!!' yells James.We all dash into the alley.'They're gone,that was close.' says Athea.'Howd you get here.' says Phillip.'A time machine.'.'Guys!Look!!'.It was the museum!       We ran into the museum,found the machine.....ZAP!!!We were back!'Were back!' said Athea and I together.'Hailey?Athea?'.'Mom!!!!' I said,ever so happily.'Glad that over!' said Micheal.We all laughed.

Item_Response: One night I was getting ready for bed. Every night before I go to sleep, I get my favorite toy, my robot. He is very small and he is silver with a little bit of purple on his arms from when I spilt grape juice on him by accident.But when I woke up, I saw that my robot was missing so I looked everywhere for him and I couldn't find him. When I was looking for him, I heard a strange noise in the kitchen so i went to check and i saw my toy robot.             Robot was fixing breakfast. I didn't know if I should've been worried or not. I had thought long and hard about having a real robot in my house. After a long time of thinking, I figured that it would actually be fun to have a real robot at my house because of all the cool things we could do together; i.e., fly everywhere, make anything we want, and we could even have a robot party.             During all of the fun time we had together, I had forgotten all about school and my parents so I had to take my robot to a far, far, far away land known as Mars. It was the hardest goodbye ever because of all the things we did together and we wanted to stay with each other forever. When I got home, I told my dad about my robot and he felt so bad for me that he let me get my robot back. I told him that I would always do my best and that I would always try harder with my robot.

Item_Response: Once there was a Gemini-Scout robot named Billy 1.0. He was programmed to help miners by: checking the air for toxic gas, carries food and water to miners, and dragging the miners out of the mine if he had to.                                                                                                                 The next day Billy 1.0 was activated and something happened, because he realized how sick and tired he was getting from helping miners every single day. About an hour later a new robot named Mr. Gower rolled into the room and said ' here you go, here you go. here you go, here you go!' Billy 1.0 was confused, he asked Mr. Gower why he was talking but was rudely interrupted by Mr. Gower saying 'Here you go, here you go, here you go!' A little while later after hearing the words of Mr. Gower Billy 1.0 finally said 'I hope your batteries die!!!' When Mr. Gower heard this he was infuriated, in fact he was so mad that he exploded!(here is a quick word about Mr Gower, he is programmed to carry medicine to patients and say something like here you go or i am here with your medicine.)                  Billy 1.0 was horrified about that explosion. Billy 1.0 was mad at humans for creating a defective robot, as mad as Billy 1.0 was at Mr. Gower saying 'here you go' over and over again, he did not think that Mr. Gower deserved to explode. At that point Billy 1.0 decided that he would rebel against humans. On the street, when Billy rode by humans he would shine his high powered flash light into their eyes and here them yell bad things at him while they couldn't see. Billy 1.0 also rebelled by taking freshly mined minerals from miners and putting them into missiles that were shot into space to put them on the moon. People and scientists and especially doctors were getting worried. The people were worried they would run into billy 1.0. The doctors were worried because there offices were getting full of blinded patients. And the scientists were worried because they said that they released the robot Billy 1.0 int o the public. So scientists conducted a search for Billy 1.0, scientists thought Billy 1.0 had come to life, pretty much. After a year of terrorizing people Billy 1.0 became careless where he hid himself. So one day the search party found Billy 1.0 and took him back to the lab. At the lab the scientists and technicians fixed and upgraded Billy. To this day Billy became known as Billy 2.0. BUT don't think that is the end because it is most definitely not! After Billy 2.0 was upgraded the scientists added a new feature... that billy 2.0 would blow up if he thought about rebelling. It was late and stormy when they upgraded the feature and forgot to nail on the self destruct bomb. The next day Billy 2.0 was playing in the grass outside of the lab, when a robot bully(don't ask why they made that) popped out of the bushes. It startled Billy 2.0, then he remembered the bomb, the bully made fun of Billy 2.O's scientists that created him. Billy 2.0 got mad and activated the bomb and threw it at the bully thus blowing the bully robot apart. The scientists heard this and ran out side to see what happened. When they saw what happened they laughed because they were trying to find the bully bot. Scientists thought billy 2.0 was a hero and congratulated him. Again something in Billy 2.0 Changed and as fast as Billy 2.0 could he ran over all of the scientists. More scientists came and caught and upgraded him again making him Billy 3.0, that final upgrade was just what Billy needed because after that he went back to helping miners. Scientists are now saying that if Billy 3.0 rebels again that they are blaming Eddy Blarby Jr. because he is a bad technician that nobody trusts. Eddy Blarby Sr. hates all of the scientists because they make fun of Eddy Blarby Jr. so he modified Billy 3.0 to rebel again but it didn't work.
