Item_Response: New Hampshire has brought robots to their limit in 1987. They were designing a robot in Gorham Laboratory of Science for cars or just to have with you in case of emergency. This robot was one foot by one foot and in an emergency it would flash, make noise and set of a signal to the emergency center. These robots did not use cell phone towers or satellites they use sound waves to hide emergency codes.       Well my family was one of the few people to test the robot. This all was because of our crash and no phones worked. So everyone in our family got one and we brought them everywhere. My family has never done something like this before so this was new to all of us.We went swimming with them, they were waterproof and had tracks and we went hiking with them. They were great to have around.        One day we were in crash way off the road. It was horrendous like the truck was going to explode after going a hundred ninety mph strait into the huge pine tree. We were in the top of NH where no one lived so it was not like people would notice. We had no cell service so we pulled out our robots and the did not work.  All the sudden they were after us. We ran and ran we at least had to be going 70 mph and they were right behind us. They were monstrous little things all scary and demanding. finally someone found us because it felt like we had been running for hours. We got home and called the laboratory and told them what happened and they told us it was just a little malfunction but the robots were alive. In the end robots weren't my thing.

Item_Response: 'Gemini-scout on line .' I heard a metallic voice say. 'Wheels on line, thermal camera on line.' That's weird my name was Gemini too, I wonder who was saying my name. All the sudden I started jerking around from left to right as if being controlled by someone or something. I saw one of my own kind, for if you haven't guessed I'm a robot, but there was something wrong with him, he was all rusty and he wasn't moving. A piece of worn, ripped cloth was in his supplies box and he was stuck under a pile of rocks my owners must have knocked down. Before I could help, I started being controlled again and swerved around the pile of rocks to a sleeping... oh, what you call them... humans! A human was stuck half way in the pile of rock. How could anyone fall asleep in a place like that, especially one of those picking humans. Well, I guess I should wake him up, but the thing who was controlling me had other plans. I was forced to nudge him. The human wouldn't budge and if I nudged  any harder my circuits would blow or its head would. 'Testing gas levels, testing gas levels. Testing complete, gas levels low.' I heard the voice say again. I was getting real tired of the voice's attitude, I didn't have gas. I mean I drank gas but I didn't pass it. I tried to take control, but the voice wouldn't let me. Instead it led me through the mines, which I lived in, and to a camp of humans. One of them uttered something to another like,'Stupid machine.' and another, 'Who owns this bucket of rust!' Why I ought to... I was about to teach those guys a lesson when the voice said, ' Opening supply crates.' Wait, no that's my supplies! Stop it, stop it!!! One of the humans walked up to me and said, ' Hey little guy I'm Mo. How about a little touch up, your stating to rust.'                       Hey, what are you doing stop that it tickles! The human named Mo took me into a little tent and started messing with my antenna and my radio and a bunch of other things too. Something obviously went wrong because my monitor went black and I couldn't see a thing. A few minutes later I awoke to see the man watching me. I have to admit it was a little creepy how he was looking at me. I could feel my body was free again, but I heard a rumbling noise. I remembered the last time this happened. All the walls started to cave in and I jumped up and tried to tell the man to follow me. He did! We raced down the caverns and into daylight with a hundred other miners following. Mo bent down, ' I owe you my life little guy how about you come live with me.' He winked at me and I finally trusted him.

Item_Response: I wake up and find my phone. The phone I made myself. My parents died in a car crash when I was six. I was living at Harvard Universety. Apparently I was the only 16 year old there. The principle of the school told me my parents had already paid as if they know I was going to go here. Then there was the fact that I got scholarships. I don't know why I was so smart when it came to technology but whenever I focused on inventing my head felt like it was going to explode.         I went to the main hall and checked the honor roll list. Of course the name Johnathan King was on there. If your wondering thats me. The robots were just sitting there making frozen yogurt for the students. I saw a poster that said Class of 2053, 2 years ago. There was one man who looked like me except he was taller and buff.                 'That was Robert King' the principle came by and told me. 'Very convinient he has the last name as you and was at this universety.' I lived alone my whole life if this guy was related to me I'd actually have a brother or a cousin or something. 'Where does he work now'I asked. 'He's working with Jake Ive, Apples designer.' Apple had been the oldest company ever. Old people told me they had an iPhone which is one of Apples oldest products. These days Apple is making robots.           I skipped all my classes today so I could go find Robert King. He was super smart. He said he created the iBot which was probably the robot made for every specific task. It uses voice command. Then he asked me my name. I told him it. Then he hugged me. He was my brother.          We're working on an intellagience helmet. Then I said a bunch of stuff not even I could understand and my head felt terrible.'Thats brilliant.' He said. Wait your head its extremely red. He told me to go inside a booth. He took an X Ray. Apparently dad had injected an intellagience chip in my head. The camera zoomed nto my head and John grabbed a piece of paper. He told me to leave and I did.          Six months later he came to the Universety and showed me The Intellegience Helmet. He had used the same chip in my head. It was amazing. Apple satrted making more helmets and Robert and I got rich.

Item_Response: The security guard was about to give the keys over to the night guard when the corky scientists told him to wait.'Not again Harold, im eventualy going to leave', the guard sighed. He had been finishing a theory he had thought of. As he ran towards the door to stop the guard from closing it, two liquids got caught on his lab coat and spilt onto a cutting machine. after the night guard locked the door and sat down, he heard a lot of beeping noises. He went to go investegate. When he found where the noise was coming from he was confused. It was a silver machine that was about three feet tall and two feet wide. The beeps and buzzes just kept getting louder and louder. He didnt know what it was or what it was doing but he was scared. As it started to move he dashed to the door and locked it behind him.        About five minutes after the guard left for good, the machine made a ear peircing sound and the whole lab lit up like someone was doing fire works in there. The light and sound ended at the same time and where it seems the source of them both was a totaly different thing. It looked as if it was living. It was still the same color but it appeared as if it had eyes and a mouth. It also had three legs with rollers on the bottom and two arms with big clippers on the end. It first started to spin around in circles and was wrecking everything. Then it raced to the door and and snipped off the the lock and was gone.        It was a new world for the little robot. It rolled into traffic and almost got hit by several cars. It went everywhere and scared off a bunch of people. One of the people called the police but they thought she was crazy. A police officer that was on duty saw it and reported seeing it. This time they knew it was real. The robot went into and alley and just sat there. When it came out there was a bunch of police officers searching in all places they could think of. One of them saw the robot and blew his wistle. The all started chasing after him until it cut through a fence and escaped.        The robot was in the suburbs now And it was the morning. It kept going until the scientist that had accidently created him saw the and was fascinated. He went outside and and tried to pick it up but it was to scared. 'Your a tricky one, arent you', the scientist laughed. He snuck up behind the robot and picked it up. 'Your heavy', he said. He brought the robot inside and set him on th floor. It started to spin around again and break stuff. 'No', harold yelled. He picked it up again and set him in the backyard and left him there.        When he went to work, he came to see a bunch of daw droopped scientist looking at the 30,000 dollars worth of equipment destroyed. 'The night guard wasnt here when i came this morning and all of that stuff was destroyed', the other guard said. All the head scientist including Harold, went to the security room and looked at the tapes. They saw all the stuff happen including Harold breaking the two liquids on the machine[now robot].

Item_Response: There once was an amazing scientist named Charlie Monnroe he made millions of robots to get a better understanding of the meaning of science and what robots are capable of doing.But after time he got very old and dicided to stop making robots but he promissed that he would make one more robot and it was going to be his best one yet.He made the plans, got the parts and he anocced that he was going to make the smartest, most lovable and the strongest robot the world has ever seen.Now all he needed was the robot.He worked twenty four hours a day every day for the next eight months.Finally after all of his hard work it was finished he was so proud.But when he went to turn it on it didnt work so he took the whole thing apart and rebult it with different plans this time.He prayed for it to work every night and luckely it turned on but it was having problems it would do everything wrong and instead of it being lovable it was eval it distroid everything.So he shut it down and brought it to another scientest to fix it because he clearly cant do it him self.The man Charlie broght the robot too was named Joseph .A. Smith he also worked with robots.Joseph said he could fix the robot but it would take about two months to fix and he kept his word.On the last day Joseph brought the robot to Charlies house.Charlie put him in the basment to anocced it to the world ina week.                                                                                                                                                      Charlie went to bed after he practiced his speech but he woke up in the middle of the night to a huge bang he went down stais to see what had happened but the door to the basment had a huge hole in it the shape of his robot but bigger.He went into the basment and the robot was gone.He had to find him he walked outside and saw all of his neighbors cars smashed next to these huge holes in the road.The robot keeps getting bigger and bigger he had to stop it or he was going to keep getting bigger and start putting peoples lives in danger.Charlie found him on the highway  and brought him home.On the day of the big anoccment millions of people came and even more people watched it on T.V everbody was so excited but when he opened the curtains nothing was there he appoligize to everyone but he said that he distriod stuff and kept growing and growing and he was just not safe to have around people.He also said that he shut the robot down and it would never be seen ever again.Charlie was so embaresed and so angy he swore he would never make a robot again but he did think of a name for the old one the name he thought abot was distrucktion.After he gave up life as a robot maker he built a shop a candy shop and he is much happier seeing children smile because he never had kids because all he wanted to do was make robots so he didnt have much friends around but it dosnt matter now because he has his own store in Maine it is one of the most visited plases in New England.Oh and he got a new door and payed for all the damages distruckion made a least he had the money from making robots for a living to pay for the damages and there were alot of damages the town thought of sueing Charlie but he said they would all get free candy for a month so they were willing to over look the whole sueing thing.

Item_Response: Jim was a born inventor, he always liked to invent things since he was a little boy. Now that he is 12 he found some more people that also liked to invent things. Jim decided to start a science group with all his friends, they would always meet up at his garage at his house to come up with ideas of things to build.                        One day, one of jim's friend suggested they should build a robot, everyone agreed to the suggestion and went back home to get materiels for the robot. When they came back everyone got some metal and welded it together into a human like shape. next they added detail to the face and added clothes, they drew eyes on his face, his mouth, and made his ears and welded them to his head. Next, they put the wiring inside of the robot. They were finished so everyone went back to their house and went to sleep.                         The next day, Jim decided to check on the robot they built the other night. When he got to the garage he was amazed to see that the robot was moving on his own, he also noticed that the switch was on 'off' mode. He was able to walk on his own without anyone controlling him. Just then the robot turned to Jim and began to speak!. The robot asked Jim 'What are your commands?' Jim said 'Walk over to the door and open it.' Just as he said that the robot walked over to the door leading to his house and opened it without a problem.                         Jim ran in the house grabbed the phone and called all of his friends over to his house. When Jim's friends arrived Jim called them to their workshop in the garage and showed them the robot. Jim's friends were just as amazed as he was when he saw the robot walking all by himself. After that Jims showed his friends how the switch they put on him is on 'off' mode, he showed how the robot obeyed his every command. Jim and his friends went to go tell his mom about the robot, at first his mom did not belive him but when Jim took her to his workshop his mom was startled to see a robot with human-like qualites as well as looks.                         In conclusion, Jim took turns with his friends to take the robots to their home, and use him by telling him to do his chores and homework week by week by week.

Item_Response: The Robot Who Came to Life                                                                          by Rudy Diaz                             Once upon a time there was a really evil (but smart) scientist named Shane. He wanted to take over his city and then countries and even the world. But he needed something something that could help him take over the world. So he started to work on a robot.                 'Almost done' Shane said. I only need one more piece to go. If only I could find that microchip. Shane has many things he has invented but he thinks they are the total opposite of useful. Once he found the microchip he put it in the robot. The lights started to flash. 'YEESSS!!!' said Shane. The robot started to come to life. What can I do for you master said the robot. I need you to help me make some weaponry so we can rule the world. I'm afraid i can not do that for you sir you have programmed me to be a nice and kind robot. WHAT!!! Professor Shane threw the robot out and began making his own weaponry.                                                                                                                                   Once the robot came out of the trash he knew that he had to warn somebody about Professor Shane. so he traveled at the speed of light to the nearest army base. Once he got there he warned all of them and they actually believed him because they knew not just anybody would go to an army base to warn them about something. Once they caught Shane they arrested him. The army base leader said thank you and asked him if he wanted to join their army base. The robot said no and also said he actually wanted to be a super hero with all of his powers so he became an unknown super hero across their city.       The End

Item_Response: Mr.Flap Decides To Wake Up                        Suddenly, I hear a strange noise coming from the garage. The first thing that pops up in my brain is that stupid dog next door. Did he jump the fence into my garage? All of my hard work with this robot for 9 years would not be chewed into tiny pieces. I sprint to the garage and I see the most breath-taking thing in the world. Mr.Flap is walking and moving!                    I go up to him and check his battery box. Everything looks fine. What did I do last night that made him finally work? This has been my dream since Day 1! I reach my phone out of my pocket and call the science observatory manager, Mark. Mark is on his way immediately. Meanwhile, Mr.Flap is doing all sorts of things. He can pick up the heavy tool box with no problem! He can push the old laundry machine. Then I see him do the unbelievable; He mumbles something. Mr.Flap can talk! What else can this robot do?                   My head is spinning of all of the thoughts I can do with him. I can sell him for millions of dollars, put him in a museum, teach him to do more tricks, or even keep him. Then I remember seeing black and Mark in my face.I have fainted.                   'Are you okay? What happened?' asked Mark.'I'm not sure. Where's Mr.Flap? I said.Mark mumbled something.' WHERE IS MR.FLAP?' I shouted. 'I think we should get you to the hospital.' Mark said. 'I am dead serious. Tell me where he is. What happened to him?' I asked. 'Well if you reall want to know.. The laudry machine has fell over him. I don't think he will make it.' Mark whispered.

Item_Response: One day I was woke up and went to the kitchen. I was very hungry and wanted to eat something. I wanted to make myself eggs for the morning but I didn't know how to make them. My family was working so I couldn't ask anybody to make them for me. I was starving and really wanted to eat some eggs. Eggs was the only food I had. I didn't have any cereal or milk. If I didn't eat right this second I was going to die of hunger.     I called my mother to tell her that I needed to eat something and the only food we had were eggs. My mom is a scientist and she has been working on a robot in the house. She said that the robot is in the basement and to tell the robot to make you eggs. Next she told me to press the big red button on its back to turn it on. I went to the basement and turned on the robot. The first thing that the robot said is 'what can I do for you'. I told it to make me eggs. The robot rushed  up the basement.        It had two legs and two arms. The machine had a shining silver color to it. It was very tall and it was light. It can communicate to people and do anything they wanted it to do. It was very intelligent and it could move very quickly. It was just a very astonishing machine.     The robot took the eggs out of the refrigerator. The robot started cooking the eggs. It was amazing to see it work. It worked very quickly and it was done it a couple of minutes! When it gave me the food it tasted wonderful. I wasn't hungry anymore. I felt revived. I should make it do my chores next time because it does it very rapidly. One day we may be asking ourselves if humans should still be allowed to work in their homes.

Item_Response: Once there lived a young scientist whose name was Casidee, she really enjoyed making new inventions, like robots. Young Casidee was only 9 years old, so she didn't expect anything huge to happen, actually she thought the most extravagant thing that could happen was one of her many inventions was them becoming a normal thing that people used in life, an invention that they sold in stores. She believed that nothing great would happen with her inventions.         One bright beautiful day Casidee was once again working on an invention. She spent nearly the whole day in her messy room trying to build a robot, but not just any robot, a robot that could talk and move. She thought that that was a perfect thing to build because she thought it could actually do something for her, unlike any of her other robots. So after a long day of working she decided to get some rest, so she put her pajamas on, brushed her teeth, and got into bed. That's when it happened. Her robot started doing its job by moving around the room, like normal, then it started repeating the only word it can say, like normal, then it did something unexpected. It when up to Casidee and said, 'Hello Casidee, my name is Patrick'.            'What? Did you just speak to me? I mean i knew you could talk, but not a complete sentence! This is amazing!' Exclaimed Casidee.     Casidee's robot was alive. Casidee's robot could now move wherever it wants, say whatever it wants and do whatever it wants.       Pretty soon Casidee's inventions were sold worldwide, and everyone wanted one. Casidee's robot, Patrick, also had a good life, helping Casidee with her inventions and acting like a normal person. Hospitals, stores, and many more places were buying the robots, the robots helped serve many popurposes. They cleaned, they helped with math, they did anything a person could do but better! Casidee's robots, and other inventions were now famous.

Item_Response: Once upon a time in one house, in a neighborhood named Harbor village, there was a scientest that lived there. This scientest was married and had one little boy named Jeremy. Jeremy loved science and he also loved building this. One day he wanted to build something that would be very rare and then one day if you didnt want one, people would think you were crazy. This, this thing he wanted to build, was a robot.            Jeremy went to school at a regular school and was very smart. He was so smart he started in preschool but he never finished preschool he went right to first grade on the second day of school. That is how smart Jeremy is. He is ten years old and he is already in sixth grade. He and everyone else thought it was kind of weird too but he enjoyed it, but other people didnt. They thought it was weird and also unfair how he was only ten.            'Dad do you think I could build a robot?' asked Jeremy on the third week of sixth grade.        'You know Jeremy robots are pretty hard to build.'        'I know but the science fair is coming up in three weeks and I want to make a robot that can be like a human. This robot is going to be able to go swimming so he can get wet, he will be able to do everything!'        'Okay you can try if you want but if you can't get it to talk or anything dont be mad okay?'        'Okay dad I wont get mad!'            So of he went into his room to go build a robot. After the next couple of days Jeremy would get home from school, get a snack, and go straight to his room to work on his robot that he would soon call Jeremy Jr. He wouldnt even come down for dinner he would have his mom or dad bring it up to him so he could work on Jeremy Jr.            One day, Jeremy's second week (he only had five more days) working on his robot he ran down the stairs and yelled 'I made a robot I created a human like robot!'        'You did let us see it!' Said Jeremy's mom. So Jeremy went upstairs and brough him down.        'His name is Jeremy Jr. I made him so he can walk, talk, get wet, and pretty much do everything I can do.'        'He can well let's see it.'        'Okay but I havent't tested it I wanted to do it when we were all here and watching.' So Jeremy pushed a couple of buttons on a remot control and they heard a couple of noises, so Jeremy pushed a button that would make him talk. They waited a second and nothing happened. So he hit the button that would make him do what he wanted but nothing happened. 'Maybe I but the green wire with the blue wire, and the blue wire with the green purple wire, adn the purple wire with the green wire. Let me go fix it, it might take a couple of hours though.            The next day when he got home from school he went straight upstairs without getting a snack to work on his robot. He only had four more days until the science fair. That day his mom came up and asked him what he wanted for dinner and he just said 'I don't care you or dad can decide' and went back to work.            The next day he did the same exact thing but he told his mom that he just wanted pasta. He had to work hard if he was going to finish his robot in three days. It was the night before the science fair. Friday night. He had been working on it since four that night and it was already ten at night. He ran down the stairs, robot in his hand, and yelled 'I did it, I finished Jeremy Jr.'   'Okay turn him on son!'   So Jeremy pushed a bunch of buttons, but he wouldnt turn on so he just said, 'I guess I will just have to take a non talking, non walking, non everything robot to the science fair' and went back upstairs.           At the science fair many people asked if he did the robot on his own and of course he said yes. Then someone accidentaly bumped the table and Jeremy Jr. started to talk! It was a miracle he walked all over the place talking to people, shaking hands it was Jeremy's best day ever! He had done it he made a real talking robot! Jeremy was so excited he even got first place! Ever since that day he had loved making things, especially robots.

Item_Response: Robot Comes Alive                 One day a robot named Joe was built in a big Magical workshop where special things can come to life. The guy that was building Joe just got the job a few weeks ago. The new guy was told to build a toy robot but when he was building Joe he had a lunch break 40 mins in. When 40 minutes past the new guy put joe down on a table where it was safe.The toy that he built before was to become alive and he left the lid open on the magic powder and he tiped it over on the table that Joe was laying on. So the new guy was off to his lunch where all the other guys ate there lunch. They were all talking to the new guy and how Joe the robot was going. The new guy said fine. Then one of the guys were joking around about if the magic powerd got on Joe. Well the new guy was done with his lunch so he went back to work into his workroom. When he got in there he noticed that Joe the robot he was working on was gone. He started to freak out,he went to look for all around his workroom but he could not find Joe. The next thing he new he heard a loud scream it was back where he was eating lunch with the other guys. He ran through the halls to get back to the lunch room and he saw Joe picking up things and throwing them around. All teh guys were freaked otu of what they were seeing and they new the new guy built Joe. All the guys were yelling at him and saying ''What powder did u use'' and the new guys said ''the one that has a angle on it''. The guys said thats the come to life one. The new guys was terrifiyed of what he done. The guys said''the only way to stop it is to make a drink or food that the robot likes to eat and put a kill posion in it''. The guys were tieing up Joe with rope but they new that they had to hurry because they new the rope would hold on long enough for a long time. So some ran to the workroom to find the posion and mix it with some robot food. Once they had it they ran back to the lunch room and forced the robot to drink it 1 minute later the robot started to die and it shut down. The new guy was mad at himself for makeing that mistake but the other guys said its fine and that problem is in history now nothing to worry about. It was time to close up shop so all of them gathered their things and left.

Item_Response: The Robot That Went Rouge   by: Christian Lopez               In 2141, a robot went rouge. This robot was meant to be a nurse in warfare. It turned against the humans in the 2nd war against the aliens. Since humans have never thought that he would do that they had no way to shut it of, so their only choice was to destroy it.       In time the Humans successfully made another robot, named john, to destroy the other robot that had went rouge. This time the new robot was remote controlled by humans. Item_Response: A Dream           I was sitting in the back of the classroom all alone under the cold,wet air vent.I was too shy to even raise my hand. I thought in my head.It was my first day at this new school. BOOM!The bell rang with a flash of of kids running home.I had walked home thinking about all my inventions that were horrible,and couldn't even work.When I got home I lied on my freshly smelled bed with now tear of sadness on the pillow.Suddenly,it came!I will make a robot!                   I went to my wooden desk and thought about the design and how to make the robot. I grabbed a piece of paper from my ripped binder and started sketching.The robot was going to be red with black stripes,blue eyes,and a bow on top.Then,I went down stairs to get a screwdriver,memory chip,and some cords from the garage. while I was walking across the kitchen my mom said to me,'Hannah what do you think your doing with all that mechanical uses?' I said,'Jasmine Gonzales,may I please use these for my invention?' My mother replied'Yes,but if you get hurt it's not going to be my fault because I warned you.' I walked upstairs,feeling like my heart was beating out of my chest.                   I started to build this incredible robot!It took me hours and hours,but finally I was dripping sweat on the floor staring at the robot.I named the robot Martha.I turned the 'on' button slowly with my shaky hands.As I stepped back,the robot said'Hello,my name is Martha.What is your name?' My voice sounding squeaky' Hannah.'I screamed with excitement because my creation worked! I went downstairs and said to mom,'Mom,mom,mom it worked!Come to my room!' She came and saw the robot and said'What is this thing?' I said excitedly,'It's a robot!'She replied back,'Well, is this harmful or helpful?' I looked at her crazily and said,'Helpful!' With confusion she said,'Ok,as it doesn't destroy anything.' My robot and I started talking about life and what we do and don't hate.It was fun and intersting.All of a sudden, the robot asked me,'How is school going for you?' I looked at my robot with a sad face and said,'Not so good.'                      Martha said,'Why?' I replied with sadness,'It's not going dso good because it's the first day of being at my new school and I don't have any friends.' Martha said,'It's ok you just have to get out of your shell and talk to people ask if they can show- Then, I opened my eyes in my bed and thought this was all a dream.

Item_Response: As I walk down the stairs and though the door, a man with a huge package went down our lawn.The man said, 'Hi,I`m looking for your mom.' I didn`t know what to say at first,but then my mom came and said,'Ohhh....it`s here!' I didn`t know what was inside that box,but I didn`t care at all. I said,'We have to go to school your just making me late,so hurry.' My mom said,'OK then go inside the car and I put the package inside then I will come.' As I went to the car, my mom came and said,'Hey while you are here,Jake,can you take my son to school.' 'OK,' said the man. I went to the man`s van so we drove off to school.            I came home the next day, and told my mom on the phone about what was inside the box. She said something about a robot inside the box. So I went where the box was,I open it and it was a robot. I felt excited when I saw the robot.It was light blue,long body,long arm,and it has wheels to steer though the tight curves though the house. I wanted to play with it so much so I decided to play with it.I played with it all afternoon,and then my mom came and was still. I came by and said,'Hi mom,what are you doing here aren`t you at wok still?' My mom said,'NO,and I get off early!' I was tired after all those running outside the house with Narmel. I called him Narmel because it looked like a narwhal. I thought I was in big trouble, but my mom said,'Are you happy with it?' I was curious about what my mom said.I said,'I am happy with it and why did you said that?'My mom said nothing after days.            I woke up and it was not there anymore.I ran down stairs and saw it doing chores for my mom. I thought I was dreaming but I wasn`t. I went to my mom and said,'Why is it doing things for us?' My mom didn`t say anything at all. I felt like I did something wrong to it like played it to long. It came and said,' Are you OK?' It sounded like it was a human but it was working for us. I didn`t know if it was the robot that I played all afternoon yesterday. I went out the door to school and while I was walking to school,my friend came and said,'Whats wrong?' I said,'Nothing.'            When I came the next day, it came and said,'Me friendly.' I said,'I guess I got to get use to you then.'

Item_Response: Robot On The Lose!             Scientist Jamie P. Esquire was conducting an experiment,  She was planning to create the worlds first babysitting robot!  She was towards the end of the experiment and was in a pinch because she forgot to order the special part to make it come alive, Part-21590 also known as the Cloud-Dreamer.  She quickly ran to her laptop and looked up that part, 'Lets see 012950, 21480, 21591 wait!' She said, ' They don't have it!' Jamie nearly had an heart attack because she then realized that she had nearly 100 top scientists coming to see this babysitting robot.  She slumped down on the examining table and exclaimed ' Jamie P. Esquire gives up on being a scientist.'  She put the robot together and leaves it on the table.  She slowly packs up the rest of her things, Not knowing she forgot her laptop and cell phone on her desk.  'Click, Click', Jamie shuts of 2 of the 3 lights leaving one on the robot.                        The next week Jamie went back to her old job, High school chemistry teacher.  She sighed as she walked to her teachers desk.  As she reached in her backpack she realized she forgot her laptop at the Opal Science Conservatory.  She ran back to her car driving as quickly as she can to get there.  'I can't believe I forgot my laptop again!', as she ran up the steps she realized the robot was gone and there were tire tracks leading to the window.  She wondered ' where is that robot?', She then heard a screams and shouts out side seeing that her robot was destroying pretty much everything in sight!  'Uh Oh, Looks like I can't be teaching today.'  As she jumped out the window she saw that there was a solar panel on top of the robot.  Then thinking, 'the light must have given the robot energy!'                                      She got to the ground as fast as she could searching for the robot seeing it was heading for the huge parking lot.  She looked around for some transportation, seeing the bike she said, 'this will have to do.'  Jumping on to the bike she sped of towards the parking lot.  She soon saw the robot up ahead but the disappeared into a bunch of bushes.  She then exclaimed, ' Oh great could this get any worse?'  Jamie answered her own question the robot started to destroy all of the cars in the lot!  She ran has fast as she could to the robot.  As she caught up to it she looked for its off switch,  She shouted, 'Ugh where is it?'  She gave up and ripped the solar panel off and the robot drove around in crazy circles and then finally shut off.  Jamie said after that,' There that should be enough destruction for one day.'  Picked up the robot and put on her lab coat and exclaimed,  ' Jamie P. Esquire is now a scientist!'  She then walked back to the conservatory and began working on her next project.

Item_Response: Robots           Here are some robots I am going to talk about. First, a robot called the Gemini scout can mine and find lost miners. Next, Dante-2 can climb down into volcanoes and has eight legs like a spider. Last, Mr. Gower works in hospitals and brings medicine to patients. To me, all of these robots are fantastic.       First, the Gemini scout works in mines and uses thermal vision to see heated objects or people. Gemini scout is also controlled, but it is less than two feet tall and can squeeze through tight spaces and corners.Wherever the Gemini scout is it collects information and tests air for gases and tells miners if it is safe or not. The Gemini scout is remotely controlled and they are similar to video game controls. Gemini scout is lees than two feet tall but it is very strong, and even carries food, water, and supplies. The Gemini scout carries injured miners to safety too. I believe this robot is very fascinating.      Next, Dante-2 has eight legs like a spider and climbs like a spider. Dante-2 gathers information on volcanoes and can stand high temperatures of heat. When a volcano is to hot Dante-2 goes in instead. Dante-2 looks for vents, or holes in the crater of the volcano. Then it collects information about the gases that come out of the vent. Back then, it was hard for scientists because they couldn't get deep into the volcano.      Last, Mr. Gower is a robot that works in hospitals and brings medicine. The body of a robot is a stack of locked drawers that store medicine. Doctors and nurses can unlock the drawers when the medicine is going to be used. It can go anywhere and Mr. Gower can even talk. The robot is so strong it can carry up to 500 pounds. Mr. Gower runs on batteries and after being charged for two hours it can work nonstop for twelve hours. Mr. Gower can say many phrases such as 'calling elevator' and 'you're delivery is here'.      In all, all of these robots are amazing. Whether its from Gemini scout to Dante 2 or Mr. Gower. But all of these robots, like I said are fantastic.

Item_Response: Brother Bot               I was in my lab working on an invention I had come up with.  The very first Brother Bot!  I am an only child and have always wanted a sibling to play around with while my parents were at work.  I am only 12 so I knew my invention would not really work but I constructed it anyway.  It was one of those days when my parents were at work and I was bored out of my mind so I went downstairs so I could work on my Brother Robot, when I noticed that he was gone.                I looked all over my house checking everywhere I could and he was nowhere to be found.  Now this scared me a little because I hadn't even put ant batteries in him yet.  The last room I checked he was there.  He was sitting on the couch playing video games.  I was so happy because I realized that I had finally had a brother!  He was just as I had expected.  But I was still wondering how he had come to life so I asked him.  I don't know how he would talk because I hadn't even put in a microphone. Though he could talk to me like any other kid.  I asked him how he came to life without my help. He said that he had grabbed batteries somehow and stuck them in his back so he could function.  Then he found a computer microphone and put that in his stomach.  It was really amazing what he had done.                I had instantly grabbed a remote and played video games with my new brother.  It felt good to not be so lonely all the time.  He had been with me for a week now and I realized that I had still not given him a name.  I had asked him what sounded cool to him so he chose Jonathan Jr.  My name was Jonathan and I was not very happy with his name choice but was flattered that he liked me, so I let him keep the name.  Soon enough I had taught Jonathan Jr. to play my favorite sport, baseball.  Surprisingly Jonathan Jr. was a lot better than half of the kids on my team!  Even me.  Then I witnessed the only bad part about creating Jonathan Jr.  Was I really becoming jealous of a robot, I think so.                 Anyway, Jonathan Jr. couldn't wait for the upcoming week.  I was going to take him to my baseball practice.  He had shown my coach what he could do and he was wowed by both of us.  Jonathan Jr. because he was such a great player, and me because he had no idea himself how to create a robot.  My coach let Jonathan Jr. on the team which was really cool!  My parents were really proud of me for being so independent.  They weren't so happy about having to take care of him though.  But when I told them that he doesn't eat or doesn't need anything we need they felt relieved.  I think that the best part about Jonathan Jr. is that he can play video games and he can go swimming.  He is really fun to be around.  The only thing I don't like about Jonathan Jr. is that he     ( like any other kid) he always wants to be first. Also, because he is a computer himself he is really good at video games and always beats me.  The only things that I really can't do with Jonathan Jr. is (a) I can't go to school with him  (b) we can't wrestle each other because he is too strong (c) Because he is a robot he can't drive so we can't ride dirt bikes together like me and a real brother could.                   I'm really happy that I created Jonathan Jr.  It's been almost 15 years that he has been with us and I don't regret any day.  I still hang around with my Brother Bot I see him all the time, probably because he lives with me and my family.  Jonathan Jr. doesn't grow up like I do so sometimes he wants do do some kid game that I'm not in the mood for.  my Brother Bot has made me who I am.

Item_Response: Frank                                                        By: CeCe Yates                          It was two months before Izzy's Birthday and she had begged her mom for a dog or cat or something for her b-day but her mom had said ' Just wait awhile .' and dismissed the subject.          Izzy and her mom lived in New York, New York.Her mo had always liked the city and she found a good job as a helicopter pilot. I know not a normal job for a mom but she is the best mom!          Izzy's mom was tired of seeing her daughter like this so she got her a robot one month before Izzy's birthday.It was just like a person but it looked like a robot.The robot would learn as it saw things.          Izzy was very happy about the robot. She decided to name he robot Frank.Frank was a shiny silver with sparkling beautiful gold eyes.          Izzy guessed it was an Agribot (a robot that picks fruit) but her mom told her no.Izzy tried every kind of robot she could think of: Gemini-Scout, Dante 2 ad even Mr. Gower but her mom told her no. Finally Izzy said ' Well... what kind of robot is it?' Izzy's mom replied ' It is a little different tan all of those. It is a little like the robot in 'I Robot.'          Izzy did not really care about what kind of robot it was. She was just glad to have a friend.          Frank and Izzy went everywhere together: Statue of Liberty , Empire State building and even on a few boat rides. When it was time to come home Izzy put Frank in his corner of the room and tuned him off so he could charge.          Izzy had just drifted off to sleep when she heard the click of  Frank being turned on.Izzy turned over and looked at Frank.He had turned on by himself. ' Oh my gosh!' Izzy thought ' Frank is alive!!' He was staring at her intently and his beautiful gold eyes had turned to a monstrous red.          Frank lost it when he seen Izzy look at him.Frank started acting like a crazy wild animal.He was throwing things and screaming at the top of his lungs.He would not calm down.          Izzy's mom called the police, then turned to Izzy and said: ' They will be here as fast as they can.'          Izzy still tried to calm Frank down but he just kept screaming. Izzy swore her head would explode soon. It sounded like nails on a chalk board.After a minute that seemed like a lifetime the police came.          The police had to throw ropes around Frank and take him apart one limb at a time. Izzy was devastated.She had to loose one of her dearest friends. Right before her  Birthday too.          Izzy's mom felt bad for Izzy so she went and bought her a B-day gift. Izzy was at the breakfast table eating her Birthday breakfast when her mom burst through the door with a brand new robot in front of her. ' HAPPY BIRTHDAY IZZY!!! her mom yelled.          The robot's head turned toward her.Its ice blue eyes seemed to bore right through her. The robot said: ' Happy Birthday Izzy.'                                                                   THE END!

Item_Response: George was admiring Dante 1 in the museum. He was so amazed that this robot could actually climb in to volcanoes and collect information for scientists. It's eight metal spiderlike legs glistened in the sunlight. George wondered if he could ever build something as amazing as Dante 1.   Just then, Dante 1 started buzzing and flashing his bright red lights. Was something wrong? He called over to a worker at the museum, 'Excuse me sir, the Dante 1 is making weird sounds and it looks like something is wrong with it.'   'Oh my!' squealed the museum worker, 'What is happening?!' He ran away to get someone to fix it. But as George waited, Dante 1 broke the glass case it was in and walked out of the museum! George ran after it.   'Hey! Dante 1! Get back here!' It was desroying everything from breaking windows to throwing trash cans. George couldn't do anything to stop it, so he whipped out his phone and called 911.   '911 what is your emergency?' the receptionist asked.   'There is a robot on the loose, his name is Dante 1, help!' George cried.   'Young man, 911 is not for prank calls, do not call here again!' said the receptionist angerly and she hung up the phone.   Since the authorities weren't going to help, he knew he had to stop the Dante 1 on his own. He bought a hammer from a local department store and chased after Dante 1.   George charged at Dante 1 and smashed it as hard as he could with the hammer. Dante 1 stopped buzzing and flashing and fell to the ground with a crash.   The museum workers thanked George for detroying Dante 1, and they even built a new robot to replace it called the Dante 2!

Item_Response: One day, there was a 9 year-old boy named Broseph, he was a nerdy kid. He loved to go to those nerdy conventions that play like star wars, and others. When he was young he just knew that he wanted to be a mechanic that designs robots. He loved robots as a kid. So he decided that, he was going to design a robot right there and then.                                                                                                                                         He worked all night, and he worked all day. He wanted to finish a robot so he could have at least one friend. He thought that when he finished it, he would be the coolest kid in school. Finally, he finished it, and he was ecstatic. He brought it to school for show and tell and showed everyone. As he showed them, they all were all like ohhh and ahhhhh. Eventually, he did become the most popular boy in school. He hung out with all the cool kids, sat with them during lunch, and noticed that there was a boy that was all alone just sitting there by himself. So he asked his friend next to him, 'Shouldn't we go sit next to him? I remember how that felt when I was like that.'                   'Na, we should just leave him like that, he deserved to feel bad,' he said. Broseph just hung his head low and didn't bring up that lonely, little boy again.   So, when he got home, he had a little snack and went straight up to his room to hang out with his robot. 'I'm going to call you Darrel,' Broseph said to his robot. After Broseph said that, he thought he saw a glint of light in Darrel's eyes. 'Probably just the light,' he thought. Broseph still had a lot of homework to do, so he finished it and went to take a nap. After he took a nap, he woke up again only to see that Darrel was gone. 'Mom, where's Darrel?' Broseph asked worridley.    'Darrel who? Are you having imaginary friends again?' Broseph's mom said.   'No mom, my robot!'   'Well I haven't seen it since you got home.' And with that, Broseph rushed up to his room and slammed the door shut with a loud bang. Broseph suddenly felt tired so he went to bed and shut his eyes with a single tear drop able to slip past his eyelids.   The next day, he woke up and was late for school. He found out that his mom left him a note that said: Had to go to work early, remember to eat your breakfast, and NO COOKIES!! 'Oh mom,' Broseph sighed. When he went to school he found out that Darrel was at school, sitting in his desk. How did he get there? No one knew.

Item_Response: When Gemini-Scout was driving in a volcano, in search of survivers, it all went hectic.   A shard of rock has fallen and hit Gemini-Scouts power supply, and he is running low on power, and he is a $1,000,000 robot. The company that is looking for the survirers can risk the survivers and Gemini-Scouts life. They have to send something down there to save him.       Mr.Gower may be made for a hospital invirement, he sure is strong. They have equipted him with a hook to be lowered down into the volcano. When he is being lowered however, the rope gets snagged and he plumets the last 20 feet.       When he lands, he's been hurt badly. Lucky, he can still get Gemini-Scout out of there. He gathers Gemini-Scouts parts and puts them in a bag, and grabbed Gemini-Scout and radioed to be pulled up.   He needed to get out of there quickly because Gemini-Scout has a cooling fan that needs to be on to cool his processor or the $75,000 processor. Since Mr.Gower is a hospital robot, who is in air-conditioning most of the time, grabs out his fan and puts it in to addition with Gemini-Scout's fan.   Gemini-Scout starts to run a boot-up program. Now that he's not dead, he could still hurt himself by falling from his arms.       When they finally get them both to the surface, they have an enginneer team for both robots. Mr.Gower took some damage from the fall but he is ok now.       While Gemini-Scout is not doing as good. The operation to fix him will be $500,000. Thats half his cost! But its worth it to fix Gemini-Scout.

Item_Response: Last Friday was the weirdest day of my life when I when hiking with my parents at Golden park. We decided to take s shorter route back to the car after we ran two miles. then my dad found a spider-looking robot.       'What's that?' my Dad asked.   'I don't know' I told my dad  picking it up, ' It seems broken.'       We all looked around to find the owner, but no one was there.My mom had a confused look on her face, but my Dad stayed calm.       'Let's take it home,' said my Dad, putting it in his backpack 'maybe we can fix it.'        So the next day, my Dad woke me up early to fix the robot. My Dad had already set all  the tools on the kitchen table. He seemed excited fixing the robot.       'Do you even know how to fix a robot?' I asked 'It seems like a waste of our time, don't you think?'   'Trust me, I took an engineer class.' my dad said proudly          After five hours of me helping my dad handing him the tools and fixing the robot, it was finally finished. It looked brand new and very shine. So, my Dad decided to take it to the Golden park and try it. golden park seemed safer than our backyard because our house is still being renovated.        When we got there somebody seemed to lost, so m Dad help him while my Mom and I stayed in the car. The guy was freaking out! Then, my Dad called us outside. So, my Mom and i slowly went outside towards them with the robot still in my hand. Once he saw the robot, he gasp.   'Is that my robot!' the guy said wit his eyes wide open.   'Your robot?' I said, 'This is your robot? We found it on the ground in the middle of the track.' I said   'Yes! Thank you so much!' said the guy trying to grab the robot.   I still held it like it was mine. I wanted to keep it and play with it.I wanted to show my friends at school   'Honey, it was his robot, now give it back.' said my Dad as he took it away from me slowly, 'Can we at least try it out, together?'   'Sure,' said the guy as he was putting it on the ground 'but I don't think it would work.'           He grabbed a remote out of his pocket and pressed the button. Then, BAM!!! It came alive. It was Walking very fast, and it even talked a little bit.       'WOW!' I said amazed 'Thats awesome!'   ' Here kid, keep it.' He said ' you worked hard for it'    We were all very happy as we walked to car. I was so excited to show my friends.    And that was my weirdest Friday

Item_Response: Janie, Marshell and Kim were all in writing class when Janie heard a stange noise. it sounded like it was coming from the class room closet but before she could say anything, Mr. Thomson the writing teacher slaped a ruler on her desk and whispered to her. 'Dont talk or you will fail, and this time you wont get a second chance'. Janie immidetly piped down and started working. Later on in class Kim passed a note to Janie, the note said, 'Do you hear that stange noise?'. Janie nodded and passed the note to Marshell. Marshell went up to the teacher and told him about the problem in the closet. The teacher told the class that all he had in there was a robot that he got last year for Christmas. Mr. Tomson creeped up to the door and opened it, BAM! The robot comes flying out and hits the wall. Everyone was in shock, terrified in so many diffrent ways. The robot started climbing up the wall and a kid named Tarence threw his lunch at the robot and hit him right on the spot. The robot fell down and broke into tiny pieces. After that the kids crowded up to look at the robots broken body. Marshell spit on the robot and kicked it at least fifty times, that way we knew it was dead for good. That class never welcomed another robot in their class ever again. They would never forget that day and neither did the teacher and they never trusted another robot, ever.

Item_Response: One hot, summer day I was walking at the park when I saw this gigantic metal ball buried in the ground. When I saw up close, I saw that it was a robot trying to get out of the rock. After it crawled out with trouble, I saw it and it was a small robot. It was about two feet tall and his eyes were a reddish color.   Before I could run to get someone, the robot jumped on me and started to play with my hair. After he was done with that I took him to my house and my parents, 'asked where did that robot came from?' So I told them, 'I didn't know but I wanted to keep it.' After one week of test to see if I was able to take care of him they gave me permission to keep him but I couldn't take him out of my room. At first it all went fine until the third week. Everyday he would make mess in my room and my was always got mad.   This was the story of my experience with a robot that I got to keep.

Item_Response: Meet The Robotsby   Erin Bregman     This story is about four robots helping save lives. The first robot is Gemini- Scout. This robot helps people who are stuck in a mine under ground. The second robot is Danta 2. This robot does and interesting job, Danta 2 climbs into valcanoes to see if it is dangerous or not or if the air isn't right.The third robot is Mr. Gower. Mr. Gower works in hospitals to bring meds. to people how need them and help nurses and doctors. The fourth robot are Agribots. Agribots pick berries and apples. They also know the berries are ripe.       Robots that Play Well With Others by Kascha Semonovitch   This story is about robots that can play well with other people. It all started with the movie called 'I Robot'. Now people started to make robots that can play like animals or with animals.Or robots that can sing, dance, and play music.The movie makers made some robotic apes and dinosours. Then some can be robot pets and act like real pets.       When the Car Is the Driver   by Steve Henn   This story takes place in Nevada. Nevada finalized these new cars that can drive themselfes. They will know the speed the traffic is going. They will also know when someone is going to cutt the car off or when to pass a trucker. Now Hawaii, Flordia and Oklahoma are already getting the cars ready. Maybe one day humans shouldn't be allowed to drive anmore.

Item_Response: Once upon a time, there was a robot named H13-Master, that was imprisoned in 1934 and is revived by an unsuspecting 6th grader named Ronald Heishmor in the 21 century.                   Ronald Heishmor was a failing student in math and science, but when it came to English, he was a GENIUS!!! Ronald was taking a math test at RoseMour Elementary  while depressed that his family had moved. When he suspected he was failing the test he decides to fill in the rest of the answers guessingly and get the test over with. When Ronald finished first, his teacher was suspicous and made him take it over again. When Ronald got home that afternoon, he was miserable, he hated how he didn't have any friends to hang out with and everyone at school had adapted to calling in 'Mister Failingheishmor'.(Which had made him cry sometimes.)              When he got home he decided to quickly grab a snack and run to his new room before his parents (Lesly, and Robert ) decided to ask him to help out. Ronald ran inside, sprinted for some kind of gummysnack, then went upstairs to his room. He decided he would be the first to find the best hiding spots so that if needed, he could use them. When Ronald opened the door to his room, he sensed something was different and began to inspect his room. When Ronald heard a lound CLAP! under his bed, he crawls under and finds a trap door. Ronald silently prayed that he would find riches, and opened the trap door.              He quickly finds a latter mounted to a wall and climbs down it. When he reached the ground, it was very dark and he needed a flashlight. He didn't have one on him so he pulled out his phone and starts looking around. He soon discovers that this was a secret part of the house and he is probably the only one in the world that knew about it. CLAP! Ronald shrieks as he heard the noise. He found a ledge and began to crawl towards the noise.            When he reached the noise, he found a giant box. When he opened the box he found a robot. Not alive, but he thought he could find a way to power up the interesting robot. Ronald grabbed the box and pulled it back to the little opening by the ladder. When he pulled the heavy little robot up into his room. Ronald herd a 'How are you master?' Coming from the robot. Ronald was afraid and wondered how it had powered up so mysteriously. Ronald walked curiously around the robot and found solar panels in the back of the robot. The robot repeated its question, 'How are you master?' Ronald quickly replied, 'Fine, My name is Ronald Heishmor. Who are you and how did you get here?' The robot said, 'I am H13-Master, I was imprisoned down there until you found me.'             Ronald quickly learns all about H-13Master and realizes that it imprisoned during WWII. Ronald decided to make this robot his friend. 'Master, I was a robot in what you call WWII. I can speak, climb, crawl, walk, store memory, and convert to play mode.' said H13-Master. Ronald couldn't believe it, he was having a conversation with a ROBOT. 'H13-Master, will you be my friend? We will have the most fun ever!' said Ronald.            Ronald and H13-Master went to school together the next day. When everyone saw Ronald with a robot, they went crazy. They all loved H13-Master and everyone wanted to be friends with Ronald. H13-Master couldn't take all of the people so he quickly went home. When Ronald noticed him missing he left school too.          H13-Master told Ronald how he hated pressure and crowds. Ronald decided H13-Master would be his at home friend. H13-Master and Ronald played video games until they got so bored. H13-Master needed a break from it all. Both of them couldnt believe the reality of this.           Ronald decides that H13-Master didn't deserve to be a slave to him. So he told H13-Master that the little robot could make his own desicions.                                                                            THE END

Item_Response: 'It's alive!' I heard my mother scream. With a sudden rush of worry I ran to the second floor of our house. Just as she had said, my robot I had purchased from a local scientist had risen and was obviously, awake..or, alive. I stood in astonishment, as my once non-living, dysfunctional robot of some sort had now come to be a living object.           'How this could have happened...well, who could know,' proclaimed the scientist I had consumed the robot from as he inspected the new-living creature. 'All I know now is that it is indeed very smart.'           'This thing...smart?' My mother looked as though it was the silliest thing on earth. But, of course it was smart.           'We will have to take it in for some tests to have the final results on its being, or type.' The scientist said. My mother looked worried, but all I could think about was all the cool things I could do with a living robot.                    Following up many weeks of waiting for the results to appear in the mail, that letter finally came. After reading it over and over again trying to make something of all of this, I finally realized what was right in front of me. This robot..wasn't ordinary. And obviously I realized that the moment I saw it living..but, this robot could sing and dance and do all sorts of things. Amazing things.                Weeks after the results came, the robot came back right along too. The scientist drove over to our house and we retrieved my new friend. 'You must take care of it..understand? This robot may be able to amazing things, but you still need to tend to it.' The doctor had told me. I quickly nodded my head in understanding, way too eager to actually understand. And I mean, what was there to understand? It was a robot. It couldn't be that hard to take care of.             In the first week, I discovered many other atonishing things my new pet...or friend...robot, could do. It could play sports. And I mean actually play sports. Not just automatically throw a ball back to me. Like some kind of ball machine. It could hit, and throw, and just everything. Having someone to practice lacrosse was awesome. And yes, he can play lacrosse. Cool right? He could sing and dance, which was great for my little sister because she is always looking for new entertainment.                 I had Greg, I called him, for a total of six months. After those sixth months, there was the phone call. It was the scientist who had once owned the robot. I thought it was just one of his ordinary check up calls to see how the robot was acting and adapting to its surroundings. But, it wasn't. 'We must have the robot back admediately. He is one of the only ones of his kind who can do all of the amazing things he is capable of. He is wanted to go on a world-wide trip, to first visit Hawaii to scout the newly erupted volcanoes. Then, he is wanted in Africa to tend at a hospital in a disaster-struck little town in need. Your robot can do amazing things...and this is the opportunity to take. You up for it?' The scientist told me. I told him yes..it was the best thing for Greg.           Greg's goodbye was the hardest. Apparently admediatly really meant admediately. The day after, Greg was taken away from me. We had a short goodbye, and he seemed almost..sad. Of course my mother was happy. She had said that having Greg in the house was like having a puppy. My mom hates puppies. The scientists had told me that Greg would be coming back. But, by the looks on their faces, I could tell Greg could be gone for years, as to the many capabilities he has. He was my best friend. And I'll never ever forget of him and all the fun times we had.

Item_Response: The Many Types of Robots                       There are several robots in the world, and many different ways we use them. Here are just a few that might be more common in the future.                       One robot is the Gemini-Scout. The Gemini-Scout does many things, but mostly it saves lives. It is a remote controlled robot that does search and rescue work in mines under the ground. Here is and example for how you might use the Gemini-Scout. If there was a big explosion in the mines and there were people that were stuck in there for days they would need food water and other sources to survive there until they were saved. This is where the Gemini-Scout comes in handy. The Gemini-Scout can go up and down stairs and make tight turns, and can even roll through water. It would look for the people stuck and carry food, water, and other supplies to them. But most of all it can drag hurt people to safety. It can test air for gases and tell miners when the air is safe. The Gemini-Scout can save many lives.                        Here is another example of how you can use a robot. The Agribot can pick fruit. It takes months for farmers to pick fruit but the Agribot can make this happen in half that time. Since it can work days and night it can twice as many fruit. Also, there is a robot that can save lives and help with time too! This robot is Mr. Gower. Mr.Gower is a robot that works in hospitals. This robot is a cabinet on wheels, it stores medicine and takes it to the doctors, and nurses when needed. This robot can help save lives, and time. For example, if someone is badly hurt and needed to be treated right away, the doctors wouldn't have time to go get supplies. Since they have Mr.Gower they can start working immediately, which can possibly save a life.                          Robots are not only used for jobs they are also used for entertainment. The I-Pet Companion is a robot that lets people play with kittens from a distance. You can play with the kitten by pulling string so the kittens will jumps to it. It would be like a computer game with kittens. This would be very helpful for people that are allergic to kittens, or have a certain disability which doesn't allow them to play with a kitten.                           Another entertaining robot is the ones you might see on television. You might not know it but there are many robot animals on television. Since dinosaurs and giant apes don't exist they use robots to play there part instead. Most common people that use this are movie-makers. For example, the movie Jurassic Park uses hundreds of robots since the movie is about dinosaurs. Also, there are lifelike pets that are robots. One of them has fur so u can pet it and it will feel just like the real thing. You can also teach it tricks! The only difference is that you don't have to let them outside or feed them! This would also be very good for people that are allergic to pets and, if parents don't there child is responsible enough to have a pet that needs to be feed, walked, let outside and much more stuff. This will help many families that aren't fortunate enough to have a real pet.                          Finally, there is the robotic car. The Google Car is one step forward to the technology of the future. It can drive while you are eating, talking, getting ready, and a big one is texting. Texting is a big problem for teenagers. Many wrecks are caused by phones. If you don't have to have you eyes on the road it wont be a problem. This car is also amazing in many ways. It can speed up or slow down if there is traffic, or a sharp turn. It is a lot like a person driving, but better. It can see above cars and many places that you wouldn't be able to. Hopefully the car of out future is on the way!

They robot goes underground and it makes tight turns, small squeezes, and goes up stairs. they help find trapped miners that are underground. Gemini is small, but it is strong enough to carry a whole person(miners)out of being trapped. These robots are true life savers! Another robot that saves people lives is Mr. Gower. He works at hospital helping nurses and doctors treat their patients. Mr. Gower is like a small cabinet on wheels! You can learn how to be responsible and how to take care of pets. This can be fun because its not a real pet so it would be interesting! Robots can be a lot of fun as well as life saving!       They also help scientists learn new things. One robot, the Dante 2, climbs into volcanoes and gathers new information. This robot has 8 legs just like a spider! Scientists use the information they collected to research about the volcano. Who knows what they will find. Also the Dante 2 collects information from looking in vents, holes, or craters. The Dante collects the infromation from the gases that come out the vent. Scientists keep the information safe in their laboratories!!       Over all we learned that robots are not only a futuristic element. We learned that people from our century use them too! Robots are so interesting! I am so glad I gained more knowledge about robots.

Item_Response: Robot Rescue       Sweat dribbled down Pete as he chipped away at the hard, crummbling rock that surrounded him in the hot cave, deep down inside the earth. The workers in the mines digg all day with little pay. In the ruins of Brazil, South America, it is impossible to find work other than in the mines. Water is scarce on the surface of the world because of dramatic global warming.  The people believe that in their beds at night, they faintly hear the rumbling of a river below the caves of the huge mines.       Day after day, the hundreds of workers march into the elevators with pic-axes resting on their shoulders. They split up in even groups and march simeltainiously to their posts working on the big hole in the center of the main work room. Who knew one normal day in the mines couldchange Pete's life for ever. The ground rumbled tremendously and the men yelled orders to get out of the mines. 30 year old Pete stood whacking away at the walls in the deepest room of the mine with his  close friend Bill. The ground shook the worst in so far down in the ground. They hurried towards the elevator, but before they reached the button, the ceiling collapsed. The breath inside Pete and Bill was pushed out of their limp bodies by mounds of hard rubble and dirt.       The usually stubborn marshall of the mines stood, counting off names of miners. When he reached the names Pete Walton and Bill Weston, no voice echoed into the dusty air. 'Anyone seen Pete and Bill? Anyone?' Everyone looked around cluelessly and shook their heads. No one realized they lay covered in dirt down 50 miles in the Earth. The marshall scurried into his office and pulled open his drawers and through pencils and notices out of the piles, searching for the single thing that could save the two innocent men in his his caves. All of the entrances were blocked by mounds of rocks and brown dirt. only Gemini-Scout could save Pete and Bill. The assistant marshall banged open the door to the cluttered office. 'The people want to know what happened to those people in the mines.'       'They will find out soon enough. Now where is that controller?' Finally, a the marshall lifted out a controller that looked as though a video game would be controlled by it.'       'This is no time for video games! There are workers trapped in your mines. Do something!'       'I am doing something. Hold on.' He pressed a small red button on a dusty computer. The screen clicked on. It showed a small robot less than two feet tall with rough wheels sputter to life. The marshall twisted the joystick and the little robot moved forward towards the elevator blocked by rocks. The little robot lifted each individual rock and put it to the side. The marshall then pushed another button and the little machine pressed the elevator button. He rolled in and pressed 7, the lowest level. It continued picking up rocks and piling them up on the side. Finally, a human foot poked out of the rubble. Gemini-Scout dragged Pete out of the rocks followed by Bill. He tugged them all the way back to the awaiting marshall at the exit of the mines.   'You did it, Marshall! That goodness for the robots!'

Item_Response: One night there was a 11 year old girl named lilly. She was smart and loved science. Lilly always dreamed of her making a robot that would save lives. Lilly called her robot Mr.Gower. Item_Response: Dr. Carter, a scientist, sat in his laboratory. It was three in the morning and he had been working on this for the past year. He was almost done with his robot, Excalibur. It would have features such as compartments to hold things, the ability to pick up to about 2000 pounds, and he had a faucet that produced ice cream (low-fat) and much more things.                     It was now 5:00 a.m. Dr. Carter took a deep breath and took of his safety goggles. He looked at Excalibur. He bit his chapped, dry lip. Something was wrong.   Was the ice cream dispenser on the wrong side? No. Was his head on backwards? No. He asked himself every question about it that could be wrong. Then he got it. Excalibur just wasn't alive.                   The Doctor spend days trying new things to make him seem more alive. He made his eyes wider, his mouth smiling and even made his hands set on his hips. Finally he got it! How he could he not have noticed it before? Excalibur needed to to talk!   The doc worked on his voice box for days and eventually after 3 months, it was done.   Excalibur could say over 300 phrases such as, 'Yes.' and 'I love You.' and 'Why?                   Dr. Carter's cousin worked on a farm and he needed help so he brought Excalibur with him. He made it so the robot could pick berries and help identify if they were ripe. ('Agribots') then when the doctor's cousin's kids were bored, he made Excalibur be able to play with them and also their pet cats. ('Robots that play well with others')                    One Summer day, Dr. Carter woke up and didn't see Excalibur in his normal spot next to his bed!   Dr. Carter looked everywhere then eventually went downstairs to find Excalibur making scrambled eggs in the kitchen humming to 'Joy to the World'!   'Excalibur?' Dr. Carter asked hesitantly, his breaths getting shorter.   'Oh hey, Master. Just making some breakfast.' The robot said and flashed the scientist a toothy grin.

Agribots have a special system tells them when the fruit can be picked or when the fruit needs water. It uses a mechanical arm to pick them. There are radars on the front the back nad both of the sides. The car can adjust its speed to help it around different road opstacles.             Now you know that robots do exist and save every day lives. There are many companies developing robots aroud the world.Maybe you will someday operate one of these robots or create one yourself.

Item_Response: The year is 2316 and technology is more advanced than ever before, so unsurprisingly there are robots everywhere. But most of them working robots. One cloudy day there was a 14 year old girl named Kendra Mathensan, and she was a very smart girl, but rarley wanted to show it. While she was watching T.V. she got an idea, she thought 'What if I build my own robot.'' She did just, that she was putting the parts together, and programming the robot to talk. It took her a long time, a year to be exact. When she was done making it she named it Emilia.                         Emilia was a female looking robot with glowing yellow eyes and a silver body. She was programmed for fun, she could dance, she could sing, she can ever make jokes! So years later Emilia became a famous robot amoung children and adults!   Kendra was truly proud of herself for creating Emilia Mathensan.

Item_Response: Fred Cooperton was in his lab one day,staring at his creations he thought were useless.He had built a computer-bot he called 1837-CB.He had originally used it as a mobile computer that walked everywhere he went.But it had broken down 4 months before.He had also built a bionic wrestler named  BW-461,or better known as Goliath.He had won a couple of tournaments,but one of the tournaments he was torn apart by another robot.                                           Then he had an idea.Fred had always loved dinosaurs.He thought to himself,'Mabye I'd be happier if I had another companion.'Fred has always been lonely with no friends.He tried Facebook,Omegle,and Zoosk,but none of them worked.Then he was certain,that he wanted a companion.Since he had a compassion for dinosaurs,he wanted a dinosaur.Then he started to build.          After 3 months of hard work,he had finally finished his masterpiece.The dino-bot was complete.He named it ARIA-831,(he programed it as a she). He used ARIA as a car when he needed to get somewhere.They went everywhere together and had fun.Until one day,they were in traffic and ARIA went A.W.O.L on every car she saw in sight.It was a HUGE mess seeing cars toppled over,semis on there side,and everything else you can imagine.Then that's when Fred realized that he couldn't go places with her anymore.Then she went A.W.O.L on everything else she saw.Fred didn't want to do this,but he had no choice.He had to shut her down.Then he was sent to prison for lethal damaging.He had missed ARIA.She was the best thing that happened to him,almost.
