Item_Response: Happy Birthday, screamed my sister as she woke me up one very early Saturday morning. i got up slowly and pulled the covers from my nose. Come on, come on we want to give you something we want to give you for your 13th birthday. At that remark i sprung up out of my bed like a rocket. Through my mind i was thinking of all the possibilities. The one gift i had wanted for ever was Playlist Live tickets or even Vidcon tickets. It is a big party almost where you get to meet your favorite YouTuber. my fingers were crossed tight. My eyes were closed even though they didn't havew to be. i put my foot in front of me but unlucky as i am i fell. SPLAT!!!! I didn't waste any time getting up off the floor. I ran for my family room to get the ultimate surprise. When my foot touched the soft, velvety carpet i opened my eyes to see and evelop sitting on the counter. Out loud I said, 'To squee or not to squee. Squeeeeeeeeeeee!!!!' i read the outside of the evelope and it said, To: Renton From: Dad. At the sight of this i started crying out of joy because my father had been stationed in Iraq for over a year and wouldn't be home until my next birthday. I opened my the evelope slowly so i wouldn't rip it. My eyes were closed tight. i put my hand in and pulled out a peice of paper, shaking like an earthquake i opened it. My heart dropped it wasnt tickets to the places but, has i started reading the note my heart went straight up to my chest again.           It read:                Dear Renton,                  I am very sorry i can't be home for you very important 13th birthday. i had sent you a present. it hope you like it. i don't have much time to write this but Happy Birthday!                                                 From, Dad                                        My mom pionted to the closet. I knew that was where the present must be hiding. I ripped open the door and saw a... robot. I started jumping up and down. it was in the shape of a cube about as big as my hand. I knew it was a robot because thats what it said on the note left on top of it.                                    Note: This is a robot for Renton. If you are reading this Renton you may have to fix it up to work it.                                     i started working on it right away. By 9:00 pm i had finished. i had added a button to turn it on. I clicked it and nothing happened. I got mad and just went to sleep. BANG! BOOM! POW! I darted from my deep slumber. BEEEEEEP! BOP!  It was coming from my closet. I crept over to look and i found my robot alive but it was in the shape of a dog. I pinched myself to see if i was dreaming i wasnt.                                           One month later...                             I had gotten used to having my weird alive by itself robot in my life. I ahd sent a thank you to my father not sure if he got it though. Life had seem great until July when my robot turned bad. He had wrecked the local park playscape and even my room. I knew there was something wrong so i fixed him up  and he was back to normal.

Item_Response: IT WAS 2198                 'WHOOF, CH, CH, WHOOF'. 'Mr. Pines the robot has arrived'. 'Good get him to the service workers'. 'Yes sir'. As the delivery man took the robot to the service workers, he felt the box tug, but he ignored it and thought that it was just the old hospital floor. 'Here you go, your new robot'. 'Thanks, that is the, um... Mr. Gower, right? 'Of course'. The workers got straight to programming the robot, while doing so, they noticed a hazard light blinking red. After a few minor adjustments, it still blinked, so they let it go. The hospital put the robot straight to work, It delivered medicine all over the hospital.                 'Your delivery has arrived'. 'Wow this robot is great tha... Whoa, hey this robot gave me the wrong medication, it could have put the patient into a coma'. 'Do not worry, Mr. Gower knows best'. 'Mr. Pines the robot is acting up I think the robot has to be serviced' said Jack, the docter. 'Alright, alright take him to the service department' 'NO' said Mr. Gower the robot. 'Whoa this thing is crazy' said Jack. Just then the robot started shooting midicine everywhere and some of the medicine that mixed created a deadly toxin that filled the air. Everyone passed out, and they wouldn't wake up. Mr. Gower left, he was headed to the hospitals main control room and put the hospital under lockdown before anyone could get out.                  Now this was a matter of a 456 lives or the entire city. Mr. Gower held a docter hostage, he asked for some men to put together more robots like him or he would wipe out the entire city. The mayor refused, Mr. Gower gave him 48 hours to comply...... or else. The hostage, his name was Dean, He asked the robot 'Why are you doing all of this'. In reply the robot answered ' You foolish humans will destroy this planet, I... I am here to liberate it. Just then Dean saw a button and remembered that it was a qaurantine lockdown that would spread gas to melt the building and everything in it. What would he do,  455 people and his life at stake. SLAM! Dean pressed the button. Quickly a dome covered the hospital and gas spread throughout the dome and hospital. In a matter of minutes the hospital and all in it disinigrated. The city and possibly the world was saved by one quick and hard decision.

Item_Response: A day of Madness           My friends little brother got a toy robot for his birthday. He played with it every day. I saw him when I went to her house. One day I was over at her house and it was just her, me, and her little brother. He was playing with his robot while we were playing on the Wii. We heard a big thump and a loud scream from upstairs. We ran up up the stairs down the hall and into his room. We opened the door seeing what was going on. There it was but bigger and alive.        We saw her little brother knocked out on the floor. Next thing we know we are shoved in the closet. When we woke up we tried to hear what was going on. But all we heard was silence. we got out knowing that we were not locked in. But when we got out the brother was missing and the robot was gone.        We looked out the window there were the two of them. We were trying to come up with a plan. It took a while but we were going to do it like spys do it. Hide where we walk. Have code signals and other plans we did it all.        When we got to the backyard we hid behind the wall. We listened we heard all but nothing was bad so me and my friend popped out with water guns ready to shoot. There we are shooting water at the robot when her brother says stop. He explained everything. It turned out to be a mistake.         All the robot was doing is celebrating the friendship that they had. We were confused at first but got it later. This day was such madness. Now what do we say when your mom gets home.

Item_Response: Today in 2021 in CA. I was sitting around watching T.V. when my remote control robot came to life. When he came to life he said, 'My name is Robo' I was so scared at first but then he said, 'I come in peace.' The whole day Robo showed me the things he could do of course he could talk, he could steer, climb walls and stairs, he was is really strong, and carry things it was so cool to have a Robot in my house.        The next day I took Robo to School with me for show in tell my teacher didn't like a Robot in the classroom so I had to take it back home Robo was really sad. After I took Robo home with me my mom saw him hiding in my room she didn't like Robo either so I had to put him in the junk yard, and I could never see him again. When I took Robo to the junk yard he was really sad. The next time I saw Robo was not good it was really bad.                                                                   When I saw Robo next he was angry he started to take over other robots and made them like him he told them that we hated them and we are better then they are, then he said, 'we should rule this world.' After that they started to take over all the robots then the state then the country then the world. The army couldn't stop them they were to powerful. All the armies in the world couldn't stop them they still were to powerful. There was two things we could do we could hide, or I could try to stop Robo and his army. I was the only one who new his weakness.                                                                                                    His weakness was that he knew that I loved him but he got mad because I was the only one who loved him, also he was mad because I had to but him in the junk yard. If I could get mom to let me keep him then I might be able to reason with him. So I set off out of hiding to stop this war vs. robots. It was a long walk to get to him but I did. When I got to him he had guards they took me but he told them to stop. I told him that he could come home and stay with me. He thought about it and said, 'yes' after that the war was over and I was a hero and Robo lives with me now.

Item_Response: Hello. I am a being known as the Watcher. No matter what, I must record all that has happenned in this galaxy. Now, I will tell you what happened to the most advanced beings in the universe.         Two millennia ago, in an alternate Earth on the other side of a star, known as your Sun, there was a planet known as the Junk World. It was a vast, barren world filled with the trash of every alien dynasty from around the galaxy.The ruling race, the Lionras, were very advanced in their technology. They had invented a bionic robot, that would clean their planet and save them from the atomic waste consuming the planet. It was known as the Tri-Absorber.         The problem was, the Tri-Absorber had no energy source. Then a freak energy storm came. It destroyed the laboratory, and the Tri-Absorber was struck by a type of lightning known as the Infinity Bolt. It was an infinite power only known to us Watchers. Amazingly, it provided the robot with the power source it desperately needed.        When the storm left, the robot was already doing its job. After seven years, it finished its duty, yet continued to serve the Lionras. It served them dutifully for 1 milennia.            When their dynasty ended, the robot rested at the heart of the Junk World, and fell into myth and legend. To this day the planet's name was changed to the Infinity Planet.

Item_Response: Yesterday, my best friend Sophie and I, were building a miniature robot that could dispense erasers, #2 pencils, and other tools for stationary at my house. This was when we finished school and started our summer break.We were already thinking of building some kind of robot, then we decided to make this machine. We chose to name it PenBot. The process of building him was difficult, but we completed it. Sophie and I were so excited to experiment the robot. When we did, it was successful! That night, we told are parents about it. They were very proud. We went to bed and the next morning, we checked out PenBot again. He was gone!!!            First, Sophie looked all over the house with me. There was no trace of him, such as pens or markers. All of a sudden we heard a robotic type of sound, like something was talking. Under my bed, there was PenBot! He sprouted stout legs and wiggly arms! He was alive! Sophie and I screamed at the top of our lungs, and hid outside of my room. We peeked in, and PenBot started to throw large erasers at us. I grabbed a baseball bat and swung it at him. I missed. I tried again, and he lost consciousness. Sophie stomped all over him into powder, and then we threw him into the dumpster. We thought about how that could've happened. Our little project was evil and also gone/dead.             During that night, I couldn't sleep, and I bet Sophie couldn't either. I laid there twisting and turning. Right when I was about to close my eyes, I heard a noise...from the dumpster.

Item_Response: 'Did you ever wish that you had a robot that does what you say?' said Edwin. 'Yeah I do, imagine how cool it will be?' said Ian. 'That will be amzing' said Edwin.'Can we build a robot that does that in our science class? We do have a lot of technology in there' said Ian. 'Thats not a bad idea lets go ask Mrs.Hartz if she will let us, we might even increase our science grades like that  and besides we have science class next and the bell is going to ring any minute now' said Edwin.       The bell rang and the boys went to go ask Mrs.Hartz about the idea.She said thats an amazing idea.She was going to let the boys stay after school and build the robot.'Alright lets build that robot!' said Ian. Edwin went to go get the parts for the robot and Ian started a place to build the robot.       'Now put that piece right here gently.............GENTLY!!' said Edwin in a worried way.'DONT PRESSURE ME! See there I put the piece.Now put in the last piece wich is the micro chip.' said Ian. 'Thats like the brain right?' said Edwin. 'Yes' he said.'There we finished....does it work?' said Ian.The boys waited and waited.Finnaly the robot started moving!'IT WORKS!!!' said Edwin in a excited way.'Alright lets test the robot' said Ian.       'Lets test this robot to grab that little metal piece over there and bring it to us' said Ian.The robot moved all the way to the metal piece, it grabbed it and brought to the boys.'Now lets try voice command, robot stay!' said Edwin loudly.The robot stayed.'Robot move!' said Ian.The robot moved.'This is just amazing' said Edwin.'Lets name it something' said Ian.'What do you want to name it?' said Edwin.The boys thought.'Lets name it Heavy because it can carry heavy stuff' said Ian.'Thats a perfect name' said Edwin.       The boys showed Heavy to Mrs.Hartz.She was amazed by what she was seeing.A perfect strong and small robot.'We can make Heavy as a school helper!' said Edwin.'Thats a perfect idea' said Mrs.Hartz.       A year later Edwin and Ian was famous for building Heavy.They built more Heavys for more schools as a helper and it was one of the best robots people have ever seen.Schools all over the world wanted this robot.This was a huge accomplishment for Ian and Edwin.The boys said this is one step closer to the future of robots.

Item_Response: Robot Adventure          'Mary! Your friends are here!' said my mom. I knew they were coming but does she really need to yell? I was getting ready to go to the desert of Nevada to explore. My friends Brooke and Joanna heard history about that desert. That's why we're going to find facts about it.        Joanna's mom planned to drop us off at the desert. Of course Brooke dad is gonna come with. Since we do need parent supervision. It was really hot once we got there.  We got all of our tools and supplies we need.         A few hours past and we got to the digging part of our session. 'Joanna! Mary!! DAD!!!' screamed Brooke. 'I think I hit something! Or at least found something!' Her father was digging something metal looking machine.          We all helped pull it out of the ground. It was.... it WAS...  A ROBOT!?!?!? How could there be a robot in the middle of nowhere? We thought it was kind of a sick joke because it looked a little fake and very light.         'Come on guys. Lets go to another area to explore.' said Brooke dad. Our group was once walking away from the 'robot'.  We kept hearing vibration in the background. Brooke turned around and saw the robot come alive! Her father ran back to see if its not dangerous or stuff like that, so we can be safe.            It started providing food and water for Brookes dad.  It said 'Atom' in the back of it.  I don't know why but its a pretty cool name. Brooke was asking her father to see if she can keep it. Since she found it first. 'Totally!! It could be a big help around the house too!!!' Brooke father replied.            He called his wife to tell her everything of what just happened.  Since she was our ride, of course shes gonna be coming here soon. She did agree to keep the robot. She said it will help a LOT with her cooking around the house.            Today was a really productive day. We became explorers today, got a HUGE prize for coming to the desert. Which is the robot. My friends and I planned to come here again in a few weeks. Got to spend time with them, especially with Brooke father!             I do wanna come here again. This time, I wanna bring Atom!

Item_Response: Robot Story               ?            Many people think of robots as things from the future, think again! To let you know, robots do many jobs. They can work at       a hospital and save lives. Robots can even explore places where humans can't. They can assemble electronic gadgets, guide trains       on track , sing, dance, and even play music. Robots can do a lot more things than humans can, more than what we think!       ?   My group (Erik, Jenny, Nick) and I decided to create something amazing, a robot! Today we were gonna start to make our       robot, our creation.???????? We had all the materials and tools to start. We had so much fun making a new 'friend'! Soon the day came, we       finished our robot! So we tried to make it alive, and we kept on trying and trying and trying! But soon ,Erick brought up       an idea, to use electricity! Out of now where the power in the house went out, 10 minutes later the lights cam on, and everybody       left.               The next day, around 11:30, we went to check up on our robot. But when we got there it wasn't there. We look all over, then        we heard a noise, a rusting noise, after being startled, we walked closer to the noise. Then we say something, something metal       moving, it was our robot! We finally did it, we made our robot come to life.  Nick soon went on his computer to check on what       robot we created, and we found out it was a Gemini- Scout. We were so excited, so we called it, Gem, for short.            Gem was a remote-control robot that can do a search and rescue work in mines under ground. He is less than two feet and has       wheels,can go up and down stairs and make tight turns, can even roll through water. Gem  is small, but he is very strong, he can       carry food, water, and other supplies. He can even drag hurt people to safety. Wherever it goes, Gem collects information, for       example he can tall miners when the air is safe. He also has a thermal camera to help it to find miners. When Gem finds the       trapped miners, the minors can use a two-way radio to talk with the rescue team. He was built to be easy to use!

He picked it up and unlocked the lock and up-rose a robot.           That was the beginning of the end. When the robot awakened he and David took over and became the dictator of every country starting with the United States and ending with Russia.            'Could that happen in real?' life Libby interrupted with her eyes like frisbees.  David the dictator turned and yelled 'It...Already...Has...You...Idiot!

Item_Response: One day as a young boy named Leon was walking threw the junk yard trying to find objects to build a fort when he came upon something.Out of the corner of his eye he saw something glimmer in the evening sun. He walked toured it being cautious that nobody was around he knelt down and wiped the dirt of of the front of it. On the front read SQ-34. Little did he know this was the beginning of a adventure.        He got his wagon and lifted the strange object into it. What is it he thought, but while he was lifting the strange object into the wagon he accidentally hit a button. Out of the blue the thing started to move. The boy jumped back and dropped the machine. ' owwwww' the machine said. The machine looked at the boy and in some awkward way the machine looked like a young boy to.         'Hi' the robot said. 'My names Robo'. The boy looked at the thing for a second then said 'my names Leon'. The two stared at each other for a while then Leon picked him up and set him in the wagon. 'Were are we going' said Robo. I'm going to take you home said Leon. 'Where's home'? The robot asked ' about a mile down the rode' said Leon. ' I've never had a home' said Robo ' we'll your going to love this one' said Leon. And they started talking, but little did they know this was going to be the start of a new friendship.

Item_Response: The Robot That Wasn't            I am writing this story to tell of the strange event that recently occured to me. On new years eve of 3015, I was playing around with the robot I'd gotten for Christmas. I named him Daniel, even though my parents insist that it's not a very good name and that I should refer to him by his actual name, which is Zanotron X-90. But I don't like that. Neither does Daniel. But that's not the point. Anyway, we were playing a nice game of Hyper-Chess and I think he was letting me win, because he a robot! He can make thousands of calculations per second that could destroy my king within his first 3 moves!                            Sorry, getting off topic AGAIN. So, we were playing chess and my parents  were watching the Plasma-Ball Drop and I could hear everybody in the background chanting '10...9...8...7...6...5...4...' then Daniel interupted.'They are off by 3.73 seconds,' you see, daniel always makes these random remarks that nobody cares about and this just happens to be one. Sometimes he will say something like 'Did you know we are the 2nd planet from the sun?'and I reply with 'Dan, Everybody know we live on Venus'. But back to the story. In the distance I can hear the rumble of the thunder. I hate rain. But I love snow. So I ask Dan, 'Hey, what are the chances of a snow storm?' He scans the weather radars for about 1.3 seconds and replies with '97.675 percent'.YES, I think.            But then the power goes out and the Hollo-TV goes blank. 'Great.' Says my dad in a sarcastic tone. Dan shuts down. 'We must've got hit by lightning bolt,' says my mom.'I think it just overloaded his circuits honey, he should be Okay by tomorrow.'and then we all head up to bed. When I wake up in the morning I hear the sizzling of bacon and think 'Mom must be up already.' But when I walk downstairs I'm greeted by the voice of a man. A man who looks surprisingly like Dan. Wait, it is Dan. Things just got weird.

Item_Response: When long ago, when robots assisted humans. There was a robot who was about to become a human also. This robot was names Albert. He was made by Donald Donohugh, a very poor scientist. The scientist worked in a small lab which was an underground basement. He worked many days on Albert and hasn't slept at all.Since Dr. Donohugh was too sick to keep on making adjustments to Albert, he died ,and Albert was shipped off to Japan where another scientist who was suppose to finish Albert, but he never found him.Albert had spend many days in an airport, but then a little boy was looking at Albert and since that little boy's father is a scientist he asked his father if he could keep him.the boy's name was Kioke. He loved making robots with his dad and Kioke asked,''Can I help you finish Albert, father,'' he said in Japanese. Kioke's father couldn't say no. So when Kioke would come back home after school he would come by his house and go around the beautiful garden his mother  likes to plant and goes into into the basement, carefully walks down the stairs and see his dad getting ready to work on Albert. They re-created Albert in a human robot. They tested him if he was water proof or if he knew any school related subjects.He passed all the tests and he could even speak. Kioke was pleased with his accomplishment and his family celebrated with Albert too with some chocolate chip mint ice cream that Kioke's mother made.

Item_Response: CHIZO          There once was a robot that was truly more advanced than the ones we have today.It was to be called Chizo (cheez-oh).There are still many things unkown about it.           This was one of the greatest inventions of all time,it was capable of doing all sorts things that you wouldn't   imagine it could do. It's creator was named Chester Dub who was very smart but poorly respected. Many said how he was insane to think of making the worlds best robot. Of course trying to discourage him with words wouldn't   do nothing but make him more determine to make his invention.He worked day & night,year by year just to find the right shape of it.Out of what he learned,he soon thought maybe he could bring it to life.Months later he got all his tools and materials then began.            He worked his true best on it as he added different changes on the way it would move. Not many people in the neighborhood   seemed to worry about him since they didn't like him,he didn't come outside as much since he was so busy. Mr.Dub didn't seem   to care either because he was so caught up in working constantly on the robot.He soon decided to get some rest, it wasn't long until   he heard a unique sound from his lab. He got up & went down there to see what happened. When he looked, there was unusual except   one of his glasses that contained a strong energy had broke. Since he was up, he decided working again on the final parts.Soon he finally finished with the robot and started transporting extreme energy to it. Suddenly the robot was alive!       Mr.Dub couldn't believe he actually did it! With excitement, he went out of his house shouting he did the impossible. Everyone   was amazed when they saw the robot who was name Chizo. Nobody knew why he gave such a unique name but they liked it.Chizo   was able to do many helpful tasks such as cleaning,translating,& much more. Mr.Dub felt as if it were his friend, somehow it was able to create a bond with him as well. Item_Response: My mom got me a robot for my birthday. It was supposed to be one that just dances and sings, and I think it's called HRP-4c. But, now I'm not so sure. It still sings and dances, but at odd times, he'll roll over to me and say something. Once, I went to school, and when I came home, he was taking a cake out of the oven. Weird, right?            Today, I came home from my friend's house and decided to talk to my mother about her birthday present to me.            'Hey, Mom?'            'Yeah?' She was busy making cookies, so when she wasn't looking, I stole some cookie dough.            'I think my singing dancing robot doesn't just singing and dancing anymore.'            'What do you mean? And stop that. The more you do it the less cookies we will have.'            How does she always know? 'I came home from school the other day, and HRP-4c was taking a cake out of the oven.'            'Oh, that's where that came from. You must have been confused when I thanked....'           All of a sudden, we heard something thudding down the stairs. My dad was on a business trip, we didn't have any pets, and HRP-4c was in my room. I think.... I ran over to the stairs, and sure enough, there it was. My birthday robot thudding down the stairs.            'I was just tired of singing and dancing.' it said in its robotic voice. 'I wanted to have some friends, like you.'            Honestly, I felt bad for the little thing. I remembered moving to a new school and not having any friends.            'It's okay. I'll be your friend. And later, we'll invite some of my other frineds over, too.'

Item_Response: 'Zoom, swish, zoom!' cars fly by on the highway. But these are not any ordinary cars, these are self-driven cars that have a mind of their own. Their purpose is only to drive their humans wherever they want.       It's been 100 years since a car has crashed. That human was careless, not caring for their car. They didn't charge their robot before they left for  a road trip across the country. But nobody ever makes that mistake anymore.       Most humans didn't want to drive, too  many were getting hurt. The government started to question whether humans should drive anymore... too prone to accidents they said.       The cars now look more like shuttles, shuttles that drive people wherever they want. They have blaring headlights that examine every robot that is in the other lane. They watch out for traffic and tight turns and they know when to slow down.       Robots are now essential to our life. They guide the blind, they assist doctors, and make clean and non-messy pets. They are our future.       When robots started to become a part of our lives humans wondered if they could mess up. But as soon as there was a  first robot surgeon, people no longer questioned the robot race.       Humans no longer consider us as the greatest species, now it is the robots.

Item_Response: BANG, BANG, BANG! 'All finished,' said Rory. She stepped back to examine her work, scrutinizing every detail. Its spider-like legs glistened under the fluorescent lighting. All of a sudden, it's eyes opened! 'That's weird, I don't remember programming it to work all on its own,' said Rory, puzzled.       Much to her surprise the robot appeared to be looking around the room for something. Curious, Rory decided to see just how smart this robot really was, but when the automaton stood up and jumped off the table, Rory started to panic.       'If Mom sees a spider robot running around the house completely out of control, she'll have a cow!' So Rory immediately slammed the door closed with a loud WHAM!       'Is everything OK Rory?' Her mom shouted from downstairs. 'Y-yes, Mom,' she stuttered, 'Everything is fine.' Except it wasn't, the robot had decided that whatever it wanted was not in Rory's hi-tech lab and was heading towards the door!       Rory was surprised by the speed it was progressing, it had already learned more than Rory had programmed it to do, and was learning more every second! Rory decided to just let the robot wander, 'I didn't give it anything to destroy the house with, so it cant do much harm, I'll just carry the remote with me and Mom won't know the difference.'       So Rory snatched the remote off the table and flung open the door. The robot scuttled out, a full 10 paces ahead of her. It didn't even seem to notice the fact that it had just completely trampled Rory's foot. She carefully hopped after the robot down the stairs because she did not want to fall.       The robot was moving so fast that before Rory even got halfway down the stairs, it was out of sight. Rory suddenly remembered her new puppy, Bunny. 'Oh no!' she said, 'Either Mr. Dante won't realize what she is and attack, or Bunny will get scared and run out the doggy door!'       Much to her dismay, Bunny was right at the bottom of the stairs! Mr. Dante had taken notice of the canine and had slowed down and started inching closer to her. But before Rory could get close enough to turn off Mr. Dante he had reached the puppy!       Surprisingly, the robot did not harm Bunny, and she stayed put, not bothering to defend her squeaky toy at all, but pushing it closer to the robot! Mr. Dante took the toy and inserted it in his middle cabinet that Rory had installed, as a way of making him like a moving bedside table.       Rory reached the bottom of the stairs quickly, the pain in her foot having subsided. She was ready at any moment to shut off her creation, but was curious to see what it would do. Bunny began to creep towards Mr. Dante warily still not 100% sure that it wasn't going to harm her.       Abruptly, Bunny sat down on her bottom and begged! Immediately Mr. Dante knew what the puppy wanted. He turned around and said to Rory, 'Your canine would like a walk.' As if on cue, Bunny sprinted into the kitchen and dragged her leash to Rory.       Rory stared open mouthed at Mr. Dante and her puppy. Bunny tossed her leash to Rory. 'Well alright, if you two are so sure about it. Do you want to walk with us Mr. Dante?' said Rory.        Again Mr. Dante turned to Bunny, but this time he made a sound like a bark.  Bunny licked him and sat. Mr. Dante told Rory that when Bunny licked him it meant that she wanted him to come.       'Well alright then!' Rory said, and clipped Bunny's leash onto her collar.

In Massachusetts Institute of Technology they fingered out a way to make the Agribots raise their own plants. Item_Response: One Christmas morning I was just waking up.I had been so excited to see Santa had brought me so many present.After I saw all my present I had ran upstairs to my parents bedroom and woke them up.They both got there robes on and tied them up then headed downstairs.When we got downstairs my mom made breakfast then we ate.After we ate breakfast we sat down and opened present.I was looking around at all my present when I realized I had missed one that was way in the back.I opened my last present and I was so amazed with what I saw.I saw a toy robot.I had been wanting a toy robot since I was 3 years old.After I opened my robot I never wanted to stop playing with it!I even let it sleep with me,but one rainy stormy night I had opened my window and all the sudden a bolt of lightning came in and shocked my robot.I got really really scared so I ran to my parents room to sleep and left my robot behind.The next morning when i went back to my room to get my robot it was gone.I had looked every were upstairs and I could not find it.So then I went downstairs and there it was just siting.I had tried to pick it up and it started talking!I was so astonished I couldn't believe my ears nor my eyes.Then it ran off and started cooking in my kitchen that's when i remembered the lightning bolt hitting it so hard it fell.After I had found out my robot was alive we became best friends I even took it to school.I have had my robot for 15 years now.My robot and i became best friends and we did everything together.My robot was the smartest thing on earth.                 A few years later on July 18,2025 I had got my income taxes back so I went out and got my robot a friend because it will live forever and I will not.When i got home i gave the robot the other robot I had just bought.But what we had to figure out was how to get it alive so we just sat and waited for a stormy night.After a couple weeks it finally came but the next problem was trying to get the lighting to hit the new robot.My robot and I finally figured it out we took medal wires and put them all over the new robot and it worked!Then we brought the robot back in and waited and waited and waited and waited until one morning it was gone and we knew it had finally came alive.So after a while of the new robot getting used to everthing we all became bestfriends and lived happily ever after!

Item_Response: Turfee            Turfee rolled over and felt himself crack something. It was pouring and Turfee's metal layer was exposed. Turfee closed his metal eyelids and accessed his memory card and read through his memories. He was a small robot dog owned by the Cree household, last, they had gone on a family picnic, Turfee was playing with the Cree's young boy, Sam when it happened. It started raining so they started to head back from where they were playing next to a ditch. Sam was playing 'ball' with Turfee so he would toss it and Turfee would fetch it. As it started raining Sam ran back to his family and thought Turfee would follow. As Sam ran the ball slipped out of Sam's left hand and rolled into the ditch. Turfee was programmed to fetch it so Turfee hopped after it. This is where Turfee slipped and fell in to to the deep ditch.            Turfee's virtual processor caught up with what was happening as he tried to stand up. He was on a small ledge on the side of a deep park ditch used to gather water flow. The rain was still pouring down as violently as it possibly could. The water in the bottom of the ditch was rising at a steady rate. The fake fur Turfee's developers had attached to him had fallen off in select places. Turfee thought of everything he could. He looked up and down for a solution. Most humans could easily climb out of the ditch but to a small robot dog, it looked as steep as the walls of the Grand Canyon. Turfee knew he couldn't swim as it would most certainly leak into his electronic insides, so what was Turfee to do!!! At that time a log that had swept down into the ditch floated by, this was Turfee's moment, the moment that would judge if he lived, he jumped, everything seemed to slow down...SPLASH!!!            Turfee landed next to the log sending water splattering everywhere.Turfee spluttered out onto the log, he was okay but he knew some water had leaked in. The rain seemed to get even harder, the only other sound Turfee heard other than the relentless rain was the sound of the rain clanging on his metal layer. Turfee lied down sensing everything as he was slowly getting closer to the top of the perilous ditch as it filled with frosty water. It was now midnight, the moonlight reflecting off of the water that marked his doom. As he got closer to the top, the wind picked up and blew huge gusts of air straight into Turfee's unprotected body. Turfee was never programmed with it but learned with his high-tec what the meaning of fear was, this was it.He was so close to the top he could literally taste salvation. Then came a massive gust of wind, this was too much, the log over-turned and Turfee fell in.            Turfee was swept down with the flow of the water hitting rock and sand. He was pulled around feeling himself break apart. He felt as if he was a mere rag-doll, he swam for his life as he finally broke the surface just to submerge again. The wind blew so hard it started causing waves, Turfee got caught in one sweeping him upwards. He was airborne for a couple seconds before he came crashing down on to hard land. He hit the ground with much velocity. He lied for a minute before standing, he was hurt, very much. Turfee found the place where he had been playing with Sam. He tried hard to remember which direction his master ran to as it started to rain. Then, he heard a noise, no normal noise, but a voice...it was Sam. Turfee ran as fast as his short stubby legs would take him, even with his injuries. He rounded a tree to see one last car parked in the parking lot. He could make out the figures of the Cree family inside, the door opened as Sam yelled out again, 'TURFEEEEEEE!!!!!!' Turfee ran over and surprised Sam. Sam looked surprised to see Turfee in such a state but it didn't matter, Sam took him into the carand hugged him and covered him in a warm blanket. Once again, Turfee's little robot mind, was happy again as they drove home.

Item_Response: One day a scientist was creating a robot to help with his studies but he had tried this many times and he always failed. No matter how much he tried he couldn't get it to work right. It would turn on but it woulg only stay on for a minute. After many days of trying he   decided to take a break. He took the robot outside and decided to sleep for the night.            That night it a meteor hit close to the scientist's house but all those days up left him deeply asleep. The meteor cracked open and a glowing orb came out of it and was rolling towards the robot which the doctor left outside and wgon the orb entered the robot something amazing happened. The robot turned on and he was like no other robot he looked human. He had emotions, he had strength, and he had brains.         The next morning the scientist woke up with a suprise. He had food on the table but who cooked it? It suprised him when he saw his robot flipping pancakes. The robot greated him and put him in a chair to eat. The scientist was overfilled with joy his invention came to live. The scientist was curious about what had happened.        The robot showed him the meteor and he saw all the blue matter  in the meteor and the scientist was amazed. He didn't care about that he had to work on his studies. they worked three days and nights but a serum spilled on Tim the robot which the scientist named him and he turned off and never  awoke again.       The scientist was sad but he learned to make more and the world became a better place. the world never forgot Tim the robot because he was the first robot to ever really live.

Item_Response: '10,000 years into the future, we still haven't managed to make a living robot.' says the leader of Science Co., Andrea Hagge. 'We made a time machine and yet we cant make a robot that lives , breaths, thinks, and talks? Wow am I... a bit disappointed.' Andrea then walks into her room, thinking.' The formula was right,' to herself. 'Maybe we should use the time machine formula.   ' She begins to work.       Five hours later, Andrea walks out of the room looking perplexed. 'I got it,' she says to an imaginary crowd. 'I got it.' All she needs to do is plug it in, start it breathing, spark its brain, well, actually a brain made of pulled pork, but anyway, it will work. Andrea is over confident, no what if it doesn't'ts in her head. She plugged it in, 'Oh my gosh' she thinks. 3...2...1... It worked. It is as simple as that.       The robot is as big as a St. Bernard, but looks like a cat. 'Meow?' it asks. 'Meow?' It gets up, purring like mad. Andrea starts to make a skin for it, using an old mountain lion pelt coat to begin. It already fit the Cat-bot, as she called the creature, but it needed to be permanent. A dash of glue here and a stitch or two there, it was on! That was when the Cat-bot saw a bird out the window, and  Andrea blacked out.       When she awoke, she had no clue why she couldn't breathe. Looking on her stomach, she saw why. Baby Cat-bots. How, where, when, and why might be good questions to ask,but she didn't. She said to herself,'Awww, arnet they cute?' And then went on to find out how she blacked out. 'Tail musta hit me' she said with a shrug. 'Where is mommy?' she said in a baby voice. 'Out catching us a birdie to eat.' Said one of the baby's.Andrea just gaped.       'You, you can talk?' She said in an astounded voice. 'Of course we can, silly.' said yet another. 'Wow did I miss a lot in 7th grade health.' Andrea said to herself.       Well how an this go anywhere? Is probably what you're thinking, but it did. The cat-bots grew up, and spontaneously had kids of their own. They went to all kinds of pet shops, hospitals, and even dentists offices. Andrea never shared her secret of how she made them, though. Only cat bots would be robots that could live and breathe. What Andrea didnt know was that if she had gone only one year more, 10,001 years into the future, that she would have seen a cat-bot!!!                                                   THE END

Item_Response: T-46 was getting built on in the garage of Rover Davidson's house. T-46 was supposed to help bring the end to electronic collapses. One thing Rover didn't know is that T-46 was already alive. Although it was painful to be tightened and screwed into place he had to pretend to not be alive. T-46 has grown a bond to this human working on him. He had spent many hours in the garage improving T-46, but since T-46 was not moving Rover was getting restless. However Rover kept building on T-46. T-46 could hear a stiffness in his voice when he was mumbling to himself. He could tell rover was depressed. T-46 couldn't bear to see Rover like this, after all Rover has done for him T-46 decided to do something that would change his and Rover's life forever. T-46 decided to move.                      Rover was completely baffled by the movement by T-46 he didn't know what to do. The next thing T-46 saw was Rover running around outside of his garage screaming 'I did it, I did it, I created a robot!' T-46 began to move around to Rover to excite him more. But the thing Rover didn't know was they weren't the only people in the garage.       There were 2 spies hiding behind a filled up trash can getting information on T-46.  Although T-46 was built to bring an end to electronic collapses. He could do much more.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Inside Rover figured out just a little bit of what T-46 could do. T-46 sprinted up the was because he was so excited. In fact he could only feel emotions of what Rover was feeling. So he was excited. T-46 could literally bounce off the wall because of his rubber wheels for legs. Also Rover had installed a one digit button code on T-46's right arm to help him speak, and finally on T-46's left arm there was another digit button code that changes his hand into many weapons. Rover didn't intentionally do that but he soon figured out when T-46 blasted his oven into particles.                                                                                                                                                                                   Chapter Two                                                                            Inside the main spy headquarters General Anthony McCullough and General Ethan Klaiss were studying the robot that could change their country's military power the 2 spies checked in. The first spy said 'General McCullough, sir did you see what hat robot just did?' General McCullough just nodded. The General Klaiss ordered, 'bug up the house, put cameras there, we need to get that robot.' The second spy spoke up, 'we will be scorched alive if we try to capture it, he will burn us to death.' General McCullough groaned at the thought, then he said, 'We payed you to take that robot, no matter what the cost.' The first spy just had a thought, 'what if we take the creator instead, then the robot will feel scared and depressed since it has the same feelings.' General Klaiss liked that idea, he nodded and said, 'we will do that, and that plan is effective immediately, boys this could change the world.'                          Rover was just finishing up on T-46's new applience, because he had the same idea as the spies about it being a weapon. Rover was always a greedy man. He always wanted to be in power. He thought 'now that I have Rover i can overthrow the US government!' he was so excited, but T-46 had mind-reading abilities and saw what Rover was planning to do. T-46 thought 'I have to escape.'                                                                 TO BE CONTINUED... Item_Response: If no one can hang out and play, what do you do? If your parents are busy or your siblings aren't home, what do you do? I wish I could hang out with someone right now. Lily thought. She went downstairs and turned on the TV. She groaned as the history channel popped up. 'Who cares about a bunch of robots? All they are is a wast of time and effort.' said Lily with annoyance in her tone. All I want to do is play make-up with Sophie and Stacy. Lily went up stairs and started to comb her hair. I love having long hair! To bad I don't know how to do cool hair designs.          'Ive got it,' she screamed with excitement,' I'll make a robot that can do my hair!'   How am I supposed to make a robot? She looked around her room. Her eyes caught sight of and old making electricity game she used to play with her brother. She went over to it and open the box. It was filled with battery's and wires and metal. She grabbed the box and ran downstairs. Into the office she went to look for her old paints and paint brushes. It was filled with tons and tons of different beautiful colors. The size of the brushes vary-ed from huge to tiny.        She took the boxes into the kitchen and put all of her supplies on the tile. opening the boxes she separated the shades of colors, sizes of brushes, batteries from wires, and wires from light-bulbs. She took the sheets of metal and began to cut into the shape of a robot. When she created the body she went and grabbed her biggest paint brush and took the prettiest dark purple and painted over the body.         'This is going to be the prettiest robot the world has ever seen!' Lily said out loud.     Then, she took the wires and the batteries and connected them. To see if it work she gently put the metal part of the wire on a lightbuld. The lightbulb instantly lite up making Lily jump. she placed the wires right where they were supposed to go and connected them to the wheels at the bottom of the robot. the arms of the robot were movable so the robot could do someones hair. She made the face all nice and cute. It looks like the robot  from wall-e. She laughed and chuckle at her own little joke and then continued her creation.         The batteries were the placed into the head along with the wires. After connecting the batteries and wires she took the blue little light-bulbs and put them into the eye holes. Inside of the box she found a light switch. she put it on the side of the robot and made all the other cords longer so it could reach it. The robot was beautiful! I cant wait to show mom! She ran downstairs to the office and saw her mom. \          'Mommy! Mommy! look what I made!' Her mother wiped around and smiled with a grin on her face.           'What do you have there?' her mother asked with concern but amusement in her voice.         'I made a robot that can do my hair!'          'Well, lets see if it works!'        Lily placed the robot on the floor as her mom sat next to her. She combed her hair real quick and then turned on the robot. The robots eyes lite up and the arms moved. Her mom jumped as they lite up. The robot rolled its way over to Lily she turned around and it braided her hair!         'The robot works mom!' she said as they both jumped into the air and celebrated.         ' Oh Lily I am so proud of you.' She flicked the switch off and gave Lily a big hug.        'Well, tell me. what are you going to name it?'        'Well I'm not really sure. I think Ill name her... Millie!'         'What a perfect name.' Her mom said.           When they went up stairs they showed her dad as he walked into the house, coming back from work. They all went out to dinner to celebrate the great invention. They even brought Millie with them.        The nexted day Sophie and Stacy came over and she showed them too. They played make-up together and had a great time.                                                                        THE END

Item_Response: Robots       Robots are usually seen in science fiction movies or read in fantasies. Not any more! There are robots all over the world doing things from picking berries to traveling deep into volcanoes! Here are some cool things that robots can do.       The robot Gemini-Scout is a life saver. The Gemini-Scout can go into collapsed mines and rescue miners! This specially programed robot uses a thermal camera to find miners. Also when and if it finds survivors it can carry the injured back to the surface. Also it can find out if there are any harmful gases and then he cane tell the miners if it is good or not. Also the Gemini-Scout can go through water. The Gemini-Scout  can carry food and supplies to the survivors. Obviously the Gemini-Scout is a real life saver!       The robot Dante 2 is a robot with a very cool job. This robot goes into or onto volcanoes and it gathers information for scientists. The Dante 2 has spider like legs to help it go up the steep slopes of volcanoes. I think that it would be very cool to be able to go into a volcano. You might think, wouldn't the Dante 2 get burnt? Well, you might think that but is built so that the heat doesn't hurt him! This helps scientist a lot to learn more about volcanoes.       Mr.Gower is a robot that helps in hospitals. This robot helps carry medicine to nurses, doctors, and patients. Mr.Gower looks like a cabinet on wheels. Mr.Gower is very strong so the weight of the medicine isn't a problem to him. The robot can go anywhere in a hospital, including elevators, hallways, and it can push things that are in the way. Mr.Gower can say various phrases like,' Calling elevator' and 'You delivery is here!' Mr.Gower is a big help for the nurses.       You may be thinking, Or they should make a robot that does my chores. If so you are in luck, if you live on a farm with berries, apples, or pears. Now you may be thinking, Well what are you waiting for tell me, tell me! Okay, the robot that can pick berries is called the Agribot. The Agribot is a robot programmed to pick berries. The robot sees if the berry is ripe by looking at the color then if it is then it picks it! The Agribot can come in all shapes and sizes. Some have giant arms and are pulled by trucks, some can move on their own. These robot can change the berry industry. I know this because the scientist are testing to see if the Agribots are able to grow a farm on their own, with no human help! They are programmed to scan the fruit, to see what it needs, then the robot tends to the fruit! It's that simple!       There are so many awesome things that robots can do! There are robots that save peoples lives, some that gather information, some that act like farmers. I believe that robots can become a huge help to people in the future, I mean, just look what they are doing now! They could also make robots that baby sit or some robots that play games like hockey or shuffleboard (they are working on that right now : ) )! I think that we should continue to create robots for today and for the future.

Item_Response: GLaDoS and John       One autumn day long ago in Seattle, 2222, there was a young boy by the name of John Infinite Rapture who loved to create things. Planes with real working propellers, trains that could travel up and down walls, but his favorite invention was a small metal robot named GLaDoS. He loved to play with GLaDoS. John once took her to the beach to swim, and on that very same day, his mother told him about the underwater city of Atlantis. He was simply fascinated hearing about the city. 'One day,' he said to GLaDoS, 'I'm going to build and underwater city where everyone can live!' And that is exactly what he did. On his 22nd birthday, the beautiful aquatic city of Rapture was unveiled to the whole world. 'Rapture spans the entire Pacific Ocean and can hold up to 5,222,222,222,002 people!' John said at the opening ceremony. And 2 years later, the city had a population of 2,222,222,222,022. After that, John lived a silent life and sometimes pulled out GLaDoS, then he got an idea. 'Wait here GLaDoS!' he exclaimed excitedly, ' Your finally going to come to life!' When John turned 32, he finished his P0RTAL machine. It had the power to bring anything to life, so of course GLaDoS was the first to test it. 'GLaDoS! I have waited may years to do this! Now our dreams will finally come true!' A gentle tear rolled down his cheek. He turned on the machine and a brilliant flash of blue and yellow appeared. 'YES! YES!' He roared. Then suddenly, POP! Everything stopped and out came GLaDoS. Walking on two legs, metal gleaming, her brilliant blue eye sparkling. 'Hello, master. I have waited many years to meet you.' John let another tear roll down. 'Oh please! Call me John.' In the years that followed, he built GLaDoS a husband and named him WALL-E, and he himself got married to a woman named Clementine and had 2 children named Lee and Carley. 'Okay we both know that last part.' said Lee. 'And why did you tell it in third-person?' added Carley. 'I think it sounded quite better than if it had been in first-person point of view.' said GLaDoS, in her same old robotic voice. 'Yes.' agreed WALL-E. 'Thank you. At least someone appreciates my stories.' I thanked. 'Time for dinner!' Clem yelled from the kitchen, 'Pasta and garlic bread!' 'YES!' Carkey and Lee exclaimed gleefully. 'We are also famished.' said WALL-E. 'I've got extra oil and gasoline.' I said. 'That would fill our tanks, yes.' 'It's in the garage.' 'Thank you, John.' added GLaDoS. I nodded and walked into the kitchen.

Item_Response: Danny had always dreamed of having an expensive electric toy that would be his.He knew that he could only dream.Everything that was in his home were from the donation basket.The basket where his clothes and shoes came from.He can still remember the time when he was 4 years old.He had asked for a teddy bear at the Cuddle Bear Toy Store,but his parents didn't buy it for him.Until now,he never touched a toy.But his whole life changed.          December was coming by rapidly.As Danny walked to school in the snowy air,he saw toy stores filled with astonishing toys.Just when he was about to reached the school area,he saw a toy robot that seemed unusual.It had wheels and was about two feet tall.It looked strong enough to drag people!He wanted to go inside and check the price of the robot,but there was only 2 minutes until school was about to start.Maybe I could check it after school,he thought.Paying attention to the teacher was difficult.Danny daydreamed about the robot during science,math,language arts,and history.He was waiting for the bell to ring when suddenly Tony sneaked up behind him.          'Hey dude!'exclaimed Tony.          'Hey.'replied Danny.          Danny didn't feel like talking to Tony.All he wanted to do was to go see if the robot was still there.          'Um,hey Tony,I have to go now;I have something to do.'          'Do what?'          'Hey look,it's personal business okay?'          'Fine you can go ahead and do whatever you want;I don't care anymore!'          Tony left Danny standing there grimacing.I don't need a friend like that,he thought to himself.By the time he was at the toy store,he was shocked.The price was too much for him to bear.It was $235!He was desperate for that much money.He left without taking a look at the robot.Danny's mom was suspicious.Ever since coming back from school,Danny looked despondent.          'Danny,are you okay?'she asked.          'I'm fine;It's just about the toy I want.'          'Oh Danny you know we do not have very much money;Just paying our apartment and bills is almost not enough.'          'But I could work at some place..like the hardware store or something!'          Danny knew it wasn't worth fighting for.His family would never have that much money.All of a sudden,Danny's older brother,Daniel,came rushing inside the apartment.          'Mom!Danny!'screamed Daniel.          'Oh what is it Daniel?'asked Mom sternly.          'Guess what?I found $1000 dollars on the sidewalk!'          Mom and Danny was surprised.Now Danny could buy the robot!          'Hey Daniel can I borrow $235?'          'What do you need it for?'asked Daniel with sarcasm in his voice.         'Since it's Christmas,I would like to purchase something from the toy store.         Daniel didn't feel like giving away $235.He wanted the money to himself.         'Daniel just give the money to Danny.'         Daniel had to obey Mom.Once the money was in his hands,Danny ran out to the toy store.         'Um, sir I would like to buy that robot over there.'         Danny pointed to the window.The cashier looked at Danny and nodded.Walking back to his home with his new toy was making the children envious.Just when he was about to put the robot on the ground,the robot turned it's head and stared at Danny.Danny was amazed.This robot is alive.He took it home and showed it to his mom and brother.They were astonished too.Cool was the word Daniel used for it.The robot could clean the house,help with homework,and talk.As years flew by,the robot started to break slowly.Danny noticed the changes the robot had made.After coming back from work and visting his mother's tomb,Danny found his robot not working properly.          'What's wrong?'          The robot looked at Danny one more time and blinked a goodbye.

Item_Response: 'RC-ARV''                                                           by Santiago B.           One day, in January 10, 2008, I got bored from staying in my house to long, then I wished I had an advanced robot.I had nothing to do so I took a shower, and went to sleep.The next morning I felt something heavy on my blankit, and to my suprise it was there, a robot!           I got up early and prepared myself as usual every morning ,then I looked at it.The robot had long wheels, a camara for an eye, a claw with three fingers, and a box you could put stuff in.It was no bigger than a foot wide, and surprisingly heavy.   I then decided it needed a name at first i suggested 'Ziggy', then I suggested ''p-47'', finally I came up with ''RC-ARV.''           I showed it to my mom and she looked surprised,''WOW'' she said ''Where did that come from'' I told her ''I don't know...'',  I took a moment to look at it, ''...it's really strange isn't it.'' I grabbed the remote and tested it, the screen showing where ''RC-ARV'' looked at,I then noticed a strange joystick, and moved it, making the claw shift from side to side.Then,I pressed the arrow buttoms which drive and steer the robot, and the red buttom which opened, and closed the claw.           At night, I noticed it glows in the dark, and looked at it,it glowed bright green, in fact enough to light a room, there was so much things I never even knew about it.During the years, the robot started becoming more useful that it is like a member of the family, I even realized it had a really strong grip that it could lift a plane.The kids that looked at it said it looked ''COOL'' or ''AWESOME'' nevertheless the robot is welcome anytime.

Item_Response: There are all types of robots around the world.A gemini-scout is a robot that people can controll. It also is a rescue robot that can detect when people are alive.They can also tell when people are introuble or when they are trapped, and they also tell miners when the air is filled with gas and when it is safe to go somewhere.Gemini-scouts can also carry things like food, water, and other things.They can collect information whereever it goes, and it has heat sensors that can when there are living things around. It looks like a viedeo controller.         Some other types of robots are Dante 2, Mr.Grower, Agribots, a HRP-4c, and the Google car.A Dante 2 can climb up steep hills they help scientists get innformation about volanoes.When there is something dangerous that scientists can't do they have the Dante 2 do it.Dante 2 also collects information for the scientists.Mr.Grower works in a hospital.They give the nurses and the doctors the medicine for the patients.Mr.Grower is like a small cabinet except on wheels, and it can also turn really hard turns.It is really strong that it could pull a 500 pound truck, and it could also go on elevators and it goes on batteries it charges about twelve hours and doesn't stop working.It could also talk it could say about hundred phrases.          An Agribot picks fruits from trees the fruits it picks are grapes, oranges,apples, and berries.It works with scientists which they grow plants like cherrys or other things.Some of them have huge arms that are towed on to trucks.They don't have peoples help planting, and they also have farms that they grew by thierselves.thier arms are mechanical. A Google car is like the most popular robot ever.If someone ever rode it they would prbably be popular.It has a $80,000 cone-shape laser mounted on its roof.The people that rode the car other people probably thought they were driving it but they actually weren't.They were probably surprised that they didn't have to drive it.           That is my story about robots and how they are helpful to  people. There could be animal robots or regular robots.People are actually interested by robots. If I ever had a robot it would be my best friend and it would do my homework for me.If you ever had a robot what would be to you.

Item_Response: My first robot I have ever seen was dead.Well I found it in a dumpster and took it in. I found a plug inside of the robot and plugged it in an outlet. Sadly, it didn't do anything.       I was so angry that I almost threw it back in the dumpster. So, I went outside and went over to my friend, Billie's house. I explained it to him how I found it. 'So you're saying that you found a robot in the dumpster in the trashcan?'   'Yes.'   'Well you should've known that it wasn't going to work because it was in the trash.'       Well I went back home then all of a sudden I get to my room and I see the robot scavenging through my room. I was astonished. I was so happy that I had a real live robot in my room. So i asked it what its name was. 'My name is Dante 2 and I help scientists look through volcanoes.' Dante 2 said. 'Do you remember who you worked for?' I asked. 'I work for a man named Dr. Parker.' So, I looked up on the internet who Dr. Parker is. I found out that he worked for NASA. Therefore, I looked up NASA phone number. When I saw the number, I called NASA and asked for Dr. Parker. 'He is on vacation today, would you like me to leave him a message?'    'Yes please, tell him I found his robot named Dante 2.'    'Okay, thank you for calling and I will contact him later today.'       So, I went over to Billie's and told him about how the robot worked for NASA.   'Really'?   'Yeah.'   'So,what are you going to do with him?'   'I'm going to return him to his owner, Dr. Parker.' So, after my talk with Billy, the man contacted me,and told me that Dr. Parker is on the other line.   'So, you have Dante 2.' he said.   'Yeah, I found him in a dumpster.'   'Well come over and give me my robot back.' he said.       So, I went and gave Dr. Parker his robot back and Dante 2 went back to searching robots.So, that was the first time I ever seen robot in real life.

Item_Response: In the big city of San Francisco, CA, lived a scientist who wanted to make the world a better place. His name is, Dr. Vectro, a 65 year old man with very little hair and a very skinny body. He lives in a small lab, just by himself and is divorced. He was divorced, because Dr. Vectro was a very odd man.               What he has been trying to do for fifty years of his life is to make a robot. Not just any robot, but a big robot. Today his dream came true. 'I've done it! I finally made the world's biggest robot!' He exclaimed. The robot measured eighty feet tall, and a whopping 300 tons!                 The strangest thing about the creation is that it needed batteries. He put in 3 D-4's to make it work. That is how he got the name for the robot, DV-4. [The V is for the start of his last name.] When he was finished with his creation, he didn't exactly know what he wanted to do with it. There was an on switch on the robot, but Dr. Vectro didn't have the guts to turn it on. Then right before he went to bed, he decided to turn it on.                  In the morning when he got his glass, of milk, he realized it fealt a little breezy. He went to his garage, and he couldn't believe what he saw, his robot was gone, and there was a big hole in his garage. He figured that his robot came to life and ran away. He was depressed, he spent all day looking for him, he even put up posters saying he had a missing robot. Then he got a call, the man on the other line told him that he found his robot and that he ripped the batteries out of it, because it was causing a riot. The man said he will return it to him shortly. The man returned the robot. Dr. Vectro gave the robot to a meuseum, but he told the meuseum this, 'Dont give the robot 3 D-4 batteries!'

The robot said,' i would like to eat.' so the professor got him some oil and the robot devoured it.                  The professor made him a bed in the basement out of straw and then went to sleep. The next morning he couldn't find his robot. he later found out that at it had died because he didn't have a very good battery and he died. The professor tried to give him a new battery but he didn't work again.                    Professor Jimmy was very sad after yje incident with the dead robot , so he tried to make a new one but he could never make a robot that worked again.                    Later the professor died of a heart attack and found the robot up in heaven.

Item_Response: John              One day I was playing with my robot toy. It was green with two hands and also two legs, kind of like a human. I had just received it for my birthday. It was the best present anyone had ever given me. I felt very happy.When I heard my sister called so I looked, suddenly I heard a noise as if something had fallen. When i turn around there was nothing there. Then another noise, so I turned around when suddenly I saw something moving, it was my robot. I could not believe my eyes, he was alive. I was scared and happy at the same time. I did not know what to do. That was when i learned that it could be a good opportunity to have fun.                     I got close to the robot, when I was there i tried to speak to it, but it would not answer. I tried to make it feel comfurtable so it would speak. Then it started to talk, he said that he wanted to be friends. From that moment i decided to name it John. I took it for a walk to ask him what sort of things did it like to do. He replied that he liked to do things as eating, walking and having electronics. So what we did was that we to eat pizza because we were both hugry, i asked it if it did alot of things. He said he could clean rooms since it had a trash holder and a thing to pick up trash. Since my room was a mess I told it to clean up my room, it was finished in 30 seconds.After that we went on a walk to the park. We got some ice cream and we palyed soccer. We had lots of fun and we did not go home until 9:30 PM. When we got home we ate again then I asked it 'do you need to sleep?' he repplied 'no, I only need to be charged since I requiered batteries.' Then I put it to charge and i went to sleep. From that day on we did the same things every day.                      In conclusion, me and my best birthday present or my robot became very good fiends. We always spent time together, we went to places and we have fun. From that moment, i knew that i had found a true friend that really cared for my.

'Alan can you hear me'  Yelled The scientist, but all could was gears winding. He got up to turn on the emergency power. Once he turned the power own. It was hit by a car. It flew across the street and hit the ground. Shaun ran over to it. 'what happened' the robot said. Shaun was so startled he dropped the robot.       He made friends with the robot. Shaun and the robot started to walk home. 'what is your name' he said. 'I don't have a name' The robot said sadly. 'I will call you Fred' said Shaun. They walk home laughing and talking. The robot fixed him self up. They helped each other. They lived happly ever after.

Item_Response: The Robot that Came Alive                                          By James Rohde                   In the year 2175, a scientist has created a robot that can do human work but without failing. This robot was named Dave after the scientist who created it, but the robot was created with a memory chip that can detect emotions, violence, and sound. The robots main memory is the 'brain'. The 'brain' has the ability to think on its own and move on its own. It was created to be human-like and can transform into a hover-bot.               Davis was one of the many functional robots but this robot was unique. The other robots can only follow orders from human beings, but Dave can think on its own and not follow orders. Soon Dave reprogramed all of the other robots and started to take over the world. Dave reprogramed him to be a hologram so he would not be destroyed by a single bullet. Instead he put himself in a anti-blast and bulletproof mainframe. If any human would get into it a nuclear bomb would detonate and wipe human beings off from the city.                   Dave was starting to conquer other continents and enslaving people. Many people rebeled but were killed by Dave's powerful robot army. Dave was practically invincible but Dave's creator, Dave Tecky, installed a tiny nuclear bomb in Dave's brain that would destroy him for good, but Dave was way ahead of his creator. Dave installed guard robots at the failsafe so no one can get through. Even if they did get through the gas in the failsafe could kill every non-robot in the room. Little did Dave know that Tecky made a secret entrance to the failsafe. Tecky went in and the room went into high alert robots from everywhere came to the room and started to get Tecky but Tecky quickly hit the failsafe and Dave was destroyed for good. To this day, robots with minds of its own were banned from the world.

Item_Response: It was just another hot summer day in Roseville. Juliet Seedsim and her older brother, Gregory, were bickering as usual.' Mom,' yelled Juliet,' Greg is hogging the fan!' Greg always enjoyed annoying his little sister.' How about you both find something else to do and try to spend some quality time together instead of arguing,' said Mr. Seedsim as he came up stairs.         For once, Greg and Juliet actually had to spend time together. They had to do something, but what? ' We should read magazines together?' asked Juliet.' That's girly,' said Greg. 'How about we play darts?' Juliet shook her head no.'I know what you two should do,' said their father.' You should make a robot. That's what your aunt and I used to do when we were kids. You'll be surprised about how magical it is.'The siblings looked at each other. ' Perfect!' said Juliet and Greg in unison.            They gathered their materials and ran to the kitchen table. Greg brought empty soup cans, wires, solar panels, and oil. Juliet brought glitter, pipe wires, blue metal, and fake eyeballs. As soon as they knew it, the robot was completed. ' Okay. Here's the moment of truth!' said Juliet pulling at her long, brown hair nervously. Once they plugged it into the outlet, it didn't work.' Let's try another outlet. If that doesn't work, than we we'll try the solar panels.' said Greg.          No matter what they did, the robot didn't work.' It's all your fault.' said  Juliet crossing her arms.' My fault?,' said Greg,' Your the one who brought all the glitter. It probably got caught inside and cut the wire when you were sprinkling it!'Juliet was astonished that Greg would blame it on her when he insisted that she should decorate it any way she wanted to.' Uh uh.'Uh ha.' They continued for an hour, until they were sent to their rooms. The next day, they couldn't believe their eyes!         'Oh my goodness!' screamed  Juliet as she came down the stairs for breakfast. ' Greg! Gregory! Mr. Seedsim! Big brother wake up!' shouted Juliet. Soon, Greg came down stairs and it didn't take long before he spit out he cup of water he was drinking. The 4 feet robot was walking around the house and got Greg another cup of water!' Did you do this?' asked Greg. ' No, I thought you did.'Juliet replied. When Greg and Juliet asked their parents if they had fixed the robot, they each said they didn't.     ' Wait a minute,' said Juliet ,' Didn't you say that you had to plug the robot in to work?' Yeah, why,' said Greg.' Well, the solar panels aren't attached, the sun hasn't completely come up, and Jonah's not plugged in.' Greg looked down at the robot and saw that the robot really wasn't plugged into the outlet.     ' Just like Dad said  it's magical.' said Juliet.' Come on Jewel, I think at age 10 you shouldn't believe in magic.' It is magic Greg. It doesn't matter if I'm 12 like you or 10. Dad said so himself.' The robot walked up to Greg and shook his hand.' If it wasn't magic then where did I come from?' Greg was speechless.After that, the siblings argued about what really happened.' Gregory Joe Seedsim! Juliet May Seedsim! Come here NOW!' shouted Mrs. Seedsim.     ' What is this?' asked Vicky Seedsim pointing to a laundry basket. 'A laundry basket?'said Gregory trying not to laugh. 'Juliet, go grab that basket for me.'demanded Mrs. Seedsim. 'Sure. Hey mom what happened to your hai-' She was cut off when her mother gave her a don't-say- it-look. Juliet got up and  to go grab the basket when she suddenly disappeared out of no where.' MOM! Where did she go?' asked Greg in a panicking voice.' Oh she'll be back in three... two... one.' Juliet came out of thin air with her hair sticking up like a mad scientist.     'HAHAHAHAHAH!' laughed Greg pointing to Juliet's hair. 'Where... HAHAH...where..HAHAHA...did you...HAHA...go?' asked Greg in-between laughs.' For your information, it was a portal that was so amazing that you should see for your self,' said Juliet as she pushed her brother into the portal.' That was awesome!' said Greg when he came back.' Do you think it was magic now?' asked Juliet with a smile as big as Mount Everest.' Definitely,' said Greg.                                                                                                      Soon, George Seedsim walked in.' I see everyone found the magic portal.' said Mr. Seedsim.' You knew about this George?' said Mrs. Seedsim. 'As a child when I would build robots, they would work at first, but then they would magically be fixed and a magic portal would take us on adventures.'         ' Hey everyone, Jonah's going to tell us all of his cool features!' Everyone listened to Jonah and learned  that he could to a lot of  activities such as save lives, turn into a car, and even go into volcanoes without melting.In the end, Jonah some how brought the family closer together, and Juliet and Greg didn't argue as much. Jonah had even saved the family by carrying them out of a mine. They all had many adventures in the portal thanks to Jonah!

Item_Response: Molly                                       Arnold was thinking about making a robot that could take care of his children           while he and his wife worked. He thought this was the greatest idea he has ever had.             Someone taking care of his children might not really be 'taking care' of them, but             a robot will do whatever it is programmed to do.                      Arnold decided that he would get his wife's approval before he started working               on the robot. When Arnold his wife and children were eating dinner, he told them                 he could make a robot that would take care of the kids better than a real babysit-                ter. His wife was astonished because she was really over protective of her children              and would never let somebody other than him alone with their chilren.                      The next day Arnold got to work. He built the robot a little taller than the child-            ren. He made a remote control so he can turn it on and off, he programmed it to make              beds, wash dishes and clothes, cook food, play with the children and understand what          people were saying. Then he named it Molly. He made sure everything functioned prop-            erly and went to sleep.                Arnold woke up the next day to the sound of his children laughing. They were playing          with the robot. He asked how it got out of his lab and they all shrugged and said that she        made them breakfast. Arnold ignored it and got dressed told the kids to behave and went         to work. When he got home his wife was arguing with the robot about her quiting and        she wasnt supposed to do that he shut her down and threw her away .
