Item_Response: Robots Equals Trouble              On day,while going back to my house from a field trip,I felt like something was following me. There wasn't anything every time I looked behind me. I started to run home because I was getting worried. When I got to my door,I checked behind me to just make sure no one was following me. I got home at about 7:25,so I just showered,ate,and went to sleep.              Later,I was about to stop playing video games and go to sleep the next day,but I heard a loud noise in the kitchen. My parents were out of town,so it couldn't be them. My sister was having a sleep party over at her friends house. She wasn't going to be back till Sunday. I looked at my iPod,but it said Saturday.'Maybe we are getting robbed',I thought.When I was about to smack this intruder upside the head,around the corner I saw a dog's outline of a shadow. 'What!', I exclaimed in my mind.               A second later,I turned the corner and to my surprise it was a dog. It looked robotic though. 'How would a dog get into my house?',I asked myself. I wasn't asking it a question,but it answered. It said it was a failed nucular project by the government. I was thinking to get that thing out of my house before my house is nuked! The dog,Moab later what he called himself,said that he was a normal dog before he was taken away from his family and experimented on by the government.He told me Moab standed for 'Mother Of All Bombs'.He also told me he was following me yesterday in order to get the whereabouts of his owners. It seemed that I new his owner about four years ago. Sussie Red was the owner's name.                 After the talk,I called Sussie to see if she still lived in the area. She only lived two miles away and it was her birthday. 'Wouldn't that be a great present to give Sussie?',I asked Moab. He paused and said his original name was Sparky. Okay...do you want me to call you Moab or Sparky',I asked. He said he would prefer Sparky.He seemed really depressed after I was about to drop him at Sussie's house.He wondered I she wouldn't love him anymore because of his robot look. I told him she will love him no matter how he looks. I gave Sparky to Sussie and the hugged each other. I told Sussie happy birthday,got some cake, and left. Sussie told me that beacause I brought Sparkey back, that was the best birthday ever. She thanked me and then I went home. I still never went to sleep.

Item_Response: The Robot             There was a boy names James and he lives in an odd town named Picklesville. Everyone that lives here are all very strange, but James is strange in a good way. One dark day, James got to school by the old rusty bus. All the cars were rusty because there were HUGE factories where they bottle up pickles and sold them. The acid like gas from the factories rusts the cars. James walks to school with great enthusiasm. James always loves to learn new things. James walks to class and sits down. 'Good morning class...', said Mrs.Ordanski boringly, the teacher. 'Good morning', said the class in unison. 'Today we will start out 9th annual science fair.' sighs Mrs.Ordanski.   The whole class moans except for James. James was very excited. During the next few hours James just thinks about what he wants to do at the science fair. The bell rings and the class files out. 'Not pickle soup again!' moans Billy, James's best friend. The pickle soup was cold and bitter like it always was.                                                          After school James ran home to tell his parents. 'Well, What do you want to do at the science fair?' said mom. 'I don't know yet.' said James. 'How about you make a robot?',said dad. 'WOW, YEA!',said James with great excitement. James sprints towards his garage and grabs the parts he needs. The next morning James started to build his robot. James and the other children only had school for 2 days. The teachers hate to teach. In the next few hours James completes his robot. James turns him on. 'Good morning', said the robot. 'Good morning to you!' said James happily.              The next morning James took his robot to school. 'Today will be such fun!',said James. When he gets to school James thinks the robot looks funny. 'Hhhhhhmmmmm', said James. The bell rings and James quickly walks into the classroom with his robot. 'Wow, James looks like you win the science project again since no one else even participates.',said Mrs.Ordanski. 'Hello everybody',said the robot painfully. After lunch James visits the robot. 'James I feel funny', said the robot. With that the robot broke apart. James had totally forgotten about the acid like gases from the pickle factories. 'Thanks for helping me with the science fair',said James in tears. James takes the robot parts home and waits until next year's science fair...

Item_Response: Scientist, have now made a robot to go to Pluto We will explore Pluto through this robot. This Robots name is Buddy. Buddy has high power, heavy duty wheels. He is about 2 feet in height and 4 feet in width. Buddy has sensors to tell if he will run into anything and crash. Scientist will be controlling Buddy from earth, and hopefully his landing will be successful. We are exploring Pluto for absolutely no reason at all. Since humans cannot get to Pluto, we decided to have a robot go and explore. We would like to see if there is any landforms, or life on Pluto.             Buddy safely, and successfully landed on Pluto. The rocket was launched at 8 am. in the morning, and landed on Pluto at 12 pm. the next day. Buddy was not hurt, he was still working. Scientist discovered that there were no landforms on Pluto, but... They did find life. We are not sure if this is a living organisim or not. To describe it, it was about 3 foot tall and it had tenticals that spread out and looked like a star. This creatures body looked like a squid, but there was something peculiar about this creature. It had ears as big as elephants, and a nose similar to a pigs. What color was this creature? It was an undescribable color. It was as black as night. and it was hard to see the details unless you were close. If you got really close you can see little sparkles and designs all down the tenticals. Different lines, nothing you have ever seen before. Suddenly this strange creature strikes the robot with one of its tenticals, leaving a big gaping hole in Buddy. The creature left a big black mark on Buddy. Buddy starts to shut down. The creature strikes again, leaving another black mark on Buddy. Now he is shut down all the way. The computers that are wirelessly connected to buddy turn all black. Blackness starts to seep out and take over the computer. All of the black goes away, and the computer monitor is back on. Buddy is not programed to talk, but he goes. He said strange words. I am not sure if they were words or not. He started moving all by himself, with no one controlling him. Either someone was haking into the system or Buddy was alive!               After an hour of watching Buddy move. It shut off and started to go home all by himself. When he got back to earth, we studied the black gaping holes in Buddy. That trip to Pluto was interesting, but we didn't gather much information, since the computer had shut down again

Item_Response: Kate the robot    Kate the robot is a fish  that goes underwater to see if there are wounded animals.Kate is taught to use echo location for sea animal that are lost or hurt. By using echo location Kate gives that she has gathered  to the scientist and rescue people  to know where the injured animals. Also to find where lost animals.        Kate is really importent to our community because she helps us know where to find animals. She has also been good to us by using her voice translater to speak the animal first and then tell us what the animal has said. When the scientists don't need kate , she gets to charge for 24 hours so she can be charged  agin and ready to use. Kate has alays has been a great robot.        Kate has blue eyes that we can control by using the black hole to make things look bigger and to make things appear upclose . Kate has a cone shaped body which helps her go into animals bodies to see if there are promblems with the body. Kate has a small tail which makes her swim really fast without bumping into anything dangerous . Kate can swim faster than any other humans on earth.        Kate protects herself from dangerous animals by camoflauging herself into anthing nearby her. Kate is a pretty smart fish for herself. When we first made Kate,we thought Kate wouldn't do so well , But now Kate has gotten even more better when she first started . This is why Kate is good robot.

Back at the lab everyone loved the Probot 2000 but secretly Bob was scared because he saw the outcome of the movie.He thought it was nothing just him being weird.So they went on building them and when one was complete they tested it.These robots could do everything humans could do.It was a hit and the country started going up in popularity.Everyone wanted a Probot 2000 may it be as a babysitter,dishwasher, or anything they wanted it to be, everyone needed the robots to do something for them. Soon the robots started reappering.But they would'nt obay their masters.Soon huge bunchs started to march around the streets.The people inside their houses where hopelessly trapped.The armies grew and grew untill their where thousands upon thousands.The creator Bob was very shameful.Every one on Earth blamed him for the robots some how growing minds of their own.       Bob was in his bomb shelter.He felt terrible.He Said to himself 'this is exactly what happened in the movie'He thought I created monsters thousands upon thousands of monsters.Now I don't know what to do.The moment I step outside I will be shouted at.I wonder weather or not they are still building the Probots?Yes they still are the goverment does'nt care about the people.All the goverment cares about is money and they are making millions.The people outside of this country don't know about the invasion. Item_Response: Albert                 One day in Washington, there was a seven year old boy named George who was really into machines. When he grew up he wanted to make one himself. George tried every day to make one come alive, but none of them did. 'I'll never be able to do it,' he said to himself one day. 'Never! Never! Never!' He gave up on trying to make machines.                  Seven years pasted a he didn't even look at the lifeless robots. Then one day he couldn't sleep. George looked at his robots that he worked on so long ago. He decided to finish his project. He worked on the one that he liked the best.                 When he was seven her named it Albert. George decided to keep that name. He gave it the name Albert because when he was little his best friend was his dog, Albert. He lived a happy life, but that all ended when Albert died of old age. George cried for weeks. He didn't even want to go to the playground or school!                 George worked on Albert all weekend. Then on Sunday, at 8:00 pm, something happened. He put two wires together. Then, there was a huge, ZAP, that knocked George off  of his chair. Then, everything went black.       When George woke up there was sonething hovering over him. It was Albert! He was alive! George was so excited. He flung himself off of the floor, sending Albert flying out the window onto an old bed. George was dancing around happily then he realized that Albert was gone. 'Albert?' George asked. He looked out the window and saw Albert driving around, bumping into everything, and then fall down. George rushed downstairs a flew out the back door. He grabbed Albert and ran back upstairs.                 All week after homework George went on adding stuff to Albert. He gave him arms, a bucket on his back, and a camera. George connected the camera to his computer so he could see what Albert saw. He also gave Albert a voice and ears! That way he could talk to Albert an hear what he was saying! George took all of the wires out of an old video game controller so he could control Albert! It took a while, but he finally did it. now Albert was finished.                 They had many adventures together. George would use Albert to steal snacks.

Item_Response: 'Whee!' I yell, as my feet hit the ground from jumping off the swing. 'Yes!' I was ecstatic. All my friend were clapping, from my perfect twirling jump off the swing. Bring! Finally school was over.       As i walked home from school I noticed that the neighbor hood was very quite. Then all of a sudden the wind whipped my face, and dirt climbed into my eyes. As I cleared my eyes from the dirt that whipped in my face a strange creature was standing write in front of me.        My reaction was the same as any other normal human being, if they saw what was right in front of me. 'Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh!' I screamed. Hoping this was all a dream, and that soon my mom would come into my room in wake me up. As I waited a few seconds, waiting for someone to pinch me. I figured out this dream was reality.         As I slowly opened my eyes, I figured out that I must of imagined something because nothing was there. As I tiptoed the last few blocks, keeping my eye out for any such creature. I started to panic. Then in a flash I ran strait to my house. As I walked in the door, I quickly locked every window and door in the house.          That night at dinner, I was shaking as much as a little frightened dog. My mom and dad were very concerned, that something was really wrong with me. I told them I was fine, but on the inside I was as scared as a mouse. As I pushed my chair back I asked if i could be excused.                 'Yes, but are you sure your ok.' My mom questioned?                'Yes!Yes, I'm fine mom.' I said quietly.                                  As I ran up stairs to my room, I ran strait under the covers. As I layed their my eyes slowly shut from the long day.            Beep!Beep!Beep! As I reached over to hit the snooze button on my alarm clock, I realized the beeping wasn't coming from that. As I turned my head to find out what that beeping noise was, I was shocked with what was in front of me. It was the biggest animated thing I've ever seen. It was Humongous! It had big feet, a T.V. for a face, tube arms and legs, and bright colored clothes. This was the weirdness thing I've ever seen. As I was about to scream the robot said,'would you like waffle or Pancake?' Too shocked to answer, the robot said it again. The second time I answered and I told the robot that I would like a pancake, please. Then a second later, a pancake popped out of one of those tube like arms.          'WOW!' I said with amazement.           'Thank you I've been working on that trick.' the robot said.     My eyes were lit up like light bulbs. Then I soon asked what else he did.           He said,'I'm Chris the robot I'm very smart, athletic,a good chef, warmhearted, and the worlds best automatic robot.       Again, I was blown away. Then as I looked at the time, I had exactly 20 minutes until school started, and I wasn't even dressed.                 'It's ok I'll help you, because I forgot to tell you I have super speed.' the robot said. So take you're time you don't need to rush.          Then it hit me wouldn't it be the best thing to have a pet robot. I was amazed with this discovery. I've always wanted a pet, so why not a pet robot. I knew this was going to be awesome, the only problem is we can't let my parents find out. Eh, its all right it will just be are secret.          A couple days later, on Friday after school. My friend wanted me too come over and hang out. Sure i thought why not. I went home, and told my mom where i was going. Then I ran up stairs to check on my robot(Chris) but he was gone. All i saw was a sticky note laying on my desk.              It said,'I'm sorry, I'm not here but other people need me so, as sad as it is for me too say, i can't be your pet robot anymore.' Love your pal robot Chris.          I dropped down to my knees and started crying, pouring tears came out of my eyes. I knew that he would have to go I thought, but i did not think it would be so soon. As i stopped crying, and wiped the tears off my face, I knew he had to leave, and I knew it would all be ok. i put a smile on face and thought if you love something it will come back.

Item_Response: My robot is named Jacob. He was one night asleep in his bed made out of a thin layer of foam. He stayed in this bed all the time asleep; afterall he wasn't alive. But, sometimes I wish he was.        The next night, asleep in my bed I heard a loud *THUD*. I jumped out of my bed to see what made the loud and almost terrifing noise. I went sraight to Jacob's room. Afterall, he was always there-but, this time he wasn't!! I bolted down my rickety steps. And into the kitchen I ran. I amediatly came to a halt. The door to the fridge was WIDE OPEN!!!! I began to want to just turn around and go up into my room! But i couldn't. I slowly and carfully turned my head around the edge of the fridge. And what did I find?! JACOB!!! His eyes wide open staring in the fridge like it was a money tree! I couldn't belive it; I tried to rub my eyes to make sure that my robot was alive. And he was!!!! I sprinted into my mom and dad's room. I explained the whole story. They ran down the stairs and replied,   ' Oh my goodness Molly your robot is now a living thing.' I tried to remain as quiet and peaceful as I could. I lept up and gave jacob a hug. I was so happy I could fall over laughing. I said,   ' Mom can we still keep him?'   ' Yes of course,' they replied. I ran back up the steps to go back to sleep. As I fell back asleep i thought,   'Wow a real live robot, how amazing.'        The next morning I woke to find that Jacob was no where to be seen. I ran down my street then back up. I still couldn't find him. I woke up my parents with a,   'Mom help me jacob is no where to be seen.'   My parents replied, ' Come molly get in the car we will find him I promise.'           About a mile up the road was the school. Boy did I hope he was roaming around there.         We found a parking spot right in the front of the school, squeezed through the gates, and ran to find Jacob.       ' I've got him,' exclaimed my mom.       ' Perfect,' I said, 'Where.'       ' Right out front of the school office,' my mom replied.         We walked home with jacob lirking behind us. We back to the house and yet another time-but this time for good back to sleep.

Item_Response: The strange Story of a Robot                                                             by: Mitchell Zurick            One day there was a scientist named Jim. Jim wanted to make a robot so he tried and tried and couldn't make one. He looked online at howtomakearobot.com but he still couldn't make one. So he got mad and threw it into the dumpster. He didn't know it took a nasty smell to activate the robot.             Then the trash truck came and dumped the robot into it. From there it went on a 20 mile journey to a landfill. The trash truck  dumped all the trash in it onto the landfill. After 5 days in the smelly trash the robot came alive!              The robot went down the landfill and stopped to think where it came from. He looked on his GPS and headed back to Jim's house. On the way he stopped to get food because he was a human robot. Then the robot continued his journey back to his house.               When he got back Jim was still sitting on his sofa depressed and sad. then there was a knock on the door. Who could that be he thought? So he got off his sofa and opened the door and... It was the robot! Jim was so happy he hugged the robot and amed him Jim Jr.                                                                                 The End

Item_Response: Light in the Darkness       'Love you honey. Goodnight,' mom says and kisses me on the head. She grabs her white lab coat from the coat hook. She turns back around and blows me and kiss. Then mom bolts out the door with her blonde hair blowing behind her. And I'm left in utter darkness.       I lurch forward in bed breathing heavily. I feel sweat trickling down my neck and my hair matted down my to my head. I glance at the clock: 12:31 P.M. My worries and fears of darkness begin to bubble up in my throat. I start breathing hard again feeling my asthma attack near. I grab my inhaler from my nightstand and suck in the medicine. I calm myself down and snuggle into bed. I close my eyes and whisper over and over, 'Mom please come home soon. Mom please come home soon. Mom please come home soon.'       Black darkness sweeps around my bed swallowing me whole. I bite my nails nervously still trying to get to sleep and out of this dark nightmare of reality. The wind rattles my window and I wish desperately that I wasn't alone in this house. I had many wishes really: I wish my fear of the dark would go away, I'm 13 for goodness sake, I wish mom wouldn't have the Scientist Lab's nightshifts, I wish I would quit dreaming that same stupid dream of mom leaving me forever in the dark of the night.       Rain begins to pour outside and my heart races faster. It's now 1:18 in the morning and still I haven't been able to get to sleep. I climb out of bed and shiver as my feet touch the cold floor of my bedroom. I run over to my door and I open it as well as turning on the lights. I shove my cold feet in my pink slippers and quietly pad down the hall.       I turn on all the lights in the house just so I'll breathe easier. I walk into the panrty to snatch a peanut butter cookie and a chip bag. I slide into the chair at the table and slowly chomp down on my midnight snack. I glance at the clock again: 1:34. I sigh agrivated at how slow Father Time is going. I rummage around in the drawers for a flashlight. I contemplate on wether I should sneak into my mom's lab downstairs or leave it be.       Thoughts swarm my mind: I've never really been in her lab before, GO GRACE! This is your one chance to see what your mom has been working on, you're such a bad daughter Grace, go on Grace, it will be fun! I take a deep breath and make my way downstairs. I flick on the lights and the dim lighting of my mom's lab encaves me. I grab the flashlight from my pocket and click it on. I walk over to a wooden work table in the middle of the lab. A metal body was lying there. The yellow eyes were dim and dead. I look over to the shelves for an ON switch but all I see are shelves and shelves of test tubes filled with blue or red or green liquid.       Bottles line her desk with long words of chemicals I don't recoginize. Well yes, the test tubes and bottles and magnifying glasses do look cool... but the metal thingy lying on the table really caught my attention. I walk back over to the table cautiously, afraid I will break the metal thing. I see a paper lying next to the metal. A lot of words was on the page but at the top it said Grace 500. My heart warms as I realize she named this metal thing after me! I stroke the metal and I realize from this angle that this pile of metal looks like a robot...       I smile and realize that all these years of me argueing with my mom of quitting her job and spending more time with me that she was really doing something useful. All this time she was making a robot! A ROBOT! I smile again contently not wanting to bother her studies anymore. I turn around and turn off the flashlight. As I turn of the lights in the lab my breasthing quickens again. I feel in my pocket for my inhaler. I'm surrounded by dark again.       I'm ready to bolt for the stairs when a bright yellow light shudders on from the middle of the room. The light flickers on and off for a secong before it gets stable and strong and bright. I turn back on the lights of the lab to see a robot sitting up on the table. 'He-lo,' the robot says. I wave kind of scared. I back away slowly toward the stairs. 'My na-me is Gr-ace 5-00,' Grace 500 says. It jumps down from the table and crawls toward me. 'I am yo-ur pro-tect-or in the ni-ght,' Grace 500 says slowly.       Tears well up in my eyes as I realize my mom's intentions. She mad a robot for me as a companion at night while she is gone! I hug Grace 500 when all of a suddent the light turns off and the robot goes limp in my arms. I lay gently back on the table just as I hear the front door open. I run up the stairs excitedly and jump into my mom's arms. 'I love your job mom!' I say, 'And dont't you ever QUIT it!'

Item_Response: Mr.Gower the Amazing Robot      Long ago, a boy, was walking in an empty field and suddenly he saw a weird object in the tall grasses. He walked over to see what is was.      The object was weird shaped, it was all metal, and it was there just by itself. Bill, the boy, who had been a major in science in college studied the object and found a number on the side which was long enough to be a phone number. Bill called the number and a person from a scientist lab picked up the phone and Bill described what the object looked like and where it was found. The man on the other end of the phone had no clue what Bill was talking about, bur the scientist asked Bill to bring the object to their lab anyway so they could study it.      When Bill arrived at the scientist's lab they brought the object into their study room. The scientist's and Bill who had also been a major in science examined the object. They had realized the object was all metal, weirdly shaped, and had camera's on it. These were all characteristics of the object being a robot! One of the scientist's friends knew a guy who studied robots and called him and told him what they found and the guy who studied robot told him it sounded like a robot!      Now that they knew it was a robot they had to figure who created the robot and what its purpose was. Bob, the head scientist, started taking the robot apart and studding each piece. Bill and Gary, one if the other scientist's, were studding other robots seeing if they had anything in common with the one they found.     The scientist's left that night and came back the next morning. When they got to their lab they found something unusual about the robot it was put back together and moving around! They walked around looking at it when they found Bill asleep on the ground. 'Bill stayed here all night and got the robot up and moving' shouted Gary. A couple days later the scientist's found out the robot was used to help doctors and nurses deliver medicine to patients. The scientist's took the robot to a local hospital and asked if they needed it. The hospital took the robot and ended up naming it Mr. Gower.      The hospital kept Mr.Gower for many years after that until one day he just crashed. Bill, Bob, Gary, and everyone at the hospital miss Mr.Gower very much.

Item_Response: One hot day in the state of  Michigan, in a lab right outside down town Grand Rapids, a pair of scientists had made a new type of robot. They were setting up a contest to see who would win the prototype of the experiment and almost everyone wanted to enter it. The prototype was the only one they were ever gonna make. The robot was not alive and it didn't do much. It was called ProBot XL and it was a cleaner. 'Its not a live robot' said the scientists 'all that it does is clean'. But that was only what the scientists thought. The contest winner didn't know what she was in for. The contest winner was a nice girl with light brown hair, gray blue eyes and a pretty, bright smile. Her name was Ally Brooks. She entered the contest to get the ProBot XL for her mom because she was only fourteen. Her mom said that Ally needed it more than she did so that her daughter could clean her room with it. The first night Ally had the robot she tested it out. It worked great. She left the ProBot plugged in so it could charge while she slept, unfourtunatlly, There was a power outage that night. When she woke up the robot would not turn on. She took the robot downstairs to ask her dad for help because he was a mechanich. He managed to fix it perfectly so se took the robot back upstairs. She plugged in the robot to se how well her dad had fixed it. There was a spark. The lights started flickering and then BOOM the lights went out. She herd a voice. At that point Ally was scared out of her skin. 'Hello' said the strange voice. 'Who are you!' shouted Ally. Suddenly the lights came on and she saw she was the only one in the room. She THOUGHT. 'I was only imagining it' said Ally to herself. 'Imagining what?' there was the voice again. Ally was scared to death at this point. She saw movement out of the corner of her eye and she jumped to grab her phone to call 911. BBefore she could dial the number, ProBot came out of her closet. 'Y-you're a-alive' she stammered. 'Yes, of course' said ProBot. 'Y-you can t-talk?!' yelled Ally. 'Of course I can!' said ProBot. Ally was half scared and half fascinated at that moment. 'Im ProBot' said ProBot after a long pause 'what's your name?'. 'My name is Ally' answered Ally amazed. 'Hello master Ally' said ProBot. 'You can just call me Ally' responded Ally a little calmer now. 'How did you come to life?' asked Ally. 'I don't really know, I mean, wasn't I always alive?' responded ProBot. 'Not until a minuet ago!' exclaimed Ally. 'Well then, lets have some fun! the scientists who created me programmed me for cleaning, didnt they?' said ProBot. 'Yes, how in the world did you know that?!' replied Ally. 'Well, it really is the duster and dustpan that gives it away, but it also is this maid dress that they put me in too, and im a boy! this is very offensive and demeaning!' answered ProBot. 'Oh' said Ally, feeling very dumb 'okay then, ProBot, what do you like to do for fun?'. 'Do you have any cats, I love casing around cats! im part robot dog, they ran out of parts for my brain, so they had to use robot dog brain instead.' said ProBot. 'If youre not supposed to be alaive, then why did they give you a brain?' said Ally curiously. 'I really do not know' said ProBot questioningly 'why did they give you a brain?'. 'I wasn't made by inventers like you were ProBot' said Ally 'I was made by...' Ally's mom was calling her down for dinner, it was pizza night and Ally did not want to miss that. 'What is pizza?' asked ProBot. 'It's my favorite food and I dont want to miss it so I got to go, i'll be back soon!' answered Ally. 'What is food?' asked ProBot, but Ally was already running down the stairs. After Ally had her pizza, she went back upstairs to her room to check on ProBot. 'Your noise machine would not stop beeping' sait ProBot annoyed 'it keeps saying 'you have one new call' and its driving me nuts!'. 'Sorry' said Ally 'let me check who the call was from.' The call was from the two scientists who invented ProBot to check that everything was all right. The message said: 'Hi! hope everything is going alright with our latest invension the ProBot XL please call us back for any inconveniance with the ProBot and feel free to return it if you dont like it. Call us back if you have any comments or questions! thanks!, bye. 'Inconveniance! what is so bad about me!' exclaimed ProBot. 'Nothing' said Ally 'lets go outside for a quick walk.' ProBot and Ally went on a nice long walk together and had a lot of fun. They got to know eachother and became best friends and ProBot finally got to go chase a cat just like he wanted to. ProBot and Ally became best friends from the day ProBot came to life and to the day ProBot ran out of batteries. Thankfully, ProBot didn't run out of batteries and Ally and ProBot lived happily ever after.       The End

Item_Response: On a sunny spring day, everyone was outside playing- well, almost everyone. Billy Bob Fred George Jr.(konwn as Billy) was inside working on his science assingment. He was asked to bring in something that he could build, and could somehow move in varius dirrections. But he did not know how much of a succes his moving robot would be.                              He powered the robot up and installed some wheels. But suddenly, he thought something amazing. He could use his old ipod to record his voice! During this time, he brought out his unfineshed robot outside to cool. Right then, his mother called him in for dinner. Completely forgetting about his robot, it started to rain. With his family of 6 , they struck up in conversation.         'Today in school I learned about long division during  math class,' said Emily the 9-year-old, who, was very interested in learning.       'I practiced my multiplication tables' said Sammy, the 2nd grader, who thought School was fun, because he saw his friends.       'What about you, Billy? You learn lots of stuff in 5th garde, don;t you?' Asked their mother . 'Ehh', replied Billy.       'Molly?' asked mother. 'Oh! We learned about decimals and how to divide them,' said Billy's twin sister.           BOOOOOOOOOOOOOM!!!!!!!!!! Thuder struck. FLAAAASH!!!!!   Ligtning hit.  'MY ROBOT! Screamed Billy, running outside. His robot was smoking. Oh no! He dragged it inside, evryone crowding aroud. But then sonething happened that made everyone jump a foot off the ground.           *Greetings, friend* said the robot. *My name is powing-gi, the talking robot. Conversation continued until their bedtime. The next day, Billy was ready to bring his robot to school. On the way, all he heard was:       'Mom! Sammy's toutcing me!' Emily complained. 'Sammy, stop.' Ordered mother. 'Ha,ha,' whispered Emily, 'I can toutch you, but you cant toutch me!' 'MOM!' Screamed Sammy 'I heard that', she said calmly. 'Kids, please don't toutch eachother.' She said. 'Yes mommy', they said together drowsilly.               This was one of Billy's best days of school he ever had. He became the most popular kid.  Everyone had fun talking and playing with powing-gi all day.           And this, is how powing-gi came to life.

Item_Response: Jack JR The Robot       There once was a little boy named Jack, it was just a normal day during summer vacation. So Jack started drawing pictures for his new creation. Then finally Jack screamed 'I am going to make a robot named Jack JR.'!!! Once he mfinished making Jack JR., Jack was very happpy with him self because Jack JR. was a magnificent creation. He was brown wit hbright blue eyes, he looked like a real person he could even talk too. He waws so excited for his new friend but there was only one problem Jack didn't want his parents to know about Jack JR. because he was afraid that his parents would take his special robot away. So before Jack can make his robot he needs to make a home for the robot so he climed down from his tree house and got some of his dad's tools (now don't worry Jack is very good with tools he won't get hurt or anything). Then Jack climed back up the latter of the tree house and started digging a whole right above the tree trunk. After he finished with the drilling he made a ELEVATOR!! just like that i dont know how but he did. And I almost forgot to tell you but Jack is a very inteligent young boy and not every mother and father get to have such an amazing child.           The reason for the elevator is to get down into Jack JR's home and let me tell you that Jack's creation is living the life because he has the BIGGEST house in the neighboorhood of Jack. After Jack showed Jack JK. the big house, Jack's mother called him inside because it was already 9:30 past his bed time. So Jack said 'Yes mommy I will be right there. So Jack tuked Jack JR. into his bed and tolled him 'I love you with all my heart I won't let anything happen to you got that? but you need to promise me that you do not get out of this bed until i come and let you. Because if you do I think my parents will take you away ok my nugget?' Jack JR. replied 'Yes creator I will not leave this bed because you said so and that I love you too and that I can't leave , you are my family so good night and see you in the morning when YOU come to wake me up ohh and love you too!               The next day Jack got up and ran out side to his elevator he keep on thinking about the night before, how much fun he had with Jack JR. and couln't wait for more fun. Jack got into the elevator to go down but once he got down there he saw the most terrible sight HIS MOTHER AND FATHER WERE DOWN THERE STAYRING AT JACK JR.!!!!!!! What was he sopost to do? this was what he wanted to avoide. Let me cut it short for you Jack did not get in trouble and he got to keep Jack JR. the best part was that Jack JR. got to stay inside the real house with Jack Jack'e mom and Jack's dad. So in the end everything turned out AMAZING for the whole family and for the first time in a long time Jack JR. felt like he was loved... and he LOVED IT!!!!....

Item_Response: On a stromy day in Manchester, England a moment of pure magic occured. This magic may never come back but this story is one for the future.       While Pablo Morris, a student who is on the Honour Roll in the East-Side Middile School that he attends. Decided, to give away his least favorite robot, Jordan, to his cousin, out of his 283 toys. You could straight away make the assumption that he was a spoiled brat, but he really was just a hard working 13 year old, that was always loved in his family of 4 sisters. (Sammy 25, Ariana 20, Louis 17, Morgan 15.) He decided to go to sleep at around 8 PM. Just after he finished his Clarinet practice. But, not even he could of imagined what happend the following night.       When the clock struck 2 AM, the weather turned bad. Rain started to fly in his window. He realised this straight away. As he shut the window down he rememberd how his rooms roof had a small hole. The bad thind that it was just over his bed. Now being one of the most naive kids in the world, he failed to report this to his father. As he was twisting and turning he heard his phone ring. As he answered it, the door bell rang. Being the quickest runner in his cross-country club, he managed to get to the door before his sister, Morgan. 'Awake already?' said Morgan with a twink of a smile. When they opened the door they were greeted by a gust of rain, and no sign of human life anywhere, 'Another ring and roll,' Said Pablo. 'I judt can't say how much I hate those kids!' replied Morgan not admitting that she had done a few before. 'Well good night,' said Morgan and Pablo replied in the exact same manner.       It was 2:30 just minutes later. And still he failed to return to sleep. Than he saw a flash. Aand then another, and another, and again. Expecting it was just lightneing he ignored it. But wait, where is the thunder? The flashed continued until Pablo had enough. Out he went and thereon his kitchen table he saw, Jordan and right nextto him was his best freind, Edin. Furios he grabbed Edin's arm and escorted him out without a peep. Next thing he knew was that Joran was on top of him. He just seconds later saw punches thrown all over his pale face. Stunned he blocked them only allowing one on his nose. BOOM! A window breaks. Following through was a rock. On the rock it was a sticky note. 'Pablo, I'm sorry he just didn't like being away from you.' Pablo read softly from the floor. Then when he was least expecting it a pain on his left thigh broke out. With a yelp he notcied that a metal thorn was in him. He had enough. With a bang Jordan smashed onto the wall. Amazed he realised that Jordan came back to his normal shape, but this time he learned from his mistake. Pablo just moments later had atleat 14 throns in his body.       The pain was aganizing. Jordan continued with his clever tactic. But, Pablo thought of a clever way to attack throw the thorns back on him. Next after being in complete pain just 16 seconds later he realised he won. But, that wasn't his main concern. His top concern was were was mom and dad. He looked everywhere. Than he rememberd. He had no dad or mom, he wasn't on the honour roll, he wasn't attending East-Side Middile, he doesn't play the clarinet, he had no sisters, he had no toys or a best friend. He was an orphan. Bursting into tears. This tears were the rain. There was no hole in the roof. The water was just his tears. He was just a 13 year old who had his life taken away, he did have all those things except one day when it was taken away by a fire, he was the only one to survive this fire, that killed his whole family except him. He was just a homeless 13 year old kid, living on the streets of Manchester, England.

Then wheels popped out the bottom plus the wierdest thing was it was talking and it was talking to me it was saying things like 'hello how are you today I an very good'. Item_Response: 'I wish you were a real person' Owen said to his robot friend one night. 'I don't like being the only child in the family and I really want someone that is a kid that I can play and talk to.' After Owen had fallen asleep his robot felt a little zap and thought Owen must be playing with me again. But then to his surprise he saw his own controller laying on the floor. 'I am moving by myself'he thought. 'I am free of my controller. Yipeeeeeeeee.'        In the morning Owen woke up to a whirring noise in his bedroom and thought 'what could that be.' When he opened his eyes he saw his beloved robot zooming all around his bedroom. 'I am free of my controller I am free of my controller' the little robot yelled. Owen was so over joyed he finely had something close to a real brother. 'We will have so much fun together' they screamed together.        'What should we do first' Owen asked. 'I would really like to taste some ice cream now that I am so independent' the little robot said. 'OK lets go to the Dary Qween down the road' Owen suggested. So off they went down the road to the Dary Qween. When they got there the robot asked 'what flavor is the best?' Owen said his favorite was the mint chocolate chip hot fudge Sunday. So they ordered a order of two mint chocolate chip hot fudge Sunday. The little robot thought his Sunday was delise. When they finished their Sundays Owen asked again 'what else should we do before we have to go to bed again? 'Lets go to the park'        Once they were at the park they took a nice long walk to burn off some of they fat from their Sundays. Then Owen showed his robot the play set. They had so much fun. They played pirates, cop and robber, macro polo, and hide and seek. But the thing that they had the most fun doing was seeing who could last the longest on the tire swing without getting sick. The little robot won this game because although he was independent of his controller one of the on things he didn't have was a sence of diseness. They played for hours in the park but when the sun started to go down they had to head home and go to bed.        When Owen and the little robot came home their mom said 'up to bed boys.' So Owen and the robot climbed the stares and went into Owen room. After Owen had gotten in bed and the little robot in his corner Owen said 'robot you are the best brother any one could ever have.' Zzzzzzzzzzzzzz.

Item_Response: 'B46-13'                              My dad is one of the people that creates the robots that can do everyday human tasks, like brushing your teeth, or cooking an egg. His newest robot was called, ' B46-13' it's job was to look after kids when there parents were gone, such as a nanny. Now you might think it's great to have a robot designer be you're dad, but you also have to test out all of them. Lucky for me, it was date night.           'Alex, will only be gone for 2 hours, it won't even seem like we left' My dad exclaimed.' But what if it goes haywire??!!' I argued. ' It won't! we've been working on this project for over 3 years!' My dad could not be convinced. They left, only leaving the B46-13, and me. ' Hello I am B46-13 but you can call me Sally' she said scratchily. 'Okay Sally, I'm Alex, can I have some dinner?' 'Sure thing, what should I cook?' She asked persistently. 'Oh! Um-mm...... Caviar and a hard boiled egg!' I said jubilantly. Those were my favorite foods. With a 'Whiz' and a 'Whirr' she shot out the food in 6 seconds flat!! 'I think we'll have a great time Sally'       Half an hour later, I was laying on the couch groaning from all of the food Sally had cooked for me. 'It is time for bed Alex.' Sally told me. 'Are you kidding?' I replied. ' It's only 8:00!!' 'ALEX BED NOW!!!' She screamed. 'AH! Okay!!' I bolted up the stairs as quick as I could. She tucked me into bed and told me if I got out of my room by even an inch, there would be serious consequences, and I knew she was serious. 'There has to be a way to reach dad!' I thought. Then it hit me, my cell phone!!! I dashed across the room, careful to not make a sound. I picked up the phone, and dialed dad's number as quickly as possible. 'Dad, there's a problem with the robot.'       'Oh, Mr. and Mrs. Johnston!' Sally said with a digital smile, ' Alex is in bed.' 'Sally.... you have been a bad robot, so it's time for you to be shut down. Forever.' Dad said as he reached for her power button. 'NOOoooo.......' Sally yelled as she shut down. 'OH ALEX!' that meant that it was safe to come down, and there wasn't a pyscopath robot anymore. 'Yes dad?' I replied. ' Your mom and I were talking on the way home, and we've decided that never again will we try out my new robots on you.' My dad said with a grin. 'WAHOO!' I yelled. I was free!!

Item_Response: George's Dream Robot             Ambitious. Thats how George felt when he was going to make his very first robot. He wanted his robot to do his chores and clean his room for him. So Goerge started to find out how to make the robot that he dreamed of. George searched the web, and finally made a solution. Once he found how to make the robot of his dreams, he started to build it.            It took George a while to make his dream robot. He had to buy the correct materials for his dream robot. Then, George had to fit the pieces together, which took a while. After that, George had to program the robot for it to clean his room and do his chores. George was almost done making his dream robot!                 Sooner or later, George was finished making his dream robot. George was so extatic to see how his dream robot would work out. The only thing that was left of the robot was how to turn it on. He thought and thought about how to make the robot turn on. After a while, George gave up. George couldn't think of any way to make his robot work, so he left it in his basement storage and forgot all about his robot.                 Five years later, when George was fifteen, he went to his basement storage to donate his clothes. George was digging into the stoage room for clothes, when he found his dream robot lying on top of a pile of his old clothes. Once George found his dream robot, he went out in the thunder, lightning, and rain to bury his dream robot for a time capsule. The rain washed off all of the rust on the robot's body. He then ran inside and looked for some more of his old clothes.              Later in the day when there was still the thunderstorm, a strike of lightning shook the ground where George's dream robot was. Boom, Crash, Bang! Suddenly the lightning struck at Goerge's dream robot, and George's dream robot came to life! The robot started to push itself out of the mud, and run towards George's house. George was so astounded when he saw his robot come to life! He hugged his dream robot, and his dream robot hugged him back. Finally George had someone for helping him with his chores and clean his room for him, but not only that, he had a friend.                  When George got older, he let his son play with George's robot. George's son loved George's robot, just like George did when he was a kid. George's son wanted George's robot to have a friend to play with when they were gone. So George and his son made a little robot for George's robot. This robot was named Jeffery. Jeffery also did chores and he cleaned rooms. Those two robots were maids, but they were also best friends with George and his son.

Item_Response: It was a dark and stormy night. The thunder shook the lab as John worked on his top secret project that he code named Project Z. John was a scientist that always worked alone. Nobody knew what Project Z was, not even his best friends and family. Only John knew. He tried to keep Project Z as secret as he could. Many people questioned him every day about what he was doing, but he gave them the same answer every time; 'The usual.' Nobody was worried that he was doing anything bad, even though he was a very mysterious man. 'Finally finished!' said John. 'Time to show the world what great power I really have!' he said as he put the finishing touches on Project Z.                BOOM!!!! The whole town was in chaos. Someone or something was causing this chaos, but nobody knew what it was. People were crying for help, cars were being crushed, and buidings were being destroyed. 'What's happening??' a little boy screamed as a building collapsed right before his eyes. The boy looked up, and nearly fainted. It was the most terrifying thing he has ever seen...                 Before his eyes stood the biggest looking creature the world had ever seen. No...it wasn't a creature, a robot!! It was 50 stories tall, a head the size of a blue whale, and eight long legs much like a spider. With each step it took, the whole earth would shake and people fell to the ground. 'Hahahaha!' John laughed evily as he suddenly appeared out of nowhere. 'With the power of Project Z, I will rule the world forever!!!!' John shouted. 'This can't be happening!' the little boy screamed. But it was happening, and it was about to get a whole lot worse.                  ZOOOOM! Something whizzed by the little boy's head as he took cover from Project Z. No way, he thought. The things that whizzed by his head were just what no one expected. Smaller versions of Project Z, that could fly!! The town was in a panic. People were storming the streets trying to evacuate, huge pieces of debris were flying everywhere, and everything was being destroyed! I have to do something, thought the boy. But what? He thought for a moment, and then he knew exactly what to do. Go to the lab.                  The boy saw John walk to his lab every day, so he knew exactly where it was. Sprinting as fast as he could, he reached the lab and entered through the door. What a strange place, the boy thought as he walked through the lab. Random wires and viles of strange substances were laying around everywhere. The place was an absolute mess! 'I have to find out what's controlling the robot,' said the boy. Then he saw it. A huge computer the size of an elephant stood before him. I have to figure out how to stop this thing! He looked around everywhere until he saw a little red button on the side of the computer. Shut down, it read. The boy pressed the button and he heard a voice. 'Shutting down in 10,' it said. '9. 8. 7...' 'Stop!! yelled John as he entered the room.                   John ran over and shoved the boy out of the way. '3. 2...' 'Noooo!' shouted John. 'Shut down complete.' said the voice. The little boy was a hero.                  In the end, the cops rushed over to the lab, arrested John, and everyone lived happily ever after.

Item_Response: When I was younger I was very shy I didnt like to talk to other people. I would Just sit in the corner and read my books. I did'nt really get lonely, when I did I would just keep reading and ignore my feeling like I did'nt even feel them             Everybody at school just ignored me. Sometimes I would just watch them laughing, and giggling wishing that I would have some friends eventually. I used to get really worked up and I did'nt know what to do with my emotions so I decided to just write a letter to my grandmother how I felt. My Grammy died about a year ago and it was the worst thing that ever happend.             When I go to dance class everything feels better like they only emotions I can feel when I am there are happy, joyful ones. All of the girls are nice with big kind hearts just filled with love.              I really like wearing my costume because it symbolises my Grammy is okay. When she died she told me she would send me butterflies signaling that she was okay in heaven.On my dress there are some many butterflies it is just filled with them. It makes me feel really happy when I wear my dress because I kow that she is happy and that is the best feeling in the world.             The next day I was reading and a girl walked by and tripped. She was really snotty and rolled her eyes. After this other girl came over and sat next to me. She asked if I was okay and said she has seen me around. She does'nt have any friends either. She then said wow isn't middle school great in a sarcastic voice and then we both giggled.She told me to meet her at the ice cream parlor a block away from school in the afternoon. I exitedly said yes.             When I got there she had yet to arrive. I wasn't worried because she seemed like a very nice girl. About five minutes later she arrived and said she was sorry she was late. We both walked up to the counter and asked for a kiddie cone vanilla with raindow sprinkles. We were really creaped out we had ordered the same thing without even planning it.

Item_Response: Alex Skirkey   4-10-13   Narrative                 One beautiful sunny morning, Andy, Joey and I were playing pass with a football. Then all of the sudden, Sidney (Joey's little sister) ran at us screaming bloody murder! She ran to Joey and held his leg with all her might, crying. All of us asked ' why are you crying?'            She said while crying 'my toy robot came to life and scared the crap out of me and started demolishing all of my things in my room!' So we all went running to Sydney's house to see the robot and stop it!            After we just entered the door to check it out we saw something unbelievable! The robot didn't destroy anything and it was sitting at the table playing with an apple. We were so amazed at what we saw, but not as amazed as Joey was. Because he fainted, so we told my parents and told them what happened.              They told us to put it in a cage and put it in the car. So we did, and got in the car with it. When the parents got in the car they said we were going to the science lab of  NH. Boy I hated science but I loved science when I heard there was money involved. I could not wait to get my hands on a million dollars.               When we showed it to the scientist they were amazed and said that they would analyze it and make more for people to buy. They said thank you and wrote us a check for $500,000. Which I was disappointed, that was not the amount of money I expected!                  So after ten years past I bought that same exact robot back when they made more robots!                                                                The End

Item_Response: Jenny look at the time and sigh she wanted it to be four o'clock, but it was only three.When the clock said four she could play with her new robot cat named Poof!  Finally when she looked at the clock for the tenth time it said four o'clock and she got up and ran to where she put it yesterday when she played with it.        She got down on her hands and open the closet door where her robot cat should have been, but it wasn't there!  When Jenny turned around there was Poof, but he didn't look like himself.  He looked alive!  Jenny knew that Poof wasn't alive because she remembered that just last week when she went to the store to buy him.         Poof crawled nearer Jenny, curled into a ball and sat on her lap. Then Jenny screamed the loudest she has ever screamed!        Her mom rushed out of her bedroom and yelled, 'What is going on here?'        Jenny replied, 'P-p-p-p-poof, he has a b-b-b-beating heart!'        Jenny's mom calmly said, 'That's rediculas,' then she thought again and said, 'Let me see him I will see if he eats, breaths and has a beating heart.'        Jenny sat there and waited for about fifteen minutes then her mom returned and said fightened , 'You were r-r-r-right he is living, but that's imposible because we went to the store and bought him just last week.'        Jenny answered,'I guess anything is possible, Mom.'        They both went into the kitchen and played with the real Poof, and he was actually very fun, just as fun as the robot Poof!  Now Jenny's mom said that she had to take caare of him, buy the food get a litter box and get him a cage. Jenny agreed to all of that because she wanted to keep Poof.         Poof stayed with Jenny's family for a long, long time andlove Jenny very much, but Jenny's family never found out how Poof turned into a really cat.

Item_Response: The End is Near        By: Jaiden Prather              The room is dark. I hear whispers all around. Suddenly, a single, bright light comes on above me. A man's voice says, 'The operation is complete.'          The man leaves through a door. I can't help but think that I have to get out of here.Then, for the first time i realize that i have no memories before i woke up in here. In fact, I don't even know my own name. I struggle to get out of the chair I'm strapped to. It almost feel like leather. then i feel a small prick and everything fades.              I jolt upright in bed and say,' It was just a dream.' But then i realize it wasn't. I'm not in my bed, I'm in a metal dentist chair. with straps. in a dark room. with a single light over my head. I remember that i can escape through the door the man went through. I run over and fling the door open. there is a room with a window, chair, and table. In the heat of the moment i grab the chair and toss it at the window.it shatters and i jump through into a field if long, yellow grass. I decide to run around the corner of the building. I sprint around the corner right into a girl. we both fell into the grass.   'Who are you and what are you doing at a robot lab?' she says.   'i don't know and i don't know.'   'well then, follow me if you want to live.'           She she said she was taking me to a shack about a mile away. while we were walking i learned that her name was max and she lived with three boys and another girl. Their names were Jay, Tom, Gary, and Angel. they were outcasts from a utopia named Farfal. A mad man created a dream inducer in which you could enter your mind and 'lucid dream'.        when we reached the shack she went in first and called out, 'I think its him.' she then explained,' for months we have been getting a report of someone we would find at the lab who would save the world. and we think its you.   'you escaped from that place, right? because if you did, there is only one explanation:   'you are a world saving robot.'

Item_Response: The Robot That came Alive   This is a story that is about a robot that came to life.   It all started one hot Winter evening.   One day little Timmy was playing with his robot toy.   His robot looked like a small version of him. It looked like this: It had bright blue eyes, a striped red and green shirt, and had dark green shoes.   But this one day was different...Much different.   The reson this day was different was because it was scorching hot, but that is not the odd part. The odd part was that It was winter.   So anyway Timmy was playing with no fear at all. Unfortunately   this was no happy day. In fact it would be the last day Timmy would ever see his parents.   It was the end of the day when Timmy was getting home and in stead of seeing his home he saw a pile of rubble. He was so   frightened that he started to cry. He ran inside the pile of rubble and tried to find his parents. They were not there. He dropped his robot toy, and wept for hours and hours.   The next day Timmy decided to search the rubble some more   after searching for what seemed like an eternity he found a slip of paper. Surprised and mad at himself for missing it before he yell,'What the heck!!'He picked up the slip of paper that seemed to be in the middle of his broken room. He read the note. It said.   Dear, Timmy   we are sorry the house is gone and we are no longer there. We are probably dead if you are reading this. But we must make this brief   You are to become an alien hunter. That is what your father did and that is what you must do. Never let enithing get this note. There is a list of all the alien fugitives.   We will never forget you Timmy. We are proud and will always    love you.   Your, mom and dad.   And with that Timmy had no more parents.   Later in lif Timmy became an enginer/alien hunter, but what ever he did he always charished that one robot. He eventualy made it 5ft 7in and it still looked the same.   The year 4000,March 22   It was timmys birth day and Timmy was looking forward to it even though it was 4000 Timmy still haden't aged a bit. he had gone through most of the alien list(He only had 3 more aliens to go.) He had given himself super powers and oh yeah he was fighting an alien at the moment. It was more like he was talking with it. He figured he could trick it.   His super powers were (and I should probly get this done quick)   he could shape shift his robot he had made so it looked as if it were alive, He could make things apper with his mind, and he could mind control.   So he is fighting the alien and all of a suden the alien is done   talking and he spits a ball of nukular waset at Timmy. It misses and hits his robot instead the robot is blasted bakward and hits a pipe.   The pipe bursts and sprays water all over the robot. Timmy ran to the robot and let the alien get away. The robot that by the way is named Jason sits up, Timmy says,' Are you ok.' and instead of giving a blue light that meens ok. It says,' I am ok' Timmy looks dumb founded. HIS ROBOT WAS NO LONGER A ROBOT IT WAS ALIVE!!!

Item_Response: A Small Friend             It all happened in a small testing lab somewhere in Arizona in the middle of nowhere.It was all on accident. But in a way, I'm glad it happened.               It was Wednesday. My usual shift had just started. We were trying, without much luck, to successfully create a certain robot named Buddy. The name didn't stand for anything, but we just decided to name it Buddy. I was standing over our first completed and safe robot for the experiment. It was just me and the  small robot. It looked like a  robotic kinkajou. I was extremely bored, so I started to mix the ingredients I thought was needed. I got so into my experiment, I didn't notice that my partner had just arrived. He put his hand on my shoulder. I jumped so hard, I dropped my experimental mix on the robot. I gasped as the robot started to shift and turn. It dramatically jjiggled and then came to a silent pause. I gasped in surprise as the robot came to life.                                                                                       The small robot sat up. It looked right at me, shakily stood up, jumped, and the next thing I knew, it was sitting on my shoulder making a strange purring noise. My partner came to get a better look. The robot made a hissing noise at him and took out a knife as if trying to protect me. 'What are you going to name it' he asked. I thought about it. ' I think that I'm going to name it...Tiny Thor.' My lab partner laughed, ' Tiny Thor? That actually fits!''  I smiled as it purred even louder at it 's new name. 'Maybe tomorrow we can see what this little guy can really do,'' I thought. My little protector. My LLittle Thor.                The next day I hurried into the lab. Little Thor was sitting on the counter staring off into space. He noticed me and gave me what looked like a makeshift smile. ''Are you ready to let us see what you can do?'' I laughed as he made little fists and made little punching gestures. 'Ready?' I threw an apple at him. He jumped high into the air, pulled out two little knives, and split the apple into tiny pieces before it  even hit the ground. We spent hours discovering what Little Thor could do.  I was sorry that I couldn't take him home with me, but  I didn't even get out the door when a mob of angry people attacked the lab.                 I screamed and ran back into the testing area where we kept Little Thor. I grabbed him and ran out the back. The mob haad broken through the front door and was flooding into the small building. Little Thor started to growl. I looked back and saw that they had started to gain on us. I pushed faster. Little Thor was tensing in my arms as I ran down the hall. He  jumped out of my arms and stood in the middle of the hall. He shoved me out of the building, locked the door, turned around, and pressed his delete button. The whole building was blown up within seconds. I stood there, shocked that he had commited suicide to save me. I heard a small noise, I looked down and saw the  tattered body of Little Thor.               I ran over to him. I could tell that he was dying, eventhough he was a robot, he still felt the pain of the explosion. He slowly closed his eyes and his small robotic body went limp.I was about to cry when I remembered that I still had what made him come to life in my lab coat. Through tears, I poured a drop a waited. Then a buzzing noise came on, a slight purr, and Little Thor came back to this world again.

Item_Response: My dad wanted me to make him a specific robot for his work. He works as a miner. He wanted me to make a replica (that works) of a Gemini-Scout robot. While preparing to make it I had to get specific supplies from the Robot Science Company. My dad bought a package that had the instructions and pieces for making the robot. In the picture, Gemini-Scout looked easy to build. When we opened the package there was a lot of small pieces, and their was a lot of huge pieces. I realized that it was going to be really complicated. Days past and we only finished the remote control. He had to go to work, so the rest of the summer I figure I could work on it alone. It was really hard for me to figure out how to read the instructions. I eventually figured it out how to read it.                 One day, I decided to stop for awhile because I really needed help. I would play basketball, soccer or read. My sister had finally came up to me one day when I was bored. She told me, ' If you are so bored, then why don't you just work on the robot you promised dad you would finish'. I was thinking about it for awhile but I responded ' Maybe sometime else'.  She just walked away. When my mom came home we got a call. It was my dad! He called us from the campsite he was working at. He told us that they moved him to a different site in Brazil. After awhile of talking to him he said he really wanted to know how I was doing with his robot. I told him,' I really haven't had time lately, but I will start working on it soon. He replied ' I would really like to test it out over here in Brazil, I hope you can finish it before I leave. It will help us a lot over here'. He hung up the phone after that because it was morning over there.                 The next day, I decided t work on the project. I had to use the screwdriver, a hammer , a torch, a mask, and a drill. The problem was that I forgot where I left them. I searched for them all day and finally at seven o'clock I found them. My sister told me to work on it tomorrow. The next day all I did was work on Gemini-Scout. I ended up finishing it. I called my dad to tell him I finished but he did not answer. His manager answered and told me to install all the needs it needed. He explained to me that it is supposed ti have a thermal camera, it has to be able to test the air, and be able to find trapped miners. I told him I had all of that. Then he explained that a rock had trapped my dad's group inside a mine and they needed the robot i made. I was so worried when they came to collect it.                   I got nervous because it was seven days since I talked to my fathers manager. Then, all of a sudden the phone rang. I ran straight to it so I could answer before my sister. My dad's maneger told me that they were working on getting them out and that my robot Gemini-Scout was very helful for finding them. They called two days later saying that they brought them out of the mine. I was very proud of myself for making a successful robot.                      At the end, my dad came home from the campsite and he was really glad that I finished Gemini-Scout in time. He told me that its important to finish things as soon as possible because you never know what will happen. I was really glad that my dad came but I was very glad for my success with the robot Gemini- Scout. Its was best for me b to try a new thing  with my dad because it can help more to be creative.

Item_Response: THE HELP                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Once upon a time, in January,19,1967there was a little girl.Her name was Gracie and she was walking to school .She had finally arrived at school and went to  her class.Her teacher said'Kid's I have a surprise for you!'Then Gracie said'Is it a project?'The teacher was happy that Gracie figured that it was a project.The teacher had assigned them a robot project.Gracie wondered 'What is mine going to look like?' Then she went to go tell her parents that she had a project to do.Gracie has a special talent.She can communicate with animals,for example:birds,mice,cats,dogs,horses,ETC.So every time she sings the animals come to her.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Next thing you know ,Gracie started singing and all the animals started to come to her. Gracie told the birds to go find her some metal on the floor.she assigned all of the animals some jobs.When she was done,she was glad.So all she needed to do was come up with a name.She called it'Chrissy.'                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     It was Friday the day she turn her project in.It was her turn to present.When she went up she said'Hi this is my robot her name is Chrissy and what she does is ,she helps me with homework.'My animal friends helped me with it.A boy named Chris said'animals can't help they run away from you.'Gracie said' they don't run away from me, I sing so beautiful!'Chris said'In your dreams!'                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         Gracie said'I will prove it!'Gracie started to sing and all the animals came to her.So Chris said'I'm sorry for not beliving you.'    So, her teacher graded them and everyone got a'B'.She was the only one who got an'A'.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          The End

The robot is less than two feet tall and it even has wheels. It can roll in water, it carries food, water, and other supplies. The robot may be small, but very strong. The Gemini-Scout collects information, wherever it goes.  The robot uses the thermal camera to find the miners. The second robot I'm going to tell you is the Dante  2 robot.  This robot has a very interesting job. It climbs into volcanoes to gather information. It is built to survive very high heat.  The next robot is the Mr. Gower. Mr. Gower works in the hospitals, helping nurses and docters by bringing medicine to patients.  He is so strong, he can pull 500 pounds.  Mr. Gower can even say hundreds of words to patients. The last robot iI'm goimg to tell you about is the Agribots. The Agribots ia the robots that picks the fruit. They can even grow plants with out any help. The Agribots are so smart, they can even tell when a plant is ripe, ready to eat, or if it needs more time to grow.            So now do you belive me. Robots are real, their not just made up. Just like the robots I just told you about, they are real just go to Mount Spurr, an active volcano in Alaska.

Item_Response: Russel The Robot            'No, Russel don't hurt me!' I yelled at the top of my lungs. I couldn't believe my family left me home alone with this monster. He looked exactly like my dad but i knew that the wasn't. Russel was much more pale and bony. i could tell that he wanted to hurt me. who could blame him, he was like my personal slave.             My dad is a scientist and had an invention that he wanted to try out at our house. The experiment was called Russel and he was a robot. He could bake, clean, and do anything you wanted. He seemed like the most perfect servant ever. Until, one day he stopped working. My dad said he blew a fuse when he was trying to dance and that he would go to the lab and get more parts. As soon as my dad left, Russel started to spark. I didn't think it was important so i went upstairs and took a nap.             I woke up wit a start. My room was all smokey and i ran downstairs to check on Russel. where was he. Russel was not on the couch where i saw him last and then i felt a hand on my neck. It looked like my dad and i gasped. Russel must have turned into my dad when i was taking a nap. He didn't look exactly like my dad but you could tel he wish he was. Russel was breathing- robots don't breath! 'Oh no, how could Russel have turned into a human. Its not possible,' I thought to myself. Right when he started to hurt me is when my dad walked through the front door.              'Russel stop hurting my daughter! You have gotten way out of control now.' My dad yelled to him. Dad tried to get Russel off of me and threw him to the other side of the living room. 'Dad he turned into a human and pretended to be like you' I yelled to my dad. Right at that moment Russel exploded. BOOM! Its was like the house flew into the sky. We were inside the house before but now i in the back yard. i tried to find my dad in all the rubbish of the house. I tripped on the ceiling fan now on the floor and everything went blank.

Item_Response: One day a little robot was laying on a wall.This robot was not alive until something strange happened.There was a storm with thunder ad lightning,no rain.The robot was zapped by the lightning and came alive.He didnt know were he was,or why he was in the middle of a storm laying down.The last thing he rememberd was his mom saying goodbye to his dad.               He was walking when he noticed a house with the lights on. He went up to it,hopeing someone would help him,and knocked.'Were comeing,'some one shouted.It sounded like a woman.'Mom are you in there,'the little robot asked.The door opened when he saw a boy with his mom.'WOW,Can it be,'the boy asked,'A robot?'The boy ran up to the robot and poked him ,'Cool.''Hi boy can I come in,''said the robot.''Of course,' said the boy,'Do you have a name?''Little Frank,'th robot said with a smile on his face.                   The little robot became part of the family and told many stories.He loved the old famliy he had,but to him he loves the new one better.They all had the most happiest times of their lives.The End.

Item_Response: It was about 8:00 at night and for my science fair project. I was going to make a robot of the future out of my old bike that I had when I was three years of age.I took the spokes off of my tire and bent them to create my form top for the chest i also hot glued some bolts to it for more class.I the n ripped the rubber off of the tire and hot glued that to the chest portion with the bolts. After a lot of tearing and hot gluing the robot final product was complete after a couple of hours.I was very tired and left my robot which i decided to name R-2D2 like in the great star wars saga my brother liked to watch all of the time.I left it in the garage and left to bed. As soon as i acme back the next morning he was gone!           I looked all over the garage and heard a squeak coming from behind a brown cardboard box. And out peeked a rubber tire chest with googly eyes. I jumped when it came out holding its bionic arm for me to slap it a high five. It said,'we be friends right?'I looked extremely puzzled when it spread its arms wide and game me a large hug!After that i looked very stunned.  picked it up with me big poster board and walked to school. I set him down and whispered (to not look crazy I hid behind a tree).I told him act natural and he posed with the hand on hip look. I giggled and people thought i was very weird i also thought this was weird but acted like it never happened. I placed him on the table and walked away. I came back a little later and he no longer was alive i knew i shouldn't have put the batteries in him to make him run I won a blue ribbon for my little buddy. Thanks R-2D2!
