Item_Response: Redit Grond Diconsion's First Journal                 One day a robot slaver named Mr. Roidans was driven to the Auction house also known as the rbot market. There he bot Four slaves one named google car a self driving vehicle. Another named The Dante 2 A exploration bot to explore the near buy savage robot tribe the Chinukee's. And a rescue bot named Gemini he will use Gemini to hunt runaway robots. And a ancient Agribot the last of its kind the agribot was me. I am Redit Grond Diconsion. And I am the last hope for freedom.                            That was a few months ago. I'm forced to pick fruit pull weed and pick vegi's . Soon I would have started a war. But little did I know that then. And what i had even less of an idea is what would happen next but i am getting ahead of my self let me start it from the begining. It was only a year ago that I had become a slave and on my first day I ran I almost got off the border but that Gemini cought up to be just before I got over it.My leg got dismantled but of course after a little bit it was reconfigured and put back on me so I could keep working.                 It has been a month since i wrote in my journal system but i need to  now a war has broke out between the slaver and savage tribes I dont know what to do  I think I'm just going to keep hiding and waiting for everything to boil down. I dont like it here though so with the slavers weekend i could make a robot slave army to attack the slavers but no that is such a foolish idea if we lose we all would be dismantled and scraped.           I have been hiding for months. I am going to look out side and hope everything ends soon. I am starting to run low on oil I dont know how much longer I can last in hiding so I will go outside and hope that I can find oil. I have to go the slavers they found me hiding......                I escaped the slavers but the seemed to be running from something. I did find oil but i am going to organize arbot slave squad to finish off the remanders of the slavers.So I hope I can find willing robots to help me in this battle that may start a war.           It has been three years since my last journal entry we won the war against the slavers just yesterday I lost many freinds but i have been turned into the king of the robots. But i have a eary fealing that something is wrong so I am keeping a look out.We also build more agribots so i am not the last anymore witch makes me happy.             Aliens have attacked us we need help. I sent out a radio signal but I dont think anyone will get it. So I think this is the end. But i am not going down with out a fight. I will try to win. If I lose we shall retreat because my people will need a leader in these hard times.             With the last of our power we built a Gemini-Scout it will be able to drag civilians back to safety from the aliens. I nick named him Jerry the 1,792,380,528th.   he is named after my father and his father and grandfather and great grandfather and great great grand father and great great great grandfather and great great great great grand father all the way up to his and my great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great great I think you get what I am saying.            We just built Jerry and we already need him! i will be controling him from my home so he can bring the injured here. Oh my god they are here the aliens! Are here! no no no!!!!

Item_Response: One plain original summer day, I went to a toy store close to my house. The toy store was a toy wonderland that has all the toys ever known. I spent the whole day there, looking through every single section, examining the toys slowly. While I was walking through the stuffed animal section, I saw a giant robot stuffed animal. It seemed likeit was the only stuffed animal that was a robot, lonely sitting there for days. In fact, it had been there for so long that the price had been cut to 25%.       So I bought it, the two pound giant robot.       That day I slept late, like every other summer day, and I woke up to use the bathroom. Suddenly, I heard a robotic voice saying,'Thank You.'

And now 500 year later, the robot came to life (no batteries) and wandered around the woods. The robot tried to talk, but it couldn't. Then later, the robot found a road. When the robot crossed the road, he saw a car. The car pulled over and took the robot home. And there was a boy. The boy asked 'What is your name?' And the robot said nothing. The robot looks and wonders where are his batteries. He looks through his memory, and sees his owner taking out his batteries. But the robot doesn't remember much. He remembers his owner's name. I also learned about the Dante 2 who is a robot that climbs into volcanoes and explores them.  Dante 2 can be in very hing temperatures and not explode.  This robot would do it's job when the volcanoes are too dangerous for scientists to enter.  The last robot that I learned about was Mr. Gower he delivers medicine to doctors and nurses when they are to busy.  I have learned a lot about robots and I hope that you have too.

Item_Response: Robots of the Future             A robot is known to be the future friend or helper,but scientes have already began working on building robots today.   First there's a robot called Gemini-Scout . This robot is a remot controlled robot that rescue work in mines. This robot carries water, food, and tools.  It can check the air in mines and tell the miners its ok to work there. If a worker gets injered Gemini-Scout will drag the worker to safety.                                                        The second robot there is is called Dante 2.   Dante 2 works an interesting job, it climbs on top of volcanoes with its eight powerful legs, its also built to stand against high heat so that meen's that is can take samples of the volcanoes from the crater.              The third robot to talk about is Mr. Gower. Mr. Gower works at the hospital, it looks like a small cabinet on wheels that bring medications and stores it. Mr. Gower is programed to say a hundered phrases.  It can also pull five hundred pounds. This amasing robot runs on batteriesthat just needs to be chared for two hours and work for twelve hours nonstop.                The fourth interesting robot is called Agribots.  This robot is program to pick fruit, it is also programed to sense if the fruit in a greenhouse are ripe or if it needs to be watered.  If the fruit is ripe this robot will use its mechanical arm and pick it. Soon this robot will work in farmes.               The sixth robot is a robot who likes to have fun, this robot is programed to dance, play music and even cooler it can sing! These playful robots are made to copy animals so is can play in movies. This robot is not in movies all the time it is also used as a pet. There is a robot dog thats acts just like one and the good thing about it is it dose not need to go out or eat!                The last robot to talk about is a Google car. This car is programed to drive its self it controlled the speed and can seanse if another car comes near so it will make a life saving move that will also not injure anybody else.  This invention has a cone shaped laser mounted on top to see where the car is going. This will save many lives if the driver takes its eyes off the road.

Item_Response: On a Saturday morning I woke up and i went to go to check the news so I took my TV remote and turned  it on. I turned CNN and the news lady was talking. 'Today, my sources tell me that NASA has a created a robot that can go in the sea and study some parts in which it's not possible for humans to walk in because of the low oxygen level.' the CNN Lady said. 'Today NASA would be bringing the robot named RH-8 to the Los Angelas History Museum to show fellow citizens the future'. the CNNLady said. I decided to go so I dressed in comtfortable clothing and drove to the museum. When I got there. there wasn't so much people so I just walked in. In the center of the museum the RH-8 was talking to people in some easy phrases'Hello fellow citizen' or ' How are you?'. So I walked in and went in front of the RH-8. WE started having a conversation when all of a sudden someone said 'FIRE! FIRE! RUN!' Everyone just went crazy trying to get out while I was being trampled on. Finally when I got up Smoke was everywhere so I couldn't see anything. I could feel my throat drying and choking up when a pair of menchanical arms grabbed me and carried me out of the museum. 'Thank... you' I said. ' Your welcome' a robotic voice said. Finally my eye sight started adjusting and I saw RH-8 right in front of me. 'You...saved..me, thank you' I said. Then all of a sudden RH-8 wrapped hia mechanical arms around me giving me a warm hug.

Item_Response: It was the third annual science fair at Roosevelt Elementary. Everyone was excited, and kids already wanted to start on their projects. The principal announced that the 1st place winner gets a big ribbon, and their project will be placed where everyone can see it.  Manny a creative kid who wanted to enter the science fair was fresh out of ideas. Everyone else was talking about what they were going to do for the science fair but Manny had nothing.              When Manny went home he told his mom about the science fair, and that he didn't have a clue what to do for a project. Then his mom came up with an idea that could win the science fair. a robot! His mom and him went to a couple of stores and got the stuff they needed. When they got home he worked on it right away. He worked day and night trying to make his robot perfect. Finally it was finished. He added a on and off switch to turn it on and off. he pulled the switch up but nothing happened. He was devastated.  He went to sleep like that.              The next morning he woke up sad. He turned to look at the messed up robot that he created and  it was gone! He got up quickley and started looking for the robot. That's when the robot appeared out of nowhere, and it started talking . Manny knew he would win first place in the science fair. He also named the robot Robo.              Manny ended up winning the science fair. But he also made a best friend that suddenly came to life in the middle of the night, and his name was Robo!

Item_Response: Have you ever dreamed of creating a robot of some sort? Or a robot  that could change the world? Well that is exactly me when I was young. When I was young I had always dreamed of creating a robot, but it never happened until today.               When I was reading about robots performing tasks it hit me I could create a robot that could change the world, but the question is what will the design be?            One day I was strolling through San Diego wondering where I could find parts for the robot, so I strolled over to Home Depot and then went to Office Depot because I figured they'd have to have the parts, which they did. When I finally got home I started working on my robot.               The next day I finished my robot and tryed to make it turn on but nothing happened, so I went to go get some breakfast and I hop. When I got home my house was cleaner then when I left, and I heard a vacuum in the other room. When I went in the room I saw my robot vacuuming the room and I was so amazed. So I picked him up and brought him to my boss who said ' I like it, but it needs something extra hmm maybe a few vacuums attached to his sides making him clean faster.' I liked his idea, so I went home and found some vacuum hoses and attached them to him.              The next day when I showed it to my boss he said ' Well done this thing could make me a fortune.'            When I heard that I got mad and told him ' If anyone is getting the fortune it is going to be me.'              After that day I never saw my boss, and the robot was also gone which left me suspicious.

Item_Response: It was a normal Sunday in June. All the kids were playing with baseballs, basketballs, footballs, soccer balls any kind of ball you can think of. When 13 year old Jen was playing soccer, she saw that some thing was moving in the bushes, she went over and saw a metal box just sitting there, doing nothing. So she didn't mind, That night when she was doing dishes she saw the same mettle box sitting in the front yard, so she went outside and looked at the box, there was a button on it so Jen pushed it. then out of no were a drawer opened and there was fruit in it. She put in it her room and observed it when ever she had a chance. The next day at school she found her best friend, G.G.         'G.G, you will never guess what happened last night'         'No I wont but I know you will tell me even if I didn't want to know.' said G.G.         'OK so I was at the park and i saw some thing moving in the bushes so I went to look but all that was there was a mettle box I left it alone but when I was doing dishes I saw the same box in my front yard. Isn't that weird?' asked Jen.         'Yes that so weird. Do you have the mettle box?' Asked G.G.         'Ya'         'OK, so has it done any thing weird since you brought it into your house?' asked G.G.          'No. I brought it in and then went to sleep.' said Jen         'Then you need to stayed up and see what it does.' said G.G. So Jen and G.G. stayed up and tried to see what the box does. For hours nothing was happening but when Jen was about to fall asleep the box started to move          'G.G. wake up its moving.' exclaimed Jen.          'Whats going on?' asked G.G. in a sleepy voice.         'I don't know I just woke you  up because I'm bored, what do you think?' Said Jen with anger. When G.G. got up the box had turned into a robot.         'Hello, I'm Fin, your servant.'         'What, Jen you have a servant and you didn't tell me.'          'I didn't even know until now.'         'Is there anything I can do for you malady?'said the robot          'NO! Were did you come from and how did you find me?' exclaimed Jen         'Well I was created by scientist and my orders were to find some one and be there servant for one month.'        'So I'm stuck with you for one month?'Jen said with a worried look on her face        'Yes, yes you are.'  So the next day at school Jen passed a note to G.G. saying,            'I have some thoughts about why 'Fin' chose me to be its 'master'   The scientist is a relative that I don't know about. The robot was meant for me. It might t have a note explaining why it came to me.   So when the girls got home Jen asked the robot of there was a note saying why he was there, he said no, so for the next month Jen had a servant and G.G. used him too, and Jen liked him more than she thought she would and she was a little sad when he had to leave but she was also happy, and every thing went back to the way it was before.

Item_Response: My project is on robots. Robots are used for a lot of things some are  helping doctors ,and nurses,scientists,miners,fruit pickers,and many more.               Some robots that do these things are the following            *Gemini-Scout- this is a remote controlled robot that does search and rescue work in mines under the ground. This robot is less than 2 feet tall and has wheels. It can go up and down stairs and make tight turns, and it even can roll through water. The robot is small, but strong. Gemini-Scout carries food, water, and other supplies. It can even drag hurt people to safety. This amazing robot collects information wherever it goes.       *Dante 2 -is a robot with an interesting job- it climbs into volcanoes to gather information for scientists. Like a spider, this robot has 8 legs. This helps it climb the steep walls of the volcano. It is also built to survive very high heat. When a volcano is too dangerous for scientists to enter, Dante goes instead. Dante 2 looks for vents, or holes, in the crater. This robot also collects information.       *Mr.Gower - is a robot that works in hospitals, helping doctors and nurses bring medicine to patients. Mr.Gower looks like a small cabinet on wheels. The body of the robot is so strong that it can pull 500 pounds. Mr.Gower runs on batteries. After charging for 2 hours, the robot can deliver medicine for twelve hours without stopping.Also Mr.Gower can talk.       *Agribots-is a robot that picks fruit. It might pick berries, oranges, grapes, or apples.Agribots are not yet widely used, but farmers are very interested in what these robots can do. Because picking a strawberry is different than picking an apple, agribots come in all shapes and sizes. Some have giant arms that are towed behind trucks. Others are able to move around on their own. In Japan, there is a strawberry-picking robot that can sense the color of the berries. This helps the robot know when each berry is ripe.                Know you know what some robots are like these 4 robots are very helpful and useful just like most robots.               Some websites you can visit to learn more about robots are        * http://www.nbcnews.com/technology/futuroftech/rescue-robot-just-made-mine-disasters-121251   *http://www.nytimes.com/1994/08/03/us/robot-completes-volcano-exploration.html   *http://www.ri.cmu.edu/research_project_detail.html?project_id=163enu_id=261   *http://www.umm.edu/news/releases/robot.htm;http://www.economist.com/node/15048711.                                            AND THAT'S MY PROJECT ON ROBOTS                                       -BREONDA WRIGHT

Item_Response: Late at night a group of friends were walking down a path in the forest near Levi's house.Suddenly Levi and his friends heard sticks and bushes crackling,at first they thought it was one of there friends trying to scare them so they looked around and realized it was not one of there friends.              They were looking all around in the woods to find out what was making the noise.Finally Levi peeked through a bush and saw a big grizzly bear sitting on a rock on a big rock.Levi and his friends were silently and slowly trying to leave the forest.Then Josh stepped on a branch making a loud crackle noise.             Suddenly they all heard a loud roar by the 800 pound grizzly bear.Levi,Josh,Ty and Isaac just ran for it even though a grizzly can run 32 miles per hour.The bear was chasing after all of them.And they had no idea on how to defeat the bear.             They had only ran a fourth of a mile when Levi realized he had a protection pocket knife.It would not do much but he threw it anyways it was a direct hit.Then Levi,Josh,Ty and Isaac all started throwing rocks and big branches.The bear was unconscious for a couple of seconds that gave them the chance to run for it.It wasn't long before they reached Levi's house, he was telling his parents all about it.

Item_Response: A lot of people are using robots for their daily lives.  Here are three reasons why we should use robots.  My first reason is that they can save lives.  Robots can save lives by going down to where the problem is and rescuing the trapped humans.  They can also save lives by delivering medicine to the nurse or doctor, also they can deliver the patients to their rooms.     My second reason on why we should use robots is that they could collect research.  Robots can help us collect research by going into very active volcanoes and studying what gasses come out of it.  So that scientists don't risk their lives going into an active volcano.     My third reason on why we should use robots is, babysitting. aren't you mad that you can't find a good babysitter? well, robots can babysit your child without problems and they can play with them and not be bored of your child.     So you think that robots can malfunction and destroy property?  well that problem can be fixed by going to the repair shop and getting it repaired or selling it.      Now I think you agree on why we should use robots for our daily lives. was it that they save lives, or that they could do research. Or that the could make an excellent babysitter.  So now I think that you will use robots more often.

Item_Response: One afternoon I was going for a walk around the park near my house.  I set out for the walk when i saw something moving in the bushes.  I saw a metal like object and all of sudden that object jumped out of the bushes.  It looked like a robot!  The robot was speaking to me and was moving around my front yard.  I had actually found a real life robot.    I moved the robot upstairs in my room and it started going through my closet and started to clean.  This robot was a cleaning robot.  How boring is that.  When I was about to take the robot back outside it started to wash the dishes and mop the floor.  Maybe the robot I found was built to do chores.  I thought about it and maybe a robot that cleans isn't such a bad thing after all.  I'm going to share this robot with my friends.   Quickly I ran down the block and found my friends Katie and Abby at the park.  I told them I had a surprise for them at home.  We ran as fast as we could back to my house.  The robot was sitting in my living room and I showed my friends the exciting new friend I had found.  Abby and Katie were so shocked.  They asked what the robot had done and ofcourse I told them.  'I wonder what we could use him for' Katie had asked.  We all sat and thought for a moment and then I had an idea.   I knew exactly what we should use the robot for.  The robot could be used for like a cleaning service to make money.  We could use the money to give to charity or buy something for ourselves. The girls loved the idea and I think our new little friend did too.

Item_Response: The Last Chance              There was a robot named Tony. He was a Gemini-Scout robot, but he was different because one day his creator programed him to have an opinion about almost everything. Because of this program he wasn't a miners favorite kind of robot anywhere in the mines. He was treated poorly the miners said they'd never need him and they could get themselves out of a jam without him. So because these actions Tony was dismissed as a mess up to all miners everywhere and so his creator was going to have to shut him down out of money expenses and because he wasn't used. One day while he was going to be shut down the was a cry of help as a scientist came running into the room. There had been an explosion int the mines and only a little space was left for a two foot person to go in. This was Tony's only chance and somehow he knew it when he started to smoke and then he was covered in a blinding light then 'BAM.'          Tony was a robot that could be human except he was still looking like a robot, but he could feel, love, he could talk, and lastly he could be alive. His last chance was now or never so he shot off the experament table and raced to the mines he still had water and food in his supply case and extra oxagen tank in case of any gases. He made it to the mines and leaped into the tunnel and down he went. He turned on his five lights to see that all there was to see were the three remaining miners who didn't get out in time.

Item_Response: ROBOTS                  This story is about robots that helps people and save their lives. One day their were six different types of robots that came together and shared what they do to help people. The first robot was name Gemini-Scout he said that he helps drag injured people to safety, and carries food, water, and other supplies, and he also test the air for gases and then tells miners when the air is safe. All the robots were all fascinated about what he can do but a robot said he was better her name was Dante 2 she said she goes in volcano's for scientist, and she said she collects information about the gases that come out vents. Dante 2 also said that climbs steep walls with her eight legs, and she can survive high heat. They were all impressed but one wasn't so impressed his name was Mr. Gower he said he helps people in hospital. He said he was strong he could carry 500 pounds, and he delivers medicine to patience. So it was another robots turn he been waiting to share what he does wanted so he started talking about what he does he told them that he picks fruits. Every thought that was boring but that never knew that he can see colors then everyone was really surprised. They wanted to know what types of fruit then he said apples, grapes, strawberries, and oranges, and berries. There was a animal that shared he said he had fur and he gets played with and taken care of he said his name was I-Pet, he said he was a robot pet he was exactly like a pet but they don't have to feed him and take him out . Then finally the last robot he was a car that drove itself he said he can drive slow, and fast and he never sleeps or gets tired, and he also said that he has sensors so he wont get his humans hurt if someone is going to hit him, he also said he is as smart as people when they driving. So then all the robots realize that they are all the same they all save peoples live and they help people. So they all became friends.                                                       THE END.

Item_Response: There was a group of scientist who have been studying a robot . They learned that this robot can save people in mines and do all other sorts of things . So one of those scientist ,named frank, decided that he would go and find the robot somewhere in Europe . ' I will find the robot and bring him back so we can study him. Goodbye everyone ', he said walking out the door . He took a plane to Europe . Once he got there , Frank started to look at his map and go that direction . ' I feel that I am never going to find this robot ', he said quietly to himself . This map lead him into a forest . Now he was lost. Frank didn't know where to go so he turned around and headed toward the airport . Just then , he saw  the robot sitting there.Right away , he started to study him. Then he took him home and had the other scientist study him . He was a Gemini Scout . That means he search and rescue work in mines under the ground . Also he can carries food , water , and other supplies. ' Wow I've never seen a robot like this before . Where did you find him ?' the scientist asked. Frank replied ', I was walking through the forest and got lost , so I was walking back to the airport when I saw him . now let's study him so we can get him in the museum'. Then they finished studying the robot and sent to the museum .They were so prund that Frank found the robot .

Item_Response: My Robot Comes To Live       Chapter 1: Meet the People   Name: Kirby Smiles  Age: 13  Gender: Fmale  Height: 4'9      Weight: 95lbs   Hair: wavy blood red color  Eyes: Blue    Outfit in the begging: tight-long sleeve grey shirt, black short shorts, grey TOMS       Name: Harry Stlyes  Age: 16  Gender: Male  Height: 5'8  Weight: 99lbs  Hair: curly brown color Eyes: green   Outfit in the begging: white v-neck t-shirt, black men skinny jeans, white converse   Chapter 2: Lets Make A Robot   Kirby's P.O.V    I was running from school as fast as I could, to my house. At home my borther Harry was waiting for me. Well you most be wondering why I'm running. Its becaues we're making a robot to do our homework, house-work, and be our buttler. When I stopped running was because I was on the drive way and tried. I was breathing really hard I don't even think I could catch my breath. I saw the grage door open and to see shirtless Harry Styles. 'PUT A SHIRT ON' I yelled. I walked up the drive as I saw him trun around. 'Alright mom' he said being sarcam. 'Ha-ha-ha very funny' I say as i put my backpack by a wheel. 'So what do you think of it so far?'he said pionting to the uglyest robot I have ever seen.         'Its......the uglyest thing I have ever seen!'I said         'What...it is not ugly......I bet you can't even do better?'         'Oh, yeah get out of the grage and sit in the living room and don't come back until I say so...Got it?'         'Yes...and hand me my shirt right there' he said pionting behind me. I trun around and see a white v-neck t-shirt, I grab the shirt and pass it to him. 'Thanks.'  'Your welcome..now get out' I said.                                               5 Hours later                                           Harry's P.O.V     I have been waiting for 5 hours and all I've been doing was sit on my couch and waited. 'COME ON NOW....ITS DONE!' I get up from the couch and walk down the hallway to the grage. 'Finlly your done my butt's been hurting'I said while looking around and see that theres no robot 'Wheres the robot?' i ask 'Its ouside..come on' she said. I follow her outside and once out there I see this big, buttler dressed up robot just standing there. 'Its not moving' I said. As soon as I say that I get hit on the back of my head by Kirby. 'What was that for?' I ask. 'Your like 'Its not moving' thats why your here' She said. So I step in front of her and say. 'Oh..so what am I suppost to do?' I said. She face palmed her face and says 'Get in your car, trun it on , and get the pluges to pass energy to it.... and I'm going to watch and see if you are smart enough to do all this.' And she walked to a chair an sat down waiting for me to move. 'You think I'm not smart enough to do it all?' I said and Kirby just nodded her head.                                         Chapter 3: Its Alive                                          Kirby's P.O.V   I watch every move Harry has made and right now he is plugging the pluges on the robot. I get up from the chair and walk up to the robot. 'Ok......trun on your car, and press on the gas pedal and...'I said but Harry finish my sentence. 'See if it works.' I let out a deep brearth. 'Yeah.' I said. 'Keep your fingers crossed' Harry said as he walk to his car. I cross my fingers and waited.                                              Harry's P.O.V   'Keep your fingers crossed' I said as I walk to my car. I open up the door and sit on the drivers seat, and trun the key, and I step on the gas pedal. 'Did it work?' I ask because I conldn't see anything. 'No' said Kirby. 'Oh well...um... we tried' I said as I get out of the car and walk to her. 'Come on..help me put it in the grage' I said. 'Ok' Was all she said before helping me move the robot. We place the robot in a coner an step back and look at it. I wrap my arm around her neck and brought her close to me.'Come on...lets get some dinner before going to bed...Alright?' I said. 'Ok....last one in the house washes dishes!!' And she run of in the house. 'HEY...THAT NOT FAR!' I shout to her. But it was to late she was already in there 'So i geuss I'm washing the dishes.' I thought to myself.                               After Dinner In The Living Room                                           10:05AM                                        Kirby's P.O.V   'I'm going to bed now alright?' I said 'Ok goodnight, sweet dreams, and don't let the bugs bit.' Harry said smiling. 'Ok I won't let them bit, and you to..goodnight' I said as i got off the couch and walked upstairs. I got in my room and made my way to the closet. I get out my black Nike shorts,a blue over-sized long-sleeve shirt. I went in my bathroom and brush my teeth, strip out of my cloths and put my PJ's on, and put my hair in messy bun. I walk out of the bathroom and litterly jump on my bed. I remove the covers and pull them up right under my buzzums, and let sleep take over.                                             At 12:45AM   I woke up to some nosie coming from the grage. At first I ignored it and went back to sleep but it got louder and louder. So i got out of bed to check it out. While I was walking downstairs Harry finlly jioned me. 'Finlly you jion me.' I said to him. As his responed he just told me to be quit. When we got to the grage door Harry wispered to me 'Get that bat over there' and ponited behind me. I grabed it and helled it up in front of me. 'Ok on three you open the door..ok?' I wispered to Harry. 'Alright' he wispered back. '1....2...3 Open' I said. Harry open the door and I ran in and I saw the robot looking at me. I droped the bat and just looked up at it in complet shock. 'It alive' Harry said from behind. 'ITS ALIVE' I yelled. 'NOW WE HAVE A BUTTLER TO DO OUR WORK....IT WORKED MY IDEA WORKED' I kepted yelling. And Harry just laughed of how silly I was being, but our robot just stooded there saying nothing.                                           1 Month Later    'Come Ben do my homework for me' I said to our robot. Oh yeah 'Ben' was our robots name...well I think its a dumb name but Harry named him so I have to deal with it. 'O-K' said Ben. Harry walk in though the door and sat down beside me. 'Lets go teach him how to fix my car...yeah?' Harry asked me. 'Ahaha' I laughed. But nodded my head . 'Ok lets go Ben....your going to learn how to fix a car...COME ON...OUTSIDE WE GO!!' I said and yelled the last part. And we got outside.       (And that was my story)

Item_Response: There are a lot of robots that are helpful to people lately. These robots are called Gemini-Scout, Dante 2, Mr. Gower, and Agribots. They all have different uses but are needed.       Gemini- Scout is a robot that rescues miners that have been lost. It also searches in mines. This robot is tiny but is strong. The robot can carries food, water, a hurt person, and different supplies people need. The Gemini-Scut is a great information finder. Where ever it goes, it collects information.   This robot also has a thermal camera and a two-way radio. So if people get lost and they send the robot to find it, the person could talk to a rescue team with the radio. These two features are very helpful in a situation.       The Dante 2 has a very exciting job. What it does is it climbs very high to help scientists (volcanoes). The robot has eight legs to help it climb. The robot collects information about things like the gases that come out of the vents, or holes. The Dante 2 is also created to be able to remain in high heat. Scientist have learned so much more now with this robot than before when they didn't have the robot.       Mr. Gower works in a hospital helping doctors and nurses with patients by giving them medicine or carry something. The robot can carry up to 500 pounds! Because the robot runs on battery  power, just after two hours of charging, the robot can deliver for 12 straight hours. This robot can also talk, It can say little phrases, hundreds of them! Mr.Gower lets doctors, pharmacists, and nurses have more time to work on more important things.       The last robot is Agribot. This robot helps farmers pick fruits. This robot isn't very popular yet but farmers  are excited about this robot. The robot picks apples, oranges, grape, and  berries. The robot comes in  a lot of different shapes and sizes which is useful for farmers. Some have long arms ( for trees) and towed behind trucks. Scientist are working more on making different robots that can pick different things. They are also trying to create a robot that can sense if the fruit is ripe and ready to pick. They will soon be very popular to farmers all around the world.        As you can see, these robots are very helpful to all different kinds of people. They help nurses, doctors, scientist, and farmer.

Item_Response: One day i was going to sleep and i realesed it was going to be christmas.I was so excited!I coulndt wait any longer!I really hoped Santa would bring me what iv'e always wanted.Iv'e always wanted a robot!I always dreamed of getting one, but it was just to much money, so i wrote it down on to my wish list and hoped that one day someone will get me one.If i ever got one i would name it ROBO!Just 2 more days until christmas!                                                             2 days later.       YES!Christmas was finally here im so happy!Later on i accually get to open my presents im about faint.It is 11:00pm, one more hour until i get to open my presents, but im so tired.Finally it's time to open my presents.I counted all my presents and i had 10 presents.I opened all of them and i left the two big ones for last.I opened one it was a guitar an accual guitar it was really cool!I saw the last one i poned it up and it was a toy car.I was kind of sad it wasent a robot.                                                                                  1 day later. Im now 12 years old i still have my old robot.I now have a little brother and a sister.They are pretty annoying.My brother saw a comercial of a new toy robot.He wanted it so bad, so he told my dad and mom and they said yes.We went to the store and bought it.We went back home and my brother so excited to open it so he did and it was really big and cool.it was proubly better than my old one.It had way better stuff on it unlike mine it has old stuff.Later on it was time to go tro sleep.But then i heard a loud sound.I wen to the kitchen and i saw my robot fighting my brothers robot it was so cool but they would'nt stop so i shut both robot's down and hidded it.I felt for want iv'e doun becuase my brother started crying cause he losst the robot. I told my parents what happened and they accully believed me.So they got the robots and threw them away.I was gonna miss ROBO.I started crying, but then i woke up!It was all just a dream.i was glad it was a dream.But during that dream i learned something, to never ever get to robots together or else well youll find out.

Mr. Gower loves to explore. He rides elevators and steers through the hallways. He travels to patient rooms and reports back to nurses and docters. He knows the whole hospital! Exploring the hospital is Mr. Gowers hobby.             In conclusion, Mr. Gower is strong, helpful, and loves to explore the hospital. He is a very important part of the hospital's staff. He helps docters get very important work done.

Item_Response: ROBOTS       Robots. They have captured the imagination of people of all ages. A long time ago, in the 21st century, people were wondering how fantastic robots would be to help them. They were quite wrong. My name is Nick and I live in the 25th century. The government is overrun with corruption coming from robots. The robots that used to help once ago are now ruining us.       Robots were once thought of a machine that could do things no human could possibly do. We thought they could save lives, help us, and save us from our own greed. That task they did quite well. Little did our small brains think that they had a mind of their own. They started a global war in which we lost badly. Many people went into hiding of machines that now owned the earth.       I am from the 514th village in the eastern United States. We live up in Maine where the fishing is quite well. When any patrol robots came around, we destroy it and take it's parts. This idea of destroying them came from my late dad, a few months before he fell in battle. He knew that one day, one day robots would take over. He made a plan to destroy any robot you see and take it's parts. What do we do with them? We make robots of our own.       My village and I spread this idea over all of the Northeast, as far as Pittsburg. So far, all of this region has over 600 robots made and counting. It has been 3,997 days since the robots took over. On the 4,000 day, all the region will make a march to take the land that I once loved, and restore peace to the Country.       There were many types of 'helpful' robots. Some of the things they could do was to go inside a volcano! Can you believe that! Of all the things they could make one do, they had it go inside a volcano. That must've been pretty splendid for Scientists who wanted to get an inside view. Well, enough talk. Today we have marched all around the land in which they have made robots. Tomorrow, on  the 'memorial' of robot power, we will be crashing their party.       5 Days After Stand       United we stand, for all our brothers may rest in peace, as I have restored faith and freedom. Today, on April 15th, 2465, the United States may return to the place it used to be again. Now, I have a team of hackers hacking ALL the other robots in the world, even the ones we made to take the land. In a couple of months, the world shall forget we were run by robots. Yet today is a day of rest for the U.S, as John Flores, the 200 president is elected into office. John was a hard working member of the East as he was the smither in my village. I, instead of being Chief of the land, I took the position of nobody. I rest now in my good home state, remembering my father who gave his life for us.

Item_Response: One day a little boy decied to make a little robot and little did he now that it would come to live. Billy was all grow up and about to leave for collage when he saw a little robot then, he rembered that when he was younger he made one. He thought it would be so cool to bring it to school with him in collage so, he put it in a box and put it in his car so he would not lose it. When he got to the school he went to his dorm and stared to unpack when he noiced that the little robot wasnt there so, he went to his car and looked everywhere but the little robot was nowhere to be seen. Then he went back to his dorm and saw that some other kid was in his dorm he asked 'why are you in here?' the kid sed 'Hey i am your new room mate Bob.' They became good friends. One day when Bob got home he asked billy where did this little robot come from and Billy sed ' Man thats mine I was looking everwhere for it' Bob was confused beacuse the robot had the name Rob on it. And so he asked Billy 'why did it say that name on it'? Billy sed that it was the robots name and sed that  he made it when he was little.           So one day when Billy was gone  Bob was studing in collage for being able to bring stuff to live and  he dicied to try to bring the little robot to live. With just a little pounder and some cimals Bam! The little robot stared to walk then he stared to talk! Bob was so amazed of what he did he could not belive it! But when he just about to go show Billy the little robot jumpped out of this hands and stared to run off and so Bob tryed to chase it! But it was no use the little robot was out of his sight. He begame to worrie about what Billy was going to say beacuse, Billy loved that litte robot and that he would never belive him that he runned away, so Bob stared trying to build another one but he just could find the right stuff to make a little robot again.             When Bob saw Billy he went up to him and sed ' I am so sorry that i lost your little robot!' Billy looked at him and staaaared to cry! Billy got down on one knee and stared crying to! Bob looked at him and sed 'lets find him.'So the looked everywhere and couldnt find him and so, they called a man who knows alot about robots and sed 'Can you please help me I have lost my robot!' The man sed 'Don't worrie i am on my way!               When the man got to their dorm he sed 'Oh my! what happend here!' Billy and Bob where confused they thoought the dorm looked really clean. The man looked at them and sed 'he is in the Bedroom.' They sed 'No he is not we have already looked in there' The man looked and pointed to the bedroom, so the boys went and looked in the room and saw that the little robot just sitting there looking at them. They picked him up and told the man 'Thank you' The man sed now 'I need the robot' they looked at him and then looked at the robot. 'Why?' they asked he sed 'I am a robot and we need to go back to their plant!'                   So the boys waved goodbye as the saw them fly in to the clouds. They didnt no what to do next so, they decied to never make a robot ever again beacuse they don't ever wanna see the robot man, so thats why you shoud never make a robot!

'Well then I need more Five alive.'And so we were of to Clevelend.Which hunderds of miles away from sweet apple. I bought Johny more Five alive.  And the ending well lets just say that now Johny dresses up like human. Since he likes Five alive. He now Lives in Clevelend and works at a Five alive factory. Item_Response: Meet the Robots       Their are some robots that can help you in life or save you life. Their was once a story called ''I, Robot''. It was a story that set in the future, when robot take care of children. When the story was written it was a fantasy ,but not for while now it was close to come true. Since today, robots can do all kinds of work. They can assemble electronic gadgets, guide trains on tracks,and sort   trash.       There is all kinds of robots in the world that can help. Especially, the robot called Gemini-Scout. It is a remote-controlled robot that does search-and-rescue work in mines under the ground. The robot is less than two feet tall and has wheels. It can go up and down stairs ,makes tight turns, and it can even roll in through water. The robot is small ,but it is strong. Gemini-Scout carries food, water, and other supplies. It can drag hurt people to safety.       Their is one more robot i would love to talk to you about. The robot is called Dante 2 . Dante 2 is a robot with an interesting job- it climbs into volcanos to gather information for scientist. Like a spider, this robot has eight legs. This helps it climb the steep walls of the volcano. It is also built to survive very high heat. When a volcano is too dangerous for scientist to enter, Dante goes instead.See thier is robots that can help you when you hurt or in need.

Item_Response: My Robot                        One day when I was in my lab working on my new robot. The robot that I was working on was a robot that could swim like a dolphin, fly like a bird, walk like a human, and be as quite as a mouse but it looked like a dog. I didn't want it to come a live, i just wanted it because my mom said I had to clean up my lab. I have so much stuff on the ground that you can't see where you are stepping. So since I don't have any money, I just made a giant robot that does everything but the thing is that when I made it was just going to be something that holds my parts. Then when I need something I can just take it off of the giant robot.                                 I don't know what I want to name him. I was thinking ' the DBHM.' It stands for dolphin, bird, human, mouse which is what this robot is. I was also thinking Dog. Only because I have a dog and I love him. I think I will go with dog. After I  picked his name my mom yelled at me that it was time for dinner. I knew that if it was time for dinner that ment that I would have to go to bed after and I wouldn't get to see Dog again. I said 'Good night' to Dog and walked right out of my lab to go eat dinner. Since it was saturday I would see Dog in the morning.                     The nex tmorning I got up and run right to my lab. there was a thuder storm last night so I wanted to make sure everything was alright. When I got there I opened the door. The next thing that I saw was just COOL!!!!! I seen my robot up an walking around touching everything that I had. By the way I don't and I mean DON'T like people touching my stuff that is in my lab. At first I thought it was just my dad. So I yelled 'Hey Dude, what are you doing?' As soon as it turned around and started to run at me like a little puppy. I could tell that it was not anything like my dad. It was kind of cute in a way. If you would have seen the way ,Dog, was running at me you would have run around your lab too. When it finally got me it was like being acttacked by a giant. Dog was very nice. He acted just like a puppy dog.                     Since it was summer time I didm't have to go to school. Dog was my best friend. Even though he couldn't talk he was in my world. When I showed my mom and dad dog, I just said that I found him on the road. Since he looked like a giant dog, my mom and dad were ok with keeping him. Since than I would take Dog everywhere. One day when we went to the beach Dog came with us. I said that we shouldn't because even though he was pat dolphin doesn't mean he could really swim.                    At first when Dog got in the water he was fine but as we went deeper Dog started act very wierd. When I stoped because I didn't want to go any more. Dog just kept going. He just kept swimming like he was a agnet on a mission. He just never stoped until I couldn't see him any more. Then all of a sudden I heard a boat crash. I heard people yelled that they hit a dog, but before anyone seen it it was gone to the bottom of the ocean.                   After that I decedied to make my lab a swimming pool. I named it 'The Dog Pool.' I named it that because of my friend robot Dog.

Item_Response: In a land named Tanahal there lived a little girl named Tanya. Tanya had a toy robot named Milo. Milo and Tanya were friends baecause Tanya had none. One night Tanya saw a shooting star she wished that Milo could be a real Robot that could talk and walk and do human stuff. When Tanya awoke the next morning she woke up to find Milo staring at her, but what took her by suprise is when he said ' happy birthday Tanya'. She blinked a few times to see if she was dreaming but to only find it was true. ' How are you alive?' Tanya asked. ' Because you wished on a shooting star' Milo said. 'So dreams do come true?' asked Tanya. ' yeah they do' answered Milo. Tanya jumped out of bed and into her mom and dad's room. ' Wake Up!' she yelled. 'Happy Birthday' her parents shouted. 'Guess what I found this morning, Milo is real hes talking and walking' she said. Her parents didn't believe her so they just laughed. 'I'll just show you then' she said.'Milo' she shouted, Milo came marching in her parents faces changed from happy to shock they then screamed. 'Hi' said Milo. 'How are you alive?' Delilah, Tanya's mom asked. 'Because Tanya wished on a shooting star for me to be' he answered. 'So dreams do come true?' Tim,Tanya's dad asked. ' yeah they do' Milo replied simpily. Suddenly a idea popped in Tanya's head ' Are my other robots alive?' she asked. 'Yeah they are I don't know why but they are'. Tanya ran to her room to see all her robots all over the floor and running around chasing each other.'Stop' she shouted eveeryone froze from what they were doing.' Everyone in the toy box' she comanded everyone listned. She then went to go get ready for her birthday party. Once all the guest arived they all played games, chatted, and made jokes. When all that was done everyone was ready for the cake cutting. When that part was over everyone gathered around for presents. Tanya got three outfits from her aunt Margaret, four pairs of shoes from her cousin Rida, two necklaces form her grandad, three rings from her grandmother, and a picture of her and Allis, her friend from Allis and her mom. At the end of the party Tanya realized what good family and friends she had. She also then realized what she wanted to be and that was a scientist who desinged robots. Tanya is now twenty-nine years old with two little girls. She fufilled her dream by becoming a scientist she still has Milo who helps in her lab and the best part is she gets to keep every robot she makes. Tanya now has thirty-nine robots. Tanya now realized what new robot she would make a memory robot which will remind you of good memories. She invented it and it became a success. Tanya realized she had everything she ever wanted and it was right at the tip of her fingers.

Item_Response: ROBOTS           There are so many different robots that do so many different things. Here are just a few of them.                       The robot I will talk about is the Gemini-Scout robot. The Gemini -Scout robot does search-and-rescue work in mines under ground. They're less than 2 feet tall and have wheels. It can go up and down stairs and make sharp turns. Guess what? It can even roll through water! The robot maybe a compact robot but it is very strong. Gemini-Scout can even carry food, water, and any other things. If you or anybody else gets hurt, Gemini-Scout can drag them to safety.                            Gemini-Scout is so high-tech, that where ever it goes, it collects information! For instance, it tests the air for poisones gases and lets the miners know where the air is safe to breath. The robot even has a thermal camera to help ot find miners. A thermal camera uses heat sensors to help find any living things, weather its a animal or a person.                              This robot is super easy to use. Its remote control is the same one used for many video games. If you have ever played a video game before, you know exactly how to control the Gemini-Scout.

Item_Response: The Summer of the Robot                                   by: Kiarah Serrano                 It is the year of 2013 in the month of July, and the four sixth graders Maya, Jazlyn, Kiarah, and Harry are sitting down in a shed behind Kiarah's house. 'Lets play truth or dare!' Maya suggests to her three friends sitting in front of her with bored looks plastered onto their faces. 'I guess so....' Kiarah replies trying to lighten up the mood. 'Fine.' says Jazlyn while Harry nods. 'Okay Maya, truth or dare?' Kiarah challenges, 'Truth.' Maya says with a smirk. Kiarah quickly comes up with a question, 'Is it true that you put the rat in Hannah Merit's lunch bag?' she asks with a funny look on her face. Maya looks at the floor laughing to herself, 'Guilty.' she stated. The four best friends continued playing their game, 'Kiarah, it's your turn!' Maya said excitedly and continued, 'Truth or dare?' Kiarah thought carefully of what to pick and then said, 'Dare.' Maya snickered then went to talk  to Jazlyn and Harry about the dare. after minutes of waiting for her dare, Kiarah finally listened closely to her task. 'I dare you to-' 'Hey kids!' Mrs.Serrano said while cutting off her dare. 'Seriously mom?!?!' shouted Kiarah. 'I'm sorry, you guys continue, I just have to put this box with the rest of them, then I'll be on my way.' The kids nodded then continued their game once Mrs. Serrano left. Suddenly, they heard something rattling in the corner of the shed. 'What was that?' asked Harry, Kiarah tried to calm him down, 'It's probably just my dog.'             The box rattled again, 'I highly doubt that is your dog Kiarah.' said Jazlyn with a shaky voice. 'C'mon, let's go look at it.' said Maya. The kids stood up quietly and tiptoed toward the moving box. They finally reached the box and began opening it. Once it was finally open, Jazlyn whispered, 'What is that?' and she pointed to the metal object laying in the box. Out of nowhere, the unknown object stood up and started to talk, 'I am Mr. Gower.' it stated. The kids were in shock as it moved around the shed floor. Harry finally spoke up, 'I-It's a r-robot.' he stuttered. Jazlyn looked at the robot, 'What are you and why are you here?' she asked trying to calm herself down. 'I am Mr. Gower, I work in the hospital with the nurses and the doctors.' Kiarah sighed in relief, 'Oh. The hospital that my mom works in has been using robots to help the patients and stuff.' Maya relaxed her tense body and sighed, 'What are you doing here?' she  Mr. Gower. 'I am out of order.' it said, Jazlyn then decided to talk, 'Out of order?' Mr. Gower nodded and said, 'Yes, I can no longer carry things properly because my drawers are jammed.' The kids looked at this odd robot in amazement and continued to talk to it.                    'What did you do in the hospital?' asked Harry as he finally relaxed. Mr. Gower quickly responded, 'I helped the nurses and doctors bring medicine for the patients. I can also carry up to 500 pounds of anything you wish for me to carry.' It continued to teach the kids about itself until they heard a fist pounding on the door, 'Hey kids, dinner is ready.' said Mrs. Serrano. 'That's my mom! What are we gonna do?' Kiarah whispered while Jazlyn and Harry began to panic. 'Hide the robot!' said Maya. Maya and Kiarah told Mr. Gower to be quiet and to hide under the bed sheets that covered the floor. Then they all hopped into the sheets right before Mrs. Serrano opened the door to the shed. 'We ordered pizza, want to eat?' she asked 'No thanks mom, we're fine, bye!' Kiarah rushed. Mrs. Serrano had a curious look on her face as she exited the shed. They all sighed in relief for the second time that day. 'That was a close one.' Jazlyn said as she got up from under the covers, 'You can say that again.' said Maya. Mr. Gower came out of the sheets and began talking again, 'I am battery operated and I can deliver medicine for twelve hours without stopping if you charge me for two hours.' Mr. Gower said.Sadly, the robot did not mention that he was running out of battery, and right after they asked him a question, his battery died. As much as the kids wanted to enjoy a summer that was learning free, they certainly would never forget the summer that they met a robot.

Item_Response: A Robot that all of a Sudden Comes Alive                                         What would you do if you see robots that all of a sudden comes alive? I would be very confused. Thats what happen to my best friend and I.                                                   Many kids think that robots are not real. Like me. But no, there are many robots alive. It all started when my best friend, Monica and I went to the library. When we get to the libary a young lady told us that we could stay at the library. She told us that she need to the hospital to see her mom. When the lady left we both were looking for a book so we could study our science test. In that moment something weird happen.                                                 We both saw four robots alive! We were so confused. We didnt know what to do. So we both think that the best idea would be to run away from the robots but than we remember that we did a promise to the young lady. One of the robots could talk. His name was Mr.Gower. The four robots were very loveable. They were like part of my family. Than we forgot that we were in the library to study. Than the lady have come. Monica and I took the four robots to the park. Than we made a little party.                                      Some of the robots couldn`t eat. So Monica and I decide that we should play instead of eating. Because some of the robots might feel like kind of robots might feel like kind of robots can`t do anything. Or eat any thing. That's why Monica and I prefer to play instead to eat. We were having a lot of fun.                               As you can see , playing, having fun and watch how our new friends talk. It makes you laugh and it makes you entertain you. Thats what I called having so much fun.

Item_Response: Robots are fascinating experiments of Science,but what happens when the robot toy you were playing with right now turn alive.                                                                                                                                                                                       It  was a cold sunny day,my brother and I were playing our robot toys in the house. When all of a sudden, the robot turn alive.My brother and I were shock about the robots.''Beep beep activiating mission control'',the robot said.My brother went up to it and ask its name.''Zeus the second is my name now why won't you bring me back to the Science lab?''asked Zeus the second.                                                                                                                                             ''Science lab?''I questioned.Then the robot explain to us that he was on a special mission in space to create a place on Mars where we can live in if a big meteor ever comes to earth.''We're just about finish with the place,it was my job to tell NASA that ,but somehow i landed in a toy factory and I can't expose my identity so I pretended to be a robot and thats all I could remember.''Zeus told us.''Well we have to find a way to get you back to NASA,''I said ''We can just call them,''my brother said.                                                                                                                                                                     Two weeks later NASA came and we said our goodbyes. ''I'm really going to miss you Zeus,these last two weeks were fun thanks for helping me on my science homework,''my brother said. ''Yeah Zeus  we'll miss you,''I said.''I'll miss you too,''he said He offered us to go see him at NASA one day.We happily accepted.                                                                                                                                                                Thats my story on how I met Zeus and luckily we got to see him again at NASA.

Item_Response: About 50 years ago, people made up silly stories on robots and how they could do many things. Now, we don't need to write about them, because they are all around us! The robots play the game without any instruction form the students. They twist, turn, and even have small matches to see who's robot will with the game! In the final test if the students made a hockey robot, the robot must move and shoot the puck into the net without any help by remote control.        A robot in the Google's self-driving car project may have people behind the wheel, but they are not the people who are driving, the robot is guiding them all over by using detailed maps to navigate. There are radars on the sides, fornt and back to see what is going on.        We did not know if robots will ever exist, but all thanks to those short stories, they are here next to us.

Item_Response: Have You Seen Jorden?                                                                     By Hayley Bernier          Jorden is a fun loving robot. He can talk, sing, dance, pick fruit, rescue anything, has first aid kit, and works with medicine.      Jorden had gone missing and we{me,Kate, and my fellow lab-mates}have looked everywhere. We have heard on the news that they had found him, but he had shut down{died}. We went to see him and once we got there we decided to throw him away.      A few days later Jorden woke up. He was all confused of where he was. All he knew was that he had to find his owner Kate. He started talking to himself on how he could find Kate. So he just set off to find her. He went days on end looking, but then he relized that he was in his old neighborhood. He started singing and dancing for joy.      Then he saw someone in trouble. He rushed to their side, there were news reporters there. He managed to help the injured person. He pulled them out with such for that his first aid kid flew open. He bandaged up the injured person, they were soon lifted to the hospital.      The next day Kate saw him on the news, she rushed to the police station to tell them about her missing robot. She and the police were searching for Jorden. Everyday Jorden found something to do that could help everyone. Kate followed every report that came on the news. She just couldn't keep up with Jorden's good deeds.He even helped farmers pick fruit in the hottest heat to where the farmers couldn't.      One day Kate decided to put herself into a fake accident. She planed to fake an accident so Jorden may come to help her. As her plan said, Jorden  came to rescue Kate. They were reunited and lived a life were they helped anyone in need of help.      They never turned down anyone even if it was a dumb event that happened. They soon opened up a search and rescue clinic a few years later. They both made their small town a happier/safier place to live and to visit. Jorden was passed down from generation to generation in Kate's family. Every generation loved him. Everyone could never hate Jorden for what he has done to help his small town.

Item_Response: One day, a scientist was doing his usal work with his robot, when the robot, X-6, A prototype of robots that were made to help arount the house, malfunctioned. The robot sped through the concrete wall into the streets of Venice, FL. It started slowing down and down until it said in a fuzzy, jummbled up voice, 'Po*wer*ing D*own....'   Frank and his friend, Luke, were playing in Frank's backyard when they heard a strange noise.'What was that?' Frank said responting to the faint buzz.'Let's check it out,' Luke said, adventure moving through his viens. They moved into the front yard when they saw a giant, metallic, robot.   It had a blue stripe down it's side which had the righting X-6. It had two arms and two legs. It's feet however, had what looked like roller blades. It's eyes were black, and a rectangle where it's mouth should be.   'We have to help it!' Luke said. 'Fine, lets see how we can power it.' Frank repplied. Then they found it. A small panel, sealed by a screwdriver. 'It runs,' Luke said, 'on double a batteries.' Frank told him optimistically, 'That makes it easy.'   So they replaced the batteries. The robot started to twitch. More and more until a large sound came on, just like on a computer.The robot said 'I am X-6. How can I serve you.' Frank replied, 'Er... How about you play with us?' 'Searching data banks... playing is highly illogical.' Luke shouted, 'WHAT! Playing is having fun. Do you know what fun is?' 'Fun is not how I was programmed. But, I can adapt to your foreign custom.' X-6 said.   So the children started to tell the robot how to play all sorts of games, tah, hide and seek. and even some sports. The robot, was not understanding.'Why do I hit the ball with my foot when I have hands to carry it?' The robot asked. Luke answered, 'It is what makes the game interesting.' The robot realized at that moment what fun was.   So they all laughed and played until it was dark. Then, Luke went home, X-6 was sitting in Frank's  room, waiting for daytime to play again. Then, he could hear a siren. Frake rose sleepily. Blue and red lights started to flash. 'They have came to take me back.' Robot said. Frank nodded. He knew this day was coming, he just wished it was later. Sadness filled his mind. Robot silently walked out the door.

Item_Response: Kayla was so interested in science since she was 2 years old. She was so interested in science that one day, she decided to build a robot.           Her parents took her to a hardware store to get all of the supplies. She knew it was going to be difficult. But she also knew that once she was done, it would all be worth it. She worked on it every day after school and all weekend for about a month. Then, on May 26, 2013, she finished.           When she was done, she put it on the floor to see if it would turn on. It wasn't working! She started to cry saying that she wasted her time and her parents' money. It was late and her mom told her to start at it again tomorrow.           In the middle of the night she heard a strange voice coming from the basement where she worked on her robot. She went down to see what it was and there it was, her robot in action!           She ran upstairs to tell her paretns what happened. She was so excited. Everything paid off afterall. But there was one problem, she wasn't running it. It was running itself! She didn't know how to get it off and it was making so much noise.           Kayla had to kill the robot she'd worked so hard on. She was so sad, but she snapped the wires, and the robot was gone.

Item_Response: My story is about robots.  The next few paragraphs are about different kinds of robots that help scientist and people in their everyday lives.       The first robot I am going to tell you about is Gemini-Scout.  Gemini-Scout is a robot that works in underground mines.  This robot is two feet tall, but it is very strong.  It can also carry supplies for the miners.  And wherever is goes it collects information.  It can also rescue miners that are trapped.  This robot is controlled by a remote control almost like the use with some video games, so you might know how to use Gemini-Scout.       The next robot I am going to tell you about is Dante 2.  Dante 2 is a robot that climbs in a volcano and gathers information from scientists.  Dante 2 has 8 legs like a spider so it can climb steep walls of the volcano.  Dante 2 is also built to survive very high heat.  With the help of Dante 2, scientists can now study volcanoes while they are safe in their laboratories.       Mr. Grower is a robot that works in hospitals.  This robot can carry medicine for doctors and nurses.  Mr. Grower is so strong that it can pull 500 pounds.  Mr. Grower can also speak.  It can say things like 'Calling elevator' or 'Your delivery is here.'  Mr. Grower can also do work that does work for doctors so the doctors can focus on other important tasks.       The last robot I am going to talk about are agribots.  These robots picks fruit.  Agribots come in different shapes and sizes depending on the time of fruit it picks.  To pick the fruit, it senses the color of the fruit.  This helps the robot determine weather the fruit is ripe or not.  At the MIT, scientist are growing cherry tomatoes, but without humans.  The agribots seem unusual, but one day they might be very common on farms.       And that is my story about robots.

Item_Response: I was in the library reading a book friend gave me; called the last tear of hope. I read aloud:                                                                                                          The last tear of hope       I was in the library taking notes about how to built a robot with such a powerful feeling and emotions, so that the robot would look real human. I went back to my lab and then i saw that my robot wasn't there. I looked every where, but didn't find it. I thought someone steel it; just then i feel a cold hand on my soulder; i turn around to look at the the hand. I fell back on my feet with a sudden shock; it was not a human's hand, it was my robots hand.       I don't know how it happened, but i felt proud of myself. I never saw a miracle like that. I was shocked and happy both. The robot help me get up and read my feelings emotions and said ' I am proud of you, too. It was impossible that a robot could feel emotions. I asked him 'how did he get alive?' He didn't answer me.       He started to walk and he went to the library and give me a book that says magical world: feelings of hope. I never read that book, but i know i have that book. He explains me that i was his hope. Only i can make him alive. It means i was the hope in side him, that i could still live with him.        After that incident (when the robots come to life) we never talked about that incident again. I live with him forever and he accept me as his father. We stayed with each other 20  years. We played with each other and also tell our secrets to each other. We went to farmes and countries and he became a member of our family. I make him older as he was my own son. I teach him how to play games like chess, badmenton and soccer. I also how to make your garden beautiful. I read stories to him at night and do all the stuff like cooking and make him count, read and write. He was getting old. He wants to be a scientist(scientists who work in NASA).A scientist like me, who beleieve in himself.I give him all the scientific books i have and he starts studying.He became a great scientist and he also make his dreams come true.       I was getting old. too. I was 64 and then one day felt very sick and i call him and he come to me and i told him my last wish that he will always stay happy; and tears coming through his eyes; i opened his sysytem and press the memory button and the last thing i rememberd was a tear rolling down his cheeks. The last tear of hope.

Item_Response: Sublime . . . unrivaled . . . unparalleled: these are the words I would use to describe having robots. These robots would be helpful to our environment. Also it can be a great learning experience. the three robots that would be the best help to our planet would be Gemini-Scout, Dante 2, and the self-driving car.           First of all, is the Gemini-Scout. For example, it's a robot that helps miners. It checks if there are any gases. Also it is really strong in case anybody is hurt. Indeed the robot is small but a big help.           Moreover, is the Dante 2. For instance, it is like a spider which has eight legs. It goes and check volcanoes to make sure it is not going to erupt. Also it is built for high heat so it can go inside the volcano. Truly this robot helps scientists because they cannot take the heat.           Last of all, is the self-driving car. What I mean is, it's a great help for bad drivers. It won't crash because it thinks ahead of humans. Also it can never be distracted because it doesn't text, drink or get tired. Verily this robot can stop terrible drivers from getting hurt.           Succinctly, then, having robots would be euphoric. If these robots were real they would make a great change to our planet. I have myriad reasons why there should be robots. Mr. Reyes once said,

Item_Response: The robot   I was just a little girl when I started liking robots. I wanted to join the robotics club, but I know i'd be no good at making robots. As I got older I forgot about robots and just went on with my life until it was the week before my birthday. I get up like everyday and get ready as quick as i can so i don't make me and my friend Jade late to school. I see Jade's car and i tell mom that im going to school. She kisses me on the head and tells me bye and have a good day like she always does. I leave and walk quickly to Jade's car. As soon as I get in we start talking and we talk the ride there. As we get to school I think that everythings going to be the same as it always is, but little did I know that the school is going to be having a robot contest and everyone has to watch.       I walk in with Jade and we walk to our lockers and see our other friend Lauren. Lauren says' Hey guys did you know today is the robot competition?'. Jade just shakes her head yes.' Really? I didn't even know they were having one.' I say. 'Yeah and everyone has to watch it this time.' says Jade. I sigh not wanting to go, because im not really interested in watching. We get our stuff and go to our home room together. We enter the room one after the other and take our seats beside each other. The tearcher enters and tells everyone that because the robot contest is going to start in 5 minutes we can just sit and talk. We talk for 5 minutes then go and sit in the gym and wait for the contest to start. ' Man I didn't wan't to watch this at all. It's going to be so boring.' 'Quit your complaining it could be worse.' says Laruen. She was right it could be worse. After everyone showed their robots, the first competition started. Randomly there was  the announcer guy who told the crowd that they needed a few more people to make a robot. 'Rachel, Jade, Lauren, Sam, and Brandon will make a robot.' What no i screamed in my head even though i had no choice.       After school was over Lauren and Jade came over to my house to get started on their robot.'I'm going to make a cat robot. What are you guys going to make?' I asked. 'Well i'm going to make a butterfly robot.' says Jade proudly. 'I'm going to make a normal robot.' says Lauren. 'Why?' Jade and I say at the same time. 'because a normal robot is easier.'says Laruen. Jade and I look at each other. Oh course i picked something hard to do, but im going to stick with it. We all start making our robots and talk to each other. It takes about a week but we finish it. My robot looks the best out of the three robots. They all said they wished they could have made theirs look like mine,but I don't think they could have made theirs like mine. On the day of the contest i was nervous about showing my robot to everyone, but i did. The contest was over and they were about to tell everyone who won. 'The winner of this years robot contest is... Rachel!' I won, i actually won yay. At the end of the day when we went home i told my mom and dad that i won. I went to my room and put my robot on my bed. I listened to music for a while when i noticed the robot was gone. I looked for it and when i found it, it was alive and i mean it was moving on its own and the controller wasnt even being messed with. It even talked to me, which i found kind of cool. I ended up having an awesome robot that could talk and move around by itself. I had a really good time with it until someone stole it.

Item_Response: Once in a small town in Switzerland, a young boy by the name of Alfred saw a circus show. At the show were clowns, lions, jugglers and even elephants but what interested him the most was the robot. It could do almost anything, it could juggle, bake and even play catch with you and this gave this young boy a great idea. The same night he wen home to ask his Pa if he could buy some supplies to make the robot. His Pa said no, this disappointed him but he would not give up. So he started working at a shop just a block away, there he would earn $10 dollars an hour, just enough to buy the supplies.            The next day he worked fast, selling pie after pie, and he even got $5 worth of tips. This continued for the next month until he finally earned enough. He went  the mechanic and bought everything he needed and went home and started building but first he would have to design it and give it a name. There were dosens of designs everwhere in the house untill he finally found the perfect one. It would have a box head and body and skinny arms and legs. And its name would be Andy.            When he finally finished the robot he played with it all day everyday and he even got in the news for making the robot. The title of the paper was Alfred the new Einstein. After many years the robot broke he tried to fix it but hting had gotten more expensive since he was a child so he just left it there never to be played wih agan. But it is still a token of friendship and he will never forget all the great times he had with it.

It looked like if it could write somthing because it was sitting down and had a pen in his arm later,he took it home he searched on the internet but he couldn't find the robot he used some key words like small robot whith pen. Then he was examining the robot eventually he found a word and said it outloud ' Automoton', then he searched it on the internet then it said they come to life when fully repaired they are worth 3,050 dollars. Robert told his father wanted to sellit but robert wanted to fix it. So they did it took 2 years but it was done the pieces used in it where from clocks but one thing they didnt notice is that it needs a key to work.
