Item_Response: Helping Hands  All About Robots                                                    By, Makenna Bouwhuis                                   Our world is filled with wonderful and interesting different kinds of robots like Gemini Scout. This robot can do many things, he is a remote-controlled robot that works in mines under ground. He is less than two feet tall. Gemini scout can go through water. he is small but strong. he collects information. For example he tests the air for gases the tells the miners when the air is safe. The robot has  a thermal camera to help find miners in mines. When the robot finds trapped miners in collapsed mines he can use a two-way radio to talk to the rescue team. Gemini Scout is easy to use and control. Its remote control is the same one that some video games use.                              Dante 2 is another robot. he can climb into volcanoes to gather information. He looks for vents. or holes, in the crater. he tests the air for gases that come out of the vents. Dante 2 is changing the way scientist learn about inside the volcanoes. scientist can learn about them while they are still in their labs and Dante 2 is in them and exploring them.               Mr. Gower is another one of the very interesting robots that have been made. He works in hospitals. His job is to bring medicine to patients. Mr. Gower looks like a small cabinet on wheels. He can ride on elevators and can go anywhere he wants in the hospital. He runs on batteries after he charges or two hours he can work for twelve hours without stopping. Mr. Gower can even talk! He can say hundreds of different phrases. He is small but can pull up yo 500 pounds.                         Agribots are a different kind of robot. This kind is programed to pick all different kinds of fruits such as berries, grapes, oranges, or apples. Agribots come in all different shapes and sizes. some have giant arms and are pulled on the back of a truck and others can move freely and can go where ever it wants to. They can sense color of the fruit before they pick it to see if it is ripe. The Massachusetts Institute of Technology scientists are working to grow cherry tomatoes with no human help at all. They are all cared by agribots. They can be a lot like farmers.  Every plant has a sensor that tells the robot when that plant is ready to be picked. When it is the robot uses its mechanical arm to pick it. The robot waters it and does all of the other stuff the farmers can do.

Item_Response: Mr. Gower you're needed in room 110. I quickly drove to room 110 and Dr. Philip unlocked my cabinet and pulled out a small container. I wasn't sure what the meds were but I could tell he needed them urgently. 'Mr. Gower you're needed in room 12.' Dr. Philip told me. I rushed down to the 2nd floor. I entered the room to see a girl no older than 5. 'Thank you Mr. Gower.' The nurse said politely. She opened my cabinet and pulled out a container filled with something orange. 'What's that?' the girl coughed.   'It's your meds Emily. They're going to make you feel better.' the nurse replied.     'I meant the robot.' Emily said quietly.     'Oh that's Mr Gower, he helps in the hospital. He helps doctors and brings medicine to the patients.' the nurse said smiling . She pours the medicine into a small plastic cup and gives it to Emily. I drive over to her bed. I'm confused because she has no hair like most of the people I've seen in the hospital. 'Hi Mr. Gower, I'm Emily.' Emily says shyly. I wish I could tell her my name but the people that made me only let me say 'Calling elevator' or 'your delivery is here.' lame right? I love being able to work with the patients and doctors. I always make the children smile when I say 'Your delivery is here' I turn around and I go over and get a cup of water for Emily. I've seen many children make faces after they have their medicine. I go over and give it to her and say 'Your delivery is here' she smiles and laughs    'Thank you Mr. Gower' before falling asleep.

Item_Response: The Robot that Suddenly came Alive and became my New Best Friend       By: Jacob Van Antwerp       First of all, this all started when I was at my mom's one day. My mom gave me a WHOLE BUNCH of money, and told me to go to a store and get whatever I wanted! So I set out to a store filled with robots on 'off' mode and with no batteries in them.       Their packages had a whole pack with batteries and robots already assembled. Well, let me tell you how it ALL fully happened...                                                                Chapter 1                                                           The Robot           When I went to the robot store, I decided to get my very own robot. I grabbed a package and, exhausted, I went to the counter. 'Here's...my...package, sir. It's really...heavy! A...little...help?' I struggled to the checkout man. 'Alright sir, there's a cart right there,' he said, pointing to a row of carts. I placed it on the counter, panting and running toward the carts. I grabbed one, the man scanned the bar code, and I ran back with the cart, and the man put it in my cart, and gave him all that money Mom gave me. 'Have a nice day!' said the man. 'You too!' I said back. I got out and ran back to Mom's. The cart automatically rolled back to that store. I struggled up the front steps and inside. I laid it on the floor and opened it. 'Wow!' said Mom! 'You got a...robot?!' 'Yes, of course! From the robot store,' I told her. 'Let me assemble it.' 'OK,' said Mom. I quickly put it all together. 'Wow-wee! How could you do it that fast?!' cried Mom. I shrugged my shoulders. The second I turned around, the robot was beginning to turn on automatically! It became 'suddenly alive'! 'Oh, my, God!' yelled Mom. 'Can it speak?' 'Yes. Let me show you,' I said. I reached in the package and pulled out a hands-on remote control and pressed the 'Speak' button. In an instant digital eyes and a sound line on the mouth appeared. 'Greetings!' the robot said. 'Uh...greetings,'' I said. Mom said the same thing. 'Hey, you said your first word,' I said to my robot. 'Affirmative, it's my first word,' said the robot. 'Uh, Jacob, I got to walk away and I'll let you have fun your robot,' said Mom. 'OK,' I said. Mom walked away, and when she did, I asked the robot, 'Do you want to be my new best friend?' 'Sure,' answered the robot. So we did. Chapter 2   The Fun Begins      'You want to play with me on the Wii?' I asked. 'Yes, I will! What're we playing?' said the robot. 'I'll look,' I said, and I looked for a game. What do you think I picked? 'A-HA! Found it,' I finally said. 'Mario Kart!' 'Mario Kart?' repeated the robot. 'Yes,' I said. We played the game for a little bit. When we were done we were hungry. 'You want to eat?' I said. 'Yeah,' said the robot. We ate when Mom made dinner. That night it was time for bed. 'I'm tired. Are you?' I asked. 'Yeah,' said the robot. We got ready for bed, then made a bed in the living room. 'May I turn you off when we lie down?' I asked. 'Whatever you say,' he said, and I hit the off button, and we slept and slept. This is Part 1. There will be more some other time.

Item_Response: Sometimes, some people say 'The robots can't feel anything!',but some people say 'No, robots can feel.' This story is about the robots' war and feel something. Begin!       Chap.1. Item_Response: Rob the Robot                 Jessica was exhausted from her science fair at school. She set her science project on her couch. For her science project she built a robot (it did not work).So many kids... *Beep* her phone cried. She polled it out of her pocket and saw it was Maddie who has been her best friend since kindergarten.   Maddie- So i got a great grade on my project @ the science fair   Jessica- O.M.G (om my GOSH)! thats really cool!!!   Jessica typed while yawning.   Maddie- i know its so cool!!! my mom says we can go 2 the Ram 2night @ 8 if u want 2 come?   Jessica- no i think im going 2 go 2 bed early   Maddie- o ok   Jessica- c u l8r   Maddie- Bye   And just like that Jessica was in bed and under the covers. Thinking about Maddie and her project then about herself and her robot and she slowly drifted into a deep sleep.    ***            As the morning sun rose Jessica started to stir. She kept on hearing a strange noise. *Bleep*Bleep*Bleep* She the turned to see her robot staring right at her! 'Ahhhhh!!!' she screamed but then again who wouldn't. 'Ahhhhh' said the robot. 'Ahhhhh!' she screamed again. 'Ahhhhh!' 'Ahhhhh!' 'Ahhhhhhhhhhh!' they both screamed. 'Who...What... How... Uhhhh?!?' Jessica said while hyperventilating. 'Um. I. Ah. Really. Don't. Know.' said the robot in a metallic voice. 'You are the one who created me.' he said calmly. 'I. I. I um. Didn't make you talk though. Last night you didn't even work!' starting to get calm Jessica said.            'Well... Oooo! I know I have a camera on all the time watching my room!' Jesica said. She had it there so she could make shur Dillan her younger brother didn't come into her room while she was gone or asleep. She learned better when Dillan drew a mustuage on her face with a permanent marker last month. As she plaid it she saw her brother Dillan come into her room! He grabed the robot and took him into his room. Then 3 minutes later he came in with a new robot. But this one actually worked! 'Dillan you are DEAD!' she mumbled to her self. 'Are you going to destroy your brother?' the robot asked without any emotion. 'Oh ya' Jessica said as a almost smile on the robots face appeared.             'Um.. Are you ok?' she said trying not to sound nervous. 'I will be back' he said then he opened and shut the door. Jessica heard the door open to her brothers room and 'Ahhhhhhhhhhhh!!!' yelled Dillan. Jessica ran out of her room and found the robot holding Dillan by his ankles. 'WHAT ARE YOU DOING!!!' demanded Jessica. 'Determanating Dillan' the robot said in his creepy voice. 'No. Don't de. detre. determin. Don't kill me!!!' Dillan said freaking out. 'Rob!!! Put him DOWN!' Jesica said forcingly. 'No. I must destroy Dillan. Then you. Then your parents. The this town. Then THE WORLD.' Now this robot was really creeping her out. 'No. Not while I'm here.' Jesica bravly said. 'I quess you'll be first then' he said. Just like that Rod let go of Dillan and started towards her. 'Oupf!' Dillan said while hitting the floor. Jesica dived to the robot and tolk a chunk of his arm with her. 'Goss.' shesaid looking at the wires spilling out where his arm use to be. 'I.. Will... Destroy... You...' the robot started to glich but was still coming her way. With the robots good arm he grabed her neck. 'Let go you stupid thing!' Jesica said as he sqizzed harder and harder. She started to feel light headed. As she slowly fell asleep she heard 'Good Bye' and then she was gone.                                 Rob's creepy voice then said, 'THE END'

Max sat under a tree reading abpout cars, thebreeze was moving gently and making the tree leaves sway back and forth. He started to drift off into a dais and then he fell asleep. Not that long after he started to have a dream, this dream was new and this is what it was....                                Max was older and was big and strong, not weak. One day he said,' I want to change the world into something good not bad, but how will I do that ?' he started to ask himself. By the morning he jump out of bed and went to get his skectch book and he started to sketch this robot. This robot wasnt any ttpe of robot you have ever seen before. It was small and silver. He ran down the stairs and to his mom ,'Mom look! look! i have this great idea and I think it might change the world some day! ' he smiled with happyness. ' Oh honey its a really good drawing , but what is it? ' she started to trail off. 'Well it helps people in hospitles , it delivers there medicine or flowers and meals and stuff like that.' 'Very nice Max have fun on working on that.' Max's mom turned back and started working on their dinner. He started working on the robot. By the time he was 19 he became a billinare. The second youngest to be a billinare. Item_Response: Meet the Medicbot   By Natalie Buffalin, Grade 6       It was just a not-so-average Monday, at River Glen High school. My girlfriend had dumped me, I'd failed my math test (which I was not surprised about) and my best friend Lucas, is in the hospital with cancer. Yeah, you could say things weren't looking very good for me. Until that one day.        It all started when I got the phone call, saying Lucas was no longer maintaining a stable condition. I rushed to the hospital in my old white Nissan, only to find it was too late. Cancer had taken the life of my best friend. The only one who respected me. Lucas, with his red hair, acne-covered face,  and glasses that he had to constantly push up onto his nose, was gone. The doctors said they couldn't get to him fast enough, and couldn't locate the correct medicine.       I was in my room that night, crying over my loss, with my head in my hands, when the thought came to me. What if there was a way to get to him faster? What if there was something to get to him faster? At first I thought bicycles, but after pondering the thought, I realized it would be hazardous to the residents of the hospital.I spent all of my free time in a little tin shed in the backyard, with a pack of number 2 pencils, stacks of paper, and a garbage can in the corner, piled up to the ceiling with papers containing all of my useless ideas, and the two or three actually possible ideas sat next to me on the table.        I was completely fed up with writing and sketching for so long. All of my ideas ended up in complete disaster. I wadded up the paper in front of me and I was about to dispose of it, when I saw a paper in the far left corner of the room. I opened it up, and I had found my solution. A robot! I would make a robot. The little robot would carry everything you would ever need in a hospital, from medicine, to bandages, to food! It could get to all of the rooms of the hospital faster than any human ever could, and help the patients. It would hopefully prevent an accident like Lucas's from happening.       I laid out  blueprint for the robot, which I had decided to name the Medicbot. I took a trip to the local hardware store and purchased everything I could possibly think of using on the robot. Sheet metal, nuts, bolts, hammers, wires, etc. I went to the gaming store and bought an old N64 controller, to control the Medicbot.       It took alot of hard work, but I eventually completed the Medicbot. It was more wonderful than I thought it would be. There was a keypad on top of the robot, and you typed in whatever you needed, the Medicbot would reach in his backpack with his electronic hand, and give you whatever you typed in. All of the controls worked perfectly, to my surprise.       I came home one day after school, and Medicbot was sitting in my kitchen. I was completely bewildered. I had no idea how he had gotten there. My mom was away on a buiness trip, and my dad died in a car wreck, so there was no explanation for this. I walked up to Medicbot, and to my surprise, he was turned on. He uttered one single word to me and that was 'Love.'       It was a few months after Lucas's death, and I was at school. Ever since I had made my robot, I had felt less lonely. I finally had a friend. Although, no one could ever measure up to the impact that Lucas made on my life, Medicbot came pretty close.

He was made to be used for carrying tools or objects 78 pounds or lighter from 1 Chinese farmer to another, for trading. He could only walk 2 miles or so and was little help. The Chinese appreciated his help, but thought he could do much more, as he only carried things. Everyday Mr. Pubble, the greatest of all Chinese farmers, would play around with LilGilly, to make him do more. He became hopeless, knowing he could not get LilGilly to change. But one day, Mr. Pubble pressed a button in the core of LilGilly, and that robot transformed completely!

Item_Response: The limo stopped on the driveway of the mansion. It was a nice and beautiful summer day and Susan was home from the last day of school. She had blond hair and blue eyes, she had good grades in school. Her parents were billionaires, instead of people they had maid robots, butlers, and cooks. As she came into the mansion  her father said ''Susan your mother and I got a present for you''. As her father said that her mother came out with box wrapped with flower wrapping paper.''Come on Susan open it'' said her mother, Susan was so excited about the present that she almost destroyed the box.When she opened the box, in it was a robot kitten. Susan exclaimed ''a kitten I've always wanted a kitten''.           That same night Susan was playing with her robot kitten when her mother went into he room. ''Susan its getting late you need to go to bed''. Susan replied '' just five more minutes mom'' her mother smiled and replied ''ok just five more minutes'' and she closed the door. Susan went to her window while her kitten was sleeping on her bed. Susan was thinking of a name for her kitten when all the sudden a shooting star shot across the midnight sky. She had heard that if you see a shooting star at night, and if you make a wish your wish will come true. at that same moment she thought of a perfect name for her kitten ' Sue ' she whispered to herself. So she made her wish ' I wish that my kitten Sue would be real'. When she made her wish she went into her bed and Sue moved so that she was at Susans feet, and then Suesan drifted of in to a deep sleep.           When Susan opened her eyes she saw the bright morning light. She looked at the end of her bed where Sue was sleeping the night before, but this time Sue was not there. Puzzled she got out of bed and  looked around the room. Then She saw a bundle of fur a feet away from her bed, it was the same fur that was on her kitten robot. She looked more closely at it and she saw the fur  rising up and down its breathing she thought. She took a step closer to make sure she was not imagining things. As she did the kitten's ears twitched and it  looked up from it napping. It is her kitten she thought and  looked in astonishment. The kitten meowed and ran over to Susan, she picked Sue up.As soon as she picked it up she knew it was real by how warm it was, and the fur  felt like the brush on a paintbrush. As she was feeling Sue her mother walked into her room, her mother looked at at the kitten her daughter was holding and asked 'where did you get that kitten? and where is the robot kitten'? Suesan replied 'i know this is going to sound crazy but i wished at a shooting star that if Sue could be real real and it happened.'. Her mother nodded and said 'ok we can keep Suesan at least we will have someting real', after that Suesan kept the kitten and had more fun with a real kitten then a fake one.

Item_Response: This is me. My name is Sam. I know, I know its not much but, its all I got. Living in Nevada is hot, and we were not very rich either. My family had been struggling to survive with the little money we had left. My dad,  was factory worker. And my mom, she taught at the one public school in that near-extinction town.        Me, you ask? Well, I was thirteen. I was geoligist, you know someone who studys  the Earth. I had but one wish. To find something extroirdinary, so amazing, so, so, peculiar. To find something so extraterrestrial that it would knock this whole towns socks off. Did I get my wish? Ill tell you right now.                 One hot forsaken day. I was walking on the dried up terrain and my metal detector started beeping like crazy! I started digging. What I found blew my mind. It looked like a UFO. Shaped like a flying saucer and guess what it had inside? Parts. Metal, clanky, precious parts.   I took it right to my lab and started tinkering. I made a robot. Well, at least it looked like one to me.         It was round, it had 'grabbers', I mean what else did a robot need? It was all a mystery from then on. I can barely remember. What I do remember was that in the end we had grass, trees, and people. I could go on and on about how happy everyone was.       All I had to do, was believe.

Item_Response: ' well, I guess this is the way things are now' I said  as I looked over the miles and miles of debre. The world was ounce beatiful and peaceful place, until it happend. My father had made something so new so fresh, we thought it would help people, but all it did was distroy our population, im margret santos and this is my story.             It all started when my father was in the running  to be president.'Marget I have some very big news, I am in the election! Isn't that just grand You will live in the white house with me if I win' He loved politics so this wasnt a surprise for anyone. 'thats great' I said sarcasticly, I definetly would not want to live in the white house . 'Hunny i know that ever since your mom died-' 'JUST STOP, THAT HAS NOTHING TO DO WITH IT !!' I barked at him then i marched into my room.            then a hop, skip, and a boat ride later.. he won and i was so upset . life seemed worthless, after a while he asked me if I wanted to see his latest project, I never evan would have answerd that question if i new what was going to happen next,I followed him down the grand hall past the dinning room dashed down the staircase and into the labratory. There I saw it a woman, a beatiful woman, but when she turned around i saw something better.'What is that remarkible thing'i was stunned 'Im calling her margret'he exclaimed 'why,thats-' he cut me off 'i know I know thats youre name, thats why I named her that, she shall be youre friend im making millions of copies of her and shiping her all over the world!' 'yes,but what kind of creature is she'i asked  he shrugged,'does it really matter thow'but yet in some wayI thought about sharing her with the rest of the world. I thought she was mine, just mine, mine to hold, mine to hang out with, but pretty soon every girl and boy will have one.I told margret to come with me to my room and she came we brushed our teeth said goodnight and went to bed .           The next morning when I woke up she was gone 'MARGRET!? MARGRET CAN YOU HERE ME ?' I heard margret in the kitchen so I ran into the kitchen and there she was eating cerial 'hi,margret' 'HELLO, HUMAN HOW ARE YOU?!'   'Margret can you lower youre voice please' I heard a buzz then the buzz quited down 'is this better human ?'

Item_Response: One day Jane was playing in her backyard, and then she tripped over something that was sticking out of the ground. She called for her brother Austin. He came to help her dig it out. two hours later they uncovered the mystery thing sticking out of the ground. They found out it was a robot! Jane and Austin went inside to get a screw driver because the robot had a screw in it's back. They saw it took 2 D batteries, so Jane ran inside to grab the batteries. They both put 1 in and then they put the cover back on, put the screw back on, and turned the switch on and their robot came to life! It started to move, and then it started talking! Jane and Austin were amazed, Their mom came to the back door and she saw the little robot, and she was amazed too.           Austin, Jane and their mother brought the robot inside to clean it off. In a few minutes the robot was sparkling because it was really clean. The robot asked what it could do and the kids said it could clean their rooms. and then do the dishes while they relaxed. The robot did everything and it cleaned the bathroom as well. Then their dad came home with Ally Jane's older sister. she asked what the robot was. Jane answered 'It is our robot maid.' She said it was awesome and then she went upstairs to her room. Jane and Austin were watching T.V. and the robot even brought them their dinner. After dinner the robot did all of their homework. Then Jane and Austin were playing video games and the robot got them ice cream and they both said 'The robot is awesome!'

Item_Response: The Contest                           On Monday, Septemember 4, 2011 at Oakland Bridge Middle school are going to have a contest. The contest was about who can make the creative and useful robot. The day of the contest is on Septemember 25th. The judges are the staff and one special guest. The winner gets a $200 check.      There was this boy name Eric who really loves to built things like toy cars, planes, robots, and more.He also loves to draw and paint. When he heard about the contest about robots, he wanted to be in it.And of course he was the very first person to sign up for the contest.      To begin, he brain storm what would the robot be like and what is the useful thing the robot could do. Well, the contest doesn't begin yet, you still got 21 days to create an amazing robot. But the next day he thought of an amazing robot that he was determind that he will win. That no one will ever make. The robot could talk, is strong, and which it is alive. The useful and important thing that the robot is going to do is do what ever it tells you to do and the important thing is it never dies.      Second, he had to draw out the robot before he could built it. Of course you have to because who would built a robot without drawing it out. After he drew it, he got all the stuff he needed to built the robot. He built a device could make the robot talk and it took him 4 days. Which in that case he has 17 days left before the contest. Next, he built parts that the robot will come alive and it took him 2 days. Which means he has 15 days left. He built a very strong thing that the robot never dies which took him 9 days. Which means he has 6 days left.      He just had to do one more thing before he is finished. He had to paint the robot gold which took him 5 days. Which means he has 1 day left before the contest begins. When it was Septmember 25th which is the contest, Eric got his robot settled and was waiting for the judges to come to his table. When the judges came they were so amazed that right away that the judges annouced that the winner is ...... Eric Sing.        The point to this story is that if you work hard you'll get rewarded in the end.                                                                The End

Item_Response: The Miracle                   Tommy was just a normal boy who loved science,and loved going to school.One day he decided  to make a robot.It took him a few days to figure out what his robot was going to do.Then one day he figured out what he wanted his robot to do.He wanted his robot to help him in his math homework,because he loved science so much he never wanted to study for math.         Tommy honestly thought that math was stupid,and that he should be doing more science than math.Tommy would think day and night all about his robot.He thought about it so much that he started flunking science!Tommy got 4 detention notes that day for not paying attention in class.Then Tommy started to get second thoughts about his robot like how was he going to afford all the parts for his robot he wanted his robot to walk,and talk to him.          So Tommy decided if he wanted to get all the parts he needed,he needed to get some money some way.Then Tommy got an idea;he should start a lemonade stand.Then days past and Tommy finally collected enough money for all the parts he needed.Tommy started assembling all the parts to make his robot once it was done he put in the batteries;he turned it on and nothing happened.He kept on turning it on an off and nothing happened.This made Tommy mad he got madder than he usually did.He went up to his room and tossed the robot in the closet and went to bed.          Then Tommy woke up to a weird robotic voice.He got up and opened the closet,and to his surprise he found his robot walking and talking.Once Tommy saw his robot walking and talking he picked it up and laid in bed with his robot.That night Tommy couldn't fall asleep because he couldn't believe that his robot actually came to life.The next day he told pretty much everybody at school about his robot.Then everybody was asking for a math robot.Ever since his robot came to life he felt like he was a king,and that was Tommy's miracle.

Item_Response: My Moble Music Robot                                                                                         By Andrew V.                  This weekend, my robot came alive. It all started when I joined the writing class at   school. 'Hey Andrew!', one of the members said as I went out the gate door. 'Since you draw really well, can you draw a model of a robot? I think it would be great for the theme for this week.' I wasn't very good at drawing robots, but I agreed.               While, I walked home, I thought about the robot's design and what it would do. I imagined it with limbs, but it looked weired. Instead, I imagined it with a Game Boy's head and wheeles for legs because it would be easier to move. I stopped day dreaming when I saw the T and Y store. A drunk man came by with sagging pants. I got out of his way and kept walking. It was very quiet in the empty lot. There was a whole garden on one side, but less vegetation on the other road I was walking on. I crossed the street and went to my grandma's house. I got out my half-split binder and started to draw.                I drew a square for the head and a short, adjustable, metal neck that was attatched to a toy car. I looked at the clock and it was fifteen minutes past five. I knew it was time to get prepared so I can go to my house. My mom picked my bothers and sisters up and she said, 'What did you do at your writing class?' I told her, 'One of the members asked me if I can draw a robot for our theme this week.' My mon replied, ' Maybe your dad can help you really make it.' I wasn't very sure because we didn't have all the pieces to assemble the machine.                 At eight o' clock, my dad came home and my mom told him about the robot I drew. I showed my dad and he said, 'I can to build this if I had a Game Boy Advanced SP.' I never knew what he was talking about because he was a nintey's kid, but he never played games. My dad got out his tool box and I asked my brother for his toy car because his birthday had just past. There was only one thing missing though. I knocked on my older brother's door and asked him for the Game Boy he had. 'Hurry and get out!',Austin said because he was FaceTiming with his girlfriend. I gave all the things to my dad and he took apart the Game Boy and toy car. My dad had some wires and from what I learned from G.A.T.E. class, they have to run on a battery. In his tool box, there was a metal neck that the robot needed for rotating. I watched my dad attatch the metal neck to the truck and the top screen of the Game Boy. The machine was complete, but didn't turn on. 'Why isn't it working?', I asked. No one had a reply.                'I think it's because we dont have a romote control.', my dad said. Then I looked towards the bottom half of the Game Boy and the romote contol for the toy car. I got a skrew driver for my dad because I knew he was going to fuse the two controls. The control for my robot was complete. It had the antena from the toy car, the shape of the Game Boy's bottom half, the A and B buttons from the nintendo consle did nothing, and the on and off button were still there. We turned it on, but nothing happened again. 'What's the problem now?', my mom asked. I looked under the remote and had noticed that the game slot was empty. I shoved in Pokemon Emerald and I turned on the remote. The robot turned on and played the music of Pokemon Emerald's title screen. I was very excited.                 I turned in the robot the next day to my writing class. They were expecting a picture instead of a real-life robot and they were curious about how I made it I told them the story. I turned on the robot and it played music. I wanted to keep it, but I had to give back the toy car to my brother. I wish I could see the robot again.

Item_Response: The Kristen Bot           A kid named Kristen was walking on the sidewalk and saw a metal object in front of her.I ran to see what it was,it was a jacked up robot.Billy Bob,the scientist threw it out. He said, 'I threw it out because it didn't work.'       She asked,'Can i keep it?' He said,'Sure.' I took it home in a really old wagon.It would squeak a lot and turned weird too.All night long,I worked on the broken robot.That morning I finished it,it looked brawn new.       That day I brought him to school.Everybody oohed and aah ed at the robot.It was lunch time and somebody accidentally spilled juice on it.The robot had a malfunction and it started to go crazy. It ran into walls and children,everybody started to scream.       The teacher told me to take home my dum robot.I did took it home and just threw it in the trash.Then my mom came in my room and asked why did I  throw away the robot.Then I told her that I didn't want it anymore.

It will cost me 1.5 to buy the things just for one Buddy ,therefore I'll only make 5,000.        When working on Buddy-15 i work alone i don't trust no one to know my secret. Item_Response: Alive Robots           I begged and plead to my mom and asked her if she could please buy the things I needed to make a robot. She had said no multiple times, but I was determined to make one. After seeing so many spectacular things at the science fair, including some robots, I couldn't stop thinking about making one.         It was Saturday night, at the dinner table, and I asked one more time, hoping she would say yes, especially since my dad was there. My mother rejected the idea again, but my father said,'We should let her do it, Letty, it would show some responsibility, and plus we would have someone else here to clean up so you won't have to worry about it so much.' My mom replied 'That would be a plus, Guero, but don't you think its creepy? having a robot in the house? And what if it leaks oil all over the floor? I won't clean it up. It will be your responsibility, Ashley. You will have to clean up its messes.'       Once I heard their responses I got so happy and almost fell out of my chair. My little sister, Leslie, asked if she could help me, and I happily replied with yes. The next morning, my brother Armando, the oldest, Angel, the second oldest, Leslie, and I headed out for every Home Depot and Walmart in the city to look for everything we needed. We looked for nuts and bolts and even looked to see if the stores sold metal. Once we found everything we needed, we headed back home, where my dad had his tools all set up and ready for Leslie and I to use.       Once we started, it took us about a three months to finish the robot. the robot took the form of a human, had pretty green eyes, had shorts, tennis shoes, and a superman shirt with long, black hair. My sister and I looked back and marveled at the beautiful sight. We decided to name her Victoria. But then, something terrible happened. I had tried to turn the switch on and off, but it wouldn't work. She wouldn't work.       We decided to abandon the idea and left her in the garage for about two years. On October 14, Leslie and I were on the couch, watching our favorite T.V. show when we heard a loud thud in the garage. We went to go see what happened, and then we saw it. The robot we had abandoned two years ago was alive.

Item_Response: It was a cold winter day, only a week for Christmas and last minute shoppers were getting the best deals of the year.There was only one store that was completely empty because of the creepy  sounds.The store was called 'Technicians'. The owner was a very serious and wise man, known as Mr. Rainer. He loved science with all his heart and dedicated his life to it.       One day like any other it was quiet at the shop, something like lighting sparks would happen out of nothing at the stores basement. It happen again the next day and the next day ,until one month later was when Mr.Rainer noticed something strange.A Wednesday morning Mr.Rainer found a plate with eggs and bacon with a cup of orange juice.Minutes later a small robot stroll by Mr.Rainer like it was a daily thing for him and said a simple hello.         Mr.Rainer just stared at him while the robot fixed things around the shop.The next day the same thing happen the robot fixed things but this time there was a few customers around the shop.It has been years since there was a single customer in this particular shop. Mr.Rainer was impressed by the success this little robot brought into his shop and Mr.Rainer was fascinated. Years past and no one knew were the little robot came from.But he was a miracle in Mr.Rainer's life, they were partners in business and friends. The mystery of the way the little robot got to the shop might always be a mystery.

Item_Response: MAGIC IN THE GIRLS CLOSET          Once there was a girl all alone in her room. Her name was Alice she was 8 years old she had the best country life someone could ever wish for. Alice loved spending time in her room with her toy robot she named him Robbie. When she was finished playing with him she would put him in her closet. Alice had a feeling that something strange was going because every time she put him in the closet there would be a glow.              A year had passed and she couldn't figure out what was going on with Robbie until the day of her birthday when she went to go get ?Robbie and there he was Robbie wasn't a toy anymore he had turned into a real life robot. Robbie wasn't Robbie anymore he was the Agribot. Alice stayed there frozen looking at Agribot she  looked at him and said“ how did you do that were is Robbie what did you do with him?” Agribot said that he was Robbie but that the glowing light transformed him into what he was right now.              A couple of days had passed and Alice had started getting used to her new robot. She kept him a secret from her friends, mom, dad, and especially her brother. She would sneak him out to the garden were there was plants,fruits, and vegetables he would help her pick them since that was her chore. She started liking Agribot since he was a big help to her with her outdoor chores. She would play with him and take him to the barn once in a while. Then one day she was planning to tell her mom,dad, and brother but Agribot told her if she told them and they told everyone else he would dissapear. That made her stay quiet instead.           Then, it was back to school she was worried that if Agribot left the closet or room her mom would find him and he would dissapear. So she started locking her room and gave him things to do while she was gone. Her mother would question her about why she locked her room and she would make up a fast excuse that her mother would barely believe. Alice decided to tell her mom and she did. Alice's mother wanted to meet Agribot so Alice introduced Agribot to her. Her mother promised to keep it a secret.                Three years had passed now and Agribot told Alice that it was time for him to leave and she asked him why he said he had come to help her and that he would really miss her. Alice said if he would ever return and Agribot said that he would he gave her a necklace with she would touch and Agribot would come back. She gave him a bracelet for memories.They said good bye and that they would miss each other . Agribot went back inside the closet with Alice watching the glowing light and when it stopped she checked inside all around but she only found her old Robbie.                                       THE END . . . .

Item_Response: There was a planet farther than pluto, bigger than the milky way called Roboville. A robot there loves to travel to other planets. He has been there to every planet... except for Earth. He wants to but its parents won't let him because there is alot of water on it. He says he'll be fine but his parents still won't let him go. He gets mad and goes to his bed and just lays on it. Then he had an genius idea that may or may not get him in trouble. He will go to Earth when his parents are asleep and only stay there for the night. He will also have a bunch of pillows to put on his bed in case his parents come to his room. His parents tucked him in bed and they quickly went to sleep.           He went down to his backyard (slowly) where his ship was. He hops in he was off. He got there pretty fast (he was speeding because he only has a day) and landed in a foresty place. He is only about a foot tall so he is pretty small on Earth. He sees a light and quickly 'runs' to it. Its a light to a house. The door has a dog door. He goes in it and sees the biggest house he has seen. He walks around the house to see that its empty. (or so he thought). He soon gets seen by the dog. The dog barks loudly. Then a nine year old boy comes to the room and makes the dog go away. Then the boy realizes that the robot is moving and is amazed. He gets closer to look at it and says,'Do you talk?' The robot says,'Ye-e-s I do.' 'What can you do?' The boy said. 'I c-an dd-o a-lot of thh-ings like run, ta-alk.' replied the robot. Then the robot saw that it was almost sun rise. He said he needed to go. The boy wanted to know where he was going. The robot said,'Back to my planet, Roboville.' The robot left and went back to his planet. He got there just in time, just as the sun was rising and got into his bed. Right about that time his parents walked in and found him sleeping.            Meanwhile the boy got interested in the planet and looked it up on the internet. He had a presentation at school about a space-related thing to do. He did Roboville and he also told that a robot came to his house. He got an A+ on his presentation. He thought 'Maybe one day I can go to Roboville?'                                           THE END!

Item_Response: The Spy Robot           Three years ago a man named Sheldon wanted all the crimes in his town to stop so he decided to build a robot to help stop the crimes. So he work so hard and so long for about six months.Sheldon tried to make the robot work but he couldn't. so he go so mad he threw it in the trash.about five to six months later the robot worked and turned on. The robot was in the dump. Within a couple of weeks he discover all his abilities and went back the find his owner. but he couldn't find him. so he went out to seek his mission to stop crime in his home town but he didn't know when to start.            Then on a dark winter day a man in a detective suit was in a dark ally. He was scared but did not show it. Before the end of an ally another man appeared. The man in the suit saw that he had a mask and was running. The man in the mask also had a bag. the man in the suit heard sirens and a police officer yell, 'Stop!' but the man in the mask kept running. The man in the suit took off his suit. He turned out to be a robot. A spy robot. He is also a crime fighting one as well.          So the robot took of his suit and went after the man in the mask. The robot couldn't catch up, so he push a button and the robot had rocket shoes. He flew up and zoomed away. He finally caught up to the man in the mask. He reached for the man in the mask but missed. then the rocket shoes ran out of fuel. The robot fell but luckily fell on the man in the mask. the police came and caught the man in the mask. In the bag was money. So the robot returned the bag.               The whole town gave the robot a big thanks. for a reward the towns mayor gave the robot 1,000 dollars. the robot found out the man in the mask was in jail. After that the robot went back down into  the ally and disappeared into the darkness. He was happy that he stop crime and seeked his mission. About a year later the robot was watching the television in his new home when he turned on the news. He found out that Sheldon was look for him but then died. The robot was in  great sorrow. He went to find Sheldon's grave and rested by his grave for eternity.

Item_Response: One day while i was swimming, I had seen something bright in the water it was not big though. Soon I got my scuba gear on and I was on my way. By the time I got to the reef i had  found it. I couldn't believe that I was a gemeni-scout, I grabbed the small robot and started to swim toward the shore on the beach. When I got home I hid it in my room so my parents wouldn't notice. Then the next day I called my cousin over, when he first seen it he yelled ''OMG'', then I told him ''I found him at a reef and that your going to help me fix it''. When I was done speaking he went home, then a hour later he brought a lot of tools. The main things we had to do was to fix the thermal imager, radio and the inner controls.       Two weeks later, we had fixed the radio and thermal imager, but we still had to fix the inner controls. But when we were taking a break the man on the news channel said '' about three weeks ago a U.S. aircraft carrying the new gemini-scout, had crashed near a coral reef and there is still no sign of the gemini-scout but if anyone knows the where abouts of the gemini-scout please contact local police.'' We both knew that we had to fix the inner controls and contact the police. We worked hard for the next week it was all worth it though. When we tried it it was a sucess. Then we cleaned and polished the gemini-scout.       Then we got our older cousin to drive us to the police station, everyone was thrilled. All the news stations at Hawaii came straight away to the police station. All the scientists who had build the gemini-scout said ''how did u do it'' and we both said '' the old fashion way'' then the whole crowd started to laugh. then a couple weeks later we got a letter in the mail, but it wasn't just any letter. it was a check worth a 100,000 thousand dollars. then with all the money my cousin and i had built 10 gemini-scouts for the sceintists. Then a year later we were working with the scientists.

Item_Response: I have a robot named Pete. Pete helps farmers pit fruits and pick vegetables. Pete has a navigation system that you have to set up. you can feed him a map and it will pop up on his screen and then all you have to do is mark the trail in order that you want him to roll across then you get your map back and continue.       pets record of picking and pitting is 1,238 Pitts in a day and 1,369 picks in a day. farmers all over the world want a copy of Pete but he costs 10,000 dollars! my invention so far has made $300,000.That's a lot of money.Pete also has a special feature, but for extra money. You can buy the Xtra Farm pack for 500 dollars extra. then Pete will do all of your farming work for you! that means no planting, no watering, and no pulling weeds!       Pete has made 300,000 dollars so far. That's a lot of money. that means that 30 Petes have been sold so far. i hope to sell at least 20 more.Pete has been sold to farmers in all separate country's. so there is no two Petes in one country.

Item_Response: Rainbow Robot                                                       It was a nice morning at school when Lily's teacher, Mrs.Sanchez, said they needed to build a robot for their science competition at school. A lot of ideas came trough Lily's head. Mrs.Sanchez said that their robot needed to be able to move. When class was over Lily asked Mrs.Sanchez if she could start it today, and Mrs.Sanchez said of course you can. Right away when Lily got home from school she told her mom about the robot. Lily was so excited of building her robot, that she went to the garage and started buildind right away.       First, Lily started building the head of the robot. Lily wanted the robot to have normal eyes,so she got the fake googly eyes and put them on her robot. After that, she drew a mouth on her robot with a permanent marker. Furthermore, Lily got to her favorite part, which was the body. She had all sorts of chemicals in her garage, so she started putting one by none in the robot's body. What Lily did not know was that the chemicals she was using were really affective. It was bearly 5:30 pm, when Lily started painting her robot. She wanted to paint it all white and then add a rainbow around the body. Her robot looked fantastic. When she finished her robot it was 8:30pm. Lily was tired so she went to sleep and left the robot drying in her garage.       When Lily woke up she got ready, so she can check on her robot. While Lily got ready she tought of a good name to name her robot. At last, Lily tought of a name. She was going to name it Rainbow Robot. When Lily was finished getting ready, she went to the garage, but Rainbow robot was not there. She checked everywhere in her house, until she saw Rainbow Robot in her kitchen cooking breakfast. When Lily's mom saw Rainbow Robot cooking she gasped and almost fainted. Lily and her mom were both surprised to see Rainbow Robot cooking. After that, Lily checked if Rainbow Robot could talk, and it could. Rainbow Robot told Lily if it could walk with her, and she said no until she could bring it to the science competiton.       When Lily got to school she could not stop thinking about Rainbow Robot. When Mrs.Sanchez asked the class who has started on their robot, everybody raise their hand. Mrs.Sanchez said that the competition was tomorrow. Everybody got excited. Moreover, she asked the class if they wanted to share how their robot was coming out, but sadly no one wanted to share because they were to shy. Also,they did not want anyone steeling their ideas. Lily wanted to go home already to check on Rainbow Robot. When school was over Lily ran to her house. First, she ate what her mom and Rainbow Robot cooked. Next, after 30 minutes she played with Rainbow Robot outside, for about 2 hours. Then, they went inside and made a chocolate cake. When they were done, they were tired. Lily putted Rainbow Robot in the garage, and she went to her room to sleep.       It was the day of the science competition. Lily dressed nicely, and did her hair nicely too. Rainbow Robot was cooking pancakes for Lily and her mom. After Lily was done eating, she went to school walking with Rainbow Robot. when she got to class all the students were next to their robots ready to got to the school gym, where the science competition was going to be. Next, when they got to the gym they ordered them by grade, Lily went to the sixth grade group where she was supposed to go. After that, people were looking at different robots. Furthermore, the principal was going to announce the winner. The principal said,'And the winner of this years science competition is Lily Flores and her Rainbow Robot.' Lily was so excited when she heard her name. She went upstage and won 3 free tickets to go to the Beach Boardwalk. In conclusion, Lily was happy that she won, she went for free to the Beach Boardwalk with her mom and Rainbow Robot.

Item_Response: One rainy day, a scientist made an robot. After 3 hrs he feels tired so goes to sleep.   On midnight suddenly the robot gets alive. He searched for food but found nothing .   Suddenly the man woke up he saw the robot awake. The robot got scared. He tried to run away but he couldn't. So the man put him in a cage so he couldn't escape.   After some days the robot gets annoyed from staying inside the cage. So he tries to   run away. After sometime the man comes and saw that the cage was open and the robot was gone. He started to get worried. He had no idea where robot went. Today was also the invention science fair. The man got dressed set off to find the robot. He looked everywhere but he couldn't find him. He thought to check at his backyard. He still couldn't find him. Suddenly he heard some weird noises behind the bushes. He walked toward it and saw that robot was sitting behind the bushes and eating apples.   Then the man decided he would never put robot in the cage again.It was almost time   for the science fair. The man took the robot to the science fair everybody loved his invention. He won the first prize.The robot was happy again.

Item_Response: The Robot Specialty             Once upon a time there was a toy maker that made toys but his specialty were his robots. He was working on a robot, he worked all night and all day for 2 nights and 3 days, until the robot was perfect, and was ready to sell in his shop. The poor little robot sat there in the toy maker's shop for days then nights then weeks then months until he had been siting there for many years. No one had come to buy him or even look at him for years. But that all changed one day when a little girl named Caroline walked into the shop.        The little girl had walked around and looked at all of the toys, but none were what she had in mind. She asked the toy maker in a sweet, quiet voice, 'Do you have any more toys in your shop?' The kind toy maker said i a deep, rusty voice, ' No, well no new toys but I do have an old specialty of mine.' 'Oh what is it' said the girl joyfully The toy maker then went back to the shelf where the old, dusty robot sat upon. He carefully took him down from the shelf. The little girl looked at the old robot and just smiled wide, from ear to ear.        The little girl then took the robot home and cleaned him up a bit then they had a relxing tea party. Once they were done with their tea they played dress up Robot was the groom and Caroline was the bride. They prertended to get married and right when they were about to go on their honeymoon the girl's mother called her down for dinner. So they had to hold up on their honeymoon. Item_Response: Jimmy and Suzie Cook were in the 'haunted' woods near the pond in their neiborhood. The pond had small ducklings swimming through it with the sunset reflecting off the water. There were daisys and sunflowers all around the pond, it was absolutey beautiful. But on the side of the lake was a dark forest, the trees were tall and their leaves hid the sun. Jimmy were twins, they both had jet balck hair, pail skin and blue eys with a hint of green. They had pink plump lips and a little tall for their age of 12. Suzie had long wavy hair put up in a messy bun and Jimmy always had his hair in a quiff.        They were walking on the borders of the forest when the saw something shining in a cave or mine deep in the woods. Suzie went to check it out, but Jimmy stopped her, holding her by the wrist.         'What if it really is haunted.' said Jimmy still holding her wrist.         'It's not. Do you really beleive that stuff?' she said shrugging him off.          She procceeded, and her was right behind her. They walked up to the object.          ' What is it?' Suzie quitioned.          'It's a robot we learned about it in class. I think it's called a Gemini-Scout. I don't remember what i does.' answered Jimmy.           He pushed a botton that said on. Nothing happend.           ' Well that stinks, it's not working. Whatever, lets look around in the cave.' she said, but as she stepped in the cave a flash of red came from it.            ' Do not proceed. Deadly toxens in the mine.' It spoke out.           She stepped back and thought.            'We better take it back to see if some scientist need it.' she comanded while piking up the small, rusted, robot. They walked to a lab they lived by to see if they needed it.            Jimmy stopped a man ready to walk through the doors and spoke, ' Excuse me sir, but we found this robot and we were wondering if you needed it for anything.'            ' Wow you found this. This is pretty old, but I think we can do something with it. Thank you!' he said while carfully taking the robot out of Suzies hands.               He walked in side the large gray building. The kids turned around and started back home.

Item_Response: How the Robot was Born                            It was October 1st and I was in a small room for almost 2 years all torn up. When a month past I was still stuck in the small room, until suddenly one day the door swung open that was from the small room  a little boy with her mom came in. When the little boy saw me all torn up on the ground he said to his mother 'Why is their torn up pieces of the robot?', the mother said ' Because somebody broke this robot and we haven't been in here for a long time, but when you grow older you could start fixing this robot.' And the mother started putting the robot pieces away in a small box.                            Years and month came by and the little boy who turned older came into the small room and started opening all the boxes to find something. Then the boy approached to my box he opened it and started putting all my little pieces on a desk. The next day the boy came back this time with tons of tools. He sat down on the chair and started fixing me. Weeks came by and the boy had finally fixed me I was so happy that I could be alive again.                             After the boy fixed me I was working with the boy in caves and trying to save some people. I was always by the boys side working, because that was my job and because I was a Gemini-Scout robot.

Item_Response: 'Hand me the hammer,' asked a man named John to his son. His son Billy handed him the hammer and he started banging away. They were trying to fix a robot they found on the side of the road. It was very beat up the head was hanging from wires the arms were barely attached. Also the robot didn't have a right leg. The man has been working for days trying to fix this robot. He decided to make a remote that if u touch him with it it shuts him down in case anything goes wrong. He had fixed the head and attached one of the arms but he still had to tighten the other arm and get a new right leg and attach it. He decided to take the next day off and sleep all day because he had been working day and night. Sleeping all day was his mistake.                 The man was so tired he forgot to unplug the charge for the robot. The robot got a surge of power and BOOM the robot was alive and more powerful than he ever had been. The problem was that he was evil inside so his plan was to take over the world by himself. He walked out of the room and onto the streets.                  When the man woke up the next morning and saw that the robot was gone he knew he was in a lot of trouble. He called the police right away he told them the story of what happened he told them how he found it, how he had forgot to unplug it, and how the robot was gone and he didn't know where he is. The police sad that they are on their way they searched the basement for clues of where the robot had gone. Soon they gave up looking for clues and decided to just go and look for him outside.                 They found some footprints outside they followed them to a little stand that was selling food they asked if they had seen a robot. They said oh yes we have. The day before the robot had broken their stand and ate all the food. Then the police and the man looked at each other and they both figured out they were dealing with something dangerous.                  They called for backup they started looking again  but this time they had nothing to follow there were no footprints or anything so they just walked along the road searching. The man just remembered that he had a remote to stop the robot if he touched it. He told the police about it and they said that would be helpful so they went back to the house and found the remote.                   Turns out the man was smart enough to make a tracking device built into the remote so he followed it into new york city. This robot was huge and he was heading right toward the empire state building. If they didn't catch it in time it would tackle the empire state building like it were a tackling dummie. They turned on their flashers and raced after the robot it heard the sirens and didn't like it so it turned around and tried to stomp on the car. The police driver being trained shot to the right and made the robot miss by a little more than a yard. The man jumped out of the car and took the remote and threw it at the foot of the robot. The towering robot fell to the ground with a mighty thump. The man wiped the sweat of his face and celebrated that the robot was dead.                   They called a dump truck to come move it to the dump but the man wanted to make the robot a working fighter in the army so he told the person driving the truck to turn it around. The person dropped the robot off the man went straight to the basement and started to work.                       The man was tired so he went to sleep leaving the robot plugged in. He woke up in the morning and the robot was gone. He said under his breath 'here we go again.'

Item_Response: Sam's Robot             One day there was a little girl, named Sam, who saw a machine that she never saw before. It was a robot and so she took it home. When she got home her parents asked, 'What do you have there.' She replied 'Oh i don't know i just found it.' Sam walked up to her room and set it on her bed then it said, 'How are you,' then she asked, 'Who are you.' The robot said, 'me the one who is on your bed,' Oh my gosh you can talk, 'Yes i can and i can do anything you want me to do.' Well i got to go to bed.         It was the next morning and the robot wasn't there any more so she looked all over in her room and she heard crashing down stairs so she ran down their. Sam found her parents screaming and she told then that he was ok and that he was a good robot.  An hour later she got them so calm down and so she took him by her parents and they asked what can he do so she said anything i want him to, i guess.           Her mother asked can you play music and he said you beat. Her father asked could you dance and he said the same thing. Her parents let her keep the robot for now, but they said that she is not going to keep the robot for long.They said they don't know if it is dangerous or not.          Dad can i have a friend over please i will do all of my chores. Really sure honey. Thank you Dad love you. Sam said ok i have to get to work and first i have to give you a name. Call me 13. Ok 13 lets get to work. Oh no just wright down a list of things you have to do and then give it to me. All i have to do is clean my room. Ok well i will do that.          An hour later my room was squeaky clean i don't know how he did it so fast. So i told my dad that i was all done cleaning my room, so he let me call Megan. Hey Megan can you come over today and hang out and her mom said yes. Luckly she lives right in town so we can walk to get her. Lets go.        We got to her house and she came out with a bag. We walked back to my house got to my room. Then she asked me 'what is that' I said, ' Well it's 13 my robot he can do anything i want him to do.' Where did you get him,' 'I found him by the junk yard,' 'Really.' Ya i know it's cool that i have him, but i don't know where he came from.' 'Ya i don't know either it's weird.' 'Ya.' 'Are you going to keep him.' 'No, my parents won't let me.'         A few months passed and 13 was just getting settled into his new home, when on the news showed a picture of a robot that looked just like 13, and the person said ' This robot is missing if you see it anywhere please call 1-715-416-869 as soon has posible.' So Sam's dad called the number and told them that they had the robot. They said that they would come and get him as soon as they can. 'Sam come down here,' 'Ok.' Sam where did you get 13. I found him by the junk yard. Well the people that lost him need him back. Twenty minutes later they came and got 13 and Sam said 'Goodbye.'

Item_Response: My name is Jim and I live out in the country.I do not really have any one to play with during the summer because my parents work all day untill five pm.So one day i went out in the woods and found a barn,I went inside the barn and I found alot of wires and electronics.       Then I went back to my house and got a bin to fill the wires and electronics in.So I was searching for more electronics and I found a robot head so I put the head in the bin and grab the rest of what was in the barn.   I ran back to my house with the bin and when I got back to my house and my grandpa was thier!I was so happy I ran up to Grandpa and gave him a hug.I ask 'Grandpa why are you here''?           Grandpa said''well I have not seen my grandson in a while so I decided to come vistit you''.Grandpa said ''what are you doin with those wires and electronics''                                             I replied ''oh I was gonna build a robot,could you help me?Grandpa said ''Sure''.So grandpa and I went up to my workbench in my room and layed all of the electronics and wires on my work bench Grandpa ask ''what do you want the robot to do ''I said ''I want it to play sports with me'' Grandpa said ''ok but its gonna take a few hours''.       So we work for a couple of hours and it was six o'clock !My mom and dad finnaly showed up and we had hammburgers for dinner they were delishious.       After dinner Grandpa and I went to bed I had bunk beds so Grandpa could sleep in my room.Then early in the morning Granpa and I work for one hour and then it was there the five foot robot with a radio as its chest and meatel pipes as its legs also the armes were made up of old ten by fours with a baseball glove as its hands it was perfect!Then it turn on and it said lets play catch so the robot and I went outside to play catch.The next day Grandpa had to leave I thank Grandpa for making me a robot and he said ''I wouldn't have done it without you'' then I wave goodbye as he was driving off.       The next Day I gave the robot a name,Rex.So Rex and I went out in the field to play catch as Rex and I continued to play catch I trip over somthing in the ground I got a shovel and dug it up and it was a big old  robot made for the war. So I change Rex's arms and legs and traded arms and legs with the big robot. Now Rex can through far and Run fast. I went exploring without Rex and I found a huge moutain . So I traveled up the moutain and look over to th nice scenerie and the I fell off the moutain .But right when I was going to hit the ground someone caught me and that someone was Rex!I guess he can do more than just play sports,he can save people.So later on that day I told my parents that Rex saved my life,my dad said''thank you Rex for saving my boy I wouldn't know what to do without you Rex''.Then my mom said good thing grandpa and you built that stunning robot of yours''. Later on in life Jim became sucessful by building Robots he was a millionare.                                                                       THE END

Item_Response: The Field Trip                   I was never a bad kid, but i wasn't a good one, either I was I guess you could say, a normal kid, until one day, it was a cold December day, and went went on a flied trip that to me, was the most boring trip ever!                   We went to a place where adults come up with ideas for new helpful robots. some were pretty cool, but some didn't interest me at all. But about an hour into the field trip with our lazy, dull constructor, I saw it.The coolest design of a robot EVER. I couldn't keep my eyes off of the electric blue robot that had 5 arms and 3 legs!               I suffered the rest of the trip thinking about that awesome robot. at the end I couldn't help but noticing that it didn't even work. it said right on the case it was in. I thought that if I had it for myself I would fix it and make it my friend and it would be my servant, too. so, at that moment when nobody was looking, I snatched it and slipped it into my backpack. And that's when the chaos began.                   For the rest of the day, I counted down the minutes until the bell would ring. When it did, i rushed to the bus. As soon as i got home, I ran up to my room, locked the door and examined the small robot. It ran on batteries. Shoot! none left... I went to ask my mom if we had spare. I just said it was for a project. Turns out we didn't. I got back upstairs and the robot was gone.                    I was totally flipped out. had someone stolen it? Or was my mind playing tricks on me? Then I heard a voice that sounded like a monstrous robot. 'Who's there...?' 'OH MY GOSH!' I cried. The robot came rolling tword me. At this point, I had to call my best friend, Justin Walker.                       The moment he picked up I told him everything. He thought I wasn't telling the truth, until Justin came over. He was amazed when he saw it, and my mom wanted me to open the door to see what all of the yelling was about. We tried to make the robot be quiet but my mom left before we could come up with an excuse.                                         The robot went crazy and crashed through the window. it was running loose through the city leaving me and Justin confused on what just happened. We had no choice but to chase it and shut it off. When we went throughgh the city everybody looked at us like we were freaks. We caught It before it could get to anything, but it slipped away and robbed 2 banks, destroyed 4 cars and almost killed me and Justin. We tried to catch it again but it was no use. the robot shut itself down and I felt very guilty.                       Well, my mom found out about my huge mistake and punished me AND Justin. My giant mistake ruined most of the city... Never again will I steal from anyone EVER AGAIN.

Item_Response: I had built a robot and called him the Juggurnaut because he was designed for the army and was basically indistructible. he was replacing the tanks for the army but one day. something terrible went wrong the chip I had programmed in his head got damaged somehow and he turned evil.   He had completely destroyed the military base and going on a rampage through the city. I assumed he was coming for me so the only option I had was to build another robot and thats exactly what I did. This one had a indistructible chip programmed to be good. I called it Titan.   It was titanium plated and was indesructible but could rip the evil robot in half. as soon as the juggurnaut got there they had a all out fight to the death.The Titan had ripped him in half and destroyed the       Juggurnaut but had exploded with the Juggurnaut when he   seldestructed. They had both been destroyed and i decided to never build robots for the army again. The End.

Item_Response: Creating A Robot              On November 21, 2012 me and my friend Jennifer were at my house. We were seeing a movie about robots. When we were seeing the movie I told her what if we make our own robot. She said we should make the robot and then I said to her that all we need is the materials.              So then the next day we went on the computer and went on Google and put what do you need to make a robot. Then it finished loading, we saw hundreds of answers so we picked the first one. It said that to buy medal, iron, screwdriver, glue, color paint so we could color it however we want and some batteries. Then right next to the directions it had a video. So we saw it when the boy was finished he put the batteries and turned the switch it was amazing the robot was dancing, singing, running, and talking. When my dad came I asked him if he could take us to the store to buy the things that we need to make the robot then he said sure. So we went to the store we got everything that we needed but it cost a lot we needed one dollar until my dad found one in his pocket we were safe.                  After we came from the store we started to built the robot. When we were finished we thought about the color so I thought since me and Jennifer like green and blue we thought about turquoise. So then we were finished I turned on the switch but it would not work then Jennifer said that you forgot about the batteries and then I said oops. So then I put the batteries then turned on the switch it was amazing it was playing music, running, dancing, singing, and was talking to us. I could not believe that we made an actual robot.             So the next day we were playing with the robot. It was super fun. We played hide and seek, tag, dancing, and watching movies. Item_Response: Robot Gone Crazy               It was very calm and quiet in B.Y.R.E.I.T. Jr. high school. B.Y.R.E.I.T. stood for best youth robot engineers in town. It was every kid's dream in town to get into this school. Luckily for Nick his dad worked for N.A.S.A. and was very smart he was also very hardworking. His dad's job also encouraged Nick to become an engineer. Nick was just three when he built his first robot out of straws and rubber bands. Unfortunately it did not move but it did stand up. Nick was now old and smart enough to enter B.Y.RE.I.T. school. Nick joined a club with the smartest kids in the school. It was him Charlie and Sandie. Everybody here was smart but not as smart as them.         One day they were building a robot in the library. They were building a Mr.Gower for their local hospital. Charlie was the designer he chose out the color and the model.He also had to measure it and cut the pieces that were too big. Sandy was instruction reader since she read and spoke both French and English. Nick was the engineer he had to use screws bolts to but everything in the right order. He also put in all the chips to make it move and programed it to talk.It took them five days to complete it.        When they finished the robot, it looked normal until they turned it on. It was not doing what it was supposed to do. It was ripping books apart and breaking desks. Charlie got a hold of the phone and called the principal. Meanwhile the principal got there Nick handed Sandy and Charlie brooms. Nick got a mop and on the count of three they were all going to hit it but when Sandy said two, Charlie went crazy and started  started to hit it. The robot was breaking and slowing down. In a couple of hits the robot shut off. They felt bad that they were not going to have a robot to turn in so they worked as fast as possible so when the principal got there he thought they were just playing a joke on him.

Item_Response: The robot ...............               One day there was a girl named Linda Lou  who was a science geek and she loved science, so much she made a robot and she knew how to make by mind. Linda was a smart girl, She had dirty blonde hair and big Blue eyes, with big bold black  glasses. Then one day when Linda got home from school she was assigned to do a robot for the 4th grade Beverly Doreen elementary schools science fair. So she went home and she got all the material eds for her science fair project, So she went to her room and searched, and searched until she found it... a box and it was made with metal, Now Linda Lou never remembered that she had a metal box but... she really didn't know what to make with it so she thought  for a minute. Thought. and thought, and thought then suddenly the greatest idea popped to her tiny little brain that held all her memory, came the idea, Linda Lou: h'm Ive got it ill build a robot!!!!!! so she went around the house looking for some stuff to decorate her robot, she found a container of liquid glue and some sparkles, some old lace and ribbon, an old pair of shoes, and some old little remote control cars that her big brother Simon used when he was a kid. Then Linda Lou found some old brown from her dance costume from kindergarten. then a card board box her dad old golf clubs and some old plastic water pipes  perfect enough to be the arms. Then she gathered all her stuff she found and took it to her craft room where she did all of her crafts and projects. So she started putting the robot together and after 1 hr and a half she had made herself a robot  then she added details. A bow on the head, an old easy bake oven in the middle a couple of batteries and an SD card from an old phone, and stuffed it into the back of the head which had a hole in it and a spot for batteries and shoved 'em in  then she found one last thing to complete it her brother old reomote control, and put a wireless device in it and into the robot so it could move with the controller. Then 1 week later was the science fair project and she brought her robot into her moms car and headed to school, Then when she got to school she was late so the science fair was about to start. So she presented it to them and then she turned it on to show the judges and then the eyes on the robot turned red and it began break thing and punching the walls and then exploded and then dies.

Item_Response: ' Are you kidding? How could a robot come to life? How would some little, cute dog be bad?' I asked.       ' You don't know the half of it,' Jack said.       'Well are you going to tell me what happened, and how you delt with it?' I asked again. This time a little more annoyed. I wasn't sure if this was going to be real or not, but I love a good story either way.       ' I was about twenty years ago,' he began,' I was down at the lab working on a new experiment. I was trying to build the first electronic animal. It would play and you would be able to teach it tricks. The ony different thing was it wouldn't need to be fed or walked.'       'So... what happened?' I asked when he suddendy stopped.       ' I was almost done with the little pup. It worked great and I thought the kids were going to love it. I was about to go home, when someone came into my office. Long story short one of my fellow scientists was getting arrested. He had been sneeking chips in some of the robots and they didn't behave correctly. The robots that carried medicne to hospital patcients refused to carry the medication. They wanted to carry poisionis substenses. Anyways the police asked if they could keep him in my lab for the moment. I told him yes and hurried out the door to get home before the storm. The next day my office was distroyed. Everything was knocked down and messed up. I thought it was just the prisionor, but I was wrong,' he said.       'Was it the dog? Did he go mad? Did the Prisioner put the chip in him too?' I asked.       'Yes. Before the dog had a chance to get out of had I had to smash it into millions and millions of pieces,' he said.   I don't know if it was true or not but that was the best story he ever told.
