Item_Response: There once was a robot. His name was Roe Bought. He was only programed to think like a Gemini- Scout robot. After the succes of the Gemini-Scout, they made more robots like it, and that is what Roe was. One day he was checking a mine for some lost miners and had to do a gas check. He let the air into his filter and sampled it. There was something not right about this air. His system started shutting down. Everything went black and Roe shutdown. He woke up later feeling funny. He then realized robots don't just wake up on their own. Someone had to program them to do it. He moved around and checked all his systems. they were good. He then looked for a place to rest. He then thought with suprise, 'I have a mind of my own. No one programed me for my own needs'              He realized he was living. He used his thermal camera to locate the miners and get them to safety. One of them was hurt. He got his medical pack and gave it to the man, something he never could of done without a will of his own. He brought them to the jeep and the driver drove them back to the lab. The hurt miner told one of the scientists of Roe's actions. The scientist was suprised. He had never programed Roe to help injered miners.The scientist got Roe and brought him to the other scientist for tests           After checking Roe's system and seeing nothing different, he let Roe go. But Roe went back to the scientist and sent a message to the scientist's computer saying Roe was living. They scientists couldn't beleive it. Roe became the top robot and was used only for the hardest of missions. He also helped the scientists in the lab. The tried to find the gas that brought Roe to life but never could. That is the story of Roe.

Item_Response: The Mysterious Robot            One day on the way home from school we saw something different. Everyone on the bus saw it but no one knew what it was. The only thing we knew was that it was not from this world. We didn't know if it wanted to hurt us or not it was just watching us. The thing also had a claw that was rust orange.             A few years went by and it was still there and no one knew what it was or what it wanted. Then one Sunday the creature moved from its spot on the side of the road. The next day we found it in the school trying to eat the brick wall. Everyone just walked by it and pretended not to notice it when they did. The next thing you knew was the swat team was filing into the school.             The swat team had brought the thing to area 675 to find out what it was. Two months went by without hearing anything then on the news two men in orange said that the creature was a robot from the planet Cyber tron. The two men said that if there were any questions to call the news station they were at and sure enough the phones were ringing of the hook with callers. Every kid in the neighbor hood was asking if it was a transformer.               The robot had not come to harm us but to protect us. It came to protect us from evil aliens. The robot also said that there will be more coming and that he was an Auto bot. One day later there were giant asteroids and everyone had watched the four asteroids land on Earth and they were all other Auto bot.               A month went by and then the aliens showed up. The Auto bots were helping the government to defeat them. Soon all the aliens were defeated. The last one said that its not over yet. The town then cheared and excepted the Auto bots.

Item_Response: Tim Murphy has been trying to make a robot his whole life.It all started when Tim became a scientist,he soon found out that he wanted to make the very first robot.Years later he never succeeded but he kept on trying.One afternoon Tim was in his laboratory doing the same as usual,failing at trying to make a robot.He had this great new invention called the G-67.This time Tim had thoughts that he would get this one up and running.after working on it for 3 months ,Tim finally wanted to quit so he went to he did and he didn't want to try to make a robot ever again.       After a week from quitting on his robot dream,Tim had to go back to his lab and get his stuff.Once he was there he felt something unusual.He went inside his lab to get his stuff when he was there G-67 was not there anymore,he thought for a minute but he just stuck with someone probably grabbed it.But no there was tables knocked down and a lot of glass.Tim heard a noise coming from the bathroom so he went in it and found G-67 wrapped up in paper towels that he grabbed.All of the sudden Tim screamed and ran back out.Tim never thought he would actually succeed,but yes Tim now made the very first robot.       Tim new this would be one of the best inventions if man-kind.He hurried home to show his family and show off his success.when he got home he grabbed G-67 and went inside he showed the robot off and everyone was amazed.He was five feet all and looked like a human but with all the metal on him.He soon showed NASA and all other scientists included the president of the U.S.G-67 popularity was getting stronger and stronger by the minute.He was in museums and showed up at schools and even went to get experimented on by other scientist.But this is not how G-67 wanted it to be like.It was time for a change...       G-67 knew he would have to run away and hide the rest of his life.So he did just that right in the middle of a school visit G-67 ran away and never wanted to return to this horrible life he had.Nobody could find him,they all worried about him.Soon everyone forgot about him.Since there were other better robots out there now everyone all forgot.Until one day G-67 was doing his normal routine,eating trash from the dump.He wanted people to know him again,so he walked to the local store.Nobody cared anymore about him.But swoosh someone with a mask on carried him and put him right in the back of his van.He tried to talk but the guy put duct tape over his mouth.G-67 was very suprised and confused.The gut told him that he was off to robot jail.Still G-67 was very confused... Item_Response: Maximum           There was a robot that suddenly becomes alive and was immediately named Maximum. The people who assembled her had designed her in a seamless humanoid form. Max was designed to do the most amazing things in the world and she passed every test she took. One day, though, she got tired of her lab-life and she sprouted her mechanical wings and took off. Max finally landed in someone's backyard with a mine behind it. she walked over and realized there was a Gemini Scout that had broken down. Maximum saw she was standing near a collapsed mine and that people might be trapped too. She went in with workers looking at her like she was crazy. Once in the tunnel, she started using her heat sensory. The trapped miners were far ahead and Max ran to that place. When Max got there, she started pounding the rock and the rock gave way. but that meant that the rest of the tunnel started crumbling.                   'Come on! Quickly!' she said to the two miners. Maximum grabbed them both by the hand and got them out of the mine before they got crushed. The miners up top as well as pediatrics came with water, food and stretchers. A week later, Max had become famous-even though she had destroyed the whole rest of the biggest mine in the area. Max also saved:   A pilot and passengers on a plane with a malfunctioning engine Passengers left behind on a sinking ship A family who were mountain climbing form a rock slide More trapped miners A family from a sinkhole the size of a house (the family survived and the house went 100 ft to the bottom of that sinkhole About a billion or so other lives   So Maximum decided to get a last name and it was Ride. You can say that Maximum Ride was a hero of ten centuries (literally). She got up-graded every year with the latest tech. That's the story of Maximum Ride.

Item_Response: ROBOTS            When you first think of robots you may just think about how unreal they are to the world today or how we can only imagine what they look like or act. But you are wrong!!! Today robots are very real to our world and everyday they are becoming more and more popular. Here are a few robots that you might enjoy to hear about how they work, what they do, what they look like, and how they are used in our world today!       The first robot that I'm going to tell you about is the Gemini-Scout. You are probably wondering what in the world does that robot do?! Well I'm going to answer your question! The Gemini-Scout is a robot that searches through mines that have been collapsed and they find people who are traped inside there and rescue them. they work in mines all over that world. The Gemini-Scout is 2 feet tall and has wheels, it can go up and downstairs and it can make tight turns. Also the robot is small but VERY strong. Wherever the robot goes it collects information about that place. The Gemini-Scout is very easy to work with, if you have ever played a video game the Gemini-Scout would be a piece of cake for you to control!       The second robot I'm going to talk to you about is the Dante 2. The Dante 2 can go into volcanoes and collect information for scientists. Lots of times if the volcano is to dangerous to go inside of they will send the Dante 2 in there and it will look for vents,or holes in the craters. And then the robot will collect information on the gases that come out of the crater holes. Dante is defentially  s big help to the scientists all around the world that study volcanoes!       Third, is the Mr. Gower robot. This robot works in hospitals and helps the doctors and nurses that work there. Mr. Gower can go anywhere in the hospital, it can ride on elevators,steer through hallways, and move things around that get in the way.   Also the robot can carry up to 500 pounds!!! And Mr. Gower can talk to many different people very easily. So Mr. Gower is a big help to nurses and doctors all over the world, and now that Mr. Gower is helping a lot and getting things done this now means that doctors and nurses can work on more important jobs.       Fourth, is the Agribots. An Agribot is a robot that can pick fruit. It can pick about any fruit you want! Because picking strawberries is different form picking bluberris Agribots come in many different shapes and sizes. these robots are extra helpful to farmers because now that a robot is doing most things they can focus on tending to other needs on the farm. Agribots can even grow there own plants! The robots have a sensor so they know when to water the plant and when the plants are ripe enough so you can pick it!   There are so many ways for Agribots to help farmers its kind of unbelievable!!!       My last robot that I am going to show is the Google car. Have you ever wanted to be able to sit in car and not worry about driving or making sure you are looking left and right, then left again?! Because I know I have! But now we don't have to worry about those things anymore, because they have now made the Google car! This car is very nice, youcanthink about your day and drive because this car can steer itself!   I'm sure that you may have people looking at you when they drive by because your hands will not be on he steering wheel.   This new car is amazing, and you have to find more about!       There are so many robots that can do so many things, fro example there are robots now that can actually be pets! Some robots are made to look like dinosaurs and some are made to look like cats and dogs. Also robots can sing, play, and even dance to music!!! I can't wait for when I get my first robot! Can you??

Item_Response: It was a cold winter day in Canada.  As usual.  The middle school janitor exited the building.  The failed robot came to life.  No purpose yet. Tom was sitting in his chair at home expecting nothing to happen.  The next morning something was happening.  The robot had entered the house and then Tom's door to a unsuspecting victim. Tom.    'I AM YOUR JANITOR!' The robot screamed.  Tom awakened immediately.   'Robots?!'   'I AM YOUR JANITOR!' The robot thundered again with a sponge in his one arm.   Tom got out of bed.  The robot stared at him for a few seconds with its one eye that it used for processing areas, and it came closer.  A note came out of a paper sized hole in it's center.  It read: A JANITOR IS REQUIRED.  Tom gave the robot a horrible look.   'Go away!'   'A PIZZA IS REQUIRED?!'  The robots voice trailed as it left temporarily with Tom's wallet.  When the robot came back with a pizza AND his wallet Tom was happy.  Until the robot blurted  'I USED A 100 AND I DON'T TAKE CHANGE!!!'    Tom kicked the robot 'WHAT IDIOT MADE YOU!!?!'   'Someone who hates CHAAANGE!!!'   Tom sat down on his bed.  He ate a slice of anchovy pizza. 'Who made you?'   'Bob!'   'Who is this Bob?'   'Take me to him- and I will leave you alone.'   Tom considered the offer 'Where is Bob?'   'He is on the other side of the city!' 'Where?'   'Bob is your next door neighbor!'   'Uh where?' 'Take me to Bob or be destroyed!'  The robot said as laser cannons came out of almost every inch of the robot's body.   'OK OK OK buddy.'  Tom blurted, saving his life.   The quest to find Bob began.  Tom put up posters everywhere saying 'Bob who makes robots wanted' Tom went to bed that day.  Many Bobs came 'fakers' would have been eliminated if Tom did not stop the robot.  Then Bob came.  The Bob.  B-O-B.  BOB.  Bob knocked on the door.    'I am robot-creator Bob.' Bob said.    Tom rushed to the door and opened it 'BOB,' Tom said 'now you can your stupid change hating robot!'   'CHANGE!' The robot yelled when he said the word as it unleashed it's laser cannons, shooting at Tom.                   Tom was burnt alive at the mention of change and Bob was charged with murder. 15 years.   The robot was auctioned in an auction with no change given.  Bob got an extra 30 years after his robot killed more people at the mention of  'No Change.'  Bob was given MORE years after his robot invented super nukes and gave them to the Iranians, right after America declared war on them.  The super nuke blew up Bob's prison cell and Bob ran free into another site that was super nuked. Bobs life is an example to us all.                                                                                     THE END

Item_Response: Getting Used to a Surprise                      One day before a little girl, named Ana, saw the most amazing thing she had ever had seen in her whole life, her parents told her that they were having a surprise for her the next day. In the morning, she still couldn't figure out what they were going to give her. When she went to school, she couldn't concentrate in anything. Because of thinking on what the surprise would be, she didn't even remember that she was going to have a test.While she was taking her test, she didn't remember what she had learned so she guessed in all the answers. At the end of the day, she got her grade which was an F. She left school very sad and disappointed.                 When she arrived home, she told her mom that she had failed the test. After talking with her mom, she went to her room to do her homework. She didn't know her surprise was waiting for her in her bedroom. When she entered her room she put her backpack on her bed and sat down. Then, she noticed a box next to her bed.There was something moving inside the box. Suddenly, she remembered that she had a surprise. She opened it very fast and a robot pops up. She yelled for a long time, but then her parents came and calmed her. She didn't know if she would ever get used to a robot being in her house.                   Finally, after so many weeks of trying to getting used to the robot she didn't get scared of seeing it every time. After getting used to it she had so much fun with it. She learned many things from it and it helped her do many things she had not learned before. As the time passed, Ana liked the robot more and more. She thought it was the best surprise her parents had given her.

Item_Response: A Rescue Robot 7272                                         One day my family and I were at the beach and we someone drowning. all of a sudden a three foot vehicle can speeding into the water. once it touched the ocean it turned into a mini boat that can carry people. As we watched we saw the robot going under water and picking up the person bringing them back to the beach. once it got on the sand it turned back into a vehicle  and sped away.                           The next day I was at a restaurant with my friends and all of a sudden a little girl was choking. Once again the robot that saved the person in the ocean was here again. Somehow it go the food out of her and she was perfectly fine like nothing happened. I was amazed now.                                On Saturday morning my mom turned on the news and it talked about the government making a new robot. It's called Rescue Robot 7272. This robot saves people whenever they call 7272. the robot tracks the phone where the call came from and it will be there in one minute. The two days on Thursday and Friday  I saw Rescue Robot 7272 rescuing people. It is a life saver.... it can rescue people in the water, in fires,  on stores/restaurant and it can even save people who are being kidnapped or being held hostile in a building. It can save people anywhere.

Item_Response: Mrs. Star   Mrs. Star is a robot developed to go into space to look for undiscovered stars. Mrs. Star gets attached to the outside of a rocket. It's fire proof, so she doesn't burn up going into space. Right after she's launched into space, and in space her light sensor is turned on. She has her own computer inside of her so she can send photos to NASA. NASA built her to be 3 feet tall and 2 feet in length. It takes awhile for Mrs. Star to get to a star. Sometimes weeks,months, or even years. So NASA's scientist check on Mrs. Star twice a month to make sure she doesn't have any problems. 1 check at the beginning at the month and 1 check at the end.       Mrs. Star has been to a total of 57 stars. 20 stars close to our planet and 37 far away from our planet. Right now she's on her way to a star 217,034 miles away from our planet! Wow! She goes 130 mph. The highest speed she ever went was 153 mph. Then she's coming back closer to our planet, about 114,783 miles away.       We hope she can take many more pictures of stars. And maybe even try to discover new planets. But for now Mrs. Star discovers stars that never been discovered before. We named 3 stars that makes a triangle, we call them Group 3. We named 2 other groups that each had 2 stars in them, but the stars turned into black holes. We wanted to get Mrs. Star away from the black holes, so the black holes don't suck her up. She would never be able to get out of the black holes. So far no problems for her, that means more exploring for more stars!

They all cheered  when they saw the robot get up.The master finally said,'The problem was that I forgot to tell you that we used a diffrent type of charger this time.'All the scientist were relived that it was just a simple mistake and it wasn't anything big.                  All of the scientist were now happy and they all  agreeded  to be more careful with what they put in the robot. The robot now is  very helpful to our community. Item_Response: What are Robots???            Robots can very interesting. Robots can help in many ways. they also can play with people, animal, and toys.Robots can take people to safe place. They can bring people food, water, and other safe things. Robots have alot of commen things with real pets.You can show them new tricks.There are new robots that have fur like animals but you dont have to feed them or take them outside.If i had a robot I would make it to go to space, because alot of people would want to know what happens out in space.      Robots are machines that are very smart. A robot are made out of differnt kinds of things. People can make them how ever they want. They can make them with fur. People like making robots to have some one to talk with or play with. Robots can be like your friend. There alot of different kinds of robots. For example:   Gemini-Scout,Dante 2,Mr. Gower,and Agribots   These are the different types of robots there are. Gemini-Scout isa robot that does resaech and rescue work. It can take people to safe places. It can also carry food, water, and other supplies.          Dante 2 is a robot that climbs into volcanoes to gather information for scientist. It also has eight legs like a spider. Ifa volcano is to dangrous for the scientist Dante goes instead. Now scientist can learn more about volcanoes. Mr. Gower is a robot that works in hospitals. It helps doctors and nursees bring medicine to patients.           Mr. Gower looks like a small cabinet with wheels. It is stacked of locked drawers that store medicine. Doctors an nurses can unlock the drawers when they need the midicine. Mr. Gower is so strong that it can pull five hundred pounds. Mr. Gower runs with batteries. After charging the robot delivers medicine for 12 hours without stopping.          Agribot is a robot that picks fruit. It can pick up different kinds of fruit berries, oranges,grapes, or apples. Farmers are very interested in those robots. In japan there are robots that can sense the color of the berries. It hepls the robot know when each berry is ripe. Item_Response: 'Cmon just a few more adjustments...and...It's ready!' until it fell apart.My dad,brother and I,Jacob,have been working on building a robot that could help us around the house.We've been ITCHING to hire a maid,but all the maids we called were too expensive.W're going to name the robot the Gemini Scout.He is going to be remote controlled,Protective,and best of all,it'll be super smart by collecting information.       Even though the Gemini Scout may take a long time to actually WORK,this isn't the only robot we're going to build.I can see more robots that we programed and built with our bare hands.My dad,my brother Logan,and I have been working on this for almost a year.and this isn't just something you pick off the street and steal.What we're making took blueprints,material,and a LOT of technonlogy reading.It was hard work,and we were hoping it would've been working by Friday(Tomorrow)But my dad lost the memory chip,but when we found it,it was a peice of JUNK.So my dad needed to buy a new one.This Gemini Scout will have a LOT of amazing details.It could help win wars,help people in the hospital,and even carry injured people to saftey.It's only less than 2 ft. and has wheels.Even though it has wheels,It can still go up stairs.ON WHEELS.By 2025 that's when that'll start becoming normal deal with robots.What I like about this robot was that I got to have a feature I wanted on the robot.The remote to control the Gemini Scout looks VERY firmiliar to a vdeo game controller.'It's done...IT'S DONE!!!' My dad yelled.At first NONE of us believed it was finished,but it was!'Guys all we need is the memory chip!' 'Dad one problem.' I said.When he heard the word 'problem',I think his thunder stopped booming on the finished Gemini Scout.'That chip was 400,000 dollars.' I said.       Dad hesitated.'Sorry guys,' he said.He head was bowed down like he was depressed.'The robot can NEVER work with THAT price of the memory chip.' a tear started to roll down his eye.I went inside and came back with a nice tall glass of cold Grape Soda for everybody.'It's okay,guys,' I said.'We just need to save up and make donation for the memory chip.' Logan was sort of more happy by my idea.'Wait a second guys.' Dad said.'We programed him with no memory chip.' Dad got exited again.'But how will he collect indformation,we have to turn him off eventually,when he comes back on,his memory will be erased.' 'No it won't'replied Dad.'Before I told another soul about the Gemini Scout, I turned it on.I told it my name and stuff and when I turned it off,I forgot about it for 10 whole years.''So you think since you turned it on in the early days it will start again?'I asked.' It's worth a try.' Dad replied.He pressed the new power button we just installed.They red eyes turned on.           'HELLO AGAIN MASTER,WHAT IS YOUR WISH?' I can't believed it worked.Hard work was a succsess.Now all we needed was another robot to replace the Gemini Scout when he has Low Battery and dies.The perfect name is Dante 2!

Item_Response: The It       'It's alive!' John shouted in amazement. John always had plans of making a robot come alive. But this one was different from all of his other failing robots. John had no clue of what type of power or quality it had. IT?? It needed a name,'How about Boxy' Jeremy his other lab partner exclaimed. 'No No, that will not do.'' answered John.                 ''Oh no!'' bellowed Jeremy from behind scientist John, ''He's leaving the laboratory!'' hurry we have to catch him!.'' They whiped off there lab coats and bolted through the hinged doors separating the laboratory from outside. ''Lets get a move on hes already by Michigan avenue!'' They sprinted all the way down to Michigan avenue and tried to get a hold of of It. (the robot) 'Hold up a second, there's no way we can get him back to the lab.'' John explained. 'Why not we just have to walk him back, don't we?'' Jeremy asked. ''No, Jeremy hes ways almost 1 ton! We'd have to get the fire department in here if we wanted to even try to move him.'' ''Ok ok'' Jeremy said glumly. ''I know what we have to do. We have to find something he likes and then lewer him back into the laboratory with it. 'Oh I know what he might like doughnuts!' ''Maybe lets try it and see.'' While Jeremy watched the robot, John ran over to the bakery and got 20 doughnuts. He quickly jogged back and handed the doughnuts to It. It took the doughnuts but didn't know what to do with it. her tried throwing it and smashing it. But then he finally gave it back to John. John then jumped to conclusions saying that It didn't like doughnuts. They scrounged for more thing that might interest It.                Then they found a giant teddy bear with bows in its fur and they picked it up from the store for It. It saw the teddy bear and took it right our of Jeremy's hand and squeezed the bear as tight as he could. Then John yanked it out of Its hands and started runnig towards the laboratory. It got so mad he mad a huge beeping noise and started dragging its brick feet towards John. Jeremy then followed It all the way back to the laboratory.    They all safely made it back to the lab and then they gave It back the teddy bear. It then grinned and fell asleep on the cold concrete floor.            While It was sleeping they were trying to figure out what his special power or quality was. Jeremy and John both looked back in there notes to see what they put in It before it became It.            ''O my goodness!'' Jeremy said in surprise. '' I know I know!'' ' What is it!'' John screamed excitedly. ''SHHHHH.'' Jeremy hushed. 'There is a robot trying to sleep.' '' I know I'm sorry I'll be quite.' Jeremy Then went on explaining what he thought it was that they put in It. 'I think we put love potion in It.'' Jeremy attested. 'Really you think so?'' John asked. 'Yes I am postive.'' '' i think you are right considering how much It loves that teddy bear.'' Ya and I also wonder how are we ever going to name It?' John asked. 'I guess we'll just have to keep calling him It until we think of one.' Jeremy answered. ''Yeah I wonder what we should name It?'
